american_desc = "国籍: アメリカ$NL;年齢: 31$NL;$NL;Houstonはダメ人間で、仕事に就く事が出来なかった。彼の生活は詐欺と窃盗が主体となっていた。 借金は膨らみ、長年の詐欺で敵が多くいた。$NL;$NL; 彼は高利子の借金を返す気などなかったが、返すアテはあると思わせる為大金が必要だった。 初めて大きな犯罪に手を染めたのは24歳の時で、成功した。それからというもの一攫千金を狙う事が増えていった。",--Nationality: American$NL;Age: 31$NL;$NL;Houston could never hold a job even if his life would depend on it. His life style turned him to a life of cons and burglary. His debts grew, as did his collection of enemies from years of swindlery. He needed to gather larger and larger sums of money to keep the loan sharks at bay. He committed his first major felony at the age of 24 and the stakes have only increased since.
bodhi_desc = "国籍: 不明$NL;年齢: 不明$NL;$NL;Bodhiは犯罪者界の伝説の一人として知られているが、そのマスクの裏に隠された男を知るものは少ない。ギャングEx-Presidentsの創設者であり、Bodhiのエクストリームスポーツへの熱や斬新な強盗のやり方が犯罪者界で有名だ。彼が最近、その能力でムンバイとオーストリアで偉業を成し遂げたことがBainの興味を引き、彼がPAYDAYギャングへと招待された。",--Nationality: Unknown$NL;Age: Unknown$NL;$NL;Bodhi is known as one of the greatest legends in the world of crime, but few know the man behind the mask. As the founding father of the Ex-Presidents gang, Bodhi's renowned in the criminal underworld for his extreme athleticism and daring heists. His recent feats of strength in Mumbai and Austria got Bain's attention, granting him an invitation to the PAYDAY gang.
bonnie_desc = "国籍: スコットランド$NL;年齢: 43$NL;$NL;Bonnieはグラスゴーからやってきた。男の心に恐怖を湧き立たせるにはそれだけで十分だろうが、Bonnieはなんと1980年代のグラスゴーからやってきたのだ。この年代と言えば、サッチャーの年代で、もう既に生き辛かった町が更に過酷な物へと変わった時期だ。その結果、決して忘れない、野心のあるスコットランドが出来上がった時代だ。Bonnieはこの時代の人間の一人なのだ。",--Nationality: Scottish$NL;Age: 43$NL;$NL;Bonnie is from Glasgow. That should be enough to strike fear into a man's heart, but Bonnie is also from 1980's Glasgow. These years, the Thatcher era, made already tough towns even harder, and bred a generation of determined, unforgiving Scots. Bonnie is cut from this cloth.
chico_desc = "",--Nationality: Cuban$NL;Age: Unknown$NL;$NL;They don't make 'em like Tony anymore. A fast talker who knows what he wants and how to get it. He's the real deal when the shit hits the fan, a true-born heister. He doesn't back down for anyone and he dishes it out just as hard as he can take it. This guy's got balls.
dragan_desc = "国籍: クロアチア$NL;年齢: 45$NL;$NL;Draganは元捜査官らしい。ただし、クロアチアのだが。そこでの彼の手段はMPDCがまるで子守でもしていると称されるほどだった。彼はThe Butcherに気に入られ、アメリカへ送り込まれると共にPAYDAYギャングに加わった。最初は彼が本当に信頼出来るのか疑いがあったが、彼の能力と献身に疑う余地はない。",--Nationality: Croatian$NL;Age: 45$NL;$NL;Dragan may be a former cop, but he's a former Croatian cop, which means his methods make the MPDC look like timid babysitters. He was brought to America and accepted into the PAYDAY gang as a favor to The Butcher. While there were some early suspicions regarding his true loyalties, his ability and commitment are indisputable.
dragon_desc = "国籍:日本$NL;年齢:52$NL;$NL;若い頃、彼は極道という道を見つけるまで孤立していた。しかしそこでも、彼はいくら忠誠心と働きを尽くしても完全には受け入れられず、終には裏切られた。長い務所暮らしの後、Jiroは長い間行方不明となっている息子、Kentoを探しにアメリカに来ている。",--Nationality: Japanese$NL;Age: 52$NL;$NL;In his youth, Jiro was never accepted, until he found his way into the yakuza. Yet even here, despite his loyalty and ability, he was never fully embraced and was ultimately betrayed. Following a lengthy prison term, Jiro has come to America to find his long-lost son, Kento.
female_1_desc = "国籍: アイルランド$NL;年齢: 27$NL;$NL;Cloverは治安の悪い街の劣悪な家庭環境で育った。彼女の先祖達はみな'戦士'だった。そして彼女もまたアイルランドの地位確立に命を削ると決意した。幸運のクローバーを身につける彼女はこう言う 'アイルランド人である事、それは誇りだ'。",--Nationality: Irish$NL;Age: 27$NL;$NL;Clover grew up in a rough house in a rough part of town. Her ancestors were fighters in every generation, and she is fiercely dedicated to her Irish heritage. She wears the clovers for luck, as well as a way to say "I'm Irish, and I'm proud".
german_desc = "国籍: スウェーデン$NL;年齢: 34$NL;$NL;Wolfは人生のほとんどにおいて、法を遵守する市民だった。2000年代後半に起きた世界経済恐慌の時に、Wolfの会社の顧客は、逃げ腰で解約希望の一社だけだった。彼の会社は破産した。$NL;$NL;今の彼はかつて会社を切り盛りしていた時と同じ熱意で犯罪キャリアを突き進んでいる。",--Nationality: Swedish$NL;Age: 34$NL;$NL;Wolf was a law abiding citizen for most of his life. During the worldwide economic slump of the late 2000's, Wolf's company temporarily had only one client that got cold feet and wanted out. His company went bankrupt.$NL;$NL;He now pursues a criminal career with the same determination that drove him when he used to run his company.
jacket_desc = "国籍: アメリカ$NL;年齢: 不明$NL;$NL;伝えられるところによると、彼はかつて、たった一人でマイアミのロシアンマフィアをまるごと一掃したとのことだ。彼の軍隊での経歴と行き過ぎた暴力に立ち向かう果敢な姿勢は、彼を素晴らしいヒットマン----或いは「メッセンジャー」とも呼べるようなものにした。理由は不明であるが、彼は全く喋らず、その代わりにテープレコーダーを使って、言語学習用のテープやPA、ドキュメンタリーのナレーション音声などの寄せ集めを再生することで、意思の疎通をすることを選んでいる。",--Nationality: American$NL;Age: Unknown$NL;$NL;Allegedly, he once wiped out the entire Russian Mafia in Miami all on his own. His background in the military and his unflinching attitude towards over-the-top violence has made him an excellent hitman - or "messenger" as some like to call it. For unknown reasons he is completely mute and chooses to communicate only with the help of a tape recorder - playing back bits and pieces of language learning tapes, PAs and documentary narrations instead of speaking.
jimmy_desc = "国籍: 不明$NL;年齢: 不明$NL;$NL;最初は疑っていたが、受け入れることにした。結果、JimmyはCrime.Net界隈の犯罪者としての能力を持ち合わせていることが分かった。 限界を知らず、契約を決裂させることもなく、毎日を人生の最後の日のように過ごしている。彼は忠実で、必要だとは思っていなかった優秀な追加メンバーの地位を証明してみせた。",--Nationality: Unknown$NL;Age: Unknown$NL;$NL;I had my doubts at first, I'll admit, but Jimmy has turned out to have all the skills to excel as a heister of Crime.Net caliber. He has no limits, never turning down a contract and lives every day like it's his last. He is loyal and has proven to be an excellent addition I never thought we needed.
jowi_desc = "国籍: アメリカ$NL;年齢: 40$NL;$NL;John Wickは静かで落ち着いた元殺し屋だ。 元ボクサーでもあった彼は、一見年齢を感じさせない体格をしている。JohnとChainsは軍にいた頃からの知り合いだ。$NL;$NL;行方をくらました後、Johnは最近再び現れ、危機的状況からChainsを助けた。その代わりとして、JohnはChainsにお前がチームに必要だと伝えた。 Chainsはどうやったら旧友を拒絶できたか?",--Nationality: American$NL;Age: 40s$NL;$NL;John Wick is a quiet and calm former hitman. He has a seemingly ageless physique, probably from his background as a boxer. John and Chains know each other from before as they used to be in the military together.$NL;$NL;After having gone dark, John recently resurfaced and helped Chains out of a delicate situation. In return, John told Chains he was in need of a crew. How could Chains say no to an old friend?
ecp_female_desc = "",--Nationality: Israeli$NL;Age: 29$NL;$NL;Rumor has it that Hila underwent extreme training in the Israeli military, and while she keeps denying it publicly, something definitely caught Bain's attention when he asked her and her spouse Ethan to join the gang. Officially, they were brought in to give the gang a much needed public PR boost in light of certain developments regarding the FBI, but as to the real reason... only Bain knows for sure.
ecp_male_desc = "",--Nationality: American$NL;Age: 32$NL;$NL;A little bit of David to the internet's proverbial Goliath, Ethan is proof that you can never really know what goes on inside Bain's head. As a skilled social media broadcaster, Ethan and his spouse Hila drew the legal ire of some individuals with their documentary work and were forced to spend a minor fortune defending themselves, leaving them financially vulnerable. His skills in public relations and engagement attracted the interest of Bain, who convinced him and his wife to join Payday with promises of restitution, fortune, and glory.
