bm_mega_clover = "",--Mega Clover
bm_mega_clover_desc = "",--The Mega Clover mask is an evolved version of the original mask. It symbolises transcendence and catharsis.$NL;$NL;Thank you for your support.$NL;$NL;OVERKILL salutes you!
bm_msk_achievement_postfix = "$NL;$NL;このマスクは実績の報酬です。PAYDAYの間にドロップすることはなく売却することも出来ません。その代わりに、カスタマイズの内容と手数料は失われますが、マスクスタッシュに無料で戻すことが出来ます。",--$NL;$NL;This mask is an achievement reward. It can't drop during a PAYDAY and it can't be sold. Instead, it can be returned to your mask stash for free, but any customization and the fee to put that together will be lost.
bm_msk_agatha_knight = "",--Agatha Knight Veteran
bm_msk_agatha_knight_desc = "",--Excavated from the arid wastelands of Tenosia, the helmet of this Agathian Knight could protect him from swords and arrows, but not from the bloody ambitions of a leader as delusional as King Alphonso.
bm_msk_agatha_vanguard_veteran = "",--Agatha Vanguard Veteran
bm_msk_agatha_vanguard_veteran_desc = "",--When you're trying to reclaim your homeland and King's law from the upstart Masons, you need strength, support and a fearsome visage. This Vanguard helm provides all three.
bm_msk_alex = "",--Alex
bm_msk_alex_desc = "",--One half of a brother and sister duo, Alex. Like swans, they are fierce. Unlike swans, they wield chainsaws and SMGs. Like swans, they are closely bonded. Unlike swans, they have a penchant for slaughter.
bm_msk_alien_helmet = "",--Alpha Gray
bm_msk_alien_helmet_desc = "グレイ型エイリアンは、地球外生命体やUMA等を信じている集団達によって存在が広められた宇宙人とされるもので、その肌の色からその名前が付けられた。",--Gray Aliens are alleged extraterrestrial beings whose existence is promoted in ufological, paranormal, and New Age communities, and who are named for their skin color.$NL;$NL;Or are they?
bm_msk_alienware = "",--Alienware
bm_msk_alienware_desc = "ある狂人が見たという、地球外生物の姿に基づいている。$NL;$NL;しかし奇妙なことに、この強靭な素材は地球上のどこにも存在しない。",--Based on the visions of a madman who thought he saw an extraterrestrial being.$NL;$NL;It is strange though, as the powerful materials are not from anywhere on Earth.
bm_msk_almirs_beard = "",--Almir's Beard
bm_msk_almirs_beard_desc = "真の男はひげを剃るべきではないと言う人間も居るが、実際のところは真の男はひげを剃る事ができない。普通の剃刀では、完全なAlmirのひげを剃る事は出来ず、折れてしまうからだ。",--Some say that real men don't shave, but the truth is that real men can't shave. Ordinary razors simply bounce off the dense, magnificent foliage that is a truly full Almir beard.
bm_msk_ami_01 = "",--Mega Rad Mutant
bm_msk_ami_01_desc = "",--As if high on radioactive spray paint, the power level has been turned up a notch and is now close to bursting. When you go on a heist, everyone around you will duck for cover as you roll on by. Every geiger counter in town is about to go haywire.
bm_msk_ami_02 = "",--Mega Famine
bm_msk_ami_02_desc = "",--That loaf of bread you wanted. Imagine that hunger one thousandfold. More than just a lack of food, your very soul is deprived of sustenance until it's as empty on nourishment as your belly. If starvation could continue beyond death, this is the visage it would take. But such a plight can be a mighty motivator for heisting.
bm_msk_ami_03 = "",--Mega Conquest
bm_msk_ami_03_desc = "",--If only the Kings of Old had such an artifact, they would have been invincible. What enemy could withstand bowing before you, as they gaze upon your magnificence? Sun Tzu can go suck a lemon, because with a mask like this, who needs to employ art in war?
bm_msk_ami_04 = "",--Mega Arch Nemesis
bm_msk_ami_04_desc = "",--One move, then another. Your opponent makes a move and you respond. He stands there, atop the mountain of gold, daring you to come forward and take on his challenge. By wearing this mask, you declare your defiance, with the game afoot, and the rivalry unending.
bm_msk_ami_05 = "",--Mega Tormentor
bm_msk_ami_05_desc = "",--Torturer or tortured? Perhaps both, as the seething glow from your eyes sends chills of terror into the souls of the Law. Hear the lamentations of the Uniformed Blue as you evade them skillfully, with evil glee flowing through your veins as you foil every one of their attempts to apprehend you.
bm_msk_ami_06 = "",--Mega Greed
bm_msk_ami_06_desc = "",--It burns into your heart and tears the flesh from your skull- orange flames to contrast the color of an unquenchable need for more. How many trips back into the vault will you make until you are satisfied? How many weapons will make you happy? All of them! Maybe.
bm_msk_amp_01 = "",--Schneider
bm_msk_amp_01_desc = "",--One of the most brutal and ruthless pirates to ever exist. But also one of the most unknown. Just the way Schneider wanted it. Instead, Schneider's moniker "the Devil" was much more well known. He found it more profitable if nobody actually knew his face. But tales of how the "devil" sailed the seven seas traveled among bars in the Caribbean. To "spot the Devil on the horizon" was a common saying when someone had disappeared out at sea. But the truth was that Schneider had forever buried them in a watery grave.
bm_msk_amp_02 = "",--Keelhauled Alex
bm_msk_amp_02_desc = "",--Every ship come bearing tales of ghost. Restless phantoms seen by tired spotters late at night. Everything from Krakens to mermaids. But the tale of Keelhauled Alex is maybe one of the most feared. Alex had been stealing food during a long sail out at sea. As he was caught, he was sentenced to be keelhauled. Not a serious crime, but a serious punishment. But as Alex was beneath the boat, another ship opened fire, and Alex was abandoned and forgotten on the bottom of the ship. As the dust settled, his corpse was thrown into the depths. But ever since then, Keelhauled Alex walks ships at night, staring down everyone from captains to simple deck hands. It is said that he can gaze into your soul and devour it.
bm_msk_amp_03 = "",--Nilam
bm_msk_amp_03_desc = "",--Nilam grew up among buccaneers, pirates and corsairs. She knew rum before she could speak, and held a sword before she could walk. Nilam was without family, and instead she found the nomadic lifestyle of a pirate her destiny. She was swift with a blade and few could match her in combat. All she sought was the same respect her peers got, but this was a world ruled by men. Finally Nilam had reached her limit. Those who wronged her were "sentenced" by getting their throats slit. Her reputation preceded her, and harbours feared the bloodshed she brought with her as her ship "Verdict" came sailing in.
bm_msk_amp_04 = "",--One-Eyed Jessicah
bm_msk_amp_04_desc = "",--With two eyes, Jessicah would never have been famous. After a shipwreck, she managed to swim to a small islet. Circled by a shark, with no rescue in sight, she was caught. With nothing more than a broken knife, her only option was to kill the shark, so that she could safely swim to shore. But she needed a decoy, a lure so she could surprise the shark. The loss of a finger or toe would make swimming difficult, so instead, she scooped out one of her eyeballs and threw the bloody mess in the water. Then she dove in.
bm_msk_ancient = "",--The Crossbreed
bm_msk_ancient_desc = "",--A powerful alien race, described by some as the most advanced beings in the universe. Different races that have come in contact with them have different names for the Crossbreed.$NL;$NL;Strong, lean and intelligent, the Crossbreed takes the best from the DNA of each alien race that it meets, always making sure it evolves in the right direction.$NL;$NL;This mask is a Humble Bundle E3 mask . It can't drop during a PAYDAY and it can't be sold. Instead, it can be returned to your mask stash for free, but any customization and the fee to put that together will be lost.
bm_msk_ancient_desc_WIN32 = "",--A powerful alien race, described by some as the most advanced beings in the universe. Different races that have come in contact with them have different names for the Crossbreed.$NL;$NL;Strong, lean and intelligent, the Crossbreed takes the best from the DNA of each alien race that it meets, always making sure it evolves in the right direction.$NL;$NL;This mask is a Humble Bundle E3 mask . It can't drop during a PAYDAY and it can't be sold. Instead, it can be returned to your mask stash for free, but any customization and the fee to put that together will be lost.
bm_msk_andromeda = "",--Augmentation
bm_msk_andromeda_desc = "",--The future is now. This special mouthpiece is believed to be developed for soldiers of the future, acting not only as a gasmask but also give the wearer the ability to breath under water. Unfortunately, this one seems broken, but it still looks cool.
bm_msk_anonymous = "",--Anonymous
bm_msk_anonymous_desc = "匿名になれば、君は君のやりたいようにやるだろう。$NL;$NL;やりたいようにやって、聞いたままにやって、笑いのためにやる。$NL;$NL社会が許さないようなことをやればいい。強盗みたいにな。",--Don the mask, become anonymous and do as you wish.$NL;$NL;Do it because you mean it, do it because you were told to, or do it for the lulz.$NL;$NL;Do all the things that regular society will not allow you. Like robbing a bank.
bm_msk_ant_01 = "",--INTERCEPTOR
bm_msk_ant_01_desc = "",--Interceptor model BX-99 was built to keep "things in order". A mission with a lof to interpret. Roaming the streets, making sure that civilians are safe and that things are "OK". This Interceptor took things too far as a situation occurred near a assembly factory. Some civilians came to harm, others destroyed, ammo slugs filled the air, and Interceptor did what it thought was absolutely necessary to not obstruct the assembly factory. Interceptor BX-99 with serial number 151010130807 was later disassembled.
bm_msk_ant_02 = "",--VIZOR
bm_msk_ant_02_desc = "",--Robot wars are easy to make fun of. Dead things that fight other dead things. But as the AI evolved, things turned real. Soldiers like Vizor played a crucial role in the mayhem orchestrated by long dead humans. Humans who pushed the button, but failed to experience the consequences. As robots turned against robots, soldiers like Vizor rose, and those with a heartbeat became a memory.
bm_msk_ant_03 = "",--MOTH
bm_msk_ant_03_desc = "",--Every war has its traitor. Moth was one of them. A sentinel robot assembled to retrieve information - by any means necessary. But hierarchy and power are often coveted. Wars breed corruption, and Moth followed his logic and switched sides - causing millions of robots to disconnect. Celebrated by one side and hated by another - Moth came to be one of the pawns that turned the war.
bm_msk_ant_04 = "",--DOME
bm_msk_ant_04_desc = "",--Dome was the centerpiece of a grand scheme, planned and set in motion by the other side. A simple robot, assembled to restore/reassemble/rearrange, Dome was on mission to reassemble a government building that got destroyed by the enemy. A stealth attack - to take out Commander Wasp - was taking place near the location as the Commander's car drove passed the debris. Dome saw the coming attack and sacrificed himself to protect the Commander by throwing himself in front of the car, making it steer away from the blast. Wasp survived, Dome did not.
bm_msk_ant_05 = "",--SKULL
bm_msk_ant_05_desc = "",--Every war requires executioners. Not a simple soldier, but someone who can take a life with a threatening demeanor. Someone working for the "system", who blindly follow orders. Skull was one of those. Someone who, tirelessly disconnected robot after robot, war criminals and everyone else deemed "dangerous" to the "cause".
bm_msk_ant_06 = "",--DRONE
bm_msk_ant_06_desc = "",--Engineered to be as lethal as robotly possible. Drone was solely responsible for the Great Purge. Forever imprinted in all minds and historical dataservers. Drone had the skills needed to go beyond what was expected by a "grunt". Someone who seemed disposable. but would prove invaluable. The Great Purge turned the war: sleeper cells got exposed, robots got disconnected, and the Hive Mind lost thousands of zettabytes. Drone became a statue to be gazed upon in Ming Ji Memorial Park.
bm_msk_ant_07 = "",--WASP
bm_msk_ant_07_desc = "",--Commander Wasp sat on incredible technical capacity. Strength and intelligence was by far superior to the other side. A prototype that would have the needed circuits to outsmart the opposing forces. But an untested prototype. Something rushed. Something that was too experimental. Madness strikes circuit boards, but we refer to it as a "bug". Killing his fellow troops in a rage of paranoia - Commander Wasp became a criminal of war.
bm_msk_ant_08 = "",--RAPTOR
bm_msk_ant_08_desc = "",--Raptor was a fighter pilot. Hooked into the central hub on each plane he flew, he steered with certainty. It became a matter of accumulated knowledge. Even though all pilots got the same software installed - an AI learns. And somehow, Raptor managed to stay alive enough to keep his knowledge. The Hive Mind was off limits to fighter pilots, as they could be captured and hacked when they crossed into enemy territory. But Raptor learned to be the best at taking out enemy bases without hesitation.
bm_msk_anubis = "",--Anubis
bm_msk_anubis_desc = "アヌビスはジャッカルの頭をしたエジプト神話の神で、墓の守り神である",--The Egyptian jackal-headed god of the afterlife, Anubis sought to protect graves rather than fill them.
bm_msk_arch_nemesis = "",--Arch Nemesis
bm_msk_arch_nemesis_desc = "ネメシスは辞書によって以下のように定義されている。$NL;$NL;名詞 [読 nem-uh-seez]$NL;$NL;1.人が達することができない事柄。例:「昼の中華のビュッフェは宿敵だった」$NL;2.負ける訳にはいかない相手の事$NL;3.ギリシア神話に登場する、「義憤」又は「復讐」の女神$NL;4.罰·天罰の事$NL;$NL;なお、Hoxtonは以下のように定義している。$NL;「クソDozerめ、最大の\"天罰\"を与える。クソ野郎め!」",--Nemesis, as defined by the dictionary$NL;$NL;Noun [ahrch nem-uh-seez]$NL;$NL;1. Something that a person cannot conquer, achieve, etc.: "That Chinese buffet at lunch proved to be my arch-nemesis."$NL;2. An opponent whom a person cannot defeat.$NL;3. In classical mythology. The goddess of divine retribution.$NL;4. An agent or act of retribution or punishment.$NL;$NL;As defined by Hoxton: "That fuckin' dozer. He's my arch-fucking-nemesis. 'Orrible cunt!"
bm_msk_area51 = "",--The Anomaly
bm_msk_area51_desc = "",--Forged from Penrose patterned rapidly quenched metallic alloys, this helmet was constructed from debris recovered from a top secret crash site. The government continues to deny any knowledge of its existence.
bm_msk_aviator = "",--The Heat
bm_msk_aviator_desc = "みんな大好きサングラス$NL;$NL;でもこれで銀行を襲うのは超クレイジーな奴です。...あなたの事ですよ。$NL;$NL;このマスクはInfamyツリーの報酬です。PAYDAYの間にドロップすることはなく売却することも出来ません。その代わりに、カスタマイズの内容と手数料は失われますが、マスクスタッシュに無料で戻すことが出来ます。",--Everyone loves a good pair of sunglasses.$NL;$NL;But only the cockiest, most wanted, cops be damned sons of bitches are crazy enough to rob a goddamn bank wearing 'em.$NL;$NL;That's you.$NL;$NL;This mask is an Infamy tree reward. It can't drop during a PAYDAY and it can't be sold. Instead, it can be returned to your mask stash for free, but any pattern, color or material as well as the customization fee to put these together will be lost.
bm_msk_baba_yaga = "",--Baba Yaga
bm_msk_baba_yaga_desc = "",--Occasionally villainous, always mysterious. The Baba Yaga stalks the dark forests of Slavic myth. She flies around in a mortar, wields a pestle and lives in a hut that stomps about on giant chicken legs.
bm_msk_baby_angry = "",--Angry Baby
bm_msk_baby_angry_desc = "ガアアアアガッルウウガガルガアアアアガルガルワアアアアアアアアガルルル$NL;$NL;ガアアルルルルガルウガアアアワァガルウウウウウワァ",--GRRRRRRRR GRRR grrr grr grr GRRRR Wah, wah, WAAAAAAAAAAH! GRRR! Grr.$NL;$NL;GRRRR grr GRRRR rawr GRRRRRRRRRRRRR, wahh, WAH, WAH, WAH, GRRR.
bm_msk_baby_cry = "",--Cry Baby
bm_msk_baby_cry_desc = "ワーン、ワーン、ウワァァァン!ワァァァン!!$NL;$NL;ワァアアアン、ワアアアアァン、ヒッッグ...ワーン、ワーン!ワァァァァァン!",--Waaaah, waah, wah, WAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAH, wah, WAAAAAAAAH, WAAAAAAH!$NL;$NL;WAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAH, wah, WAAAAAAAAH, WAAAAAAH, Waaaah, waah, wah. Wah. WAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAH!
bm_msk_baby_happy = "",--Happy Baby
bm_msk_baby_happy_desc = "ふー、ばぶー、ぶーだぁだぁ?だぁだぁだぁ?だぁぶぅ?$NL;$NL;だぁ、だぁだぁ!だぁだぁだぁ、だぁどぅどぅ、だぁだぁだぁ?だぁどぅだぁ?だぁだぁだぁ、ふぅー!",--Ffff, gaga, bo, gaga bo GAGA GAGA? GAGAGAGA? GAGA? Gagag GOGOGO GAGA? GAGA! GOGO! Bah. Gaga bah gogo go.$NL;$NL;GAGA? GAGA! GOGO! Bah. GAGAGA? GAGA GOGO GAGAGA? GAGA! Gagaga gogoga. Fff.
bm_msk_babyrhino = "",--Baby Rhino
bm_msk_babyrhino_desc = "誰も子サイの頭を着けたがらない。可愛くない? これを装着すると、ちょっと自分を間抜けだと感じるかもしれない。多分見た目の所為だ。$NL;$NL;身に着けている間は、ちょっとキツイ見た目で友達から心配される。 が、そんな頑固な奴に付き合わなければ、大丈夫だろう。",--Who would not want to wear the head of a baby rhino. Is it not cute? Putting it on makes you feel a little stupid, maybe because how it looks.$NL;$NL;While wearing it, you are worried that it is a bit hard seeing through the mask. You will do fine as long as you do not wander off with your pig-headed friends.
bm_msk_baitface = "",--Funnyman
bm_msk_baitface_desc = "",--The Funnyman knows how to make people laugh. The Funnyman might go too far and take a hit or two. Beware though, because a person who can control others laughter knows how to get the last laugh.
bm_msk_balaclava = "",--Balaclava
bm_msk_balaclava_desc = "武器やイデオロギーは常に変化し続けているが、Balaclavaは数十年、強盗やテロリストのトレードマークで有り続けている。過酷な寒さでも、目だし帽は君を温かく包んでくれるだろう。",--The weapons may change, the ideologies may shift and the accents may swap, but the balaclava has been a mainstay for the armed robber and terrorist for decades. Covering all but your steely, flint-like eyes and your cruel, twisted mouth, it keeps you warm when it's chilly too.
bm_msk_bandit = "",--Wild West Classic
bm_msk_bandit_desc = "",--The wide-brimmed hat, the steely gaze and the scarf pulled up over the mouth. A combination so iconic, so classic and so effective that it remains the staple for gangsters and heisters everywhere.
bm_msk_bear = "",--Mark
bm_msk_bear_desc = "ロシアからこんにちは。$NL;$NL;私が思うに、このゲームは世界で一番になるでしょう。$NL;$NL;これはまさにクマだね。$NL;$NL;ちょっと前までコレに意味なんて無かったけどさ。$NL;$NL;ありがとう。",--hello from Russia.$NL;$NL;I think it will be the best game in the world.$NL;$NL;It's just a bear.$NL;$NL;Just before there was an empty.$NL;$NL;Thank you$NL;$NL;- Vasiliy
bm_msk_biglips = "",--The Big lips
bm_msk_biglips_desc = "このマスクを付けて、誰かにキスをしろ。$NL;$NL;受け取った人はマスクの様に、あなたが今まで見た中で一番大きく肉付きの良い唇になる。$NL;$NL;口を開いて絶叫しろ、銀行強盗としての指針だ。",--Throw someone a lip by wearing this mask.$NL;$NL;The thing that gets people is the two fleshy folds that surround the mouth of this mask, the biggest lips you ever saw.$NL;$NL;Open your mouth and say 'aaah', directed the bank robber.
bm_msk_biker = "",--Biker
bm_msk_biker_classic = "",--The Classic
bm_msk_biker_classic_desc = "",--This old school motorcycle helmet is part of a legacy that all bikers around the world cherish. And it's more about nostalgia rather than style. This helmet transports you back to the golden biker days of the 1940's.
bm_msk_biker_desc = "",--When you're a thrill-seeker, and a risk-taker, and a live-for-the-moment kind of heister, it is important to have at least some measure of protection. That also goes if you are a meat-cleaver waving maniac.
bm_msk_bny_01 = "",--Navy Beanie
bm_msk_bny_01_desc = "",--This fetching number will make you the talk of the town. You're guaranteed to hear things like: "SEND IN THE TAZERS!", "THIS IS THE POLICE, COME OUT WITH YOUR HANDS UP!", or "WHO ARE THESE GUYS, EX-MILITARY?!"
bm_msk_bny_02 = "",--Green Beanie
bm_msk_bny_02_desc = "",--A murky green that adds a touch of subtle mystery to your profile. The FBI will appreciate your fondness for their own green uniformed team. Not that it won't stop them firing on you openly anyway!
bm_msk_bny_03 = "",--Black Beanie
bm_msk_bny_03_desc = "",--Most robbers choose this snug, concealing headwear to help them blend in with the night. Unfortunately, it won't do you much good to conceal yourself carrying all that equipment.
bm_msk_bny_04 = "",--Red Beanie
bm_msk_bny_04_desc = "",--This supposedly "three million dollar hat" is either soaked in the blood of your enemies, or was just made with some red woolen material. Just wash it after each heist!
bm_msk_bobblehead_dozer = "",--Dozer Mask
bm_msk_bobblehead_dozer_desc = "センパイが私に気が付いた/// >ω<)キャー!!!$NL;$NL;このマスクは「OVERKILL公式オンラインストア」でのみ入手可能な、『PAYDAY 2 DOZER BOBBLEHEAD』にのみ付属している専用コードを適用することで入手できるマスクです。$NL;$NL;元ネタを作った Far2close 氏に感謝!!",--"Senpai Noticed Me!!! :3"$NL;$NL;A big thank you to community member Far2close for making a hilarious version of an otherwise intimidating dozer face plate.$NL;$NL;This mask can only be obtained from a code accompanying the PAYDAY 2 DOZER BOBBLEHEAD bought from the online OVERKILL merchandise store.
bm_msk_bodhi = "",--Bodhi
bm_msk_bodhi_begins = "",--Bodhi Begins
bm_msk_bodhi_begins_desc = "Bodhiを象徴するマスクの、まだペイントされていない無地のバージョン。$NL;$NL;まだオリジナルの様に着こなせていない? これは歴史を塗り替えるチャンスだ。",--This is a clean version of the iconic Bodhi mask, before it was painted.$NL;$NL;Never liked how the original one turned out? This is your chance to change history.
bm_msk_bodhi_desc = "",--Masks have always been used in spiritual traditions that relate to deities, the divine and those chasing the apotheosis of the self. Bodhi's mask reflects the man behind it. Strong, cunning, single-minded and centered.
bm_msk_bonnie = "",--Bonnie
bm_msk_bonnie_begins = "",--Bonnie Begins
bm_msk_bonnie_begins_desc = "Bonnieを象徴するマスクの、まだペイントされていない無地のバージョン。$NL;$NL;まだオリジナルの様に着こなせていない? これは歴史を塗り替えるチャンスだ。",--This is a clean version of the iconic Bonnie mask, before it was painted.$NL;$NL;Never liked how the original one turned out? This is your chance to change history.
bm_msk_bonnie_desc = "",--Few nations have contributed to humanity as Scotland has. In every field of endeavor - science, arts, cuisine - it is the people of this blessed land that give freely and generously. With this mask, Bonnie is determined to reverse this trend.
bm_msk_boombox = "",--Boom Box
bm_msk_boombox_desc = "",--According to the brochure, Alesso's Boom Box features include "No batteries to slay your vibe, sound insulation to keep suckas from hearing your beats and full-face armor to keep cops from checking your clock."
bm_msk_borsuk = "",--Borsuk
bm_msk_borsuk_desc = "",--There is more to being a world-class heister than picking up a gun. It requires training, conditioning and a singular focus on developing far beyond the norm. Such heisters are near mutants, who wade into furious battle and always emerge victorious.
bm_msk_brainiack = "",--The Brainiac
bm_msk_brainiack_desc = "このマスクは、誰かの精神を詰めた何かだ。$NL;$NL;このマスクを付けると極端に活発になり、犯罪とそれに身をゆだねる方法を学ぶ為に欲望を爆発させる。",--This is the mask of someone who has a lot on his mind.$NL;$NL;Putting on this mask sparks an excessive, almost explosive desire to learn more about crimes and how to commit them.
bm_msk_brazil_baby = "",--Brazil Baby
bm_msk_brazil_baby_desc = "",--GAGA? GAGA! GOGO! Boo! GAGAGA? GAGA GOGO GAGAGA? GAGA? GAGA! GAGAGA? GAGA GAGAGA?$NL;$NL;GAGAGA? GAGAGAGOGO? Boo! BOOO! Gagagaga boo gaga.
bm_msk_brutal = "",--Road Rage
bm_msk_brutal_desc = "",--This helmet is reserved for the top dog in a biker gang. It demands respect and authority from your brothers, and when it's time to do battle, you wear this helmet proudly and ride at the front.
bm_msk_buha = "",--The Rage
bm_msk_buha_desc = "あなたが今まで見たクラウンマスクで、きっと一番険悪なマスク。$NL;$NL;ほとんど、Wolfのマスクを凌ぐものである。$NL;$NL;ほとんどね。",--Probably one of the angriest looking clown masks you have ever seen.$NL;$NL;It almost puts Wolf's mask to shame.$NL;$NL;Almost.
bm_msk_bullet = "",--The Bullet
bm_msk_bullet_desc = "高火力で顔に撃ち込まれて困っている?$NL;$NL;同時にBulldozer、Cloaker、Shieldがやってくるのが怖い?$NL;$NL;このマスクを装着しても助けにはならないが、堂々と倒れる事は出来るだろう。The Bullet、あなたの近くの ブラックマーケットに行こう、今すぐ!",--Worried about getting shot in the face with a high powered firearm?$NL;$NL;Scared that you will get stomped by a bulldozer, cloaker and a shield at the same time?$NL;$NL;Wearing this mask will not help you, but you will get downed in style. The Bullet - out in Black Markets near you, right now!
bm_msk_bullskull = "",--Desert Skull
bm_msk_bullskull_desc = "",--When staggering through desolate barrancas, with only thoughts for company, the last thing you want to see is the parched bones of those who went before you. Suddenly those thoughts are screams.
bm_msk_bush = "",--The 43rd
bm_msk_bush_desc = "政治家であり、最高司令官であり、父である。8年間、この国に努めた。$NL;$NL;間違いなく、言葉巧みな奴だ。$NL;$NL;The 43rdは歴史上最も不人気な大統領の一人だった。しかし犯罪者の中では、未だに人気が衰えていない。",--Politician, Commander-In-Chief, father. Served this great nation for 8 years.$NL;$NL;A wordsmith, no doubt.$NL;$NL;The 43rd was one of the most unpopular presidents in history. Among criminals however, he remains extremely popular.
bm_msk_butcher = "",--The Butcher from Hell
bm_msk_butcher_desc = "東部より現われた狂気の肉屋については、色々な噂がある。その1つによると、ある男が豚を屠殺する喜びに溺れ、ゆっくりとこのような外見になってきたとか。$NL;$NL;屠殺場で働くのは地獄のごとく厳しいもので、彼の皮膚は水ぶくれと切り傷で醜く変質していった。人々は、屠殺場の中から聞こえる悲鳴について語る...それは、豚の鳴き声だけではないのだ。",--There are many rumours about the mad butcher from the east, one of them tells of a man who found such pleasure in butchering pigs that he slowly started to look like one.$NL;$NL;Working in a butchery as hot as hell itself his skin became disfigured with blisters and cuts, people tell of screams coming from inside... And not just the screams of pigs.
bm_msk_cantus = "",--Cantus
bm_msk_cantus_desc = "",--Whether you're on the bus or in the boardroom, when Alesso is filling your ears with heavenly tunes, it's important to show the world a suitable face. Presenting Cantus - the Angel of Music and Song. Let your spirit soar!
bm_msk_card_jack = "",--Jack of Cards
bm_msk_card_jack_desc = "",--A classic made into a mask. The standard 52-card deck is the most played deck of playing cards used today, and regardless if you are a rookie or professional player, you will most likely recognize this face. A proper poker face-mask.
bm_msk_card_joker = "",--Joker of Cards
bm_msk_card_joker_desc = "",--A classic made into a mask. The standard 52-card deck is the most played deck of playing cards used today, and regardless if you are a rookie or professional player, you will most likely recognize this face. A proper poker face-mask.
bm_msk_card_king = "",--King of Cards
bm_msk_card_king_desc = "",--A classic made into a mask. The standard 52-card deck is the most played deck of playing cards used today, and regardless if you are a rookie or professional player, you will most likely recognize this face. A proper poker face-mask.
bm_msk_card_queen = "",--Queen of Cards
bm_msk_card_queen_desc = "",--A classic made into a mask. The standard 52-card deck is the most played deck of playing cards used today, and regardless if you are a rookie or professional player, you will most likely recognize this face. A proper poker face-mask.
bm_msk_carnotaurus = "",--Alfred
bm_msk_carnotaurus_desc = "アルフレッドこと「カルノタウルス」は、奴が元気に走り回っていた時代においてとても素早い恐竜だった。奴の特徴的な角といかつい首は、どんな恐竜よりも目立っていた。奴のでかい頭と角は衝撃を吸収し、とりわけ他の恐竜にかます頭突きにおいては有史以前最大の「金槌」となった。",--Alfred the Carnotaurus was a very fast dinosaur when he was alive and kicking. His distinctive horns and his muscular neck made him stand out next to all the other dinosaurs. His large head along with his horns working as shock absorbers made him particularly skilled at head butting other dinosaurs in order to show who had the largest prehistoric d-peen.
bm_msk_chains = "",--Chains
bm_msk_chains_clean = "",--Chains Begins
bm_msk_chains_clean_desc = "Chainsを象徴するマスクの、まだペイントされていない無地のバージョン。$NL;$NL;まだオリジナルの様に着こなせていない? これは歴史を塗り替えるチャンスだ。",--This is a clean version of the iconic Chains mask, before it was painted.$NL;$NL;Never liked how the original one turned out? This is your chance to change history.
bm_msk_chains_desc = "Chainsのマスク",--The mask of Chains.
bm_msk_chains_glow = "",--Mega Chains
bm_msk_chains_glow_desc = "Mega Chainsマスクは、元のマスクが進化したものだ。そしてこれは、超越と浄化を象徴するものなのだ。$NL;$NL;応援ありがとう。$NL;$NL;OVERKILLより敬意を!",--The Mega Chains mask is an evolved version of the original mask. It symbolises transcendence and catharsis.$NL;$NL;Thank you for your support.$NL;$NL;OVERKILL salutes you!
bm_msk_champion_dallas = "",--The Champ
bm_msk_champion_dallas_desc = "これはチャンピオンのマスクだ。ツイてない日のDallasが元だ。どんな感じにツイてないかって?考えてもみろ、プロボクサーと13ラウンド殴り合って、なんでもかんでも、目は腫れ、頭はアザだらけ、顎は外れ...で、このマスクがそれな訳だ。ああ、本当に酷い日のDallasだ。",--This is the Champ mask. Based on a bad day for Dallas. How bad? Well, imagine being on the business end of thirteen rounds with a professional boxer. Swollen brow, broken nose, fat lip, black eye, contusions, concussions, dislocated jaw - you name it, and this mask has it. Yeah, a really bad day for Dallas.
bm_msk_character_locked = "キャラ固有マスク",--Character's Mask
bm_msk_character_locked_desc = "このスロットのマスクを装備することで、あなたが設定した使用キャラクターのマスクを装備します。",--Equipping this mask slot will make you wear your preferred character's mask.
bm_msk_cheat_error = "不正なマスク!",--CHEATED MASK!
bm_msk_chef_hat = "",--The Chef
bm_msk_chef_hat_desc = "",--Whether you're a line cook flipping patties at a roadside diner, or an itamae dissecting toadfish at a $1000-a-table joint, this hat means one thing: you're the chef.
bm_msk_chico = "",--Scarface
bm_msk_chico_begins = "",--Scarface Begins
bm_msk_chico_begins_desc = "Scarfaceを象徴するマスクの、まだペイントされていない無地のバージョン。$NL;$NL;まだオリジナルの様に着こなせていない? これは歴史を塗り替えるチャンスだ。",--This is a clean version of the iconic Scarface mask, before it was painted.$NL;$NL;Never liked how the original one turned out? This is your chance to change history.
bm_msk_chico_desc = "",--Scarface came to the US with nothing more than two empty hands and a bad attitude, the darkness in his heart matched only by the brilliance of his criminal mind. His mask tells the story, complete with the trail of blood that he left in his wake as he began to make his mark.
bm_msk_churchill = "",--British Bulldog
bm_msk_churchill_desc = "政治家、受賞者、多数の勲章を持つ最初のアメリカ合衆国名誉市民である。ある男は彼の性格に問題があると言い、「一人の男に対し、賞賛と軽蔑を同時に注いだことなど決してなかった。真逆の両極端が同じ人間の中で1つになったことなどなかった」と語った。",--Politician, prize winner, owner of many medals and the first honorary citizen of the United States of America. By some it was said that he had a flawed character, saying; "never had people admired and despised a man simultaneously to the same extent; never had such opposite extremes been combined in the same human being."
bm_msk_clinton = "",--The 42nd
bm_msk_clinton_desc = "政治家であり、最高司令官であり、父である。8年間、この国に努めた。$NL;$NL;間違いなく、色男だ。$NL;$NL;The 42ndは歴史上最も平和な大統領の一人だった。しかし犯罪者の中では、未だに人気が衰えていない。",--Politician, Commander-In-Chief, father. Served this great nation for 8 years.$NL;$NL;A ladies man, no doubt.$NL;$NL;The 42nd was one of the most peaceful presidents in history. Among criminals however, he remains extremely popular.
bm_msk_cloth_commander = "",--Commander Crime
bm_msk_cloth_commander_desc = "Commander CrimeはOVERKILL Comicsに登場する、アメリカ生まれの犯罪ネットワークC.R.I.M.E.の最高指導者である悪の親玉です。$NL;$NL;このキャラクターは世界に名を知られる作家·編集者·画家でありプロバドミントン選手であるMax Elmberg Sjöholmによって作られました。$NL;$NL;Commander Crimeの初登場は\"The Amazing Career Criminals: The PAYDAY gang gets a C.R.I.M.E. offer they can't refuse!\"の中です。",--Commander Crime is an American fictional character, a supervillain and the supreme leader of the criminal network C.R.I.M.E. who appears in comic books by OVERKILL Comics.$NL;$NL;The character was created by now world renowned writer-editor-artist and professional badminton player Max Elmberg Sjöholm.$NL;$NL;Commander Crime made his first appearance in The Amazing Career Criminals: The PAYDAY gang gets a C.R.I.M.E. offer they can't refuse!
bm_msk_clown_56 = "",--The Starved
bm_msk_clown_56_desc = "このマスクは酷く醜い外見、痩せた顔の形、そして乾燥した肌をしている。$NL;$NL;使用者に悪夢を与えるタイプのマスクだ。",--This mask has a hideous appearance, a bony facial structure and dehydrated skin.$NL;$NL;It is the kind of mask gives you nightmares.
bm_msk_clowncry = "",--The Crybaby
bm_msk_clowncry_desc = "泣き声を上げるピエロより悲しいことがありますか?$NL;$NL;恐らく、怖ろしいマスクに身を包んだ強盗に叫ばれ、泣きながら地に伏せた民間人ぐらいなものだろう。$NL;$NL;あるいは、もぬけの殻となった金庫を見た銀行の支店長か。",--Is there anything sadder than a crying clown?$NL;$NL;Probably crying civilians, being shouted to the ground by a criminal wearing a horrific mask.$NL;$NL;Or maybe a bank manager with an empty vault.
bm_msk_cmo_01 = "",--Retro Dallas
bm_msk_cmo_01_desc = "",--A good tactical game is the perfect way to prep before a big heist. Dallas prefers to kick-start his strategic mind with something difficult and calculating where you need to manage units and resources to achieve victory.
bm_msk_cmo_02 = "",--Retro Hoxton
bm_msk_cmo_02_desc = "",--Solving logic puzzles as a brain teaser is a great way to unwind after some intense criminal activity. Hoxton likes games that lets him wrap his head around a problem and figure it out one step at a time with the clues given.
bm_msk_cmo_03 = "",--Retro Wolf
bm_msk_cmo_03_desc = "",--Violent games help Wolf getting into the mood for a heist. The more blood, gore and carnage the better. He prefers games that test your reaction and speed. Games where every second counts for your survival against a nearly endless horde of enemies.
bm_msk_cmo_04 = "",--Retro Chains
bm_msk_cmo_04_desc = "",--Combat and shooter games that simulate intense situations between players is a great way to keep up your skills in between jobs. Chains likes games that train your situational awareness and award skillfull play by gaining the upperhand in a fight.
bm_msk_cmt_01 = "",--Alces
bm_msk_cmt_01_desc = "",--Make the hunted become the hunter just like the legendary Thomoose who could stagger his way through any heist with these impressive horns.
bm_msk_cmt_02 = "",--Canis Lupus
bm_msk_cmt_02_desc = "",--Blow down the bank vaults and scare the crap out of all the little pigs while wearing this mask.
bm_msk_cmt_03 = "",--Felis Lynx
bm_msk_cmt_03_desc = "",--Never come between a cat and his prey, or a heister and his loot!
bm_msk_cmt_04 = "",--Ursus Maritimus
bm_msk_cmt_04_desc = "",--Fight global warming with a mighty roar while wearing this magnificent face covering.
bm_msk_combusto = "",--Firestarter
bm_msk_combusto_desc = "",--This clown used to be a master of pyrotechnics, having a fire breathing number that no one could top. His competitors in the not-so-known-firebreathing-clown-scene were unhappy with his success... And spiked his cocktail.$NL;$NL;With third degree burns on his face and an evil look in his eyes he fought fire with fire and set the other clowns ablaze. But he didn't stop there, the fiery hatred in him burned too bright. Now he seeks to set the world on fire.
bm_msk_concert_female = "",--Female Concert Goer
bm_msk_concert_female_desc = "",--When you descend into the roiling whirlpool that is the ecstasy of an Alesso concert, you better be wearing your best face. The Female Concert Goer is impassive and detached, because nothing matters but the music.
bm_msk_concert_male = "",--Male Concert Goer
bm_msk_concert_male_desc = "",--Tie-dyed shirts are so 70's. Holding up a lighter went out in the 80's. Whistles and glow sticks were left behind in the 90's, and the 00's, well, the less said the better. The modern concert goer, however, favors the mask.
bm_msk_conquest = "",--Conquest
bm_msk_conquest_desc = "",--The identity of the first horseman of the Apocalypse, and exactly what he represents is something still greatly debated to this day. Some call him Conquest, some say he was Christ himself, and some claim he was even the Antichrist.
bm_msk_corey = "",--Corey
bm_msk_corey_desc = "",--When you're the most delicious lunch on the savannah, you have to be fast, agile and cunning if you're going to survive. Corey is all of these things. Zebras are also peaceful, gentle and herbivorous. Corey is none of these things.
bm_msk_crazy_lion = "",--Mad Lion
bm_msk_crazy_lion_desc = "",--A horrifying mask shaped like the head of a lion.$NL;$NL;Little is known about this mask. It is said it was made by a crazy Balkan scientist who had a sick fascination for lions. Only he could see the beauty in this mask.$NL;$NL;The mask was given to you by someone who wishes you well.
bm_msk_croupier_hat = "",--Wheeler Dealer
bm_msk_croupier_hat_desc = "",--Spruce up your glamorous neon 80's look! This kind of mint-green headwear has been in use since the 19th century as a method of preventing eyestrain from intense light sources. Coked out gamblers and gonzo journalists have propelled the croupier's hat into the focus of the mainstream. They are also perfect for beach-front raves, picking up hotties on the beach, signing a contract on the 18th hole of your nearest country club and generally looking like an octogenarian.
bm_msk_crowgoblin = "",--Crow Goblin
bm_msk_crowgoblin_desc = "",--For the longest time ever no one knew who the real identity behind the Crow Goblin was. Twenty years later people found out, but it was unsatisfactory so they said that that person was an imposter or something. The real Crow Goblin was someone else.$NL;$NL;I don't want to bore you with the rest of it but the mask looks pretty nice, yeah? It's got a purple hat, or maybe it's a hoodie, I don't know. It sports a pretty cool grin and some thread sewn across its face. I wonder who hides behind the mask though.
bm_msk_cthulhu = "",--Cthulhu
bm_msk_cthulhu_desc = "怖ろしい姿のマスク。恐怖の頂点に立つ顔だ。$NL;$NL;皆はこの怪物が様々な名前を持っていると言う。Tuluu、Cluluu、Clooloou、Cthuluu、C'thulhuu、Cighuluu、Cathulu、C'thlu、数え切れないほどあるだろう。$NL;$NL;人間、蛸、龍が混ざったものである、ということしか我々にはわからない。",--A mask with a hideous appearance, the very face of terror.$NL;$NL;They say that an evil beast has many names. That must be why this beast is known as Tulu, Clulu, Clooloo, Cthulu, Cthullu, C'thulhu, Cighulu, Cathulu, C'thlu among other names.$NL;$NL;Part human, part octopus and part dragon, this is one of the greatest evils known to man.
bm_msk_cursed_crown = "",--The Cursed One
bm_msk_cursed_crown_desc = "彼の名は、歴史の中に埋もれてしまった。彼は王であったか、あるいは強大な魔導師だったのだろう。だが、偉大な存在であろうと、The Diamondの前では破滅を迎えるのだ。",--His name is lost to legend. He might have been a King, or a mighty Sorceror. But even the great are undone by the Diamond.
bm_msk_daft = "",--Android
bm_msk_daft_desc = "外界との真の隔離のために、このAndroidマスクを提供する。軽量合金、メッキ仕上げ、素晴らしいLEDライトは、強盗の時を待っている。残念ながら、600万言語を理解できるようになるわけじゃない。",--For the truly detached and impassive, we provide the Android mask. Lightweight alloys, chromium finish and really cool LED lights means this mask is ready for the bank job or the dancefloor. Alas, it does not make you fluent in six million languages.
bm_msk_dallas = "",--Dallas
bm_msk_dallas_clean = "",--Dallas Begins
bm_msk_dallas_clean_desc = "Dallasを象徴するマスクの、まだペイントされていない無地のバージョン。$NL;$NL;まだオリジナルの様に着こなせていない? これは歴史を塗り替えるチャンスだ。",--This is a clean version of the iconic Dallas mask, before it was painted.$NL;$NL;Never liked how the original one turned out? This is your chance to change history.
bm_msk_dallas_desc = "誰もが恐れるマスク。",--The mask that everyone fears.
bm_msk_dallas_glow = "",--Mega Dallas
bm_msk_dallas_glow_desc = "Mega Dallasマスクは、元のマスクが進化したものだ。そしてこれは、超越と浄化を象徴するものなのだ。$NL;$NL;応援ありがとう。$NL;$NL;OVERKILLより敬意を!",--The Mega Dallas mask is an evolved version of the original mask. It symbolises transcendence and catharsis.$NL;$NL;Thank you for your support.$NL;$NL;OVERKILL salutes you!
bm_msk_damned = "",--Floating Guy
bm_msk_damned_desc = "",--As you walk down the corridor you see this scary, but also somewhat slow guy. Hovering there, ominously. Hard to tell if he's a threat or just floating around a bit. But then. A blast breaks the silence and you cease to exist. So next time you meet Floating Guy: come prepared and don't take him lightly.
bm_msk_dawg = "",--Dawg
bm_msk_dawg_desc = "マスクだわ。変装に使うの。まさに強盗ね。",--Such mask. Much disguise. Very robber.
bm_msk_dawn_of_the_dead = "",--The Undead
bm_msk_dawn_of_the_dead_desc = "アンデッドは死んだにもかかわらず生きているかのように振る舞うもののことだ。$NL;$NL;神秘的な方法で生成され、ゾンビやヴァンパイアにもなりうる。$NL;$NL;もし君が強盗しようとしているなら、なぜ人として生きているうちに地獄を味わっておかない?",--An undead is a being that is dead yet somehow behaves like it is still alive.$NL;$NL;Created in mysterious ways, this might as well be a zombie as it could be a Vampire.$NL;$NL;If you are going to rob a bank, why not scare the living hell out of people while doing so?
bm_msk_day_of_the_dead = "",--Calaca
bm_msk_day_of_the_dead_desc = "メキシコのDay of the Deadフェスティバルと関係のあるスケルトンマスク。$NL;$NL;始まりはアステカ族の紋様の模写だが、それも本当かどうかは解らない。$NL;$NL;Calacaを身に纏うという事は、自分の周りで起きる全ての死のハプニングから喜びを見つけ出すという事だ。他者の死を喜びの儀式に変えよう!",--A skeleton mask connected to the Mexican Day of the Dead festival.$NL;$NL;Origins have been traced back to Aztec imagery, but no one is really sure.$NL;$NL;Wearing the Calaca is all about finding the joy in death happening all around you. The death of others should be a joyous occasion!
bm_msk_dbd_00 = "",--Blister Head
bm_msk_dbd_00_desc = "",--This blister stricken creature is the embodiment of true terror. All your childhood fears poured into something unfathomable and horrendous. Question is if you will even need bullets anymore.
bm_msk_dbd_01 = "",--The Clawer
bm_msk_dbd_01_desc = "",--On gloomy nights when the moon is bright, one might witness how The Clawer emerges from the watery depths. It yearns for fresh meat and won't stop until its hunger is still. The Clawer is one of those urban myths that campfire teens tell - just before The Clawer strikes. Afterwards, it returns to the deep. Hibernating until its stomach growls yet again.
bm_msk_dbd_02 = "",--Feeder
bm_msk_dbd_02_desc = "",--Feeder has dislodged his jaw with one sole purpose: to be able to swallow a whole, human heart. This explains why his teeth and tongue is of no use, as chewing is not important. When he roams the night he seeks out teens with strong hearts that can sustain him. So if you spot a corpse with a ripped chest - run.
bm_msk_dbd_03 = "",--Dendron
bm_msk_dbd_03_desc = "",--A dark forest is scary to anyone, no matter how old you are. You fear whatever is in it, and the things lurking in the shadows. But you seldom think of the actual trees. You never think of Dendron. And when you do, it's already too late. Dendron strikes without mercy. So fear not what's behind the trees, but instead the trees.
bm_msk_dbd_04 = "",--The Killer
bm_msk_dbd_04_desc = "",--Even stark raving mad Killers need cash. It's a fact. So sometimes you simply must take a break from slashing teens and hang up the blood stained machete. But killing can be done in so many ways and it's real important with a hobby - and remember that cops bleed too.
bm_msk_de_gaulle = "",--The Constable
bm_msk_de_gaulle_desc = "1940年から1969年までずっと、The Constableはフランスにおける軍部の大物にして政治的指導者だった。1940年、彼はドイツの侵略者と祖国の休戦協定締結を受け入れず、ロンドンに拠点を設置し、彼自身のフランス、つまり自由フランスの設立を宣言した。戦争中、彼は海外植民地、特にアフリカを団結させ、レジスタンス運動を組織しつつ、一方では米英の完全な承認を得ようと努めた。",--For much between 1940-1969, the Constable was the dominant military and political leader of France. Refusing to accept his government's armistice with the German invaders in 1940, he set up his base in London, proclaimed himself the incarnation of France, and created the Free French movement. During the war he rallied the overseas colonies, especially those in Africa, organized the Resistance from abroad, and struggled to gain full recognition from the British and Americans.
bm_msk_death_rider = "",--Death
bm_msk_death_rider_desc = "",--The fourth and final horseman of the Apocalypse is Death himself. Wherever Death went, Hades always followed with jaws wide open, ready to devour the souls of the victims slain by Death.
bm_msk_deltaforce = "",--Alpha Force
bm_msk_deltaforce_desc = "第4国内展開執行部隊アルファ(4th DOGE-A)――一般にAlpha Forceとあざ笑われている――は、米陸軍統合特殊作戦コマンド部隊である。彼らの評判はかなり悪く、立派だった対処力はますます少なくなっている。$NL;$NL;メンバーの一人が、おそらくあなたから逃げる時、このヘルメットを落としたようだ。",--4th Domestic Operation Group-force Enforcers-Alpha (4th DOGE-A), popularly ridiculed as Alpha Force, is a U.S. Army component of the Joint Common Operations Command. Their reputation is pretty poor and have become a less and less respected force to deal with.$NL;$NL;One of the members probably dropped this helmet when he fled from you.
bm_msk_demon = "",--The Horned Beast
bm_msk_demon_desc = "この野獣は闇の奥より現れる。$NL;$NL;獅子の胴、熊の足、豹の口を持つ。$NL;$NL;この獣を知る者は少ない、そしてこのマスクを造った者を知る者もまた少ない。",--A beast that came from the abyss.$NL;$NL;It has a lion's body, bear feet and a leopard's mouth.$NL;$NL;Not much else is known of this beast, nor who designed the mask.
bm_msk_demonictender = "",--Kenneth
bm_msk_demonictender_desc = "悪魔のような怖ろしいデザインをしたマスク。$NL;$NL;このマスクについて、Kennethという名前以外はよく分かっていない。$NL;$NL;そして今、この怨霊は人間に取り憑かんと、再び地上で出没するようになった。",--A horrifying mask shaped like the head of a demon.$NL;$NL;Not much is known about it other than the name - Kenneth.$NL;$NL;Now, this vengeful spirit has returned to earth to haunt mankind once more.
bm_msk_destroyer = "",--Demonshank
bm_msk_destroyer_desc = "戦士の精神というのはよく見られるものではない。生まれ持ったものではなく、鋼の様に、戦火の中で生まれるものだ。炉の中で繰り返し打たれ、その身を研ぎ澄ます。このマスクは、戦士の誕生を祝うものだ。炎から生まれた鋼は翼を持って飛び立つ。",--A warrior spirit doesn't appear naturally. It isn't something you are born with. Like steel, it is forged in fire. It is beaten in the furnace of battle - tempered, polished and sharpened. This mask celebrates the birth of this warrior spirit - the furnace-born steel given wings.
bm_msk_devourer = "",--Devourer
bm_msk_devourer_desc = "",--This mask, heavily inspired by the Great Old Ones that rule below the seas was recovered from a police storage where it had been kept since it was found during a raid on a murderous cult. It's monstrous look makes you wonder what beings lurk out in the dark.
bm_msk_dgm = "",--Golden Dallas
bm_msk_dgm_desc = "",--To commemorate the day PAYDAY became the most played co-op game in a single day - 10th of June 2017. Some 221k heisters per hour were robbing banks together in style. Earning us the Top 5 Position among Most Played Games in a day of all time - PAYDAY leaves its golden mark on history. Dallas is pleased.
bm_msk_dillinger_death_mask = "",--The Dillinger Death Mask
bm_msk_dillinger_death_mask_desc = "ジョン·ハーバート·ディリンジャーは、著名なアメリカの強盗だ。$NL;$NL;彼の組織は24の銀行と4つの警察署を襲った。$NL;$NL;彼は二度の脱獄を経て、大恐慌時代のアメリカの糞野郎の一人として知られた。",--John Herbert Dillinger was a famous American bank robber.$NL;$NL;His gang robbed two dozen banks and even four police stations.$NL;$NL;Dillinger himself escaped jail twice and was widely known as one of the meanest motherfuckers in the depression-era United States.
bm_msk_divided = "",--Trickster Demon
bm_msk_divided_desc = "",--The Trickster Demon is a mischievous being, who thrives on creating chaos and spreading mayhem. It might not look that scary, but don't let that smirk fool you; its idea of "fun" differ greatly from what you or me would enjoy. Trust me on this.
bm_msk_dnm = "",--The Normal Skull
bm_msk_dnm_desc = "",--A strange thing, the human skull. It's both simple and beautiful. Humans can often recognize a human skull, even if it's only partially shown. The human brain even has a special region for it.$NL;$NL;You finished all heists on the Normal difficulty? What are you, some kind of gangster? Maybe this mask will suit you after all.
bm_msk_doctor = "",--The Doctor
bm_msk_doctor_desc = "",--A naso-buccal mask usually associated with hospitals and ambulances. This mask disables the host from spreading airborne viruses by catching the bacteria-laden saliva and mucus that is discharged upon sneezing or coughing. Both doctors and patients wear this, so you should ask yourself: am I the sick or the healthy one? The disease or the cure?$NL;$NL;In any case - it's fever season, and the only prescription is dead Bulldozers.
bm_msk_dragan = "",--Dragan
bm_msk_dragan_begins = "",--Dragan Begins
bm_msk_dragan_begins_desc = "Draganを象徴するマスクの、まだペイントされていない無地のバージョン。$NL;$NL;まだオリジナルの様に着こなせていない? これは歴史を塗り替えるチャンスだ。",--This is a clean version of Dragan's iconic mask, before it was painted.$NL;$NL;Never liked how the original one turned out? This is your chance to change history.
bm_msk_dragan_desc = "Draganのような男が持っているバックグラウンドを考えれば、犯罪界での名声を切望するのは驚くべきことではない。$NL;$NL;彼のマスクは、彼自身の性格を、つまり元祖メンバーのマスクが表現していることによく似て、彼のスキルは潜入と潜伏であることを示し、また彼の終わりない残忍さも表している。$NL;$NL;額のクロアチアン·チェッカーは、彼の敵と彼自身に、単なるチンピラでないことを思い出させている。",--With a background like the one Dragan has, there's no surprise he aspires to greatness in the criminal underworld.$NL;$NL;His mask represents a lot of his own characteristics, with the clear resemblance to some of the original crew's masks that tells of his ability to infiltrate and blend in while still having some features that tells of his unending ruthlessness.$NL;$NL;The Croatian checker on the forehead serves as a reminder for both himself and his enemies to be aware that he is not your common western street thug.
bm_msk_dripper = "",--The Dripper
bm_msk_dripper_desc = "The Dripperは、荒いマテリアルの表面 をどうにか滑らかにする為に、加工中は大量の液体を噴霧する事で作られた。$NL;$NL;このマスクを見た人は、それぞれ違う事を考える。$NL;$NL;あなたにはどう見える?",--The Dripper was made by atomization of a larger mass of liquid, somehow made into a hard material while retaining a smooth surface.$NL;$NL;Everyone who looks at it sees different things.$NL;$NL;What do you see?
bm_msk_eagle = "",--Chuck
bm_msk_eagle_desc = "チャック \"イーグル\" ノリスは正義、善と真実を示す。$NL;$NL;チャックはアラスカの山中で空手を磨いている最中にこの巨大な鷲を見つけた。$NL;$NL;チャックと鷲は数時間に渡り死闘を繰り広げ、チャックは敗れた鷲の首をマスクにし、自分の名前を付けた",--Chuck the Eagle represents everything that is righteous, good and true.$NL;$NL;A famous Martial Artist found this huge eagle while he was doing karate in the mountains of Alaska.$NL;$NL;They had a fight for several hours but eventually the Martial Artist won. He took the head, made it into a mask and named it after himself.
bm_msk_ecp_female = "",--Hila
bm_msk_ecp_female_begins = "",--Hila Begins
bm_msk_ecp_female_begins_desc = "",--This is a clean version of the iconic Hila mask as it looked before it was painted.$NL;$NL;Never liked how the original one turned out? This is your chance to change history.
bm_msk_ecp_female_desc = "",--Something about this mask radiates a playful malice and most who gaze upon it immediately feel a sense of unease, which is just the kind of thing you need when you're robbing a bank!
bm_msk_ecp_male = "",--Ethan
bm_msk_ecp_male_begins = "",--Ethan Begins
bm_msk_ecp_male_begins_desc = "",--This is a clean version of Ethan's mask as it looked before it was painted.$NL;$NL;Never liked how the original one turned out? This is your chance to change history.
bm_msk_ecp_male_desc = "",--This mask exudes power and brute force, in stark contrast to the man who wears it. Equal parts clown-like sadness and begrudging anger, it perfectly captures the mood of someone who has somewhat reluctantly chosen to become a heister.
bm_msk_eggian = "",--Eggian
bm_msk_eggian_desc = "",--In 'Xenogogs', these creatures embodied fear itself, as it tore its way from the butt of Troy Templeton during that scene.
bm_msk_eng_01 = "",--The Bullet
bm_msk_eng_01_desc = "",--Equipped with his Blasphemy sword of infinite ammo the Bullet unleashes his full power when fighting with all his heart.
bm_msk_eng_02 = "",--The Robot
bm_msk_eng_02_desc = "",--The Robot was an honored member of the killbot army. When commanded by his master, EMP-R0R to kill the leader of the human resistance, he broke protocol, failing to eliminate humanity.
bm_msk_eng_03 = "",--The Cultist
bm_msk_eng_03_desc = "",--Always being referred to as "Number 2" the Cultist will challenge anyone that gets in his way. Armed with with a Dart Gun, this challenger shouldn't be taken easy!
bm_msk_eng_04 = "",--The Marine
bm_msk_eng_04_desc = "",--The Marine was a guard stationed at Primerdyne R&D when an experiment went awry and unleashing an Interdimensional Horror into the facility. Some say he left everyone behind to die, others celebrate him as a hero who saved everyone!
bm_msk_evil = "",--Black Death
bm_msk_evil_desc = "",--Bob Robertson worked at a purple stuff factory. The purple stuff factory was old and in need of reperations. Bob mentioned this to his supervisors but they ignored him. Bob kept on hardly working, playing pre-installed games on his operative system. One day when he was checking out early, cracks started to form in a container filled with purple stuff. Just when he went past, the container burst and Bob was drenched in purple stuff.$NL;$NL;When he got out of hospital, he had become a super villain. His face has been purple ever since.
bm_msk_fable_cat = "",--The Cat
bm_msk_fable_cat_desc = "",--Agile as a Cat, and lucky as one too, you will dare any heist and successfully breach any defenses. When the shit hits the fan, you will always dodge and land on your feet. There is no better way to spend your nine lives - a stone-cold killer is what you are and everyone knows it.
bm_msk_fable_fox = "",--The Fox
bm_msk_fable_fox_desc = "",--The Fox - slickest and slyest of all predators. No locks can keep you out, no defensive plan can withstand your guile and artifice. You will take what you want and leave everyone wondering who did it, or if it even happened at all.
bm_msk_fable_hare = "",--The Hare
bm_msk_fable_hare_desc = "",--Mad as March Hare. As they stare into your crazed yellow eyes, they'd better hand the cash over quick. Then take the money and run. No one outruns a hare.
bm_msk_fable_mouse = "",--The Mouse
bm_msk_fable_mouse_desc = "",--Quiet as a Mouse, you'll enter and exit silently and none will be the wiser. And if they should spot you, who would suspect such wickedness from such a small creature? But yes, you are capable of it - all of it.
bm_msk_falcon = "",--The Falcon
bm_msk_falcon_desc = "",--Life's not all about speed and running! With his livelihood destroyed from a speedy accident, he became the hero that New Rush City truly deserves. Falcon vows to take down SpeedRunner and get the city back. Is Falcon the only one sane in a world gone mad- or is he a man in a chicken suit?
bm_msk_famine = "",--Famine
bm_msk_famine_desc = "",--The third horseman of the Apocalypse is the embodiment of Famine, a force so powerful he would leave people starving to their deaths if they laid eyes upon him.
bm_msk_fancy_goat = "",--Slick Goat
bm_msk_fancy_goat_desc = "",--The penguin is the slickest heister in the animal kingdom, walking around with a "know-it-all" attitude, taking their time and taking what they want - when they want, not giving a damn. Put on this mask and show everyone you're the boss of things.
bm_msk_fatboy = "",--Fatboy
bm_msk_fatboy_desc = "",--It's the full-cheeked, pink, healthy face that represents the wonderful, magical alchemy of deep-fried dough and sugar found in the lobby of theaters across the States.
bm_msk_fdm = "",--The Fedora
bm_msk_fdm_desc = "",--The fedora, the very height of fashion and class. Where the line is drawn between boys and men. Carry this classical headgear with the pride and resolve that it deserves. Feel the legacy and tradition of the millions of gentlemen and gangsters that wore a fedora throughout the ages.
bm_msk_finger = "",--The Griefer
bm_msk_finger_desc = "",--The Griefer is a mythical beast, known to have been a part of this world long ago. The beast deliberately chased and harassed common folk in villages and towns, hunting them down in unsuspecting ways. The Griefer derived pleasure from these acts and was a threat to the peace until the King's men finally found him and destroyed him.
bm_msk_firedemon = "",--Graug
bm_msk_firedemon_desc = "",--The head of the legendary Graug. A towering being of fire and smoking darkness, bound in blackened iron mail. Shaped like a man, but horned and visaged like a cruel demon. Body consumed by a furnace heat, hotter than Hell itself. Knows all the best tunes.
bm_msk_firemask = "",--Firefighter's Helmet
bm_msk_firemask_desc = "",--The crew may show scant respect to the police authorities, but they have huge respect for the men and women that clean up the burning messes left in their wake. This mask is a tribute to their efforts.
bm_msk_frank = "",--Frank
bm_msk_frank_desc = "",--Frank is a monster, but he is - contrary to popular belief - a sensitive, emotional creature whose only aim is to share his life with another monster.$NL;$NL;However, he realized from the moment of his "birth" that even his own creator cannot stand being around him. Knowing this, Frank decided to become a bank robber instead. The end.
bm_msk_franklin = "",--The First American
bm_msk_franklin_desc = "世界的に有名な博学者、作家、印刷業者、政治理論化、郵便局長、科学者、発明家、市民運動家、政治家、外交官にして、建国の父である。$NL;$NL;「最初のアメリカ人」の肩書を持つ、100ドル札の顔である。$NL;$NL;犯罪者の中でも、彼の人気は変わらない。",--World-renowned polymath, author, printer, political theorist, postmaster, scientist, inventor, civic activist, statesman, diplomat, Founding Father.$NL;$NL;Titulated as "The First American" and the face of the $100 bill.$NL;$NL;Among criminals, he remains extremely popular.
bm_msk_gagball = "",--The Gagball
bm_msk_gagball_desc = "自分の顔にギャグボールを付けて奴隷として散歩する為のマスク。$NL;$NL;さまざまな理由でこれを着る人が居るが、理由の一つとして奴隷として演じさせられる為だ。今回の場合は必ずしも必要では無いが、ギャグボールも銀行強盗で使われている様だ。",--Take a walk on the submissive side with a gagball stuck to your face.$NL;$NL;People wear these for a variety of reasons, one being roleplays involving bondage. This isn't necessarily the case though, as gagballs apparently can be used in bank robberies too.
bm_msk_gage_blade = "",--The Gage Blade
bm_msk_gage_blade_desc = "The Gage BladeはGageのお気に入りの頭部保護マスクだ。このマスクは、あなたの頭が吹っ飛ばされる直前に、あなたの顔を1、2発程度の9mm弾から守れるだろう。$NL;$NL;このマスクが無ければ、Gageは今ここにいるような素晴らしい奴じゃなかったかもしれない。",--The Gage Blade is one of Gage's own personal favorite ballistic face masks. It will protect your face from one or two 9mm bullets before your head explodes.$NL;$NL;Without this mask, Gage wouldn't be the wonderful human being he is today.
bm_msk_galax = "",--Professor Wrath
bm_msk_galax_desc = "",--Milhouse Anderson worked at a chemical plant handling dangerous chemical waste. As a prank, his friends thought it would be a good idea to lock him up in the room where they kept the dangerous chemical waste. What they didn't know was that the dangerous chemical waste was dangerous, and while being locked in for several hours, Milhouse was exposed to high levels of radiation and other bad stuff.$NL;$NL;When they finally let him out, he had become a super villain. He's been super angry ever since.
bm_msk_gasmask = "",--The Gas Mask
bm_msk_gasmask_desc = "ガスマスクは昔の戦争で使われた過去の産物だと思われがちだが、現代の戦場でもガスが蔓延する事はある。あとゼーゼーという音も特徴的だな。",--The gas mask may seem like it belongs to the wars of an older era, but it is a crucial piece of equipment on the urban battlefield, where gas can still be deployed. Also, gives you a cool, wheezy breathing sound.
bm_msk_gcm = "",--Golden Chains
bm_msk_gcm_desc = "",--It's been four years. Four years of hard work, meth cooked, shots fired and loot hauled. But we've only just began. We do feel a bit nostalgic. It's been four years since we came to Washington and took on our first heist here and now we're pros. And when it's someone's birthday, you need to get them a gift. Therefore we've poured 24k hot, luscious gold all over Chains mask. Happy Birthday PAYDAY 2!
bm_msk_ggac = "",--The One Down Skull
bm_msk_ggac_desc = "",--So arrives the Harbinger! Humans can often recognize a human skull, even if it's only partially shown. The brain even has a special region for it. This is definitely not a human skull, it belongs to a demon of carnage.$NL;$NL;Look ye into the sky, as fire rains down from the heavens, followed by molten gold, to cover the land in a glittering metal blanket of awesome to illuminate your greatness as a heister. With every bar that is raised, you step up to the challenge, and have so done yet again. Construction of a throne is underway here at the OVERKILL office, so that we may bow to and worship your utterly divine skills at not getting beaten by anything we throw at you.
bm_msk_ghost = "",--The Spectre
bm_msk_ghost_desc = "このGhostマスクは未来から来たようなものであり、実際にそうかもしれない。$NL;$NL;炭素繊維と改造された蜘蛛の糸を使用し、完璧な頭部保護を実現させた。人々は時々このマスクをMoto GPのライダー用のヘルメットと勘違いするようだ。$NL;$NL;その間違いも、君の番で終わりだ。$NL;$NL;このマスクはInfamyツリーの報酬です。PAYDAYの間にドロップすることはなく売却することも出来ません。その代わりに、カスタマイズの内容と手数料は失われますが、マスクスタッシュに無料で戻すことが出来ます。",--This Ghost mask looks like it's from the future and it might as well be.$NL;$NL;Full head protection, made out of carbon fiber and genetically engineered spider-silk. People might even mistake you for a high-end Moto GP rider.$NL;$NL;Last mistake they'll make.$NL;$NL;This mask is an Infamy tree reward. It can't drop during a PAYDAY and it can't be sold. Instead, it can be returned to your mask stash for free, but any pattern, color or material as well as the customization fee to put these together will be lost.
bm_msk_gladiator_helmet = "",--Murmillo Galea Helmet
bm_msk_gladiator_helmet_desc = "",--Gladiators were members of a brutal caste in Ancient Rome whose sole duty was to entertain by way of public exhibitions of horrific violence. This style of helmet with its high crest resembles a fish. It was worn by a Murmillo - a heavy class of gladiator that fought with a sword and tower shield. They symbolize Vulcan - the roman god of fire, and they stand for strength and honor.
bm_msk_goat = "",--Dolph
bm_msk_goat_desc = "ドルフ \"ゴート\" ラングレンは自然の持つ力強さと岩を示す。$NL;$NL;スウェーデン最北の洞窟の中でこの山羊を見つけた。$NL;$NL;伝説によれば、雷の神トールは2頭の山羊によって引っ張られた戦車に乗っていたという。しかしこのマスクは恐らく伝説とは何の関係もないだろう。きっとこいつはクレイジーだ",--Dolph the Goat represents natural strength and stone.$NL;$NL;It was found by a group of adventurers in a mountain cave in the most northern parts of Sweden.$NL;$NL;Legend has it that the god of thunder, Thor, had a chariot that was pulled by two goats. This mask probably has nothing to do with that legend though. That would be crazy.
bm_msk_goat_goat = "",--Goat Goat
bm_msk_goat_goat_desc = "",--The goat doesn't get much respect in the animal kingdom, and often find themselves to be mocked by the other animals - but that works perfectly in their favor. Putting on this foolish mask might give you the same advantage and make the cops underestimate you.
bm_msk_goggles = "",--Cloaker-san
bm_msk_goggles_desc = "",--It's not only the American government that uses specially trained operatives for infiltration missions. Japan has their own unit called the Anbu, and while this mask is only a prototype, it's very similar to the actual thing they use.
bm_msk_grant = "",--The 18th
bm_msk_grant_desc = "軍人であり、最高司令官であり、父である。8年間、この国に努めた。$NL;$NL;間違いなく、素晴らしい戦士であり擁護者だ。$NL;$NL;The 18thは歴史上最も人気のない大統領の一人だった。しかし犯罪者の中では、未だに人気が衰えていない。",--Soldier, Commander-In-Chief, father. Served this great nation for 8 years.$NL;$NL;A protector and a warrior, and a great one at that.$NL;$NL;The 18th was one of the most unpopular presidents in history. Among criminals however, he remains extremely popular.
bm_msk_greedy_the_elf = "",--Greedy The Elf
bm_msk_greedy_the_elf_desc = "",--Santa's elves have a tough job. No medical, dental and they endure the whip of Mrs. Claus, but at least they have these fucking sweet hats.
bm_msk_greek_tragedy = "",--Greek Tragedy
bm_msk_greek_tragedy_desc = "ギリシャ悲劇の全ての場面を象徴するマスク。$NL;$NL;古代ギリシャでは、マスクは特別な儀式や結婚式で神に崇拝する為に用いられてきた。$NL;$NL;特にこのマスクは、現存する強盗の全要素を集約している。誰かが警報を鳴らした時の怒り、金庫を開く喜び、そして逮捕される悲しみだ。",--A mask that symbolizes all the parts in a greek tragedy.$NL;$NL;In old Greece, masks were used to worship the gods in ceremonial rites and celebrations.$NL;$NL;This particular mask summarizes every heist in existence; the anger of someone triggering the alarm, the joy of opening the vault and the tragedy of being caught.
bm_msk_grendel = "",--Rad Mutant
bm_msk_grendel_desc = "",--Genetic mutation is the key to our evolution. Assuming that our evolution is of the green, scaly, homicidal, irradiated kind.
bm_msk_grin = "",--The Grin
bm_msk_grin_desc = "昔、ある男とその弟がいた。彼らは一緒に、首尾の良い会社を経営していた。$NL;$NL;ある日、兄弟の会社は一時的にクライアントが1社のみとなった。そのクライアントも怖気づいて提携を解消してしまった。と言うより、単純に資金を引き上げて契約不履行による罰金を払う為に、クライアントは兄弟の会社を倒産に追いやったのだ。$NL;$NL;男とその弟は何もかも失い、その日を境に男は精神が狂ってしまった。このマスクは、その時の男の表情を精巧に映した物だと言われている。",--There once was a man and his brother. Together, they owned a successful company. One day, the man and his brother temporarily only had one client. The client got cold feet and wanted out. Rather than simply pulling out and having to pay a fine for breach of contract, the client starved the man and his brother's company to death.$NL;$NL;The man and his brother lost everything, and it is said that this mask was the very image of the man's facial expression the day that he went mad.
bm_msk_grizel_clean = "",--Clover Begins
bm_msk_grizel_clean_desc = "Cloverを象徴するマスクの、まだペイントされていない無地のバージョン。$NL;$NL;まだオリジナルの様に着こなせていない? これは歴史を塗り替えるチャンスだ。",--This is a clean version of Clover's iconic mask, before it was painted.$NL;$NL;Never liked how the original one turned out? This is your chance to change history.
bm_msk_groucho = "",--Groucho
bm_msk_groucho_desc = "",--A perfect disguise doesn't have to mean dying your hair, changing your iris and burning off your fingerprints. Sometimes looking obviously strange makes people uncomfortable enough to look away and pay you no mind.
bm_msk_grv_01 = "",--War Balaclava
bm_msk_grv_01_desc = "",--Half a block, half a block$NL;Half a block onward$NL;Into the First World Bank$NL;Walked the four heisters$NL;Forward the Payday Gang$NL;Charge for the gold, they said$NL;Into the First World Bank$NL;Walked the four heisters
bm_msk_grv_02 = "",--Matryoshka
bm_msk_grv_02_desc = "",--Things are not always what they seem. Behind the mask there is a face, true. But what's behind the face? Another face, perhaps. How do you know where the real person is, and how many layers must be removed before you reach the core - the inner self?
bm_msk_grv_03 = "",--Kokoshnik
bm_msk_grv_03_desc = "",--Finely crested for glory, this elaborate headpiece will impress. Wear it proudly, displaying the fine embroidery for all to envy. But watch out for low doorways.
bm_msk_grv_04 = "",--Red Machine
bm_msk_grv_04_desc = "",--No one can stop the Red Machine! It's fast, ice-cold and merciless. With swift moves, lightning strikes and flawless tactics it humiliates the opposition, leaving them crying in desperation. Just like the Payday Gang.
bm_msk_gumbo = "",--Gumbo
bm_msk_gumbo_desc = "",--Little is known about the man known as the devouring clown, but for a long time people believed that his red eyes were part of his outfit. Needless to say, they were wrong. Now people fear the red eyed clown with a laugh so evil it makes even the most seasoned badasses quiver in fear.$NL;$NL;Word on the street is that he haunts alleyways in a demonic shape looking for something... Or someone. All that is known is that people end up dead, more dead than you thought possible...
bm_msk_heat = "",--Hockey Heat
bm_msk_heat_desc = "古臭いホッケーのマスク。$NL;$NL;ある男が以前俺にこう教えてくれた。$NL;$NL;「30秒フラットで高飛び出来るよう面倒な関係は持つな」",--A classic hockey mask.$NL;$NL;A guy told me one time...$NL;$NL;"Don't let yourself get attached to anything you are not willing to walk out on in 30 seconds flat if you feel the heat around the corner."
bm_msk_hectors_helmet = "",--The Hard Hat
bm_msk_hectors_helmet_desc = "PAYDAYギャングの事を密告する時は、復讐に備えておいた方がいいでしょう。ギャングは断固たる復讐をしてくるでしょう。恐らくあなたの死体を穴だらけにしてくるだろうと予想できます。重い鉄に囲まれ、正面は強化ガラスのThe Hard Hatは古臭い機動隊員のヘルメットです。うまく切り抜けられるよう、幸運を祈っておきますよ。",--When you rat out the PAYDAY gang, you need to expect some form of retribution. And the gang aren't big on wagging fingers and a stern telling off. You can expect bullets, and plenty of them. This hard hat is old school riot cop tech - heavy iron, fronted with reinforced glass. Good luck getting through it.
bm_msk_hockey = "",--Hockey Mask
bm_msk_hockey_desc = "ホッケーマスクは、ゴール前を守るホッケープレーヤーが怪我から顔を守るために着用する。$NL;$NL;そしてまた、高品質な素材で手作りされた、強盗のアイコン的なマスクでもある。パックから身を守る代わりに、コイツはお前が仕事をしている時に、身元がバレるのを防いでくれる。$NL;$NL;分かるだろ?お前が得意な仕事--盗みだ。",--A hockey mask is a mask worn by hockey goaltenders to protect their heads from injury.$NL;$NL;It is also the iconic robber mask, hand-crafted using only high-quality materials. Instead of protecting you from pucks, it protects you from being recognized while going about, doing your thing.$NL;$NL;You know, the thing you do so well. Stealing.
bm_msk_hog = "",--The Hog
bm_msk_hog_desc = "新しいメッセージを受け取った! *BEEP*$NL;$NL;やあ、私はOVERKILLのAlmirだ。 君が要求したマスクは今すぐそちらに送らせよう...$NL;$NL;君への指示リストも一緒にだ...$NL;$NL;必ずリストを読むように!$NL;$NL;他人を傷つけるのは好きか? なら、このマスクは君の役に立つ。",--You have a new message! *BEEP*$NL;$NL;Salutations, this is 'Almir' at OVERKILL. The mask that you ordered should be delivered by now...$NL;$NL;A list of instructions are included...$NL;$NL;Make sure that you read them carefully!$NL;$NL;Do you like hurting other people? Then this mask is for you.
bm_msk_horned_king = "",--The Viking
bm_msk_horned_king_desc = "",--The Germanic Norse seafarers known as Vikings were fierce warriors during the late 8th to late 11th centuries. Equipped with their mighty axes and horned helmets, they stood tall and proud in the heat of battle. If you want to capture the spirit of these old fighters, this mask will do the job.
bm_msk_horse = "",--Don Juan
bm_msk_horse_desc = "Don Juanはドアをぶち開けるのが大好きだ。$NL;$NL;コンコン、どちら様? わたしDon Juan、覚悟はいい?$NL;$NL;プロTIP:ホットライン·マイアミでは、このマスクを被った状態で壁に向かってグラウンド·キルを決めると2,200ポイントもらえるぞ。",--Don Juan loves slamming doors in.$NL;$NL;Knock, knock. Who's there? It's Don Juan. Prepare yourself.$NL;$NL;Pro tip: In Hotline Miami, you get 2200 points while performing ground kills against the wall when using this mask.
bm_msk_hothead = "",--Hothead
bm_msk_hothead_desc = "",--With the rage of a fearsome volcano, the hostile Hothead lights up the night with blazing speed! What ignites his frenzied flame? From what does the raging bull run? Very few have caught up close enough to ask, and even fewer have gotten a coherent response!
bm_msk_hoxton = "",--Hoxton
bm_msk_hoxton_clean = "",--Hoxton Begins
bm_msk_hoxton_clean_desc = "Hoxtonを象徴するマスクの、まだペイントされていない無地のバージョン。$NL;$NL;まだオリジナルの様に着こなせていない? これは歴史を塗り替えるチャンスだ。",--This is a clean version of the iconic Hoxton mask, before it was painted.$NL;$NL;Never liked how the original one turned out? This is your chance to change history.
bm_msk_hoxton_desc = "Hoxtonのマスク。",--The mask of Hoxton.
bm_msk_hoxton_glow = "",--Mega Hoxton
bm_msk_hoxton_glow_desc = "Mega Hoxtonマスクは、元のマスクが進化したものだ。そしてこれは、超越と浄化を象徴するものなのだ。$NL;$NL;応援ありがとう。$NL;$NL;OVERKILLより敬意を!",--The Mega Hoxton mask is an evolved version of the original mask. It symbolises transcendence and catharsis.$NL;$NL;Thank you for your support.$NL;$NL;OVERKILL salutes you!
bm_msk_hunter = "",--Mega Kevin
bm_msk_hunter_desc = "",--For Kevin it was never enough to rip out the spine and scream defiantly at the sky. He always proceeded to also fuck the skull.$NL;$NL;Thank you for your support.$NL;$NL;OVERKILL salutes you!
bm_msk_infamy_hood = "",--Kamul
bm_msk_infamy_hood_desc = "闇の世界ではギャングより古く、卑劣なものが存在している。その一つがKamulだ。彼は大昔に死んだ者の彷徨える魂なのか、陰の領域を超えて現世へ現れた何かなのか、我々には知る由もない。はっきりしているのは、誰かがこの顔を覗きこみ、後世に伝えねばならないという事だ。",--There are things older and fouler than heisters in the dark places of the world. And one of them is Kamul. We do not know if he is the lingering spirit of a long dead man, or something that has crossed from the realm of shade. All we know is that few look into this face and live to tell of it.
bm_msk_infamy_lurker = "",--Lurker
bm_msk_infamy_lurker_desc = "歯ってのは怖いもんだ。大きな歯はもっと怖い。鋭く、牙のような歯は闇に潜んでは怖ろしい歯ぎしりを起こす。...ということを念頭に置いて考えれば、このマスクは民間人の統制に使えるんじゃないか?",--Teeth are scary. Big teeth are scarier. And giant sharp fang-like teeth suddenly gnashing out where they lurk in the darkness are downright shit-yourself-terrifying. With all of that in mind, can you think of a better mask to keep the civilians in line?
bm_msk_instinct = "",--The Intuition
bm_msk_instinct_desc = "",--This mask belonged to a mysterious warrior from far away place. He walked the lands, guided by his intuition, hunting evil forces across the world. He ventured to dungeons and slew thousands of evil beings he came across. In the end, he found peace, knowing that the next generation would continue as he did.
bm_msk_invader = "",--Invader
bm_msk_invader_desc = "",--I want to belie... ZAP! May the fo... ZAP! Live long a.. ZAP! Why can't we all just get along? Because ZAP! That's why.
bm_msk_irondoom = "",--Doctor Crime
bm_msk_irondoom_desc = "Doctor Crimeはアメリカの架空の キャラクターで、OVERKILL Comics が出版するコミックに現れる怪人だ。$NL;$NL;このキャラクターは、原作のDavid Goldfarbと作画のMax Elmberg Sjöholmによって生み出された。$NL;$NL;彼は次の作品で初登場した、The Amazing Career Criminals: The PAYDAY meets Doctor Crime!",--Doctor Crime is an American fictional character, a supervillain who appears in comic books by OVERKILL Comics.$NL;$NL;The character was created by writer-editor David Goldfarb and designed by artist Max Elmberg Sjöholm.$NL;$NL;He made his first appearance in The Amazing Career Criminals: The PAYDAY gang meets Doctor Crime!
bm_msk_jake = "",--Jake
bm_msk_jake_desc = "「良い蛇」なんてものは存在しないが、それでも毒蛇のコブラは最悪だ。大きいエリ － 自らの脅威を知らしめる部位 － が見えたら、逃げろ。長い牙は、ゾウの皮も突き通す。だから逃げろ。そいつの毒液は、1滴だけでもブルドーザーを昏倒させるぞ。だから...つまり、基本的に、こいつを見たら、とにかく逃げろ。連中、毒を飛ばすこともできるからな。",--There's no such thing as a good snake, but even among the deadly serpents the cobra is bad news. The broad hood, when seen, is a display of threat - so run. Its long fangs can pierce elephant skin - so run. And just a drop of its venom can fell a dozer - so... look, basically, when you see this, just run. Because they also spit.
bm_msk_jaw = "",--The Jaw
bm_msk_jaw_desc = "鋼鉄のマスクで貧弱なアゴを守る。$NL;$NL;このマスクを今から使うという事は、自分が公僕ではと考えさせられるという事だ、わかるか?",--Protect your glass chin with a metal jaw.$NL;$NL;The only thing you will be chewing from now on with your jaw is law enforcers, right?
bm_msk_jfr_01 = "",--Sterling's Beret
bm_msk_jfr_01_desc = "",--It would be lovely to think Sterling earned the beret and badge through hard-training and combat. The truth, however, is that he saw how it impressed a couple of young fillies at the Officers Club. An invitation to step outside, a few dirty punches and a knocked out Colonel later, and Sterling had his very own red beret. And a couple of fillies. Smashing!
bm_msk_jfr_02 = "",--Wolfgang's Cap
bm_msk_jfr_02_desc = "",--This cap may look like a normal, standard-issue M43 field cap. And you may think such humble headgear is an unusual choice for a man as vain as Wolfgang. But this cap holds special meaning for him. It may surprise you that Wolfgang can truly love. Pinned inside is a picture of his beloved. For whom he fights the good fight.
bm_msk_jfr_03 = "",--Kurgan's Gas Mask
bm_msk_jfr_03_desc = "",--Kurgan doesn't wear the gas-mask to keep the fumes of war out. He wears it to keep the flames of fury in. Betrayed by his own side, Kurgan barely survived an ambush by armored flamers. Inside the mask, there is only the smell of his own immolated flesh, a constant reminder to trust no-one.
bm_msk_jfr_04 = "",--Rivet's Bandana
bm_msk_jfr_04_desc = "",--Rivet is American, and Americans value tradition. From the office of the President, to the lowliest scum-sucker in the land, tradition matters. So if you're going to stick a gun in a chump's face and demand they \"hand it over\" you better damn well know your history. Like Jesse James, like Billy The Kid, you wear a bandana.
bm_msk_jig_01 = "",--Garreth
bm_msk_jig_01_desc = "",--In space you need a trusted companion. As everything from huge monsters on distant planets to space itself is deadly - you need an ally. Not just a hired gun. But instead a friend and a soldier that makes sure that you survive and others don't. Be happy that Garreth is on your team. Be happy that he helps you shepherd the herd.
bm_msk_jig_02 = "",--The Judge
bm_msk_jig_02_desc = "",--Those pesky youngsters think they can just run around doing whatever they feel like. Don't they understand? I exist for a reason. One must obey me - my ruling and my saying. Escaping the world, just feeling free? What kind of life is that? Riding around on those yellow bird creations. No respect for the empire or the emperor. Disgraceful!
bm_msk_jimmy = "",--The White Death
bm_msk_jimmy_desc = "",--Jimmy's second attempt at making a mask went much better - that's because he got some help from Gage. It represents the Grim Reaper himself if he was coked up. The mask captures both the crazy and deadly side of Jimmy, aimed to sending fear into his enemies.
bm_msk_jimmy_duct = "",--Jimmy
bm_msk_jimmy_duct_desc = "",--Jimmy hasn't really made that many masks before he made his signature mask - and it shows. His mask design captures his free spirit and his disregard to things as appearance, planning and such. Good is good enough for Jimmy, he doesn't get stuck on details and wants to move forward at all times.
bm_msk_jiro = "",--Jiro
bm_msk_jiro_begins = "",--Jiro Begins
bm_msk_jiro_begins_desc = "Jiroを象徴するマスクの、まだペイントされていない無地のバージョン。$NL;$NL;まだオリジナルの様に着こなせていない? これは歴史を塗り替えるチャンスだ。",--This is a clean version of Jiro's iconic mask, before it was painted.$NL;$NL;Never liked how the original one turned out? This is your chance to change history.
bm_msk_jiro_desc = "",--Japan is a land of tradition. A land of warriors. Jiro's mask reflects this. The mask expresses Jiro's love for a traditional Japan, while the bared snarl represents his unshakable determination.
bm_msk_jw_shades = "",--Collateral
bm_msk_jw_shades_desc = "",--These shades belonged to a colleague of John's that he was hired to kill.$NL;$NL;It started like any other night. Only this night, he got a contract to kill another contract killer who was making rounds that day. John knew he had five stops to make and was using the same taxi cab between all of them.$NL;$NL;In the end, he didn't even need to do the deed himself - he was already dead when he found him.
bm_msk_kage = "",--Kage
bm_msk_kage_desc = "",--The kage mask was said to be haunted, originally from a kabuki theater in Osaka where the actor fell down dead on stage while wearing the mask. The last thing he said was "No, I will not kill them, I will not". Legend says that the kage mask will kill whoever wears it if its thirst for blood is not satisfied.
bm_msk_kangee = "",--Apache Mystic
bm_msk_kangee_desc = "",--The West that the white men entered was a land of mystery. A land populated with civilizations of warriors, who marked themselves, their lands and their mythologies with these sacred carvings.
bm_msk_kawaii = "",--Kawaii
bm_msk_kawaii_desc = "愛らしい、キレイ、カワイイ、 カッコいい、魅力的、怖くない、 無邪気、楽天的。$NL;$NL;これらの言葉は、犯罪学では一般に用いられない。$NL;$NL;あなたの所為で、今は使われているが。",--Lovable, cute, adorable, cool and hip, charming, non-threatening, innocent, happy-go-lucky.$NL;$NL;These are words not commonly used in criminology.$NL;$NL;Because of you, they now are.
bm_msk_king_of_jesters = "",--King of Jesters
bm_msk_king_of_jesters_desc = "",--Wearing brightly coloured clothes and eccentric hats in a motley pattern, jesters have always had a place in these parts.$NL;$NL;Whether walking on stilts, performing with fire or telling jokes; their sole purpose is to spread joy in our hearts.$NL;$NL;However, this is your time to shine so why not put on the mask and spread some joy.$NL;$NL;So, pull out your gun, rob your guests and tell them it was all a big ploy.
bm_msk_krampus = "",--Krampus
bm_msk_krampus_desc = "今年は悪い子だったんだって? なら、Krampusが訪ねてくるのを覚悟しな。もしくは、Bainからの電話かも。",--Been a bad boy or girl this year? Then you can expect a visit from Krampus. Or a phone-call from Bain.
bm_msk_kwm = "",--Rhubarb
bm_msk_kwm_desc = "",--A tribute to our legendary adventurer [MANY GUN] CLOVERAPTOR- solver of mysteries and bringer of The Mega Death! Giving up a dream of being a banker, he faced his destiny and defeated the Cop Wizard and his minions, the Law Elementals. Who knows if it was his own will, or that of his pushy Crime Dad, that allowed him to prevail, but we will be forever grateful for his service.$NL;$NL;OVERKILL Salutes You!
bm_msk_lady_butcher = "",--Lady Butcher
bm_msk_lady_butcher_desc = "",--If you received a dollar every time the Butcher was called a "witch", a "harlot" or a "banshee" by her peers you could earn enough money to buy the entirety of Croatia. Cynical men around her bemoaned the fact that she was female, and felt endangered and distressed at the sight of her meteoric rise in the criminal underground. Keep in mind that the Balkans are not exactly known for their capacity to tolerate anybody who is in any way different, and one can only image the flat-out chauvinism and misogyny she must have dealt with while working with some of the most ruthless criminals every day of her existence. This mask shows how she is seen by both her rivals and her associates. It makes people feel afraid. As they should be.
bm_msk_lcv = "",--Le Castle Vania
bm_msk_lcv_desc = "",--It's modern, dynamic and a real crowd-pleaser. It's sleek, slick and totally stylish. It's both the music of Le Castle Vania, and his mask.
bm_msk_lincoln = "",--The 16th
bm_msk_lincoln_desc = "法律家であり、最高司令官であり、父である。8年間、この国に尽くす野心を持った男だ。$NL;$NL;学者も大衆も、誰もが史上最高の合衆国大統領の1人だと認めている。$NL;$NL;The 16thは史上最も愛された大統領だ。犯罪者の中でも、彼への敬意は変わらない。",--Lawyer, Commander-In-Chief, father. Had an ambition to serve this great nation for 8 years.$NL;$NL;Consistently ranked by scholars and the public as one of the greatest U.S. presidents of all time.$NL;$NL;The 16th is one of the most beloved presidents in history. Among criminals, he remains well respected.
bm_msk_lone = "",--Lone Heister
bm_msk_lone_desc = "",--Whether you're a murderous desperado or a lone, brooding ranger, sometimes you need to hide your identity. What does that better than a slender black eye-mask, covering a third of your face?
bm_msk_lycanwulf = "",--Lycanwulf
bm_msk_lycanwulf_desc = "「人狼だ、人狼だ!」彼ら、怯えた村人は叫び、忌むべき存在、人狼を見た。無力な人間は、壁も、天井もカギもない檻の中で野獣に囚われた。唯一の逃げ道は、「死」だけだったのだ。",--"Lycanwulf, Lycanwulf!" they yelled, the frightened villagers, as they laid eyes upon this abomination known as the Lycanwulf. The petty humans were now prisoners of the beast, in a prison without walls, ceilings or a key, where the only escape was death.
bm_msk_mad_mask = "",--Zero 68
bm_msk_mad_mask_desc = "",--Inspired by the immensely popular anime Zero 68, this mask is modeled after the helmet of the cyborg-ninja hero of the show.
bm_msk_mandril = "",--John
bm_msk_mandril_desc = "",--John the mandrill monkey. Mandrill's are closely related to baboons and even more to the drill. Not the kind of drill you use in a bank robbery, but the monkey drill, silly you! John is a monkey known for his sardonic one-liners, including the catch phrase "unidentified monkey screech".
bm_msk_mantis = "",--Sphodromantis
bm_msk_mantis_desc = "この小さくてかわいらしい仲間たちは、一般的にその名を「Praying Mantis（カマキリ）」として知られる。なぜかって? 祈るような姿勢に前足を折り畳むという意味だ。より一般的には、その性質から奴らはpreying (捕食する) mantisである。$NL;$NL;基本的に、奴らは捕まえてむさぼり食えるものなら何でも食べる。",--The common name for these lovely little fellows is "praying mantis". The reason? It refers to the prayer-like posture where it folds its fore-limbs. More commonly however it's refered to as the preying mantis, because of it's nature.$NL;$NL;Basically, they eat anything they can successfully capture and devour.
bm_msk_mason_knight_veteran = "",--Mason Knight Veteran
bm_msk_mason_knight_veteran_desc = "",--The helmet of the Knight Veterans of the Masons were effectively symbols of this powerful, upstart order. When peasants saw this helm, they knew that Malric's new order was close behind.
bm_msk_mason_vanguard_veteran = "",--Mason Vanguard Veteran
bm_msk_mason_vanguard_veteran_desc = "",--This helmet was unearthed in an elaborate barrow, indicating that the wearer enjoyed prestige in the Mason army. These great warriors appear to have been Malric's elite troops, perhaps having served with him in the failed Tenosian crusade.
bm_msk_maui = "",--Maui
bm_msk_maui_desc = "",--Exploring the Pacific "Ring of Fire" in his youth, Bodhi came to the following revelation: honoring oneself means honoring the myths. A myth that stuck with him was that of Maui. Like Bodhi, Maui was a dauntless champion of humankind, a trickster and adventurer.
bm_msk_max = "",--Sangres
bm_msk_max_begins = "",--Sangres Begins
bm_msk_max_begins_desc = "",--This is a clean version of the iconic Sangres mask, before it was painted.$NL;$NL;Never liked how the original one turned out? This is your chance to change history.
bm_msk_max_desc = "",--The skull is Death, Sangres' faithful companion throughout his career. The gold tooth is the coin that has been paid. The kill counter represents his past as a hitman, the blood-red ruby the new wealth he's seeking in the US. Sangres' name speaks of the many bloody episodes in his life, and that red blood is also present on his mask.
bm_msk_mdm = "",--Mega Death
bm_msk_mdm_desc = "",--Death can be the end but it can also be a beginning, a transcendence and catharsis. And Mega Death has a million times the power of Death.
bm_msk_medusa = "",--Medusa
bm_msk_medusa_desc = "",--A hideous visage, snakes for hair, a petrifying gaze and a hate for men. Her gazing eyes still sends chills down spines... But this is just a mask, right?
bm_msk_mega_alien = "",--Mega Watcher
bm_msk_mega_alien_desc = "",--The Watchers are a species of extraterrestrials that act as spies on planet Earth. They communicate by using their minds and use their large eyes to witness, gather and share information about humankind, preparing themselves for the coming invasion.$NL;$NL;Thank you for your support.$NL;$NL;OVERKILL salutes you!
bm_msk_mega_blade = "",--Mega Gage Blade
bm_msk_mega_blade_desc = "",--The original Gage Blade is one of Gage's own personal favorite ballistic face masks. With the Mega Gage Blade, he's decided to give his favorite ballistic mask an upgrade. Before it was only practical, now it's also stylish.$NL;$NL;Thank you for your support.$NL;$NL;OVERKILL salutes you!
bm_msk_mega_doctor = "",--Mega Doctor Crime
bm_msk_mega_doctor_desc = "",--In issue #34 of The Amazing Career Criminals, we saw the assumed death of Doctor Crime, but fear not - the Doctor is back! With a new power armor and a fancy new mask, he's set to take out his vengeance against our unknowing heroes.$NL;$NL;Thank you for your support.$NL;$NL;OVERKILL salutes you!
bm_msk_mega_grin = "",--Mega Grin
bm_msk_mega_grin_desc = "",--The Grin was once the face representing a man's breakdown as he had to accept defeat. But now the times have changed, and the same man is back again, stronger than ever before. Rejuvenated and ready to take on the world with a determined fierceness and cunning, the mask still represents the face of a mad man, but a mad man that is winning.$NL;$NL;Thank you for your support.$NL;$NL;OVERKILL salutes you!
bm_msk_mega_mark = "",--Mega Mark
bm_msk_mega_mark_desc = "",--The mask is modeled after a legendary bear that was known to terrorize humans and other animals in an Eastern land far, far away. The story is wildly popular in the criminal underworld, and getting compared to the fierce beast is considered a great honor, reserved only to the greatest and most ruthless criminals.$NL;$NL;Thank you for your support.$NL;$NL;OVERKILL salutes you!
bm_msk_mega_sydney = "",--Mega Sydney
bm_msk_mega_sydney_desc = "",--The Mega Sydney mask is an evolved version of the original mask. It symbolises transcendence and catharsis.$NL;$NL;Thank you for your support.$NL;$NL;OVERKILL salutes you!
bm_msk_megacthulhu = "",--Mega Cthulhu
bm_msk_megacthulhu_desc = "",--Somewhere, deep in the oceanic darkness dwells our lord and savior, Chtulhu. Praise be to Him who spares us His giant wrath and blesses us with His mind controlling tenderness. Don't eat squids or eternal damnation is yours.$NL;$NL;Thank you for your support.$NL;$NL;OVERKILL salutes you!
bm_msk_metalhead = "",--Metalhead
bm_msk_metalhead_desc = "Metalheadの起源は不明だ。$NL;$NL;これはマスクというよりヘルメットに見える。トゲが突き出ていて、その姿は魅惑の鉄製のガスマスクともよく似ている。しかし、このマスクは装着者に防護効果を及ぼすかどうかは不明だ。$NL;$NL;とにかく、これはとても魅力的に見えるな。$NL;$NL;このマスクはPoetry Jamのマスクです。PAYDAYの間にドロップすることはなく売却することも出来ません。その代わりに、カスタマイズの内容と手数料は失われますが、マスクスタッシュに無料で戻すことが出来ます。",--The origin of the Metalhead is unclear.$NL;$NL;It looks more of a helmet than a mask. It has spikes pointing out of it and looks very much like a pimped out gas mask made of iron. It's unclear if it protects the wearer from any gas or melee weapons however.$NL;$NL;It looks pretty rad though.$NL;$NL;This mask is Poetry Jam mask. It can't drop during a PAYDAY and it can't be sold. Instead, it can be returned to your mask stash for free, but any customization and the fee to put that together will be lost.
bm_msk_mmj = "",--Z.A.M.S Helmet
bm_msk_mmj_desc = "",--Classic gear can be a wonderful thing. The mindset of a heroic thrill-seeker riding a 200BHP steel horse has many things in common with a heister that are not obvious at first glance- the aesthetic value of a piece of custom headgear being one of them!
bm_msk_monkeybiss = "",--Monkey Business
bm_msk_monkeybiss_desc = "このマスクは、人生を真面目に生きていない奴が被る。$NL;$NL;なぜならこれはサルのマスクだからだ。",--Worn by someone who does not take life that seriously.$NL;$NL;Because it is a mask of a monkey.
bm_msk_moon = "",--Mask of the Moon
bm_msk_moon_desc = "",--Legend speaks of an entity so malevolent it tried to smash the Moon into the Earth. Though defeated by four masked warriors, the entity escaped and inhabited... something. We hope it will never return, but remember: sometimes the man wears the mask, and sometimes the mask wears the man.
bm_msk_mp2_01 = "",--Fluffedup
bm_msk_mp2_01_desc = "",--Our darling Fluffedup is gone. He's 95 years old, and part of our family. Fluffedup is a happy little individual who's absolutely not been trying to throw himself into the blender or off the roof several times. We just want to keep him forever, and never let him go. So it's super important that we get him back to us, to our home where he lives and loves and absolutely doesn't hate!
bm_msk_mp2_02 = "",--Stoibs
bm_msk_mp2_02_desc = "",--Stoibs is a bit frantic and "speedy". He ran away last tuesday night and we would be glad to get him back. We have had a hard time finding a chinchilla with a good pedigree. So for us to start all over again with a new one, feeding him corn to get him fat and tender will be tedious. If you find him, we'll invite you to the dinner where we enjoy Stoibs!
bm_msk_mp2_03 = "",--Byrne
bm_msk_mp2_03_desc = "",--Byrne is gone. He's our koala and our "pet". But we don't want him back. He's boring and tedious and all he does is eat eucalyptus leaves. And we mean like ALL day. He doesn't like when you touch him or even talk to him. So now he's gone and we wanna keep it that way. If you find him (he looks like a douchebag pet) you can keep him or whatever. Consider this a warning of boredom.
bm_msk_mp2_04 = "",--Tempy
bm_msk_mp2_04_desc = "",--Tempy is our tame lion. He's been away for 2 weeks now and we miss him. Tempy loves all kind of cuddle, as long as it's done by us. If you spot Tempy: Do not approach him in any way. Please tell us where you've seen him. But you will get mutilated if he gets close. Other than that, he's a doll and he loves sleeping in the sun. Also don't let him see any kids...that doesn't end well.
bm_msk_mr_sinister = "",--Blackhearted
bm_msk_mr_sinister_desc = "忘れられない程の凶悪さと不実さで、このマスクは着用者を不可解に変化させると言われている。$NL;$NL;長く着用していると、着けた者の心を黒く染め上げ、悪行への欲望で満たしてしまうらしい。",--Evil and treacherous in a haunting way, this mask is said to change the wearer in mysterious ways.$NL;$NL;Worn long enough, it is said it turns the wearers heart into a black one, filled with lust for black deeds.
bm_msk_mrm = "",--Mega Rust
bm_msk_mrm_desc = "",--The Mega Rust mask is an evolved version of the original mask. It symbolises transcendence and catharsis.$NL;$NL;Thank you for your support.$NL;$NL;OVERKILL salutes you!
bm_msk_mrs_claus = "",--Mrs. Claus
bm_msk_mrs_claus_desc = "サンタクロースが12月の空を飛び回っている時は、誰かが留守番をしてエルフ達を見張っていないといけない。ムチを鳴らしてタバコをくゆらすクロース一家の鬼将軍以外には、何者にも務まらないことだ。",--When Santa is flying through December skies, someone has to stay home and keep the elves in line. No-one does that better than the whip-cracking, cigar-smoking kommandant of the Claus household.
bm_msk_msk_grizel = "",--Clover
bm_msk_msk_grizel_desc = "Cloverのマスクは、彼女がとりわけ恐れ、嫌うもの － 「マスク」を自分の顔とすることを表している。整形して縮めた鼻、ボトックスされた唇、そして全ての異常な虚栄心と執着心 － こういったものは恐怖と弱さのシンボルであり、こうして歪められた恐怖のパロディとなっている。",--Clover's mask represents what Clover both fears and hates most of all - wearing a mask as your normal face. The surgically-shrunken nose, the botox'd lips and the expression of all-consuming vanity and self-obsession - all are symbols of fear and weakness, twisted into a horrifying parody.
bm_msk_mummy = "",--The Mummy
bm_msk_mummy_desc = "皮膚と臓器が長期間保護されたミイラの顔。これは意図的または偶発的に露出させて、極端に低温に(アイスミイラ!)、湿度を下げ、真空で化学反応を抑える事でミイラ化させている。$NL;$NL;マスクが世界の何処からやって来たのか誰が知っているだろう? 長い間保管された今、このマスクは再び世界に現れようとしている。",--The face of a mummy that has had its skin and organs preserved. Either intentional or incidental exposure to extreme cold (ice mummies!), low humidity, lack of air or chemicals might have caused this.$NL;$NL;Who knows what part of the world it is from? Having been preserved for the longest time, its ready to be exposed to the world again.
bm_msk_myh = "",--Duke
bm_msk_myh_begins = "",--Duke Begins
bm_msk_myh_begins_desc = "",--This is a clean version of the iconic Duke mask, before it was painted.$NL;$NL;Never liked how the original one turned out? This is your chance to change history.
bm_msk_myh_desc = "",--Duke is a man of culture, virtue and stone-hard composure. Thus his mask has been modeled after the great historical statues as a reflection of his personality. The mask is a window into the mind and heart of this determined agent of sophisticated crime, elegant and unbreakable in the face of any heist.$NL;$NL;A big draw for Duke is his love of mystery- you never really know what's inside the safe until you open it, or behind the painting until you take it out of the frame. And with the Payday gang, the biggest mystery may be just around the corner...
bm_msk_ninja_hood = "",--Kuro Zukin
bm_msk_ninja_hood_desc = "",--A simple piece of cloth tied around their heads will transform anyone, be it beggar, farmer or common man into a ninja. A shadow among shadows, a dagger in the dark. He can be fierce or stealthy and can be anyone in a crowd. He does what he sets out to do and then disappears.
bm_msk_nixon = "",--The 37th
bm_msk_nixon_desc = "政治家であり、最高司令官であり、父である。8年間、この国に尽くす野心を持った男だ。$NL;$NL;間違いなく、詐欺師の類じゃない。$NL;$NL;The 37thは唯一の辞任した大統領だ。しかし犯罪者の中では、未だに人気が衰えていない。",--Politician, Commander-In-Chief, father. Had an ambition to serve this great nation for 8 years.$NL;$NL;He wasn't a crook, for sure.$NL;$NL;The 37th was the only president who resigned from office. Among criminals however, he remains extremely popular.
bm_msk_nomegusta = "",--No Me Gusta
bm_msk_nomegusta_desc = "強盗した銀行の口座にトーストしかない件",--When you're robbing a bank and there's only a toast in the deposit box.
bm_msk_nun_town = "",--The Nun
bm_msk_nun_town_desc = "",--A Catholic nun may not seem like the obvious choice for a terrifying mask, unless you know an actual Catholic nun. In which case, you'll know any notions of gentle, grandmotherly penguins are without merit. These bitter crones are the personification of evil, dishing out thrashings to any young buttocks within reach.
bm_msk_nutcracker = "",--Hans
bm_msk_nutcracker_desc = "",--Hans hates people and will crack the skull of anyone who opposes him. But under his frightening appearance, Hans is a good boy. You could almost say he's a prince in disguise. Treat him well and he might take you to the Land of Sweets.
bm_msk_obama = "",--The 44th
bm_msk_obama_desc = "政治家であり、最高司令官であり、父である。8年間、この国に努めた。$NL;$NL;有望な奴で、章を貰ったような奴だ。$NL;$NL;The 44thは歴史上最も野心的な大統領の一人だった。しかし犯罪者の中では、未だに人気が衰えていない。",--Politican, Commander-In-Chief, father. Served this great nation for 8 years. A hopeful man, no doubt..$NL;$NL;The 44th was one of the most ambitious presidents in history. Among criminals however, he remains extremely popular.
bm_msk_old_hoxton = "",--Hoxton Reborn
bm_msk_old_hoxton_begins = "",--Hoxton Reborn Begins
bm_msk_old_hoxton_begins_desc = "Hoxton Rebornマスクの、まだペイントされていない無地のバージョン。$NL;$NL;まだオリジナルの様に着こなせていない? これは歴史を塗り替えるチャンスだ。",--This is a clean version of the iconic Hoxton Reborn mask, before it was painted.$NL;$NL;Never liked how the original one turned out? This is your chance to change history.
bm_msk_old_hoxton_desc = "Hoxton RebornマスクはHoxtonがブタ箱の中で作ったものだ。彼にとって、このマスクはこれまでの経験と自らが欠けたPAYDAYギャングの象徴だ。刑務所の何がお前をこうさせたのか、と聞いても、Hoxtonは口を開かないだろう。$NL;$NL;俺達が受け入れられるのは...これまでとは違う何かになったHoxtonだ",--The Hoxton Reborn mask is a mask that Hoxton made while in prison. For him, it's a symbol of everything he experienced in the past years while the PAYDAY gang kept on going without him. No one knows how his experiences in prison has changed him, and he won't talk about it when asked.$NL;$NL;All we can assume is that he has been changed forever, and that he is reborn into... Something different.
bm_msk_oliver = "",--Oliver
bm_msk_oliver_desc = "「世界で最も偉大なHeistersの候補者である.....」",--"And the nominees for The Greatest Heisters In The World are....."
bm_msk_onebelow = "",--The One Below
bm_msk_onebelow_desc = "",--The head is what remains of this aquatic horror from the old days, when dark lords ruled the lands and good men grew up only to die; when the summer was short and the winter felt like an eternity; when the One Below stepped out of the ocean and walked the earth.
bm_msk_oni = "",--Oni
bm_msk_oni_desc = "Oniは日本の悪魔だ。$NL;$NL;巨大なオーガーに似た凶悪なクリーチャーであり、爪は鋭く頭には二本の角が生えている。$NL;$NL;彼らは何種類かの皮膚色を持つことで知られており、中でも赤と青が一般的だ。",--The Oni is a Japanese devil.$NL;$NL;They are hideous, gigantic ogre-like creatures that have sharp claws and two horns growing from their heads.$NL;$NL;Their skin may have any number of colors, though red and blue are most common.
bm_msk_optimist_prime = "",--The Optimist
bm_msk_optimist_prime_desc = "\"世のために自らを変えろ\"$NL;$NL;これがOptimistが信じるものだ。$NL;$NL;正義のロボット軍団のリーダーとして、否定と破滅に取り憑かれたライバルの軍団と戦うことが自らの責務と考えている。彼の武器は、建設的な根拠と公平な論理を持って積極的に出撃することだ。$NL;$NL;それか、強制的な進化。$NL;$NL;このマスクはPoetry Jamのマスクです。PAYDAYの間にドロップすることはなく売却することも出来ません。その代わりに、カスタマイズの内容と手数料は失われますが、マスクスタッシュに無料で戻すことが出来ます。",--"Be the change you want to see in the world."$NL;$NL;That's what the Optimist believes.$NL;$NL;As the leader of a peaceful group of robots, he feels it is his responsibility to combat rival bands of robots obsessed with negativity and extermination. His prime weapon: rolling out positivity through constructive reasoning and unbiased logic.$NL;$NL;Or through forced upgrades. Which are compulsory.$NL;$NL;This mask is Poetry Jam mask. It can't drop during a PAYDAY and it can't be sold. Instead, it can be returned to your mask stash for free, but any customization and the fee to put that together will be lost.
bm_msk_orangutang = "",--Rutger
bm_msk_orangutang_desc = "",--Rutger the motherfucking orangutan. If you're strolling down the jungle and suddenly face an orangutan, you're in trouble. Statistics show that one orangutan is as dangerous as ten hobos with shotguns. You remember that movie about dinosaurs with the big dinosaur in the end saving the kids? Know who killed the dinosaur after the credits? The kids did, but you know who killed the kids? Rutger the motherfucking orangutan did.
bm_msk_oro = "",--Oro
bm_msk_oro_desc = "",--It was exploring the Islands of French Polynesia, Bodhi encountered the disciples of the war-god Oro. The young adventurer quickly became enamored of this god, who valued the appreciation of beautiful crafts as much as the art of struggle.
bm_msk_outlandish_a = "",--The Cannula
bm_msk_outlandish_a_desc = "このマスクは不思議なマテリアルで作られており、無様に感じると思うだろう。装着すれば、さらに変に感じるだろう。$NL;$NL;このマスクを被る事で自分が無法者、余所者、所在地をころころ変え、家を空けて、誰にも認められようとしない人間と感じる様になる。",--This mask is made of strange materials, holding it feels awkward. Wearing it feels even stranger.$NL;$NL;Putting on the mask, you feel like an outsider, a foreigner, someone who constantly changes locations, staying away, not wanting to be recognized by anyone.
bm_msk_outlandish_b = "",--The Outlander
bm_msk_outlandish_b_desc = "口が無いのに叫ばずには居られなくなることはないか?$NL;$NL;それはあなたが民間人で、このマスクをつけた強盗に、銃を向けられ、床に伏せるように叫ばれている時に、そう感じるだろう。",--Have you ever had that feeling when you have no mouth but feel the urge to scream?$NL;$NL;That is how you are going to feel if you are a civilian looking at a criminal wearing this mask, pointing a gun at you, shouting you to the floor.
bm_msk_outlandish_c = "",--The Perfect Stranger
bm_msk_outlandish_c_desc = "異国での外来者を表すマスク。$NL;$NL;マスクは、失われた文明の戦士や戦争で兵士が、葬式や悪魔の精神を退ける呪術の儀式に於いて、厳かな方法で使われる事を好む。",--The mask of a stranger in a strange land.$NL;$NL;Masks like these were used in a lost civilization, in war, on soldiers; ceremonially, for burial rites and for shamanistic ceremonies to drive away evil spirits.
bm_msk_owl = "",--Rasmus
bm_msk_owl_desc = "Rasmusは、シークレットを見つける眼を持っている。$NL;$NL;フクロウは、夜行性の猛禽類だ。頭蓋骨と比べられるほどの大きな眼を持つ。眼を動かすことはできないが、代わりに270度も頭を回転させることができる。フン、知らなかったろ。な?$NL;$NL;「お前なんて知るか!」「俺はお前なんか呼んじゃいねぇ!」",--Rasmus has an eye for secrets.$NL;$NL;Owls are nocturnal birds of prey. They are known for their large eyes in comparison to their skulls. They can't actually move their eyes, they swivel their heads instead and are able to swivel 270 degrees. Shit you didn't know, amirite.$NL;$NL;"I don't know you!" "You're no guest of mine!"
bm_msk_pachy = "",--Pachy
bm_msk_pachy_desc = "",--Pachy the Pachycephalosaurus, meaning thick headed lizard, wasn't never that thick headed really. He never took that name for himself, the other dinosaurs gave it to him because they were jealous of his high rolls in intelligence, spirit and wisdom. Having earned a robe and a wizard hat as a second prize at the local prehistoric spelling bee didn't make it any better.
bm_msk_pain = "",--Venger
bm_msk_pain_desc = "闇の頂点に立った男が元になっている。これの用途は呼吸器具だの発話装置だのと言われているが、実際のところは良くわかっていない。ある識者は、彼の超人的な強さと怒りを制御する麻薬投与システムだった、とみている。",--Based on the crazed leader of the League of Darkness. It's unclear if this was a breathing apparatus or a vocabulator. Some speculate that it was a delivery system, designed to provide Nemesis with the narcotics that gave him both his superhuman strength and psychotic rage.
bm_msk_panda = "",--Jean-Claude
bm_msk_panda_desc = "ジャン＝クロード \"パンダ\" ヴァン·ダムはクレイジーでクールなスターだ。$NL;$NL;しかし、悲しいことに麻薬中毒で落ち目となったことがあった。トレーニングにより再びそのスターを取り戻した。$NL;$NL;最近は、二台のトラックの上で立つ彼を見ることが出来る。それはもう奇妙なものだ。一度は見ておけ",--Jean-Claude the Panda used to be really cool and star in all sorts of crazy stuff.$NL;$NL;Sadly, he later became a drug addict and stopped being cool. Because of training however, he managed to get back on track.$NL;$NL;Most recently, you could see him do this weird things with two trucks. That shit was fucked up. You should check it out if you haven't.
bm_msk_panther = "",--Brandon
bm_msk_panther_desc = "",--Brandon has a thing for walking really, really fast.$NL;$NL;Brandon is a panther, and panthers are large cats. One funny thing is that only the tiger, lion, leopard and jaguar has the anatomical structure which enables them to roar. Poor panther.
bm_msk_patton = "",--Old Blood and Guts
bm_msk_patton_desc = "私がアフリカ戦線で目にした勇敢な男の1人は、チュニスを目指している最中、猛烈な銃火の中で電柱に登っていた。私は立ち止まり、何をしてるんだと彼に尋ねた。すると彼は「電線を直しています、閣下」と答える。「今やるにはちょいと危険じゃないかね」と私は応じる。「はい、閣下。しかしこのクソ電線を固定しなければならないのです」と彼が言う。「敵機の機銃掃射は気にならないのかね?」と尋ねると、「いいえ、閣下。けれど、必ずやり遂げてご覧に入れます」と答えた。'$NL;$NL;ああ、そこに本当の兵士がいた。本物の男だ。あまりに大きな代償にも関わらず、一見して些細な任務にも関わらず、その任務に命を捧げた男だ。",--One of the bravest men I saw in the African campaign was on a telegraph pole in the midst of furious fire while we were moving toward Tunis. I stopped and asked him what the hell he was doing up there. He answered, 'Fixing the wire, sir.' 'Isn't it a little unhealthy up there right now?' I asked. 'Yes sir, but this goddamn wire has got to be fixed.' I asked, 'Don't those planes strafing the road bother you?' And he answered, 'No sir, but you sure as hell do.'$NL;$NL;Now, there was a real soldier. A real man. A man who devoted all he had to his duty, no matter how great the odds, no matter how seemingly insignificant his duty appeared at the time.
bm_msk_pazuzu = "",--Pazuzu
bm_msk_pazuzu_desc = "",--Pazuzu was the king of the wind demons according to ancient Babylonian mythology. Legends also tell of him as a beastial behemoth fighting groups of adveturers in far away lands, and some even say he walked the earth as an immortal warrior in human form.
bm_msk_pbm = "",--Simon
bm_msk_pbm_desc = "",--A wanna-be robber tried to knock over a liquor store, but neglected to properly conceil his identity, opting instead to use the paper bag he got when he last shopped there! Needless to say, the idiot was quickly identified and taken into custody. With no hostages to trade for freedom, his criminal career was cut short. The event, which did not even prompt a local news headline, now stands as a stark reminder that some things are best left to professionals.
bm_msk_pig = "",--Aubrey
bm_msk_pig_desc = "",--Aubrey is a real gun lover.$NL;$NL;Large headed and long snouted Aubrey is a master of arms and knows nothing better than to kill using some fine weaponry.$NL;$NL;Pigs have pretty small lungs though so Aubrey can't run that far.
bm_msk_pim_daisy = "",--Daisy
bm_msk_pim_daisy_desc = "",--They might have not known what they did and to who, but that doesn't matter. They got what they deserved and then some. John is back.
bm_msk_pim_dirty_russian = "",--Zashchita
bm_msk_pim_dirty_russian_desc = "",--A good way to not get shot in the head is to wear a helmet, but when you want to protect just your face from bullets and identification this will do. Does it really look bulletproof? What are you? A coward? Grab your fear by the balls and headbutt it in the face with this mask on.
bm_msk_pim_hotelier = "",--Hotelier
bm_msk_pim_hotelier_desc = "",--The Continental only serves the people who can respect the rules of the assassins' sanctuary. It's not a cult or a secret society, it's a necessity in a business where everybody is willing to kill for money and everybody in there is on someone's list of targets.
bm_msk_pim_mustang = "",--Mustang
bm_msk_pim_mustang_desc = "",--Do you think you're a car? Oh? But do you think you're a MUSCLE car? No? Heisting isn't about looking fast and sleek, it's about looking furious and dangerous. Vroom, vroom motherfuckers!
bm_msk_pirate_skull = "",--Pirate Skull
bm_msk_pirate_skull_desc = "",--In 'Buccaneers Ahoy!', these swashbuckling undead heisters terrorized the treasure-laden galleons of the Caribbean for years, proving forever that....pirates arrrrrrrrrrrr cool.
bm_msk_pitbull = "",--Arnold
bm_msk_pitbull_desc = "アーノルド \"ブルドッグ\" シュワルツネッガーは常に偉大な野心の先を行っている。$NL;$NL;彼はずっと強い体を欲していた - そして彼はそれを成し遂げた。彼は山奥の小さな町で大きな夢を抱き、賞を得た。$NL;$NL;彼はアメリカに渡り、\"The Dogenator\"と\"The Dogenator II - such judgement\"に主役として出演を果たした",--Arnold the Bulldog has always been a doge of great ambition.$NL;$NL;He wanted to build much body - and he did. He became the biggest doge in his little mountain town and received such prize.$NL;$NL;He then moved to the States, got into office, starred in a couple of weird doge movies called "The Dogenator" and "The Dogenator II - such judgement".
bm_msk_plague = "",--The Plague Doctor
bm_msk_plague_desc = "Mastermindのためのペスト医師のマスクだ。$NL;$NL;バガヴァッド·ギーターから引用すれば: \"私は死となり、世界の破壊者となった\"$NL;$NL;あるいは、アートだ。$NL;$NL;このマスクはInfamyツリーの報酬です。PAYDAYの間にドロップすることはなく売却することも出来ません。その代わりに、カスタマイズの内容と手数料は失われますが、マスクスタッシュに無料で戻すことが出来ます。",--A plague doctor mask for the Mastermind.$NL;$NL;In the words of the Bhagavad-Gita: "Now I am become death, destroyer of worlds."$NL;$NL;Or at least, that was the art direction.$NL;$NL;This mask is an Infamy tree reward. It can't drop during a PAYDAY and it can't be sold. Instead, it can be returned to your mask stash for free, but any pattern, color or material as well as the customization fee to put these together will be lost.
bm_msk_pokachu = "",--Electarodent
bm_msk_pokachu_desc = "",--Untrained, the Electarodent can be found nibbling sweet carrots or frolicking across Alpine meadows. However, fully trained, the Electarodent is most often found wielding Bernetti 9's and eating through the face-plates of Skulldozers.
bm_msk_pumpkin_king = "",--Pumpkin King
bm_msk_pumpkin_king_desc = "",--Legend has it that a boy named Jack was getting chased by some villagers from whom he had stolen, when he suddenly bumped into the Devil$NL;$NL;Jack was a clever little heister and managed to convince the devil that the loot he was carrying was worth to be shared. The Devil agreed and the two ran to the escape horses and got away.
bm_msk_punk = "",--The Being
bm_msk_punk_desc = "このマスクは奇妙なRudolf Mastaba博士の研究が元になっている。現代のプロメテウスと呼ばれた彼は、科学技術で死者の息を吹き返す実験をしていた。噂では部分的に成功して生き返ったって言われているが - 穀物を異常に欲したらしいな。",--This mask is based on the experiments of the peculiar Dr Rudolf Mastaba. A modern Prometheus, he sought to return life to the dead with the application of Industrial Revolution technology. Rumour suggests that he was partly successful - the undead rose, but had an insatiable appetite for wheat, barley and maize.
bm_msk_rabbit = "",--Graham
bm_msk_rabbit_desc = "",--Graham enjoys long walks in the sun.$NL;$NL;Rabbits are small mammals that practically can be found anywhere. If confronted by a potential threat, rabbits will instantly freeze and warn others in the warren with powerful thumps on the ground.$NL;$NL;When fleeing, they hop in a zig-zag pattern, much like many Counter-Strike players do.
bm_msk_rage_demon = "",--Flaming Skull
bm_msk_rage_demon_desc = "",--The skull as a symbol can either mean death or mortality, and we humans have always had a fascination for it. Wearing this motorcycle helmet looks powerful and intimidating.
bm_msk_rageface = "",--Rageface
bm_msk_rageface_desc = "Cloakerの蹴りを避けたら味方に当たって草",--Dodging a cloaker kick and your buddy gets hit. Lol.
bm_msk_rambo = "",--The Troubled War Veteran
bm_msk_rambo_desc = "The Troubled War VeteranはGageが手間をかけて仕上げたマスクだ。ベトナム戦争の頃、Gageは近代火器の代わりに弓を使う巨大なマッチョマン、それも気が狂った奴に会った。そいつは早々に戦死したが、しかしどういうわけか、Gageは彼の顔を忘れることができなかった。",--The Troubled War Veteran is a mask that Gage has worked on for some time. Back in the Vietnam war Gage met this big-muscled guy who went nuts and started to use a bow instead of modern weapons.$NL;$NL;He died pretty early in the war, but for some strange reason Gage couldn't forget his face.
bm_msk_ranger = "",--Heister Sentry
bm_msk_ranger_desc = "元々は全身用強盗装備として設計されたが、テストの結果派手な全身タイツは全く防御性がなかった。しかしマスクは軽くて防弾性がありスタイリッシュである事が認められた。さぁ強盗だ!",--This mask was originally designed to be part of a complete head-to-toe heisting outfit. However, field testing revealed that the gaudy spandex suit offered no protection against bullets, knives or grenades. The mask, however, was found to be lightweight, durable and stylish. It's heistin' time!
bm_msk_red_hurricane = "",--The Red Bear
bm_msk_red_hurricane_desc = "「ソビエトロシアでは、赤い熊があなたを殺す!」The Red Bearが誰だったのか、正確に知る者はいない。ただの神話だと語る者もいれば、母なる祖国や力強さや諸々の統一された象徴と語るものもいる。唯一知られているのは、何度も何度も語られた物語だ。ある時、彼は熊の群れを殺し、血で全身真っ赤になって家に帰ってきたという。",--"In Soviet Russia, Red Bear kills you." No one knows exactly who the Red Bear was; some say he was just a myth, a symbol of the motherland and everything that was strong, combined into one being. Only the stories are known and told again and again. Like that one time, when he killed a bunch of bears and came back home all in red, drenched in blood.
bm_msk_richard_begins = "",--Richard Returns Begins
bm_msk_richard_begins_desc = "Richard Returnsマスクの、まだペイントされていない無地のバージョン。$NL;$NL;まだオリジナルの様に着こなせていない? これは歴史を塗り替えるチャンスだ。",--This is a clean version of the iconic Richard Returns mask, before it was painted.$NL;$NL;Never liked how the original one turned out? This is your chance to change history.
bm_msk_richard_returns = "",--Richard Returns
bm_msk_richard_returns_desc = "この覆面は、深く横たわる精神的な疾患の投影なのか? もしくは、解離性人格障害? 精神分裂症? 割れ乱れた心のトラウマか? それとも、何かを映しているのではなく、これらの根源なのか?",--Is this mask a reflection of a deep-seated psychological problem? Possibly a dissociative identity disorder? Schizophrenia? Trauma of a disturbed psyche? Or is it not a reflection at all, but instead something to cause them?
bm_msk_richter = "",--Richter
bm_msk_richter_desc = "ネズミのように、Richterは静かな殺し屋だ。どこからでも － 警戒が最高度の銀行やマンションにも － 侵入できる。奴が望めば見つかることもなく、ひとたび中に入れば、伝染病のように死をばら撒く。良心の呵責も無く殺すのだ。個人的な恨みは無い。",--Like the rat, Richter is a silent killer. It can make its way into just about anywhere - into the most secure banks and apartments. It can avoid detection when it wants, and, once there, spread death like a plague. It kills without remorse. Nothing personal.
bm_msk_robberfly = "",--Asilidae
bm_msk_robberfly_desc = "強盗バエや暗殺バエとしても呼ばれるAsilidae（ムシヒキアブ）は、がっしりとした体格と固い毛で覆われており、その攻撃的な捕食習慣で知られる。彼らは他の昆虫を餌とし、一般的には待ちぶせして飛行中の獲物を捕える。",--The Asilidae, also known as robber fly or assassin fly, are powerfully built, bristly flies who are known for their notoriously aggressive predatory habits. They feed on other insects and as a rule, they wait in ambush and catch their prey in flight.
bm_msk_robo_arnold = "",--Robo-Arnold
bm_msk_robo_arnold_desc = "有名な映画シリーズの、タイムトラベラーのサイボーグ·スター「エクスターミネーター」だ。第1作目では、彼は、実は過去で彼自身の母親の父親でもあった未来の反乱軍のリーダーの母親が彼女の息子に遺されたチップを盗み出せるようになる前に抹殺するために送られたのだ。彼のキャッチフレーズは、無表情で「戻ってくるのを待て」だ。",--Iconic, time-travelling cyborg star of the 'Exterminator' movie series. In the first movie, he was sent to kill the mother of the leader of the future rebellion before she can steal the chip left by her son who was also her father... In the past. Noted for his deadpan delivery of the catchphrase "Await my return".
bm_msk_robo_santa = "",--Mechanical Santa
bm_msk_robo_santa_desc = "今年のクリスマスは、全自動の心付きサンタマシーンが祝ってくれます。彼は妖精の死体と切断されたトナカイの首に囲まれて、プレゼントを持っています。",--This jolly, festive automaton has the heart of Santa. He keeps it in a box, under a pile of elf corpses, and surrounded by severed reindeer heads.
bm_msk_rooster = "",--Richard
bm_msk_rooster_desc = "Richardは異なる人格に質問をして過ごす時間を楽しんでいる。$NL;$NL;他人を傷つけるのは好きか?$NL;$NL;お前の電話にメッセージを残すのは誰だ?$NL;$NL;お前は「今」、どこにいる?$NL;$NL;俺達はどうして、こうやって話しているんだ?",--Richard enjoys spending time with different personas and asking questions.$NL;$NL;Do you like hurting other people?$NL;$NL;Who is leaving messages on your answering machine?$NL;$NL;Where are you right now?$NL;$NL;Why are we having this conversation?
bm_msk_rubber_female = "",--Mrs. Mannequin
bm_msk_rubber_female_desc = "女性のマネキン。$NL;$NL;その多関節の人形の顔は仕立て屋や裁縫師、アーティストやショーウィンドウ、そして銀行強盗にも用いられている。$NL;$NL;普通マネキンは陳列や試着に使うが、応急処置や心肺蘇生、気管挿管を学ぶ為にも使用され、今や銀行強盗の練習にも持ち出されている。",--The Female Mannequin.$NL;$NL;The face of an articulated doll used by tailors, dressmakers, artists, windowdressers and now bank robbers.$NL;$NL;They are most often used to display or fit clothing, but are also used to simulate how to teach first aid, CPR, tracheal intubation and now bank robbery.
bm_msk_rubber_male = "",--Mr. Mannequin
bm_msk_rubber_male_desc = "男性のマネキン。$NL;$NL;その多関節の人形の顔は仕立て屋や裁縫師、アーティストやショーウィンドウ、そして銀行強盗にも用いられている。$NL;$NL;普通マネキンは陳列や試着に使うが、応急処置や心肺蘇生、気管挿管を学ぶ為にも使用され、今や銀行強盗の練習にも持ち出されている。",--The Male Mannequin.$NL;$NL;The face of an articulated doll used by tailors, dressmakers, artists, windowdressers and now bank robbers.$NL;$NL;They are most often used to display or fit clothing, but are also used to simulate how to teach first aid, CPR, tracheal intubation and now bank robbery.
bm_msk_rudeolph = "",--Rudelf
bm_msk_rudeolph_desc = "",--Houston wore these at the Payday crews' Christmas party until Hoxton told him he "looked a proper tit". Ignore Hox. Embrace the spirit of Christmas.
bm_msk_rus_hat = "",--Russian Hat
bm_msk_rus_hat_desc = "",--The world would be very different were it not for the howling, freezing Russian winter. Napoleon and Hitler both learned this. History could be very different if they only packed a warm hat.
bm_msk_rust = "",--Rust
bm_msk_rust_begins = "",--Rust Begins
bm_msk_rust_begins_desc = "Rustを象徴するマスクの、まだペイントされていない無地のバージョン。$NL;$NL;まだオリジナルの様に着こなせていない? これは歴史を塗り替えるチャンスだ。",--This is a clean version of Rust's iconic mask, before it was painted.$NL;$NL;Never liked how the original one turned out? This is your chance to change history.
bm_msk_rust_desc = "",--The Devil is a moniker that has followed Rust through most of his life. Therefore, Rust's mask is a combination of a smiling clown with ominous horns protruding from the forehead, letting everyone know that the Devil is here.
bm_msk_rvd_01 = "",--The Dons
bm_msk_rvd_01_desc = "",--True class is eternal when accepted by scoundrels and heroes alike.
bm_msk_rvd_02 = "",--Futuras
bm_msk_rvd_02_desc = "",--Look no further for a bad ass cherry to put on top of your Ice Cream of Minigun mayhem.
bm_msk_rvd_03 = "",--Producers
bm_msk_rvd_03_desc = "",--These frames harken back to a time when moon-landings were envisioned, all dreams were possible and people all dressed a little nicer.
bm_msk_samurai = "",--Somen Mempo
bm_msk_samurai_desc = "かつての日本では、侍は敵に恐怖を植え付けるため面頬を兜に結びつけた。面頬は地獄からでも悪魔の様に見える。$NL;$NL;誰もが、かつての戦いのためにこのマスクが使われたという事を知っている。だが、今がもう一度の戦だ。$NL;$NL;\"Boku no ikari wo osoreru\"",--In ancient Japan, samurai warriors wore somen masks to protect themselves in war and to incite fear in their enemies. Somen masks were made from iron and leather and were tied to the large kabuto helmets, making the samurai look like demons from jigoku.$NL;$NL;No one knows what fierce and ruthless warrior wore this intimidating mask in the past. Now however, it is ready for battle once more.$NL;$NL;"Boku no ikari wo osoreru"
bm_msk_santa_drunk = "",--Tipsy Santa
bm_msk_santa_drunk_desc = "サンタクロース、聖ニコラス、クリスマスの父やクリス·クリングル(?)として知られるサンタは、非常に大きなスケールの男です。伝説的な、神話上の、歴史的な、というのはこの人のための言葉だ。$NL;$NL;このマスクは酔ったサンタのマスクだ。あなたは酔ったときの気分というのを知っているだろうが、まだぶん殴られた事はないようだ。酔うのはそんなときのためだ。",--Santa, more known as Santa Claus, Saint Nicholas, Father Christmas and Kris Kringle (?) is a man of epic proportions. Words like legendary, mythical, historical and folkloric best describe this beast of a man.$NL;$NL;This particular mask is the Tipsy Santa mask. You know that type of feeling when you're tipsy and are feeling something's going on but you aren't hammered yet. That's tipsy for ya.
bm_msk_santa_happy = "",--Happy Santa
bm_msk_santa_happy_desc = "",--Santa, more known as Santa Claus, Saint Nicholas, Father Christmas and Kris Kringle (?) is a man of epic proportions. Words like legendary, mythical, historical and folkloric best describe this beast of a man.$NL;$NL;This particular mask is the Happy Santa mask. Big smile and super jolly with red cheeks and all, wearing this you'll even bring the most negative of Bulldozers into a joyous smile.
bm_msk_santa_mad = "",--Furious Santa
bm_msk_santa_mad_desc = "サンタクロース、聖ニコラス、クリスマスの父やクリス·クリングル(?)として知られるサンタは、非常に大きなスケールの男です。伝説的な、神話上の、歴史的な、というのはこの人のための言葉だ。$NL;$NL;このマスクは激怒したサンタのマスクだ。プレゼントを貰えなかった怒れるネットの民や悪い子供がつけるマスクだ。",--Santa, more known as Santa Claus, Saint Nicholas, Father Christmas and Kris Kringle (?) is a man of epic proportions. Words like legendary, mythical, historical and folkloric best describe this beast of a man.$NL;$NL;This particular mask is the Furious Santa. It's worn by angry internet users and bad children who didn't get the presents they wanted.
bm_msk_santa_surprise = "",--Surprised Santa
bm_msk_santa_surprise_desc = "サンタクロース、聖ニコラス、クリスマスの父やクリス·クリングル(?)として知られるサンタは、非常に大きなスケールの男です。伝説的な、神話上の、歴史的な、というのはこの人のための言葉だ。$NL;$NL;このマスクは驚いたサンタのマスクだ。何に驚いているか知っている奴は居るか?誰かがソリを盗んだか?トナカイを盗まれたか?それとも今まさに強盗を見ているのか?",--Santa, more known as Santa Claus, Saint Nicholas, Father Christmas and Kris Kringle (?) is a man of epic proportions. Words like legendary, mythical, historical and folkloric best describe this beast of a man.$NL;$NL;This particular mask is the Surprised Santa mask. Who knows why he's surprised? Maybe someone stole his sled? Maybe someone stole his reindeers? Maybe he just saw someone rob a bank?
bm_msk_satan = "",--Satan
bm_msk_satan_desc = "",--The second greatest trick the devil ever pulled was to be depicted as a big horned, red skinned demon. Now nobody knows who the person listening to music through their phone's speakers on the subway truly is.
bm_msk_scarecrow = "",--Mr. Sackcloth
bm_msk_scarecrow_desc = "カラスやスズメそして公僕が、あなたの恐怖の領域に足を踏み入れる事を防ぐマスク。$NL;$NL;遠く離れた土地の言い伝えによると、そこには全知だが歩く事が出来ない神が住んでいた。欲深い人々がその神を見つけると、自分らが神の知恵を得る為に、神の首を切り落とした。$NL;$NL;その代わり、人々は恐怖によって呪われてしまった.",--Discourage crows, sparrows and law enforcers from entering your field of terror.$NL;$NL;The legend goes that in distant lands, there lived a god who knew everything yet could not walk. The greed of man found the god and beheaded it, thinking they could gain its wisdom.$NL;$NL;Instead, they were cursed with terror.
bm_msk_shirai = "",--Shirai
bm_msk_shirai_desc = "",--Get over here! And let me tell you about the most badass ninjas you ever heard about. They are the protectors of our world and they only accept the best warriors. They are given the most kickass mask to show that they are better than everyone else. Here is your mask, welcome to the clan.
bm_msk_shogun = "",--The Shogun
bm_msk_shogun_desc = "このマスクを着用すると、まるでかつての日本の将軍と化したような錯覚を得る。$NL;$NL;それは、狂ったように手柄を上げ、地位を上げて挙句に将軍とならんとする足軽のものであるという。$NL;$NL;一般的には偉大なことを成し遂げる事はない。怒ったように必死にそうしなければならないからだ。",--Don the mask and feel like a Japanese general from a distant past.$NL;$NL;It is said that this mask was the mask of a mad and desperate warrior, who rose above the ranks and became a great general, winning many battles.$NL;$NL;Common sense will not accomplish great things. You must become mad and desperate to do so.
bm_msk_shrunken = "",--The Shrunken Head
bm_msk_shrunken_desc = "儀式のために、目や口などが縫い合わされた頭蓋骨。熱湯で煮られ、岩と砂で乾燥させて顔の形を維持している。$NL;$NL;大昔に西洋人によりアメリカ大陸に持ち込まれ、どういうわけかこのマスクは君の物になっている。",--Ritually prepared, the cranium removed from the head, eyes and mouth sewn shut. Boiled in hot water, dried with hot rocks and sand and molded to keep the features of a human face.$NL;$NL;Taken by ship to the Americas by Westerners long ago, it now somehow has ended up in your possession.
bm_msk_silverback = "",--Steven
bm_msk_silverback_desc = "",--Steven the silverback gorilla. Not only is he fucking huge, he's strong as hell too. He can break your back by just looking at you. You'll be hospitilized for weeks. Not only that, but there'll be months of therapy as well. Do you know how hard it is learning to walk again? Want to know what else that is hard? Steven's muscles. 22 years ago he worked as a chef on a military ship. Killed everyone in 103 minutes.
bm_msk_simpson = "",--The Tids
bm_msk_simpson_desc = "噂では、彼のレーシングスーツは漂白したイルカの肌で作られ、彼の油性分泌物は中国の医学賞を手に入れたとか。私達が知っているのは...彼がThe Tidsと呼ばれていることだけだ。",--Some say his racing leathers are made from bleached dolphin skin, and that his oily secretions are prized in Chinese medicine. All we know is... he's called The Tids.
bm_msk_skull = "",--The Skull
bm_msk_skull_desc = "死とその運命を表す唯一のマスク。$NL;$NL;早くから神の存在を信んじていた人々は祭壇を造り、各地に信仰を広めた。神は彼らに贈り物として、天国でこのマスクを作成した。$NL;$NL;OVERKILLを信じていてくれてありがとう! 私たちはあなたに敬意を表します!",--An exclusive mask representing death and mortality.$NL;$NL;Created in the heavens as a gift by the gods to men and women who believed in them early on, who built their shrines and spread their beliefs across the lands.$NL;$NL;Thank you for believing in us! We salute you!
bm_msk_skullhard = "",--The Hard Skull
bm_msk_skullhard_desc = "奇妙な人間の骸骨。人間というのは、示された一部分から全体を想像することが出来るという。人間の脳はそれだけ特別なものがあるらしい。$NL;$NL;どうやら君は全てのJobをHardでクリアしたらしいな。プロの強盗か何かか?たぶん、このマスクは似合うと思うぜ$NL;$NL;このマスクは難易度全クリアによる報酬です。PAYDAYの間にドロップすることはなく売却することも出来ません。その代わりに、カスタマイズの内容と手数料は失われますが、マスクスタッシュに無料で戻すことが出来ます。",--A strange thing, the human skull. Humans can often recognize a human skull, even if it's only partially shown. The human brain even has a specific region for it.$NL;$NL;You finished all heists on the Hard difficulty? What are you, some kind of pro? Maybe this mask will suit you after all.$NL;$NL;This mask is a difficulty reward. It can't drop during a PAYDAY and it can't be sold. Instead, it can be returned to your mask stash for free, but any pattern, color or material as well as the customization fee to put these together will be lost.
bm_msk_skullhard_desc_WIN32 = "奇妙な人間の骸骨。人間というのは、示された一部分から全体を想像することが出来るという。人間の脳はそれだけ特別なものがあるらしい。$NL;$NL;どうやら君は全てのJobをHardでクリアしたらしいな。プロの強盗か何かか?たぶん、このマスクは似合うと思うぜ$NL;$NL;このマスクは難易度全クリアによる報酬です。PAYDAYの間にドロップすることはなく売却することも出来ません。その代わりに、カスタマイズの内容と手数料は失われますが、マスクスタッシュに無料で戻すことが出来ます。",--A strange thing, the human skull. Humans can often recognize a human skull, even if it's only partially shown. The human brain even has a specific region for it.$NL;$NL;You finished all heists on the Hard difficulty? What are you, some kind of pro? Maybe this mask will suit you after all.$NL;$NL;This mask is a difficulty reward. It can't drop during a PAYDAY and it can't be sold. Instead, it can be returned to your mask stash for free, but any pattern, color or material as well as the customization fee to put these together will be lost.
bm_msk_skullmonkey = "",--Clint
bm_msk_skullmonkey_desc = "",--Clint the black-capped squirrel monkey. Not really a monkey without a name. Just like the real Clint, this monkey doesn't fuck around. It minds its own business. Doesn't talk unless talked to, knowing that the less it says the stronger it becomes. When it actually tries to say something it ends up screeching because it's a FUCKING MONKEY.
bm_msk_skulloverkill = "",--The OVERKILL Skull
bm_msk_skulloverkill_desc = "なんてこった - この悪魔みてーなのは何だ?人間ってのは一部分から全体を見出すらしいが、この骸骨はもはや人間のものじゃない。$NL;$NL;どうやら君は全てのJobをOVERKILLでクリアしたらしいな。何だ、Pit Fiend何かか?たぶん、このマスクはあんたにバッチリ似合うと思うぜ$NL;$NL;このマスクは難易度全クリアによる報酬です。PAYDAYの間にドロップすることはなく売却することも出来ません。その代わりに、カスタマイズの内容と手数料は失われますが、マスクスタッシュに無料で戻すことが出来ます。",--Holy shit - what is this new devilry? Humans can often recognize a human skull, even if it's only partially shown. The human brain even has a specific region for it. This doesn't look like a human skull however.$NL;$NL;You finished all heists on the OVERKILL difficulty? What are you, some kind of pit fiend? Maybe this mask will suit you after all.$NL;$NL;This mask is a difficulty reward. It can't drop during a PAYDAY and it can't be sold. Instead, it can be returned to your mask stash for free, but any pattern, color or material as well as the customization fee to put these together will be lost.
bm_msk_skulloverkill_desc_WIN32 = "なんてこった - この悪魔みてーなのは何だ?人間ってのは一部分から全体を見出すらしいが、この骸骨はもはや人間のものじゃない。$NL;$NL;どうやら君は全てのJobをOVERKILLでクリアしたらしいな。何だ、Pit Fiend何かか?たぶん、このマスクはあんたにバッチリ似合うと思うぜ$NL;$NL;このマスクは難易度全クリアによる報酬です。PAYDAYの間にドロップすることはなく売却することも出来ません。その代わりに、カスタマイズの内容と手数料は失われますが、マスクスタッシュに無料で戻すことが出来ます。",--Holy shit - what is this new devilry? Humans can often recognize a human skull, even if it's only partially shown. The human brain even has a specific region for it. This doesn't look like a human skull however.$NL;$NL;You finished all heists on the OVERKILL difficulty? What are you, some kind of pit fiend? Maybe this mask will suit you after all.$NL;$NL;This mask is a difficulty reward. It can't drop during a PAYDAY and it can't be sold. Instead, it can be returned to your mask stash for free, but any pattern, color or material as well as the customization fee to put these together will be lost.
bm_msk_skulloverkillplus = "",--The Death Wish Skull
bm_msk_skulloverkillplus_desc = "OVERKILLはお前に土下座してるぜ。死神だの、警察殺しだのってな。人間ってのは一部分から全体を見通すらしいが、こいつは人間の頭蓋骨なんかじゃねーぞ。$NL;$NL;どうやら君は全てのJobをDeath Wishでクリアしたらしいな。まったく、あんたは悪魔か何かなのか?どうせ、このマスクはあんたにピッタリ似合うと思うぜ$NL;$NL;このマスクは難易度全クリアによる報酬です。PAYDAYの間にドロップすることはなく売却することも出来ません。その代わりに、カスタマイズの内容と手数料は失われますが、マスクスタッシュに無料で戻すことが出来ます。",--OVERKILL salutes you, bringer of death, slayer of law enforcers and finisher of difficulties. Humans can often recognize a human skull, even if only partially shown. The human brain even has a specific region for it. This isn't a human skull however, this is something completely different.$NL;$NL;You finished all heists on the Death Wish difficulty? What are you, some kind of demon? Maybe this mask will suit you after all.$NL;$NL;This mask is a difficulty reward. It can't drop during a PAYDAY and it can't be sold. Instead, it can be returned to your mask stash for free, but any pattern, color or material as well as the customization fee to put these together will be lost.
bm_msk_skulloverkillplus_desc_WIN32 = "OVERKILLはお前に土下座してるぜ。死神だの、警察殺しだのってな。人間ってのは一部分から全体を見通すらしいが、こいつは人間の頭蓋骨なんかじゃねーぞ。$NL;$NL;どうやら君は全てのJobをDeath Wishでクリアしたらしいな。まったく、あんたは悪魔か何かなのか?どうせ、このマスクはあんたにピッタリ似合うと思うぜ$NL;$NL;このマスクは難易度全クリアによる報酬です。PAYDAYの間にドロップすることはなく売却することも出来ません。その代わりに、カスタマイズの内容と手数料は失われますが、マスクスタッシュに無料で戻すことが出来ます。",--OVERKILL salutes you, bringer of death, slayer of law enforcers and finisher of difficulties. Humans can often recognize a human skull, even if only partially shown. The human brain even has a specific region for it. This isn't a human skull however, this is something completely different.$NL;$NL;You finished all heists on the Death Wish difficulty? What are you, some kind of demon? Maybe this mask will suit you after all.$NL;$NL;This mask is a difficulty reward. It can't drop during a PAYDAY and it can't be sold. Instead, it can be returned to your mask stash for free, but any pattern, color or material as well as the customization fee to put these together will be lost.
bm_msk_skullveryhard = "",--The Very Hard Skull
bm_msk_skullveryhard_desc = "奇妙な人間の骸骨。人間というのは、示された一部分から全体を想像することが出来るという。人間の脳はそれだけ特別なものがあるらしい。しかし、この骸骨は奇妙な部分がある。$NL;$NL;どうやら君は全てのJobをVery Hardでクリアしたらしいな。怪物かか何かか?たぶん、このマスクはバッチリ似合うと思うぜ$NL;$NL;このマスクは難易度全クリアによる報酬です。PAYDAYの間にドロップすることはなく売却することも出来ません。その代わりに、カスタマイズの内容と手数料は失われますが、マスクスタッシュに無料で戻すことが出来ます。",--A strange thing, the human skull. Not that this skull looks that human anymore. Humans can often recognize a human skull, even if it's only partially shown. The human brain even has a specific region for it. There's something strange with this skull though.$NL;$NL;You finished all heists on the Very Hard difficulty? What are you, some kind of monster? Maybe this mask will suit you after all.$NL;$NL;This mask is a difficulty reward. It can't drop during a PAYDAY and it can't be sold. Instead, it can be returned to your mask stash for free, but any pattern, color or material as well as the customization fee to put these together will be lost.
bm_msk_skullveryhard_desc_WIN32 = "奇妙な人間の骸骨。人間というのは、示された一部分から全体を想像することが出来るという。人間の脳はそれだけ特別なものがあるらしい。しかし、この骸骨は奇妙な部分がある。$NL;$NL;どうやら君は全てのJobをVery Hardでクリアしたらしいな。怪物かか何かか?たぶん、このマスクはバッチリ似合うと思うぜ$NL;$NL;このマスクは難易度全クリアによる報酬です。PAYDAYの間にドロップすることはなく売却することも出来ません。その代わりに、カスタマイズの内容と手数料は失われますが、マスクスタッシュに無料で戻すことが出来ます。",--A strange thing, the human skull. Not that this skull looks that human anymore. Humans can often recognize a human skull, even if it's only partially shown. The human brain even has a specific region for it. There's something strange with this skull though.$NL;$NL;You finished all heists on the Very Hard difficulty? What are you, some kind of monster? Maybe this mask will suit you after all.$NL;$NL;This mask is a difficulty reward. It can't drop during a PAYDAY and it can't be sold. Instead, it can be returned to your mask stash for free, but any pattern, color or material as well as the customization fee to put these together will be lost.
bm_msk_slicer = "",--Slicer
bm_msk_slicer_desc = "",--After his brother's murder, Ikas joined an underground clan of ninjas to train and become their deadliest warrior. Ikas quickly proved himself and was put in charge of the whole American branch of the clan. His signature mask now inspires fear and respect and anyone who wears a mask like this will be seen as a brother of the Achilles Clan.
bm_msk_slimy_goat = "",--Mastermind Goat
bm_msk_slimy_goat_desc = "",--The dolphin is the most sinister and vicious heister in the animal kingdom, tricking everyone with its friendly and cute appearance. But it's all a facade! The dolphin only cares about itself and the loot, and won't hesitate a second to leave anyone behind. Caution is advised if you meet a fellow heister with this mask.
bm_msk_smiley = "",--Smiley
bm_msk_smiley_desc = "",--There was once a clown who couldn't smile. He watched as the other clowns brought joy and happiness to both young and old. He grew envious and angry, so to the point that he stapled his lips to his cheecks, giving him a wide grin. But instead of making everyone happy, they were all afraid, why, he did not understand.$NL;$NL;He came to the conclusion perhaps this was his calling, to make people afraid... Very afraid.
bm_msk_smoker = "",--The Specialist
bm_msk_smoker_desc = "真のTechnicianはこのようなマスクを作り上げるという。$NL;$NL;最先端の空気循環システムを使用しており、Methを作らねばならない科学者のマスクにも使える。$NL;$NL;このマスクはInfamyツリーの報酬です。PAYDAYの間にドロップすることはなく売却することも出来ません。その代わりに、カスタマイズの内容と手数料は失われますが、マスクスタッシュに無料で戻すことが出来ます。",--Only a true Technician could come up with a mask like this.$NL;$NL;Featuring a state of the art air filtration system, the mask can double as a chemist's hood in those unlikely "must cook meth" scenarios.$NL;$NL;This mask is an Infamy tree reward. It can't drop during a PAYDAY and it can't be sold. Instead, it can be returned to your mask stash for free, but any customization and the fee to put that together will be lost.
bm_msk_sokol = "",--Sokol
bm_msk_sokol_begins = "",--Sokol Begins
bm_msk_sokol_begins_desc = "Sokolを象徴するマスクの、まだペイントされていない無地のバージョン。$NL;$NL;まだオリジナルの様に着こなせていない? これは歴史を塗り替えるチャンスだ。",--This is a clean version of Sokol's iconic mask, before it was painted.$NL;$NL;Never liked how the original one turned out? This is your chance to change history.
bm_msk_sokol_desc = "",--If playing as a grinder for the St Petersburg Bombers hockey team taught Sokol the value of one thing, it was the importance of a terrifying mask that protects his handsome Russian face.
bm_msk_solus = "",--Planetary Tomb Guardian
bm_msk_solus_desc = "",--Being a Planetary Tomb Guardian is a lonely job. But a job that must be done. Eons of time float by without a single living organism in sight. Stars and suns brighten the day and night. But solitude is a horrid thing. But then one day, a spacecraft breaks the silence and you are not alone anymore. Someone is visiting this planet you call home.
bm_msk_spa_01 = "",--Captain
bm_msk_spa_01_desc = "",--Captain on the bridge! Guide your crew safely through the banks, and a favorable wind will lead you to great adventures. Strike the coast and take their treasure, then disappear over the horizon.
bm_msk_spa_02 = "",--Sailor
bm_msk_spa_02_desc = "",--Sail on the treasure fleet - climb the rigging and keep an eye out for pursuing ships as you scour the sea for sunken gold. If they catch up with you, abandon ship like the rat you are - but don't forget to bring the gold.
bm_msk_spa_03 = "",--Bird of Prey
bm_msk_spa_03_desc = "",--Soar high, swoop down and strike your prey with merciless, deadly claws. Then fly home to your lofty nest, enjoying the spoils of your hunt. You are the apex predator and you shall devour it all.
bm_msk_spa_04 = "",--Lady Liberty
bm_msk_spa_04_desc = "",--Liberty. Liberty for all those heisters that have fallen and been sent to prison. Liberty for all that gold which sits sadly in dark basement vaults of banks. Liberty for the spirit of enterprise, the will to take what you want, the rule of the gun. Liberty for those seeking a bigger PAYDAY.
bm_msk_spackle = "",--Spackle
bm_msk_spackle_desc = "",--Once a well renowned circus clown Spackle was the best make-up artist in the scene. Known for her skill and ability to make people look so unlike themselves, she became obsessed with the art.$NL;$NL;With her own face as canvas she tirelessly applied layer after layer, each becoming more twisted. She was sent to an asylum after killing five people during their make-up process.
bm_msk_speed_demon = "",--Speed Devil
bm_msk_speed_demon_desc = "",--What better way to symbolize the do-not-give-a-fuck attitude of the biker lifestyle, than by wearing the face of the Devil. The ultimate symbol for breaking the law.
bm_msk_speedrunner = "",--SpeedRunner
bm_msk_speedrunner_desc = "",--It's time for a speedy run! SpeedRunner is the people's champ in New Rush City. Running, sliding, swinging his way toward crime and those in need, he accepts no less than first place. SpeedRunner's got the need... for running!
bm_msk_spider = "",--Tarantula
bm_msk_spider_desc = "Tarantulaは、その八本の屈強な足を完全に伸ばした際には拳銃と同じ位に、縮めれば指の爪ぐらいのサイズに収まるような生き物だ。その名前はコモリグモ種タランチュラコモリグモ（Lycosa tarantula）から来ている。Tarantulaは一般的に、木か地表またはその近くで狩りをする。また、ペットとしても人気がある。",--Eight legs strong, tarantula sizes range from as small as a fingernail to as large as a handgun when the legs are fully extended. The name originally comes from the name Lycosa tarantula, a species of wolf spider. Tarantulas generally hunt in trees, on or near the ground. They're also popular as pets.
bm_msk_sports_utility_mask = "",--Sports Utility Mask
bm_msk_sports_utility_mask_desc = "",--Forget bulky and unfashionable helmets, this glorious sucker is the best friend of every adrenaline junkie. The face-guard is made out of tough ABS plastic and it provides solid protection against snow, sand blasts and hail drops. Just avoid heavy blows to the head. Be the envy of your airboarding friends, brah!
bm_msk_sputnik = "",--Sputnik
bm_msk_sputnik_desc = "",--Despite being just a tiny, beeping sphere, the original Sputnik sent political shock-waves across 1950's Washington. Send some criminal shock-waves around the capital with this vintage-yet-pimped version.
bm_msk_starvr = "",--StarVR
bm_msk_starvr_desc = "現実世界は不潔で不愉快でキモいです。そして、あなたは年を取りやがて死にます。しかしStarVRをつければ現実世界からおさらば!! あなたをビックリするほどリアルな仮想世界に招待します。",--Real life is dirty, uncomfortable, sticky, sweaty, stinky, it tastes bad and it leaves you old and broken. Screw that. The StarVR Headset lets you immerse yourself in a virtual world of incredible realism.
bm_msk_stoneface = "",--Terminator
bm_msk_stoneface_desc = "",--These shades belonged to an assassin from a distant land. The assassin John was sent to kill was built like a machine. This one would prove to be hard. He used a customized Improved Combined Tactical Vest. He was fully armored and very tough. Behind all that armor however, John knew there was only flesh and bones.$NL;$NL;John managed to to kill him in the end. He knew however that when he removed him from his place, another would replace him.
bm_msk_stonekisses = "",--The Pout
bm_msk_stonekisses_desc = "The pout \"ふくれっ面\" は人間が出来る表情の一つ。$NL;$NL;不機嫌や不満の表現として、唇を尖らせる。$NL;$NL;こんな感じに角を切り落とされたら誰だって不満だろう。",--The pout is a facial expression that humans can make.$NL;$NL;It is a protrusion of the lips, especially as an expression of sullen discontent.$NL;$NL;Who would not be discontent, having had their horns sawed off like that.
bm_msk_surprise = "",--War Face
bm_msk_surprise_desc = "殺すときの顔が出来るか! アアアアッ! これが殺すときの顔だ、やってみろ!$NL;$NL;...$NL;$NL;それで殺せるか! 気合を入れろ! 殺すときの顔をしろ!$NL;$NL;...よし、いいぞ...$NL;$NL;このマスクはPoetry Jamのマスクです。PAYDAYの間にドロップすることはなく売却することも出来ません。その代わりに、カスタマイズの内容と手数料は失われますが、マスクスタッシュに無料で戻すことが出来ます。",--You got a war face! AAAAAAAAHH! That's a war face, let me see your war face!$NL;$NL;...$NL;$NL;Bullshit. You didn't convince me. let me see your REAL war face!$NL;$NL;...Actually, that one's pretty good...$NL;$NL;This mask is Poetry Jam mask. It can't drop during a PAYDAY and it can't be sold. Instead, it can be returned to your mask stash for free, but any customization and the fee to put that together will be lost.
bm_msk_sweettooth = "",--Sweet Tooth
bm_msk_sweettooth_desc = "",--Sweet Tooth, real name Marcus "Needles" Kane is a character from the Twisted Metal video game series. Sweet Tooth is best known for being a killer clown that drives a combat ice cream truck.$NL;$NL;It's said that he once had escaped from a mental institution. He now leads a life of crime.
bm_msk_sydney = "",--Sydney
bm_msk_sydney_begins = "",--Sydney Begins
bm_msk_sydney_begins_desc = "Sydneyを象徴するマスクの、まだペイントされていない無地のバージョン。$NL;$NL;まだオリジナルの様に着こなせていない? これは歴史を塗り替えるチャンスだ。",--This is a clean version of Sydney's iconic mask, before it was painted.$NL;$NL;Never liked how the original one turned out? This is your chance to change history.
bm_msk_sydney_desc = "",--Smirk, Grin, Sneer - call it what you want. As you see this smiling punker mask approaching it's not synonyms that'll run through your head - it's bullets. Sydney will make sure of it.
bm_msk_tall_goat = "",--Scout Goat
bm_msk_tall_goat_desc = "",--The giraffe doesn't miss a thing, always in complete control of its surroundings, acting as the perfect "look-out" companion for heisting in the animal kingdom. Whatever it is, you'll see it coming miles away and the cops can forget to take you by surprise.
bm_msk_tane = "",--Tane
bm_msk_tane_desc = "",--Tane was the god of the forest who used his mighty strength to separate his parents, the earth and the sky. Legends also credit him with creating Tiki, the first man. Thus, he created the world as we know it, and the people within it.
bm_msk_tcn = "",--Criminal Ambitions
bm_msk_tcn_desc = "最も野心的な強盗のためのマスク。$NL;$NL;全ての金を奪い取り、去った後には何も残らない。$NL;これが真の犯罪者の印だ。$NL;全てのダイヤモンドとちょっとを盗む。$NL;あなたは今、犯罪者の野心を持つ人間だ。$NL;$NL;このマスクはPoetry Jamのマスクです。PAYDAYの間にドロップすることはなく売却することも出来ません。その代わりに、カスタマイズの内容と手数料は失われますが、マスクスタッシュに無料で戻すことが出来ます。",--A mask only for the most ambitious heister.$NL;$NL;Take all the loot, leave nothing behind.$NL;This is the sign of a true criminal mind.$NL;Grab all the diamonds and small additions.$NL;Now you're a person with criminal ambitions.$NL;$NL;This mask is Poetry Jam mask. It can't drop during a PAYDAY and it can't be sold. Instead, it can be returned to your mask stash for free, but any customization and the fee to put that together will be lost.
bm_msk_tech_lion = "",--Tech Lion
bm_msk_tech_lion_desc = "",--This mask is a modern interpretation of the Egyptian war-god Maahes. Known as the "Wield of the Knife", "Lord of Slaughter" and "Avenger of Wrongs", Maahes punished those who transgressed from the rules of Ma`at - the personification of order and balance. Considered the embodiment of the burning heat of the sun, he was also seen as a protective deity that defended the Pharaoh during battle.$NL;$NL;He is usually depicted as lion-headed man carrying a knife wearing the Atef crown, the Solar Disk or is pictured as a lion devouring a victim.
bm_msk_the_king_mask = "",--The King
bm_msk_the_king_mask_desc = "",--Mercy! Are you bad enough of a dude or dudette to rock the royal trifecta of slick aviators ,bad-ass pompadour and tactical sideburns? Summon forth the indomitable spirit of various used-car dealers and shotgun-wedding ministers all around Vegas who wore this thing all the way to success. Or at least mild public awkwardness. Hail to the king!
bm_msk_the_overkill_mask = "",--General Overkill
bm_msk_the_overkill_mask_desc = "",--Ten-shun! Right, listen up, you heisting bastards. You're heading into war. You're gonna feel the sting of battle. And in war you need a leader. Meet General Overkill. He'll be there to make sure you go through those cop bastards like crap through a goose. Dismissed!
bm_msk_the_strinch = "",--The Strinch
bm_msk_the_strinch_desc = "祭りの間に盗みを働く事で知られるThe Strinchは1957年のクリスマス以来活動している。また、1972年のハロウィーンにも盗みを働いたことがある。",--A seasoned heister over the festival period, the Strinch has been stealing Christmases since 1957. Also linked with the Halloween Heist of 1972.
bm_msk_tiara = "",--Tiara
bm_msk_tiara_desc = "",--Okay, it doesn't hide your face and it is certainly not going to stop any bullets whizzing your way....but, damn. You're going to look like the belle of the ball wearing Mrs Volkov's wedding tiara.
bm_msk_tiger = "",--Tony
bm_msk_tiger_desc = "",--Tony uses his fists of fury to beat the crap of anyone who messes with him.$NL;$NL;Tony was born in the 1970s and was of Italian-American nationality. Many people easily recognize Tony. Probably in part because of his Tiger mask, and in part because of his physical brutality when dealing with people he don't like.
bm_msk_tinted_love = "",--Tinted Love
bm_msk_tinted_love_desc = "",--Murder, extortion, violence, destruction, drugs, guns, and theft. These are all crimes associated with Vlad, but none are as great as his fashion sense.
bm_msk_titan = "",--Titan
bm_msk_titan_desc = "",--Once, they strode among us. Cyclopean beings, tall as towers. They were old, even when our primate ancestors howled at fire. Now, they are gone, and only their shades come to us in half-dreamt race memories.
bm_msk_tonys_revenge = "",--Tony's Revenge
bm_msk_tonys_revenge_desc = "",--The near-perfect predator. Tigers are immensely strong, yet fast. They are brutal, yet patient. They can stalk silently, before exploding into violence. The perfect killing machine. Despite this, the tiger is in decline. Poachers prize the tiger penis in traditional medicine. So don't get taken alive.
bm_msk_tormentor = "",--Tormentor
bm_msk_tormentor_desc = "",--A smile can hide the most murderous thought, but the eyes can never lie. Reading a person is mostly looking straight into their eyes. What's truly terrifying is people who wear their thoughts on their face and within a second it's hard for the beholder to suppress a scream.
bm_msk_tounge = "",--Mr. Smooth
bm_msk_tounge_desc = "このマスクは何らかの手段を使い相反する感情、信念、動機を表現する。$NL;$NL;伝説によれば、4体の怪物がお互いに合体し、このマスクの顔を形成したと言われている。$NL;$NL;つまるところ、このマスクはクソ怖いってことだ。",--This mask somehow simultaneously conveys and expresses opposing or contradictory feelings, beliefs, and motivations.$NL;$NL;Legend says that four creatures merged together, forming a greater entity with the face of this mask.$NL;$NL;To summarize, it is a scary fucking mask.
bm_msk_trex = "",--The Tyrannosaurus
bm_msk_triceratops = "",--Timothy
bm_msk_triceratops_desc = "",--Timothy the Triceratops is one of the most popular dinosaurs at the Jurassic High. He had a huge grudge with Teddy the Tyrannosaurus though. Even though they were massive and lived together during the last epoch of the age of dinosaurs, they couldn't find it in them to be friends. Especially not since that one time when they went to that cabin during Spring Break and Teddy and his pals pranked Timothy with that horror movie and the phone call about seven days left before the meteorite would hit. Timothy did not think that was funny at all.
bm_msk_troll = "",--The Troll
bm_msk_troll_desc = "さて、ここにあるのは疲れて橋の下で休んでいるトロールだ。$NL;$NL;代わりに世の中を見たり、村を襲ったり、宝物を奪ったり、怒れる民衆の逆襲に遭ってみてはどうだろうか。",--Now here is a troll that is tired of hiding under the bridge.$NL;$NL;Why not see the world, pillage a village, take the local inhabitants gold treasures and flee from the the angry mobs instead?
bm_msk_twitch_orc = "",--The Orc
bm_msk_twitch_orc_desc = "",--Brutish, aggressive and generally repulsive, the orcs have always been a hated race. Orcs are larger and stronger than their goblin cousins but smaller and less powerful than their ogre brethren. This particular purple-skinned orc came from the Stonetremble clan who were known for their fierce warriors and overpowered, hybrid shamans.$NL;$NL;This mask is a Humble Bundle E3 mask . It can't drop during a PAYDAY and it can't be sold. Instead, it can be returned to your mask stash for free, but any customization and the fee to put that together will be lost.
bm_msk_twitch_orc_desc_WIN32 = "",--Brutish, aggressive and generally repulsive, the orcs have always been a hated race. Orcs are larger and stronger than their goblin cousins but smaller and less powerful than their ogre brethren. This particular purple-skinned orc came from the Stonetremble clan who were known for their fierce warriors and overpowered, hybrid shamans.$NL;$NL;This mask is a Humble Bundle E3 mask . It can't drop during a PAYDAY and it can't be sold. Instead, it can be returned to your mask stash for free, but any customization and the fee to put that together will be lost.
bm_msk_unborn = "",--Unborn
bm_msk_unborn_desc = "",--A once great actor who claimed to have become possessed by a demonic spirit started to wear a mask to hide his deformed appearance. The mask one day broke and what was hiding underneath could never be sealed again.
bm_msk_unforsaken = "",--The Unforsaken
bm_msk_unforsaken_desc = "",--This legendary mask is a token of our appreciation to our community's dedication, understanding and continued support. From us in the OVERKILL crew - we salute you.$NL;$NL;Through thick and thin, let those helmets fly.
bm_msk_unic = "",--Unic
bm_msk_unic_desc = "",--Clop Clop- who's there? It's Unic! In the dark streets of New Rush City, what could shine brighter than an honest smile? Galloping in meadows, and sharing time with his friends, Unic is dedicated to showing the world's positive side. A pink leotard and purple boots make this speedy runner truly unique!
bm_msk_unicorn = "",--Peter
bm_msk_unicorn_desc = "",--Peter is a true legend and has been so for like, forever. A beast with a large, pointed, spiraling horn projected from its forehead, Peter is known by all of mankind as the go-to guy whenever you need to touch the rainbow. No, touch it. Touch the motherfucking rainbow. Now taste it.$NL;$NL;Shh. It's OK. You did good.
bm_msk_vampire = "",--The Vampire
bm_msk_vampire_desc = "ヴァンパイアは伝説に登場する不死の怪物で、生き血を餌にするという。$NL;$NL;ヴァンパイアは人間として現れる事がある。$NL;$NL;噛み付く瞬間、ヴァンパイアはその顔を変え、牙をむき出しにする。",--The Vampire is a mythological undead creature, said to feed on the blood of the living.$NL;$NL;Vampires can appear as normal humans.$NL;$NL;When attacked they will reveal their vampire visage where their face changes and they grow fangs and pointed teeth.
bm_msk_velociraptor = "",--Vincent
bm_msk_velociraptor_desc = "",--Vincent the Velociraptor and his best friend Andreas Häll Penninger the Protoceratops were out and about one day in the jungle when they got in a fight. It wasn't a big thing really but Vincent just wouldn't let it go. Andreas, being the stubborn Protoceratops he was, continued to mouth off to Vincent. Violent fighting ensued and to this day, no one is sure who actually won.
bm_msk_venomorph = "",--Venomorph
bm_msk_venomorph_desc = "",--When you see the Venomorph, you know it's game over, man. GAME OVER!$NL;Maybe you can build a fire, try sing a couple of songs.$NL;$NL;In reality, you better go back and hide, because it will be dark soon, and these babies mostly only come at night... Mostly.
bm_msk_viking = "",--The Dragon Head
bm_msk_viking_desc = "",--Mounting the prow of Viking ships, the dragon head was used to scare off sea monsters and evil spirits. Dozers and Cloakers are evil, right? Why not give it a go and see if it can scare them away? But have your gun ready just in case. For safety.
bm_msk_visor = "",--Safety First
bm_msk_visor_desc = "",--A scientist inspired by the virtual-reality sex scene in Demolition Man made his own attempt at building a device where no physical contact would actually be needed when performing intercourse. The experiment was an utter failure but a few of the early prototypes still exist.
bm_msk_vlad_armor = "",--Vlad Armor
bm_msk_vlad_armor_desc = "",--"Hey! Payday clowns! Vlad here with a little something from the Motherland. I wore this beautiful heavy bastard all through my days in Donetsk. It ain't pretty like your delicate American masks, but it kept me safe!"
bm_msk_volt = "",--Volt
bm_msk_volt_desc = "",--Being a snoopy lowlife, janitor David Davidson snuck around the military research facility he worked at, looking for something easy to steal. He found a door that he didn't have a key for. Curious, he kicked the door open and was instantly attacked by some kind of bright light. Somehow he survived the attack and got superhuman powers.$NL;$NL;With his new powers, he called himself Volt.
bm_msk_voodoo = "",--The Voodoo
bm_msk_war = "",--War
bm_msk_war_desc = "",--The second horseman of the Apocalypse is War and the violent spirit of mankind. War believes humans are naturally vicious, and that they don't require a real reason to fight or kill. He rode a fiery red horse, suggesting that blood would flow wherever he went.
bm_msk_washington = "",--The 1st
bm_msk_washington_desc = "大元帥であり、最高司令官であり、建国の父である。8年間、この偉大な国に尽くした。$NL;$NL;史上初の大統領、そして当時最高の男の1人だった。$NL;$NL;The 1stは史上最も人気のある大統領にして、1ドル札の顔である。犯罪者の中でも、彼の人気は変わらない。",--General of the Armies, Commander-In-Chief, Founding Father. Served this great nation for 8 years.$NL;$NL;The first ever president, and a great one at that.$NL;$NL;The 1st was one of the most popular presidents in history and the face of the $1 bill. Among criminals, he remains extremely popular.
bm_msk_wasp = "",--Vespula
bm_msk_wasp_desc = "二対の羽と産卵管と針、細い毛と対の鉤爪。それはお前のためのハチだ。ほぼすべての害虫種は捕食か寄生のために寄生バチを持っている。これは自然界のバランスを保つために重要だ。",--Two pairs of wings, an ovipositor or stinger, no thickened hairs and a pair of talons. That's the wasp for you. Almost every pest insect species has at least one wasp species that preys upon it or parasitizes it. This makes the wasps very important in natural control of their numbers.
bm_msk_water_spirit = "",--Tawhiri
bm_msk_water_spirit_desc = "",--Brother of Tane, Tawhiri is the god of weather, most particularly violent storms and lightning. Bodhi experienced plenty of both, and it was during a particularly vicious explosion while reef-diving in Tuvalu that Bodhi gained a true appreciation for this powerful deity.
bm_msk_wayfarer = "",--Reservoir Dog
bm_msk_wayfarer_desc = "",--These shades belonged to five strangers. John was hired to kill a group of people who were about to commit the perfect crime. They all dressed the same and had code names so they were easy to identify.$NL;$NL;However, John arrived too late to the scene. The police were already there. He made sure the strangers were all dead before he left the scene.
bm_msk_welder = "",--The Butcher
bm_msk_welder_desc = "Enforcerのための伝統的なマスク。$NL;$NL;ピンクパンサー·ギャングの最高のメンバーのために作ったと言われているが、本人にそれを付ける勇気がなかったらしい。このマスクはとても目立つからな。$NL;$NL;君はそうじゃ無い事を祈っているよ。$NL;$NL;このマスクはInfamyツリーの報酬です。PAYDAYの間にドロップすることはなく売却することも出来ません。その代わりに、カスタマイズの内容と手数料は失われますが、マスクスタッシュに無料で戻すことが出来ます。",--A truly legendary Enforcer mask.$NL;$NL;The story goes it was made for one of the premier hitters in the Pink Panther crew years back but he didn't have the guts to wear it. It'd draw too much attention.$NL;$NL;Not your concern.$NL;$NL;This mask is an Infamy tree reward. It can't drop during a PAYDAY and it can't be sold. Instead, it can be returned to your mask stash for free, but any customization and the fee to put that together will be lost.
bm_msk_white_wolf = "",--Dennis
bm_msk_white_wolf_desc = "",--Dennis loves knives.$NL;$NL;The gray wolf is one of the best known and well researched animals on the entire planet. It was the first animal and only large carnivore to be domesticated by humans.$NL;$NL;Today, there's only one third of the population left because of human persecution.
bm_msk_witch = "",--Witch
bm_msk_witch_desc = "",--A witch is someone practicing black witchcraft, often with the aid of a devil or familiar.$NL;$NL;It can be anything from an ugly old hag to a charming, alluring woman.$NL;$NL;And then you have the broom, the hat and all that. Boo.
bm_msk_wmp_01 = "",--The Survivor's Pilot Hat
bm_msk_wmp_01_desc = "",--A pilot in the Royal Air Force went down during WW2 a few miles outside Bialystok, Poland. Considered K.I.A, he was later found deep in the Bialowieza Forest where he'd survived on fish, roots and animals he managed to caught - alive and well but madness had sunk his teeth into him. He'd been forced to amputate his left leg. But still managed to survive without infections. A small hut was also found, together with salvaged parts from his aircraft. He was found in 1978.
bm_msk_wmp_02 = "",--The Trophy Helmet
bm_msk_wmp_02_desc = "",--In the small village of Pomtsburg, you can find a small monument. Few read the plaque covered with moss, but it holds the tale of a young boy. As the Germans came marching into Pomtsburg he lead the resistance with bravery and determination. Pomtsburg was his birthplace and no one were to destroy it. The Battle of Pomtsburg never reached the history books, and few even remember how it ended. But the boy managed to steal this souvenir. Something to remind him and others that you shall always stand up to oppression.
bm_msk_wmp_03 = "",--A Proud Pilotka
bm_msk_wmp_03_desc = "",--This pilotka was found on a corpse near Lake Müritz in Germany. It was attached with a string around the poor, dead soldier's head. There were no other bodies next to unnamed fellow, and as the origin of the pilotka was russian, it's fair to assume that he stemmed from the same country. Speculations were many, none were true, but the most inspiring story was the one about a soldier so proud of the motherland that he tied his pilotka to his head before he died.
bm_msk_wmp_04 = "",--The Officer's Hat
bm_msk_wmp_04_desc = "",--This item popped up at an auction in North France during the 1990s. Among the auction goers sat a woman in her 50s. She recognized it and even though she could not remember the name of the officer who wore it, she paid a hefty sum for it. As a young girl she visited a square to buy vegetables when paratroopers came dropping down. Gunfire, explosions and screams of fear and pain filled the air. The officer took her to a shelter in a government building. He had no reason but kindness to save her. But even as his life was on stake, he risked it to save hers. She was just a young girl, but still recognized the hat.
bm_msk_wolf = "",--Wolf
bm_msk_wolf_clean = "",--Wolf Begins
bm_msk_wolf_clean_desc = "Wolfを象徴するマスクの、まだペイントされていない無地のバージョン。$NL;$NL;まだオリジナルの様に着こなせていない? これは歴史を塗り替えるチャンスだ。",--This is a clean version of the iconic Wolf mask, before it was painted.$NL;$NL;Never liked how the original one turned out? This is your chance to change history.
bm_msk_wolf_desc = "Wolfのマスク。",--The mask of Wolf.
bm_msk_wolf_glow = "",--Mega Wolf
bm_msk_wolf_glow_desc = "Mega Wolfマスクは、元のマスクが進化したものだ。そしてこれは、超越と浄化を象徴するものなのだ。$NL;$NL;応援ありがとう。$NL;$NL;OVERKILLより敬意を!",--The Mega Wolf mask is an evolved version of the original mask. It symbolises transcendence and catharsis.$NL;$NL;Thank you for your support.$NL;$NL;OVERKILL salutes you!
bm_msk_yor = "",--Fire Rooster
bm_msk_yor_desc = "",--You're a reliable firestarter, always on time and always on target. As the new year begins, you will set your sights on that shining gold, the most noble metal of them all. Your motives may be shady, but seven is magnificent and before you know it you'll be high-fiving to celebrate that perfect heist. Maybe you'll finally get that eight-ball tattoo.
bm_msk_zipper = "",--The Zipper
bm_msk_zipper_desc = "The Zipperマスクはスライドによって分離·結合が可能な平行な二つの歯のレールによって構成されている。$NL;$NL;もし会話する必要が出来たら、そのジッパーを開こう。",--The zipper mask consists of two parallel tracks of teeth that can be interlocked or separated by the pulling of a slide between them.$NL;$NL;Separate the zipper when you need to communicate.
bm_msk_zombie = "",--The Zombie
bm_msk_zombie_desc = "Zombieは、何らかの方法で蘇った、動きまわる死体だ。$NL;$NL;ブレェェェイン?",--A zombie is an animated corpse that somehow has been brought to life again.$NL;$NL;Brains?
bm_msl_sds_01 = "",--Lust
bm_msl_sds_01_desc = "",--You lock your eyes on your prize until they water. Unattended, your slacking jaw lets slip a drop of saliva onto the floor as the need for possession takes over. The person you pine for is an object, the object is a person. It matters not, to your blinded senses.
bm_msl_sds_02 = "",--Sloth
bm_msl_sds_02_desc = "",--Why bother? Let the universe expand, die and grow dark. You have endless time to lift your fingers in protest at whatever mindless chore that demands you exert yourself in the slightest. Your life energy oozes from your soul, wasted and dissolved in the emptiness as you remain perpetually drained of ambition.
bm_msl_sds_03 = "",--Envy
bm_msl_sds_03_desc = "",--It isn't fair, is it? There you stand, deserving of everything in life and the cosmos refuse to give unto you. The Others smile and dance, while you twist inward, wondering why no one has gifted you with whatever success everyone else has been given for free. Oh, you want it so, but how could you ever dare to take it?
bm_msl_sds_04 = "",--Wrath
bm_msl_sds_04_desc = "",--There is a cold fire in your heart. All those who have wronged you will pay. If you so have to burn with them in the conflagration, you will extract payment for any perceived or actual slight against your person. There is no rationality to your rage- it must simply be indulged.
bm_msl_sds_05 = "",--Pride
bm_msl_sds_05_desc = "",--You are unbreakable. The ship is filling with water, but you refuse to move. Such are your principles that you would rather go into the deep with a failing institution than admit your folly and admit yourself as fallible as your peers. Justice is what you deem it to be, and damned be those who would oppose your righteous wisdom.
bm_msl_sds_06 = "",--Gluttony
bm_msl_sds_06_desc = "",--There it is, your unquenchable need to stuff your face and fill your belly with the ravaging furor of someone in a constant state of starvation. And when you stop, it's like a gaping hole opens up in the pit of your stomache, craving to be satiated.
bm_msl_sds_07 = "",--Greed
bm_msl_sds_07_desc = "",--More is never enough. No amount of gold or treasure can satisfy you. It's all about obtaining the next pile of needless wealth to add to your bloated coffers, be they spiritual or physical. The plights of your fellows matter are inconsequential if you can gain from their suffering.
bm_paycheck_chains = "",--Paycheck Chains
bm_paycheck_chains_desc = "",--Paycheck Chains longs to be completely bonkers. But truth to be told, behind that mask he's just a regular guy trying to make an indecent living. When trying to push his normal self into craziness, he took a poodle hostage during a robbery when a police showed up. What crazy person would do that, right? But he picked the wrong vicious mongrel to mess with. The dog ended up biting everyone in the crew before they managed to escape the beast. News report after the robbery claimed the dog showed symptoms of rabies. Maybe Paycheck Chains will finally become as crazy as he wants to be...
bm_paycheck_dallas = "",--Paycheck Dallas
bm_paycheck_dallas_desc = "",--Paycheck Dallas finally made the decision to stop using black plastic bags for concealment. He gathered the nerve to order a real Dallas-mask to honor his idol, but that online printing service didn't exactly deliver the real deal... Even so, with the mask, he's trying to step up his game and convinced the Paycheck gang to raid a china shop. The CCTV footage shows that Paycheck Dallas accidentally broke the biggest vase while storming in. That made him apologize to the owner, grab all small changes from register and run for the door. Probably blushing like a tomato behind that smiling neon mask.
bm_sad_seal = "",--The Awkward Seal
bm_sad_seal_desc = "",--That moment when you're going to finish off a Dozer but when you pull the trigger you're out of ammo. Or that moment when you're throwing the last bag straight into the sea. Or that moment when other robbers give you compliments about your mask but you didn't put any effort into it. Or that moment when someone is repairing the drill the same time as you.
bm_sfm_01 = "",--Exalted
bm_sfm_01_desc = "",--Cold and unmoving, you watch them from above. They shall envy your majesty as your golden gaze falls on them, an undeserved blessing on these wretched soft ones. You unite the hard chill of the night with the dazzling radiance of the sun. Glorious, golden and beautiful, you shall turn their heads mad with desire - and it shall be their undoing.
bm_sfm_02 = "",--Golden Hour
bm_sfm_02_desc = "",--Timothy Miller dreamt of working with movie lightning when he grew up. For a Halloween-party, he created the Golden Hour mask. But when he put it on and looked in the mirror, his eyes stared back surrounded by the perfect soft, red glow of the sunset. In that moment, a new dream was born. He wanted people to view the serenity of the sunset close-up, wanted it imprinted on their retina forever. The only thing the coroner could confirm was that all victims were killed shortly before sunset, their eyes always left wide open.
bm_sfm_03 = "",--Barrori Flex
bm_sfm_03_desc = "",--The day Chad got the Barrori Flex sunglasses, everything changed.They gave him a brand new perspective on what's important in life. Looking cool and blase became his purpose, his reason to live. With his Italian sports coat, beige linen pants and loafers he caught jealous looks and turned necks wherever he went. But it couldn't last and when Chad's beauty faded so did his will to live. He made a good-looking corpse, best clothes on, when he swallowed a whole can of diet pills.
bm_sfm_04 = "",--Panthera Tigris
bm_sfm_04_desc = "",--The rage of the tiger is legendary, and the king of the jungle will not be contained willingly. They may think they have you under control, but hell hath no fury like a caged tiger. As you break out, they will come to know this. Claws will rip and teeth will tear, flesh from bone, as you claim your kingdom.
bm_sha_01 = "",--Ameonna
bm_sha_01_desc = "",--Mighty horned demon. Vengeful, weeping destroyer. Do not arouse her anger.
bm_sha_02 = "",--Co-Cop Ninja
bm_sha_02_desc = "",--Strike fast, strike hard, strike silently. You will leave even the cloakers sulking in shame.
bm_sha_03 = "",--Thorntail
bm_sha_03_desc = "",--Be an aggressive, merciless, swarming menace. As you roll into town, death follows in the form of fire.
bm_sha_04 = "",--Hata Mari
bm_sha_04_desc = "",--A fast and agile killer, sending blades flying through the air. Always ready to strike. A popular killer with many fans.
bm_sm_wish = "",--The Death Sentence Skull
bm_sm_wish_desc = "",--DEMON! The Humans can often recognize a human skull, even if it's only partially shown. The human brain even has a specific region for it. This is definitely not a human skull anymore. This is what happens when you summon your demonic powers to get good.$NL;$NL;We at OVERKILL are surprised, baffled and genuinely impressed. You did it. You are among a certain few who stuck with it and actually finished the hardest difficulty we could think of. You fought, you suffered and you persevered. You have our eternal respect, you ruler of demons.
bm_sparkle_party = "",--Party Hat
bm_sparkle_party_desc = "",--Party hats never get old. It's an essential accessory to any fun event, be it a festivity of misdeeds or a celebration of moving into a new home. Strap one on and loosen that tie. It's party time. Excellent.
bm_wolf_rising = "",--Risen Wolf Mask
bm_wolf_rising_desc = "",--The sheer sight is enough to drive an opponent into madness. As if made of blood and old bones, it's like a second skin on your face. Always listen to choir of voices in the back of your head. The ones that keep telling you of all the destructive things you should be doing. Succumb to the temptation, relish in your own insanity. This time, do not hold back. Not for anything. This time, drive any foes into your own roaming and frothing madness. Become the demon you truly are, cause you've been to hell and you liked it. It's pointless to hold back, the only soothing is to feel an enemy's blood gently trickle down your lips.
bm_zeal_mask = "",--Dark Legion
bm_zeal_mask_desc = "",--He did not exist, not officially. Not since he came aboard Zeal, the top-secret strike force. He was always the last resort, deployed when extreme violence was needed. He never held back. For every operation, he lost a bit of his humanity. For every operation, he gained an edge as an instrument of death. He did not separate right from wrong, not anymore. Only obeyed the orders from above. Just one shadow in the dark legion of secret super soldiers. One day, he woke up and could only think of killing others. He had finally found his true purpose.
