bm_melee_fists = "",--Fists
bm_melee_fists_desc = "",--You're no boxer, but you can still throw a pretty good punch. All it takes is some strength, speed and timing and you'll land a striking blow in no-time.$NL;$NL;You can charge your punch in order to deal more damage by holding the melee button.
