bm_melee_switchblade = "",--Switchblade
bm_melee_switchblade_desc = "50年代にニューヨークの2つのティーンエイジギャングが傷をつけあうためによく使用されていました。一緒に歌うことさえできますよ。",--Commonly used for settling the score between two New York teenage street gangs in the fifties. You can even sing along.
bm_melee_sword = "",--The Pen
bm_melee_sword_desc = "",--Sharp, accurate and with high concealment, the Pen is your best friend when everything is depleted, and you want to puncture an aorta.
bm_melee_taser = "",--Buzzer
bm_melee_taser_desc = "これを待ち続けていたことでしょう。スイートで、エレクトリックな復讐をキザなTazer達にしてやりましょう。電撃をくらえ!",--This is the one you have been waiting for. Exact sweet, electrifying revenge against those smug tasers. Eat it, lightning bolt!
bm_melee_taser_info = "触れた相手を感電させて動けなくするデバイス",--Device that electrocutes and interrupts targets on touch
bm_melee_tenderizer = "",--Tenderizer
bm_melee_tiger = "",--Talons
bm_melee_tiger_desc = "どうして複数持つことが出来るのにひとつの刃で納得するの?",--Why settle with one blade when you can have multiple?
bm_melee_tomahawk = "",--Survival Tomahawk
bm_melee_tomahawk_desc = "",--Historically used as a general purpose tool, for throwing at people and the occasional hand-to-hand melee. A weapon with which almost any crook can attain some degree of proficiency. Only through proper heisting can one begin to realize the full potential of the tomahawk as both a tool and weapon. But mostly weapon.$NL;$NL;This weapon can be charged to deal more damage by holding the melee button.
bm_melee_toothbrush = "",--Nova's Shank
bm_melee_topaz = "",--Ice Pick
bm_melee_twins = "",--Okinawan Style Sai
bm_melee_twins_desc = "琉球の役人が使っていたサイは強盗の時にも攻撃と防御に使える。攻撃に対して反撃をおこなうのに完璧な道具です。",--Used by Okinawan Law enforcers, the Sai could be offensive and defensive, and when heisting it's an perfect tool for dealing out quick blows to any opposition.
bm_melee_weapon = "",--Weapon Butt
bm_melee_weapon_desc = "武装した強盗たちの間では通常、銃器で被害者を殴りつける行為は、発砲したり刺したりするよりも慣用的です。通常は、ライフルで銃床打撃かピストルの銃把打撃を使うでしょう。$NL;$NL;これは最も速い近接攻撃です。",--In armed robberies, beating the victims with firearms is usually more common than to shoot or stab them. You usually either Buttstroke someone with a rifle or Pistol-whip them with a handgun.$NL;$NL;This is the quickest melee attack.
bm_melee_whiskey = "",--Rivertown Glen Bottle
bm_melee_wing = "",--Wing Butterfly Knife
bm_melee_x46 = "",--X-46 Knife
bm_melee_sap = "",--Leather Sap
bm_melee_zeus = "",--Electrical Brass Knuckles
bm_melee_zeus_info = "触れた相手を感電させて行動不能にさせるデバイス",--Device that electrocutes and interrupts targets on touch
bm_ability_chico_injector = "",--Injector
bm_ability_chico_injector_desc = "",--When consumed the user cease to feel pain and become fearless. The lack of pain let the user rampage through the heart of battles longer than any other and the lack of fear make him a frightening and obvious threat for his enemies.
bm_dynamite = "",--Dynamite
bm_dynamite_desc = "スウェーデンの発明家、アルフレッド·ノーベルは、岩すら破壊できるダイナマイトを発明しました。しかし、ダイナマイトの有効性を発見したのは彼ではなく、人々をダイナマイトでブッ飛ばした酔っ払いの探鉱者のケネス老人でした。",--Swedish engineer, Alfred Nobel, discovered dynamite and its effectiveness in blasting rock. But it was drunk prospector, Ol' Kenneth, who discovered its effectiveness in blasting people.
bm_grenade_dada_com = "",--Matryoshka Grenade
bm_grenade_dada_com_desc = "",--The Matryoshka Grenade is a throwable explosive device. The doll's outer layers hides its inner workings. Creates substantial damage at the same time as it pays tribute to the motherland.
bm_grenade_tag_team = "",--Gas Dispenser
bm_grenade_tag_team_desc = "",--A small gas dispenser that temporarily enhance the body's senses and provide a healing effect for two allies.
bm_grenade_damage_control = "",--Stoic's Hip Flask
bm_grenade_damage_control_desc = "",--An antique flask from 1882 bearing the inscription \"Stoic\" and \"JW Spirits\", given to Duke in his youth when he trained with Buddhist monks. Duke keeps it filled with his favorite whiskey; taking a swig is a symbolic gesture of calming and gives the bearer a moment of zen-like focus, easing away damage.
bm_grenade_fir_com = "",--Incendiary Grenade
bm_grenade_fir_com_desc = "",--The Incendiary Grenade is a nasty self igniting phosphorus container. It ignites after a few seconds, making it perfect for bouncing off walls towards your enemies. Upon ignition it causes serious damage - setting enemies ablaze.
bm_grenade_frag = "",--Frag Grenade
bm_grenade_frag_com = "",--HEF Grenade
bm_grenade_frag_com_desc = "この手榴弾は、伝統的な手榴弾の改良版です。手榴弾も現役の武器ですが、この新しく滑らかなデザインは、\"OVERKILL\"な爆発をしてくれるでしょう。安っぽいですが、効果に安っぽさはありません。",--This is an updated version of the classic hand grenade. Even though the original frag grenade is still in use, this new sleek design will provide that OVERKILL touch to each blast. Still as cheap and still as effective.
bm_grenade_frag_desc = "手榴弾は、発明されてから殆ど変化がありません。安価な武器ですが、その効果には伊達ではなく、投擲後の爆発で破片を拡散させ、相手の肉体や骨、防具を貫通し切り裂きます。",--The frag grenade is a concept that has changed little from its inception. It is a thrown casing that explodes, sending shards and splinters away with such force they can slice through flesh, bone and light armor. Cheap and effective.
bm_grenade_molotov = "",--Molotov Cocktail
bm_grenade_molotov_desc = "火炎瓶は、恐らく投擲武器として扱われる物の中で、最もシンプルな武器でありながら、安価で手軽なおかつ強力です。割れやすいビンに、可燃性の液体と導線変わりのボロキレが入ったもので、それ以上でもそれ以下でもありません。",--The Molotov cocktail is perhaps the simplest weapon that can call itself a grenade. Nothing more than a breakable bottle of flammable liquid with a 'fuse' replaced by a burning rag. It is cheap, simple and highly effective.
bm_grenade_smoke_screen_grenade = "",--Smoke Bomb
bm_grenade_smoke_screen_grenade_desc = "",--Drop one of these and you'll vanish in a cloud of smoke, leaving your enemies struggling to take aim at you. Dodging bullets is a piece of cake when they can't see you properly.
bm_wpn_prj_ace = "",--Ace of Spades
bm_wpn_prj_ace_desc = "カード投げは、一般的にマジシャンがステージを横切ってスイカを割る場面を連想させますが、ナタの重さとカミソリの切れ味を加えてやることで、静音殺傷兵器になります。これらの鋼のエースの一つを袖の下に持っていれば、あなたはどんな状況でも常に自分でカードを配れる準備ができているということです。$NL;$NL;\"スペードのエース\"はPAYDAY2の2周年を記念してコミュニティで配布された無料の投擲武器です!",--Throwing cards are generally associated with magicians splitting watermelons across a stage, but add weight and razor edges and you have a silent killer. Have one of these steel aces in your sleeves and you will always be ready to deal yourself into the game, regardless of the circumstances.$NL;$NL;The Ace of Spades is a free throwable given to the community to celebrate two years of PAYDAY 2!
bm_wpn_prj_four = "",--Shuriken
bm_wpn_prj_four_desc = "使用者の手の中に隠された剣のように、Shurikenは完璧な静音の凶器である。はじめは釘や針で作られていた、投げる星型のこの武器は血と戦いに満ちた長い歴史を持っている。これらのステンレス鋼で出来た近代的な星型は、あなたの前に立ちはだかる如何なるものにも致命的な脅威をもたらし、そしてあなたがそれらを見つけることさえできれば、あなたを止めるものは存在しないだろう。$NL;$NL;Shurikenには毒が塗られていて、時間をかけてダメージを与え続け、敵の行動を妨害するチャンスがある。",--Like a sword hidden in the user's hand the shuriken is a deadly weapon and perfectly silent. First made of nails and needles, the throwing star has had a long history filled with blood and battle. These modern stars of stainless steel will pose a lethal threat to anyone in front of you, and as long as you can find them there will be no stopping you.$NL;$NL;The Shurikens have been coated in poison which deals damage over time and has a chance to interrupt enemies.
bm_wpn_prj_hur = "",--Throwing Axe
bm_wpn_prj_hur_desc = "",--A sharp axe is never wrong, and as this one is especially good when throwing, it got popular amongst bikers. Riding a bike, can sometimes be dangerous, and you need some \"protection\". So this sporting axe suddenly ran out of stock as bikers found it extra handy for highway battles.
bm_wpn_prj_jav = "",--Javelin
bm_wpn_prj_jav_desc = "ジャベリンの起源は遠い昔に忘れられている。実のところ、誰かの1日を無駄にして尖らせた先端をくっつけた投げる棒である。単純な構造に反して、その扱いにはかなりの技量が必要だ。",--With its origins lost in murky pre-history, the javelin is a simple weapon. After all, it's a thrown stick with a pointy end that ruins someone's day. Despite this simplicity, it still requires skill and strength to use.
bm_wpn_prj_target = "",--Throwing Knife
bm_wpn_prj_target_desc = "",--A solid backup plan and a reliable tactic for a precise and silent kill. The Throwing Knife has been present in martial history for as long as people grew tired of throwing objects in a general direction and wanted a reliable weapon instead.
bm_armor_level_1 = "",--Two-piece Suit
bm_armor_level_1_desc = "移動速度減少:無し / 発見リスク増加:無し$NL;$NL;標準的なビジネススーツで自惚れている犯罪者なら着るべきだ。$NL;$NL;防弾性は皆無だが高い隠密性を持ち、発見されたくない場合や群集に紛れ込みたい場合において最適である。$NL;$NL;通常、このスーツは結婚式や葬式、ついでに銀行強盗といった特別な出来事を行う際に予約されている。",--No movement penalty, no visibility.$NL;$NL;This is the standard two-piece suit that any self-respecting criminal should wear.$NL;$NL;It provides no extra protection but has the highest concealment factor, making it the best choice for a heist where you want to go undetected and blend into the crowd.$NL;$NL;Suits are usually reserved for special occasions, such as weddings, funerals and bank robberies.
bm_armor_level_2 = "",--Lightweight Ballistic Vest
bm_armor_level_2_desc = "移動速度減少:極小 / 発見リスク増加:低$NL;$NL;Lightweight Ballistic Vestは着用が容易で比較的隠密性のある防弾ベストだ。スーツの下に着込むライナーとしては防弾性能を持ち、気軽に身を守るには丁度良いだろう。$NL;$NL;政府高官やVIP、執行権のある航空機警乗警察官、外交官のSPがよく着用している。",--Little movement penalty, low visibility.$NL;$NL;The lightweight ballistic vest is easy to wear, concealable bullet proof vest. It offers a specially developed trauma liner which provides effective blunt trauma protection, making it a good choice to protect yourself.$NL;$NL;Lightweight ballistic vests are used by dignitaries and VIP's, sky marshals as well as executive and diplomatic security professionals.
bm_armor_level_3 = "",--Ballistic Vest
bm_armor_level_3_desc = "移動速度減少:極小 / 発見リスク増加:低$$NL;$NL;Ballistic vestは胴体用の標準的な軽量防弾ベストだ。低威力のハンドガンやショットガンに対して有効で、銃撃戦を行う上で必要不可欠な防弾性能を持つ。$NL;$NL;Ballistic vestは武装した警察官や警備員、ボディガードがよく着用している。",--Little movement penalty, low visibility.$NL;$NL;The ballistic vest is a standard issue bullet-resistant soft vest that is worn on the torso. It offers good protection from small-caliber handgun and shotgun projectiles, making it essential for anyone in the line of fire.$NL;$NL;Ballistic vests are used by police forces, security guards and bodyguards.
bm_armor_level_4 = "",--Heavy Ballistic Vest
bm_armor_level_4_desc = "移動速度減少:小 / 発見リスク増加:中$NL;$NL;Heavy ballistic vestは防弾ベストの胴回りを硬いプレートで補強したものだ。$NL;$NL;肩当付きの防弾ベストと脇の保護装甲の組み合わせで高い防弾性を誇る現代的な防具である。$NL;$NL;Heavy ballistic vestは多くの兵士や警察の作戦部隊、人質救出部隊で運用されている。",--Small movement penalty, medium visibility.$NL;$NL;The heavy ballistic vest is a hard-plate reinforced vest that is worn on the torso. It is a modern body armor combining a ballistic vest with shoulder and side protection armor components, making it a great protection of choice.$NL;$NL;Heavy ballistic vests are worn by soldiers, police tactical units, and hostage rescue teams.
bm_armor_level_5 = "",--Flak Jacket
bm_armor_level_5_desc = "移動速度減少:中 / 発見リスク増加:中$NL;$NL;Flak jacketはGensec Security Industriesが従来の防弾ベストに近代改修を施したものだ。銃弾による衝撃や爆発の破片を吸収する。$NL;$NL;肩当付きの重い防弾ベストと脇の保護装甲の構成となっており、脊柱も防御することが出来る。$NL;$NL;Flak jacketは海兵隊や戦闘員、Gensec FTSU task forcesで運用されている。",--Medium movement penalty, medium visibility.$NL;$NL;The flak jacket by Gensec Security Industries is a modern take on the classic version. It absorbs the impact from firearm projectiles and shrapnel from explosions.$NL;$NL;It combines a heavy ballistic vest with shoulder and side protection armor components, offering spine protection as well.$NL;$NL;Flak jackets are worn by Marines, combat soldiers and Gensec FTSU task forces.
bm_armor_level_6 = "",--Combined Tactical Vest
bm_armor_level_6_desc = "移動速度減少:中 / 発見リスク増加:大$NL;$NL;Combined Tactical Vestは、現代戦での要望を受け開発されたタクティカルベストだ。高防弾性素材を使用しており、弾薬や無線機等の重装備の携行も想定して設計されている。$NL;$NL;Combined tactical vestは、世界中の兵士や特殊部隊など組織化された部隊に配備されている。",--Medium movement penalty, high visibility.$NL;$NL;The combined tactical vest was developed due to the challenges of modern warfare. It is made of high performance ballistic materials and is designed to carry heavy loads, such as ammo pouches, radios and other accessories. $NL;$NL;Combined tactical vests are worn by soldiers, special forces and other organized military units across the world.
bm_armor_level_7 = "",--Improved Combined Tactical Vest
bm_armor_level_7_desc = "移動速度減少:大 / 発見リスク増加:大$NL;着用条件:スキル\"IRON MAN\"のACEを所持$NL;$NL;Improved combined tactical vestは、Gensecの試作品を強奪したタクティカルベストだ。アーマーの素材にWhite Mesaの技術を応用して開発されている。$NL;$NL;金属プレートと強く結びつき、完全にフィットした結合繊維層は特殊な変形をし、爆発の衝撃を軽減する。$NL;$NL;要するに文句なしの防御性能を持つ。$NL;$NL;注意:この防具を着用したまま、スキル\"IRON MAN\"のACEを外すと強制的にアーマーが外れ、Two-piece Suitを着用した状態になります。",--Large movement penalty, high visibility.$NL;$NL;The improved combined tactical vest is a stolen experimental prototype made by Gensec Security Industries.$NL;$NL;Based on White Mesa technology it uses both soft and hard armor solutions. The perfectly fitted interlocking fiber layers tightly woven together with metal plates are specially angled to deflect projectiles and shield from explosions. In short, it provides complete protection.
bm_equipment_ammo_bag = "",--Ammo Bag
bm_equipment_ammo_bag_desc = "Ammo Bagは、予備弾薬が詰まった携帯用の$NL;カバンです。$NL;$NL;使用するには$BTN_USE_ITEM;を長押しして地面に設置する必要があります。1度設置すると回収や移動させられませんが、あなたとあなたのクルーは$BTN_INTERACT;を長押しすると、現在している銃の弾薬を補充出来ます。$NL;$NL;Ammo Bagの弾薬には限りがあり、使い切る$NL;と消滅します。残りの量はAmmo Bagの減り$NL;具合で判断出来ます。",--To use the Ammo Bag, you place it by holding $BTN_USE_ITEM;. Once placed it cannot be moved, but it can be used by you and your crew by holding $BTN_INTERACT; to gain more ammunition. It can fully replenish the ammunition of one your weapons 4 times. When the Ammo Bag is depleted, it will disappear. You can see how many uses are left by looking at the Ammo Bag. $NL;$NL;The ammo bag is a portable bag, originally intended to allow soldiers to carry extra ammunition with them into combat.
bm_equipment_armor_kit = "",--Armor Bag
bm_equipment_armor_kit_desc = "Armor Bagは、あなたが選んだアーマーを$NL;Heistに持っていくための携帯用のカバンです。$NL;$NL;使用するには$BTN_USE_ITEM;を長押しして着替える必要があります。使用するまでは、あなたはTwo-piece Suitを着用します。$NL;$NL;アーマーに着替えた地点でArmor Bagは消滅$NL;し、Two-piece Suitに戻すことはできなくな$NL;ります。",--To use the Armor Bag, hold $BTN_USE_ITEM; to put on your equipped armor. Until that, you will wear the Two-piece Suit.$NL;$NL;The armor bag has only one use and when it is consumed, it disappears. The Armor Bag is a portable bag used to transport an armor of your choice, that can be used during a heist.
bm_equipment_bodybags_bag = "",--Body Bag Case
bm_equipment_bodybags_bag_desc = "Body Bag Caseは殺害した死体を袋詰めし、$NL;移動させるためのBody bagが複数入った$NL;カバンです。$NL;$NL;使用するには$BTN_USE_ITEM;を長押しして地面に設置する必要があります。1度設置すると回収や移動させられませんが、あなたとあなたのクルーは$BTN_INTERACT;を長押ししてBody bagを補充出来ます。$NL;$NL;Body Bag Caseには限りがあり、数回消費し$NL;た時点で消滅します。残り使用回数はBody Bag Caseの減り具合を見ると判断できます。",--To use the Body Bag Case, you place it by holding $BTN_USE_ITEM;. Once placed, it cannot be moved, but it can be used by you and your crew by holding $BTN_INTERACT; to gain a body bag.$NL;$NL;The Body Bag Case has limited uses. You can see how many uses are left by looking at the Body Bag Case. The Body Bag Case carries additional bags, used for the transportation of corpses during stealth.
bm_equipment_doctor_bag = "",--Doctor Bag
bm_equipment_doctor_bag_desc = "Doctor Bagは、医者達が医療品を運ぶ際に$NL;使用する携帯用のカバンです。$NL;$NL;使用するには$BTN_USE_ITEM;を長押しして地面に設置する必要があります。1度設置すると回収や移動させられませんが、あなたとあなたのクルーは$BTN_INTERACT;を長押ししてヘルスとダウン回数を回復出来ます。$NL;$NL;Doctor Bagには限りがあり、数回消費した$NL;時点で消滅します。残り使用回数はDoctor Bagの減り具合を見ると判断できます。",--To use the doctor bag, you need to place it by holding $BTN_USE_ITEM;. Once placed it cannot be moved, but it can be used by you and your crew by holding $BTN_INTERACT; to regain health. Using the doctor bag will reset the amount of times the player can get downed before going into custody. It can only be used twice.$NL;$NL;When the Doctor Bag is consumed, it disappears. You can see how many uses are left by looking at the Doctor Bag. $NL;$NL;The Doctor Bag is a portable bag, usually used by a physician or other medical profession to transport medical supplies and medicine.
bm_equipment_ecm_jammer = "",--ECM Jammer
bm_equipment_ecm_jammer_desc = "ECM Jammerはレーダー等の検知システムの$NL;機能を阻害するために作られた電子機器です。$NL;$NL;使用するには$BTN_USE_ITEM;を長押しして設置する必要があります。1度設置すると回収や移動させられません。$NL;$NL;また、ジャミングモード中か、ジャミングモードが切れた後のECM Jammerに$BTN_INTERACT;を$NL;押すと、ジャミングモードからフィードバックモードに切り替わり、周囲の敵を無力化することがあります。ジャミングモードとフィードバックモードはともに効果時間が切れると動作を停止します。",--To use the ECM Jammer, you need to place it by holding $BTN_USE_ITEM;. Once placed it cannot be moved and it will be active for 20 seconds.$NL;$NL;You can toggle the ECM Jammer by pressing $BTN_INTERACT;. The ECM Jammer then has a chance to incapacitate your enemies within a certain radius. When consumed, it stops working.$NL;$NL;An Electronic Countermeasure (ECM) is an electronic device designed to trick radar, sonar and other detection systems, easing your way towards your goal.
bm_equipment_first_aid_kit = "",--First Aid Kit
bm_equipment_first_aid_kit_desc = "First Aid Kitは、応急処置を行うための消耗品$NL;です。$NL;$NL;使用するには$BTN_USE_ITEM;を長押しして地面に設置する必要があります。1度設置すると回収や移動させられませんが、あなたとあなたのクルーは$BTN_INTERACT;を長押ししてヘルスを回復出来ます。$NL;$NL;First Aid Kitには限りがあり、1回消費した$NL;時点で消滅します。残りの残量はHUDを見ると判断できます。",--The first aid kit is a collection of supplies and equipment for use in giving first aid.$NL;$NL;To use the first aid kit, you need to place it by holding $BTN_USE_ITEM;. Once placed it cannot be moved, but it can be used by you and your crew by holding $BTN_INTERACT; to regain health.$NL;$NL;A deployed first aid kit can be used once and when it is consumed, it disappears.
bm_equipment_sentry_gun = "",--Sentry Gun
bm_equipment_sentry_gun_desc = "Sentry Gunは、センサーがターゲットを感知し、自動で照準を合わせ攻撃を行う携帯装備です。$NL;過去には、対空装備として軍用セントリーが使用されました。$NL;$NL;使用するには$BTN_USE_ITEM;を長押しして地面に設置する必要があり、設置すると移動はできませんが、もう1度回収することが可能です。$NL;$NL;Sentry Gunは自動で敵を攻撃します。Sentry Gunは敵に攻撃されることで破壊されてしまいますが、完全に破壊される前なら回収すれば自動的に修復され、残弾は手持ちの武器に還元されます。$NL;また、弾切れになると停止しますが、再び設置することで弾薬が補給されます。",--To use the Sentry Gun, you need to place it by holding $BTN_USE_ITEM;. Upon deployment it will use up 30% of your weapons' total ammo. It can be destroyed by firing at it, but as long as it is not completely destroyed, picking it up will automatically repair it and return the remaining Sentry Gun ammo. As it runs out of ammo it will stop firing but it can be reloaded by re-deploying it after pick up.$NL;$NL;The Sentry Gun automatically aims and fires at targets that are detected by its sensors. It's commonly used as a distraction, drawing attention from you and your team.
bm_equipment_sentry_gun_silent = "",--Suppressed Sentry Gun
bm_equipment_sentry_gun_silent_desc = "Suppressed Sentry Gunは、かつてのやかまし$NL;く目立ったSentry Gunと違い、静かに目標を$NL;攻撃します。$NL;$NL;使用するには$BTN_USE_ITEM;を長押しして地面に設置する必要があり、設置することで装備中の武器の総弾数の30%を消費します。$NL;$NL;Suppressed Sentry Gunは自動で敵を攻撃します。$NL;Suppressed Sentry Gunは敵に攻撃される$NL;ことで破壊されてしまいますが、完全に破壊される前なら回収すれば自動的に修復され、残弾は手持ちの武器に還元されます。また、弾切れになると停止しますが、再び設置することで弾薬が補給されます。",--To use the Suppressed Sentry Gun, you need to place it by holding $BTN_USE_ITEM;. Upon deployment it will use up 30% of your weapons' total ammo. It can be destroyed by firing at it, but as long as it is not completely destroyed, picking it up will automatically repair it and return the remaining Sentry Gun ammo. As it runs out of ammo it will stop firing but it can be reloaded by re-deploying it after pick up.$NL;$NL;The Suppressed Sentry Gun is the counterpart to the regular, louder Sentry Gun as it's more used to take out enemies than a classic distraction.
bm_equipment_trip_mine = "",--Trip Mines and Shaped Charges
bm_equipment_trip_mine_desc = "Trip Mineを使用するには$BTN_USE_ITEM;を長押しして$NL;設置する必要があります。あなたとあなたのクルーは$BTN_INTERACT;を押すことで、起爆モードとセンサーモードを切り替えることができます。$NL;$NL;Shaped Chargesを使用するには$BTN_USE_ITEM;を長押しして設置する必要があります。$NL;設置すると数秒後に爆発します。$NL;$NL;Trip Mineはセンサーを通過した敵を殺傷する基本的なトラップです。$NL;Shaped Chargesは一般的に金庫やドアを開けるために使います。$NL;どちらも戦闘で活躍できるでしょう。",--To use the Trip Mine, you need to place it by holding $BTN_USE_ITEM;. The trigger laser can be toggled between explosive mode and sensor by pressing $BTN_INTERACT;.$NL;$NL;To use Shaped Charges, you need to place it by holding $BTN_USE_ITEM;. Once placed it will detonate within a few seconds. Trip Mines are basically traps that will hurt or kill enemies crossing the beam. Shaped Charges are commonly used to open safes and doors. Both are a good addition to all combat situations.
