pln_al1_04_02 = "",--Nice work. The C4 will alert the crowd unless we time it with Alesso's pyrotechnics. Head upstairs and patch me into the tech booth.
pln_al1_04_03 = "",--Perfect! Now, to mask the explosions, we need to time the concerts pyros. Get up to the booth and patch me in.
