pln_pal_brf_01 = "Sunshine stateへようこそ! 女はカネ目当て、男はペテン師といった場所だ。Mitchell氏に会いに行け。表向きはカントリークラブの頼れるゴルフコーチだが、裏ではマネーロンダリングから紙幣偽造までこなす犯罪王だ。Mitchellとその犯罪仲間のWilsonはうまいこと摘発を逃れて文字通り何百万と資産を「作り」あげてきた。今まではな。",--Welcome to the sunshine state! Where the women are gold diggers and the men are crooks. Meet Mr. Mitchell: on the surface, a golf coach for a respectable country club. Under the surface, a professional money launderer and counterfeiter - a master criminal. Mitchell and his partner in crime, Wilson, have managed to stay under the radar literally making millions. Until now.
pln_pal_cbf_01 = "荷物は詰めたか、ギャング共。こいつはMason-Dixie南での仕事だ。MitchellとWilson - Pensacolaの偽札職人を追う。地下室で印刷している。常にやってるわけじゃないが、うまいことやって奴の貯蓄はすげえことになってる。一枚噛んでやろう!",--Pack your bags, gang. This one is south of the Mason-Dixie. We're going after Mitchell and Wilson - couple of counterfeiters down in Pensacola. Running a printing operation out of his basement. It's a discrete operation, and this guy's work is solid, so he's making serious bank. Let's grab a piece!
pln_pal_cnc_01 = "よその町での仕事だ。Pensacolaの郊外での偽札作りを追うぞ。",--Out of town job. We're headed after a counterfeiting operation in the Pensacola suburbs.
pln_pal_cnc_02 = "Floridaに向かって偽札作りに励もうじゃないか。",--Head to Florida and muscle in on a counterfeiting job.
pln_pal_cnc_03 = "Sunshine stateに行って、Pensacolaの郊外で偽札作りだ。",--Head to the Sunshine State, and a counterfeiting operation in the Pensacola suburbs.
pln_pal_01_01 = "俺たちは印刷版のために来たんだ。あいつらは今日までの数ヶ月間、カネを刷っては派手に使っていたのさ。俺たちは血の臭いを嗅ぎつけたサメといったところだな。",--We're here for the plates. They've been printing fortunes over the last months, spending wildly. Blood's in the water and we're the sharks!
pln_pal_01_02 = "野郎共、俺達はカネの刷版を追って来たんだ。地下室にあるはずだ。Mitchellに会ってそいつを頂け。",--Guys, we're after the counterfeit money plates. Supposed to be stashed in the basement. Get friendly with Mitchell and get them.
pln_pal_01_03 = "オーケー、ここでタダでランチが食える。こいつらは地下室でカネを刷ってやがる。その印刷版を奪ってやるんだ。それをちゃんとしたところに売れば大儲けさ!",--Okay, we got a free lunch here. These guys are printing money in the basement. We're going to relieve them of their plates. If we sell it to the right party we're good for millions!
pln_pal_02_01 = "Mitchellはプールのそばだ。",--Mitchell's over by the pool.
pln_pal_02_02 = "水漏れは地下室だ。Mitchellに確認しろ。",--The leak willl be in the basement. See Mitchell about it.
pln_pal_02_03 = "Mitchellはピンクのシャツを着ている奴だ。",--Mitchell's the one in the pink shirt.
pln_pal_02_04 = "さあ入れ。Mitchellに会うんだ。",--Get in there. Meet up with Mitchell.
pln_pal_02_05 = "Mitchellはプールのそばにいる。挨拶しに行け。",--Mitchell's by the pool. Introduce yourselves.
pln_pal_02_06 = "オーケー、Mitchellを探せ。奴は依頼人だ。",--Ok, find Mitchell. He's our guy.
pln_pal_03_01 = "オーケー。バーベキューをしてる奴がそうだ。",--Okay. That's him barbecuing.
