pln_pal_05_02 = "誰かが通報しやがったな。住所を確認しにポリ公が2人来るぞ。",--Someone must've seen something 'cause the police are sending a couple of officers to check out the address.
pln_pal_05_03 = "お巡りだ。何もないか確認するんだろう。直に来るぞ。",--Just picked up a call to a cop patrol. They've been asked to make sure everything's okay. They're on their way.
