pln_pal_22_01 = "オーライ、見られずにやってたがバレちまったみたいだ。警官の応答がないからSWATを送るんだとよ。パーティの始まりだ。",--Alright, you got far without getting detected, but it's over now. The cops are reported missing and they're sending in a SWAT team. The party just got started.
