pln_pal_28_04 = "このドアの先に印刷版がある。",--Through this door we should get to the money plates.
pln_pal_29_01 = "見たところ、そいつはFranz Jaeger Safeだな。ロックはドリル出来ないし、金庫全体が頑丈に出来てる。前に見たことがあるぜ。中を水で満たしてちょっとのC4を中で爆発させたんだ。そうしたら中身は無事なまま水圧で扉が開いたぜ。",--Apparently that's a Franz Jaeger Safe. That lock cannot be drilled, and the entire safe is heavily reinforced. I ran into one of those back in the days. We filled the safe with water and detonated a bit of C4 inside. The water pressure just threw the door open without damaging any of the content inside the safe.
pln_pal_29_02 = "おい、そいつはfranz-Jaeger Safeじゃねえか。予想外だ。開ける方法は1つ。水圧だ!",--Hey, that's a Franz-Jaeger Safe. This is unexpected. Well, only one way to crack it with the time we got. Water pressure!
pln_pal_29_03 = "おお、こいつらfranz-Jaeger Safeなんか使ってんのか。予想外だぜ! オーケー... ぶち破るにはあれしかねえ。水だ!",--Man, these boys got themselves a Franz-Jaeger safe. Wasn't expecting that! Okay....well, with what we got there's only one way we're cracking that - water!
pln_pal_30_01 = "それじゃ計画はこうだ、金庫の天井に穴を開けて、庭のホースで水を満たしてC4を中に入れる。金庫の中身を頂いたら、後は逃げる。さあ行くぞ!",--So the plan is this, drill a hole through the top of the safe, get a garden hose to fill the safe with water and drop some C4 inside. After that you take what's inside the safe and escape. Let's roll.
pln_pal_30_02 = "で、計画はこうだ。上にホースをつないで、水でいっぱいになった金庫にC4を入れる。その後は中身を貰って帰るだけだ。",--So, here's the plan. Get a hose down the hole from up top, and blow a pack of C4 inside the water filled safe. After that, grab the loot and get out of there.
pln_pal_30_03 = "前に見たことがあるぜ。中を水で満たしてちょっとのC4を中で爆発させたんだ。そうしたら中身は無事なまま水圧で扉が開いたぜ。",--I run into one of those back in the days. We fill the safe with water and detonated a bit of C4 inside. The water pressure threw the door open without damaging any of the content inside the safe.
pln_pal_31_01 = "オーライ。さあ金庫にドリルを取り付けて庭のホースを地下室まで引っ張ってくるんだ。",--Alright. Now apply the drill to that safe and drag the garden hose down into the shelter.
pln_pal_31_02 = "まず金庫にドリルを付けて、穴を開ける。そして金庫を水で満たすんだ。庭のホースが役に立つだろう。",--First, get the drill onto the safe, make a little hole. Then we need to fill the safe with water. The garden hose will do.
pln_pal_31_03 = "オーライ、やることはだな、まず金庫にドリルを付けろ。穴を開けるんだ。それで、中を水で満たすんだ。庭のホースを引っ張ってこい。",--Alright, here's what you do. Get a drill onto the safe. Make a hole in it. Then, we need to fill it with water. Drag the garden hose down.
