hnc_man_01_03 = "データを持ってきましたか、Mr.Sturr?",--Did you bring the data, Mr. Sturr?
pln_man_brf_01 = "あの収税吏の奴、大企業と裏取引をしているらしい。本人は秘密にしてるつもりなんだろうが、情報がこっちに漏れてきた。あいつの代わりに、俺達がまるごと頂戴してやろう。取引現場を見下ろせる廃ビルを丸々一つ占拠した。 パソコンのセットアップも完璧だ。Alexがクレーンでリムジンごと”ビビらせて”やればあいつは間違いなくサーバーとパスワードを差し出すだろう。2500万ドルのためだ、何だってやるさ。",--The Taxman thought he was clever making a deal with a big corporation, but the information leaked, and now bigger sharks want in - all in. We have a complete, run-down building to ourselves, overlooking the deal. We've got a set-up installed. Alex will help with the crane. Scare the Taxman into his limo, shake him up, and he'll be sure to give us the server and the codes. When it's about $25,000,000, anything goes.
pln_man_cbf_01 = "Okayギャング共、荷物をまとめてWashington D.Cに向かえ。Sturrと呼ばれてる紳士を追うんだ。奴はきたねえ大企業との裏取引で多額の報酬を得ようとする卑劣な国税庁職員だが、その金は俺たちの方が有効に使えるだろう。頂いてやろうぜ。",--Okay gang, pack your things and head for Washington D.C. We're going after a gentleman by the name of Sturr. Mr Sturr is a sneaky IRS employee looking to make a lot of money by striking a deal with some dirty big-ass corporation, but I say we could put that money to better use. Let's do it.
pln_man_cnc_01 = "",--I have a little . . . surprise interview set up with a greedy IRS employee in Washington D.C.
pln_man_cnc_02 = "",--Head to Washington D.C. and kidnap a scum bag taxman trying to strike a dirty deal.
pln_man_cnc_03 = "",--We're gonna break up a dirty deal between a Taxman and some big corporation and make a lot of cash doing it.
pln_man_00a_01 = "リムジンが到着したぞ。収税吏はそこだ。",--The limo has arrived. Taxman is here.
pln_man_00a_02 = "よし、繰り返す。収税吏は国税庁職員で、ある大企業と不法な取引をしている。奴は機密の入ったサーバーをそいつらに売っている。",--Alright to repeat: Taxman is IRS, making a shady deal with some big corporation. He's selling them a server some with vital data.
pln_man_00a_03 = "奴らを襲って、収税吏とサーバーの両方を奪う。そしたらハックして 25,000,000ドルを生み出せる。Alex、クレーンの準備はいいか?",--We screw 'em over, snatch both Taxman and the server. With those, we'll make a $25,000,000 hack. Alex, crane ready?
pln_man_00b_01 = "よしお前ら、適切なタイミングで取引を中断させるぞ。そしたらAlexがリムジンを持ちあげる。準備はいいか!",--Okay guys, at the right moment, disrupt the deal. Then Alex lifts the limo outta there. Ready now!
pln_man_01_01 = "収税吏とサーバーの両方が必要なのを忘れるなよ、みんな。奴がサーバーを持っているのを確認したら、奴をビビらせてリムジンに入れてやれ。",--Remember we need both the Taxman and the server, people. Scare him and make him go into the limo once we've confirmed that he has the server on him.
pln_man_01_02 = "ギャング共、手はず通りにな。収税吏とサーバーの両方がいる。片方だけじゃただのクソだ。奴がサーバーを持っていることを確認しろ。",--Gang, we need to do this right; both the Taxman and the server is needed, otherwise it all goes to shit. Make sure he has the server on him.
