pln_man_69_02 = "ようし、ASIMは対処した。奴らには誰の仕事か分からなくなったぜ。",--Alright, we're past the ASIM. They won't know what hit em.
pln_man_69_03 = "ASIMチェック完了! 俺たちは絶好調だ!",--ASIM - Check! We're on a roll!
pln_man_70_01 = "OKお前ら、認証はほぼ完了だ。タイマーから目を離すなよ。",--OK guys, the authentication is almost complete. Keep an eye on that timer.
pln_man_70_02 = "次のステップへ行こう、認証だ。これはしばらく時間がかかる。タイマーから目を離すなよ。",--Next step is authentication. It will take a while so keep an eye on the timer.
pln_man_70_03 = "オーケー、認証チェックだ。これはかなり時間がかかりそうだ、タイマーから目を離すなよ。",--Okay, it's checking authentication. It might take some time, so keep your eyes on the timer.
pln_man_71_01 = "OK コールバックだ、全部クリアだ。最後のステップだ。タイマーが終了すれば- その時、カネが舞い降りる。",--Ok got the callback, everything is clear. Last step. When the timer is done - it's time to cash in.
pln_man_71_02 = "野郎ども、コールバックだ。タイマーが0になれば - この取引は完了だ。",--Guys, I got a callback from the accounting name, When that timer hits zero - we are clear for the transaction.
pln_man_71_03 = "コールバックだな。タイマーが0になれば、俺らは大金持ちの少年少女だ。",--That's the callback, it's seems to have worked. When the timer hits zero - we get rich boys and girls.
pln_man_72_01 = "出来たー! 俺たちの積荷は完了だ。こい、こい、こい、こい...",--Done! We're through with loading up. Gimme, gimme, gimme, gimme...
pln_man_72_02 = "いよっしゃあ! カネ、カネ、カネ、カネ - カネだー!",--Yes! Money, money, money, money - money!
pln_man_72_03 = "終わり! カネの時間だぜ、ベイビー!",--That's it! Time to cash in, baby!
pln_man_73_01 = "すばらしい! 2500万ドルの取引を確認した。",--Fantastic! I confirmed the transaction of 25 million.
pln_man_73_02 = "よくやった! ちょうど2500万ドルの取引が行われたことを確認したぜ。",--Excellent! I just got a confirmation on a 25 million dollar transaction.
pln_man_73_03 = "見事だ! 見事としか言いようがない! 2500万ドルの取引を確認した。",--Splendid, absolutely splendid! I confirmed the transaction of 25 million.
pln_man_74_01 = "さあ行こうぜ。税金は良い事につかってやろう。",--Here we go. Tax money put to good use.
pln_man_75_01 = "よしお前ら、外に出る時間だ。",--Alright guys, It's time to get outta there.
pln_man_75_02 = "終わりだ、とっとと出る時間だぜ。",--That's it, time to get the hell outta here.
pln_man_75_03 = "仕事完了。さあここを出よう!",--We're done, let's move and get out!
pln_man_76_01 = "屋上に上がって隣のビルに飛び移れ。",--Get up on the roof and run over to the connecting rooftop.
pln_man_76_02 = "屋上に上がって左の建物だ。Alexがヘリで来ているぞ。",--Up to the roof and away from the building to the left. Alex has the chopper coming in.
pln_man_76_03 = "屋上に上がって、隣の屋上まで飛び越えて来い!",--Hit the roof and run over to the connecting rooftop.
pln_man_77_01 = "野郎ども、足を止めるなよ!",--Keep going guys!
pln_man_77_02 = "行くぞ、行くぞ!",--Let's go, let's go!
pln_man_77_03 = "速く、速く、急げ!",--Chop, chop, people!
pln_man_78_01 = "ジャンプしなきゃ来れないぞ、お前ら!",--You gotta make the jump, guys!
pln_man_78_02 = "来い野郎ども、お前なら出来る!",--Come on guys! You can do it!
pln_man_78_03 = "そうだ、ペルシャの王子様になったつもりで飛べ!",--Yeah, you gotta be a Persian prince to make this jump!
pln_man_79_01 = "やりやがった! ガス! ガスだ!",--Dammit! Gas! Gas!
pln_man_80_01 = "ヘリが来たぞ! 屋上だお前ら、屋上に来い!",--Chopper coming in! Roof guys, roof!
pln_mad_brf_01_01 = "良心を培うってのは大事なことなんだろうが、別に今じゃなくたっていいだろう?この計画、俺は完全に賛成する気にはなれないが、しかしお前達の良心を責めることもできんな。このJimmyって奴の話を信じるなら、Akanの計画は絶対に止めなければならん。お前達の行き先は人里離れた何もない場所にぽつんと建っている製材所だ。ここは実は、とあるロシア組織の秘密の研究施設になっている。Jimmyが言うには、奴らは現実のものとは思えない何かに関する実験をしているらしい。研究所に押し入り、Akanのデータを奪ってこい。野郎ども、幸運を祈る。",--Of all the times to grow a conscience, you decide now is the time? I can't say I like it, but I can't say you are making a mistake either. Based on what this Jimmy character is telling us, Akan really needs to be stopped. Your destination is a lumber mill in the middle of nowhere, that is secretly a laboratory run by a strange Russian organization. Jimmy tells me they are conducting some experiments that involve things out of this reality. Break into the lab and get the data Akan is after. Good luck, gang.
pln_mad_intro_01_01 = "くそう! 奴ら工場の周りの対空防御が敷かれている! 近くに飛行機を回わせ、Bile! ギャング、お前らはパラシュートを使って出るんだ。今すぐに!",--Damn! They have anti-air defenses set up around the whole factory. Turn the plane around, Bile! Gang, you need to use the parachutes and get out! Right now!
pln_mad_intro_01_02 = "クソッ! 対空陣地が敷かれているぞ! Bile、すぐに飛行機を旋回させろ! お前らはパラシュートで飛び出せ! 何とかするんだ!",--Shit! These bastards have anti-air defenses set up! Bile, turn the plane around immediately! Guys, use the parachutes and get out! We'll figure something out!
pln_mad_intro_01_03 = "冗談だろ、対空防御だと!? Bile、すぐに飛行機の向きを変えるんだ! お前ら、パラシュートを持って飛び出せ!",--Anti-air defenses?! Are you shitting me?! Turn the plane around, Bile! Do it now! Guys, take the parachutes and jump out!
pln_mad_01_01 = "お前達、ロシアへようこそ! どうだ、\"盛大な歓迎会\"だろ?",--Welcome to Russia, gang! Nice welcoming party, right?
pln_mad_01_02 = "ロシアへようこそ、ギャング! ここの連中は真面目だぞ!",--That's Russia for you, gang! These guys do not mess around!
pln_mad_01_03 = "ふぅ...危なかったな! ここのロシア人は誰にもパーティーを邪魔させたくないらしいな。",--Holy... that was close! These Russians really don't want anyone to crash their party.
pln_mad_02_01 = "この対空防御システムが機能してる限り、FedorはEMPを投下することが出来ない。無効化する方法を探せ、ギャング!",--As long as those anti-air defenses are functional, Fedor won't be able to drop the EMP. Find a way to disable them, gang.
pln_mad_02_02 = "対空防御システムを破壊するか無力化する必要がある。なんとかしろ、さもないと全滅するぞ。",--You need to disable or destroy the anti-air defenses. Find a way, otherwise we're screwed.
pln_mad_02_03 = "お前ら、急いで対空防御システムを処理する必要がある。なんとかしろ!",--Gang, you need to take care of those anti-air guns ASAP. Find a way!
pln_mad_03_01 = "お前ら、コンピューターステーションが役に立つはずだ。ノートパソコンなどがないか探してみてくれ。",--Gang, the computer station there could be useful. See if you can find me a laptop or something.
pln_mad_03_02 = "コンピューターステーションにノートパソコンがあるはずだ。探してみてくれ。",--That computer station should have a laptop laying around. See if you can find one.
pln_mad_03_03 = "コンピューターステーションでノートパソコンでも見つけてくれれば、それでサポートできるぞ。",--If you find a laptop at the computer station, I could use it to help you.
pln_mad_04_01 = "ノートパソコンを対空砲に設置してくれ!",--Hook up the laptop to the anti-aircraft gun!
pln_mad_04_02 = "対空砲にノートパソコンを設置するんだ。俺の魔法が使えるはずだ。",--Set up the laptop to the anti-aircraft gun. Maybe I can work my magic.
pln_mad_04_03 = "対空砲にノートパソコンを持って行くんだ。接続できるか見てくれ。",--Bring the laptop to the AA gun. See if you can hook it up.
pln_mad_05_01 = "オーケー、もういいぞ。ハッキング開始だ。",--Okay, you're good to go. Start the hack.
pln_mad_05_02 = "パーフェクト、これでハッキングを始められる。",--Perfect, I can do this. Beginning hacking.
pln_mad_05_03 = "オーケー、1分か2分、時間をくれ。対空砲を無力化してみる。",--Okay, give me a minute or two. I'll disable this AA gun.
pln_mad_06_01 = "ハッキングが止められたぞ! 再開させろ!",--They interrupted the hack! Restart it!
pln_mad_06_02 = "クソッ、ハッキングが止められたぞ! 再開させるんだ!",--Damn, they interrupted the hacking.Get it started again!
pln_mad_06_03 = "ハッキングが止まったぞ。確認して再開させるんだ!",--The hacking has been stopped. Get it up and running again!
pln_mad_07_01 = "対空砲の1つを無力化したぞ! よし、次のやつに向かってくれ!",--The AA gun has been disabled! Now, grab the laptop and head over to the next one!
pln_mad_07_02 = "終わったぞ、お前ら。この対空砲は無力化した。だがもう1つ残っている。",--That's it, guys. The AA gun has been disabled. But there's still one more.
pln_mad_07_03 = "オーケー、こいつを無力化した。だがもう1つ残ってるな!",--Okay, I got this one disabled, but there's still one more to go!
pln_mad_08_01 = "さて、傭兵というものは戦争のためにいる。だとしたら俺たちが使える爆薬がそこらに転がってるはずだ。",--Man, these mercenaries have set up for war. There should be some explosives laying around that we could use.
pln_mad_08_02 = "そこらに爆薬が転がってると俺は思うな。探してみてくれ。",--I bet you there are some explosives laying around here. See if you can find any.
pln_mad_08_03 = "その傭兵どもならC4か何か、俺たちが使えるものを持ってるはずだ。",--These mercenaries must have some C4 or something around here that we could use.
pln_mad_09_01 = "やることはわかってるな。C4をセットして残りを処理するんだ。",--You know what to do. Set the C4 up and let it take care of the rest.
pln_mad_09_02 = "C4を設置して爆発まで待て。",--Plant the C4 and enjoy the moment.
pln_mad_09_03 = "C4を設置しろ。",--Place the C4.
pln_mad_10_01 = "下がれ、お前ら!",--Stand back, gang!
pln_mad_10_02 = "遮蔽物に隠れろ!",--Take cover!
pln_mad_10_03 = "爆発するぞ、下がれ!",--They are about to blow, stand back!
pln_mad_11_01 = "やったぞ、お前ら!",--That's it, gang!
pln_mad_11_02 = "パーフェクト! 奴らはもうこいつを使えないな。",--Perfect! They won't be able to use that anymore.
pln_mad_11_03 = "ドーン! よくやった、お前ら。",--Boom! Great job, gang.
pln_mad_12_01 = "クソッ、EMPが製材所の屋根を突き破ったぞ。",--Damn, the EMP crashed right through the roof of the lumber mill.
pln_mad_12_02 = "何やってんだ、Bile... EMPが製材所の屋根を突き破って中に落ちたぞ、外じゃなくてな。",--God dammit, Bile... The EMP fell through the roof and is now inside the lumber mill instead of outside.
pln_mad_12_03 = "本当か、Bile? お前ら、EMPは外じゃなくて製材所の中に落ちた。中に入る必要がある。",--Really, Bile? Gang, the EMP ended up inside the lumber mill instead of outside.Need to get in there now.
pln_mad_13_01 = "ナイスだ、Bile! お前ら、EMPは製材所の庭にあるぞ。",--Nice drop, Bile! Gang, the EMP is in the yard outside the lumber mill.
pln_mad_13_02 = "オーケー、お前ら。Bileは製材所の庭にEMPを投下したぞ。向かってくれ!",--Okay, guys. Bile dropped the EMP just outside the lumber mill.Go get it!
pln_mad_13_03 = "EMPが投下されたぞ。製材所の庭に向かってくれ。",--The EMP has been dropped. Head over just outside the lumber mill and pick it up.
pln_mad_14_01 = "OK、お前ら。製材所に入る方法を探す必要がある。これはイカれた方法かもしれんが、さっきハックした対空砲が使えないか?向きを変えれば壁を吹き飛ばせるんじゃないか?",--Ok, gang. We need to find a way into the lumber mill. This might be crazy, but maybe we could use the anti-air gun we hacked earlier? Just redirect its position and blow the wall up?
pln_mad_14_02 = "俺たちは製材所に入る方法を探す必要がある。ハックした対空砲で壁に穴を開けてそこを通れないか?",--We are going to need to find a way inside the lumber mill. Maybe we can blow a hole through the wall using the AA gun we hacked?
pln_mad_14_03 = "俺たちは製材所に入る必要がある。さっきハックした対空砲の向きを変えてみたらどうだ? やる価値はあると思うぜ。",--We need to get inside the lumber mill. Why not see if you could use the anti-air gun we hacked earlier and redirect its position? Might be worth a shot.
pln_mad_15_01 = "やったぜ! 最高だな、お前ら! さあ、入ろうぜ。",--Hell yeah! That was crazy, gang! Now get in there.
pln_mad_15_02 = "これが俺たちのやり方だ! よくやった、お前ら。さあ、入るぞ。",--That's how we do it! Good job, guys. Get inside the mill now.
pln_mad_15_03 = "奴らのおもちゃを奴らに使う。好きだぜこういうの。さあ、製材所に入るぞ。",--Use their own toys against them - I love it. Now get inside the lumber mill.
pln_mad_16_01 = "オーケー、お前ら。この子を使うには充電が必要だ。少し時間がかかるぞ。",--Okay, gang. We need to charge this baby up before it can be used. Gonna take a little while.
pln_mad_16_02 = "お前ら、EMPは使う前に充電する必要がある。少し時間がかかるぞ。",--Gang, the EMP needs to charge up before we can use it. It will take some time.
pln_mad_16_03 = "オーケー、EMPを使うには充電する必要がある。我慢してくれ。",--Okay, we need to charge the EMP before can we use it.Patience is a virtue.
pln_mad_17_01 = "傭兵共が押し寄せてくるぞ! EMPを守れ、お前ら!",--The mercenaries are gonna come at you hard! Protect the EMP, gang!
pln_mad_17_02 = "EMPを守れ! 傭兵共が止めに来るぞ!",--Protect the EMP! The mercenaries will do anything to stop you!
pln_mad_17_03 = "お前ら、EMPのチャージが完了するまで守る必要がある! 戦闘に備えろ!",--Gang, you need to protect the EMP while it charges! Prepare to fight!
pln_mad_18_01 = "クソッ、奴らに充電を止められた!",--Damn it, they stopped the charge!
pln_mad_18_02 = "充電が中断したぞ! 再開させろ!",--The charging has been interrupted! Get it started again!
pln_mad_18_03 = "クソッ、傭兵共がEMPの充電を止めちまったぞ。",--Damn, the mercenaries got to the EMP and stopped the charging.
pln_mad_19_01 = "傭兵共がEMPの充電を中断させやがった! 止められると少しずつ放電されちまう!",--The mercenaries interrupted the EMP charge! Every time that happens, the EMP is slowly discharged!
pln_mad_19_02 = "クソッ、傭兵共が充電を止めやがった! 放電がはじまるぞ!",--Shit, the mercenaries stopped the EMP charge! It's beginning to discharge!
pln_mad_19_03 = "お前ら! 傭兵共がEMPの充電を邪魔するたびに、放電されていくぞ! 奴らに触れさせるな!",--Guys! Every time the mercenaries mess with the EMP, the charging process decreases! Don't let them touch it!
pln_mad_20_01 = "よし、いいぞ。充電が再開されたぞ。",--Ok, good. The charging has been restarted.
pln_mad_20_02 = "いいぞ、EMPが充電を再開したぞ。",--Good, the EMP is charging again.
pln_mad_20_03 = "EMPが充電を再開したぞ。",--The EMP is charging again.
pln_mad_21_01 = "お前ら聞いてくれ! EMPが爆発したら、しばらくの間俺はお前らとの通信が出来なくなってしまう可能性が高い。お前らはハッチから隠された研究室まで行く必要がある。",--Guys, listen! When the EMP goes off I most likely won't be able to communicate with you for a while. You need to get down to the hidden laboratory via the hatch.
pln_mad_21_01a = "EMPが電磁ロックを解除するはずだ。地下の研究所に降りたら、検査装置と被験者を探せ。",--The EMP should have released the magnetic lock. Once you're down there, find the scanner and the test-subjects.
pln_mad_21_02 = "お前ら、EMPが爆発したら通信に障害が出る可能性が高い。だからやる事を覚えておけ、研究所に入り被験者を探すんだ。",--Guys, the EMP will most likely take out our communication when it goes off. But you know what to do, enter the laboratory via the hatch and look for the test subjects.
pln_mad_21_03 = "EMPは殆ど準備完了だ、聞いてくれ! この赤ちゃんは物凄い鳴き声を上げる、俺たちの交信が途絶えても、驚くなよ。",--The EMP is almost done, so listen up! This baby is powerful so don't be surprised if it breaks our communication among other things.
pln_mad_21_03a = "とにかく計画を忠実に遂行すればいい。ハッチを通って研究所に入り、検査装置と被験者を見つけろ。",--But just stick to the plan and we should be good. Get inside the laboratory through the hatchet and find the scanner and the test-subjects.
pln_mad_22_01 = "ギャング? お前らに俺の声が届いているかは分からんが、やるべき事ははっきりしている:ハッチを開けて研究室へ入るんだ。",--Gang? I'm not sure you can hear me, but you know what you're supposed to do: enter the laboratory via the hatchet.
pln_mad_22_02 = "EMPは磁気ロックを解除した、これで研究室には自由に入れるぞ。行くぜ!",--The EMP took care of the magnetic lock, so you have free passage to the laboratory.Let's go!
pln_mad_22_03 = "よし、いいぞ! EMPの仕事は終わった! ハッチから研究室に入るんだ。",--That's it! The EMP did its job! Now enter the laboratory via the hatch.
pln_mad_22_04 = "お前ら、聞こえるか?もしもし?ハッチから研究室に入るんだ、開いてる筈だ。",--Guys, can you hear me? Hello? Enter the laboratory via the hatch. It should be open.
pln_mad_23_01 = "どうやらEMPが施設全体を破壊しちまったらしい...フラッシュライトを使ってX線装置を探し出せ。",--Man, the EMP took out the whole factory it seems... Use your flashlights and find the X-ray device.
pln_mad_23_02 = "Elephantが必要としているデータを手に入れるにはX線装置が必要だ。",--We're going to need an X-ray device to get the data the Elephant needs.
pln_mad_23_03 = "俺たちがデータを手に入れるのに必要なX線装置を探してくれ。でないと何も出来ないぞ。",--See if you can find the X-ray device we need to get the data. Without it we can't do much.
pln_mad_24_01 = "クソッ! 俺たちが研究所に侵入したのを見て、部屋にガスを充満させたに違いない。どこから流し込んでるか探して止めるんだ!",--Damn! They must have filled the room with gas the second we entered the lab. Find out where it's dispensed from and shut it off!
pln_mad_24_02 = "なんてこった! 部屋にガスが充満しているぞ。急げ! どこから流入してるか探し止めるんだ!",--What the hell! The whole room is filled with gas. Quickly! Find out where it's coming from and find a way to shut it off!
pln_mad_24_03 = "クソッ! 傭兵共が俺たちを止めるために部屋にガスを流し込んでいるぞ。お前ら、急いで止める方法を探すんだ!",--Damn it! The bastards have filled the room with gas to stop us. Gang, be quick and find a way to shut it off!
pln_mad_25_01 = "ガスを止める方法を見つける必要がある。",--You need to find a way to shut off the gas.
pln_mad_25_02 = "お前ら、ガスを止める方法を探せ!",--Guys, look for a way to shut off the gas!
pln_mad_25_03 = "ガスを止める方法があるはずだ!",--There must be some way to shut off the gas!
pln_mad_26_01 = "よくやった、お前ら。それで検査室のガスを取り除けるはずだ。",--Good job, guys. That should get rid of the gas in the scanning room.
pln_mad_26_02 = "それだ、お前ら。これで検査室のガスが取り除かれるはずだ。",--That's it, gang. That should take care of the gas in the scanning room.
pln_mad_26_03 = "いいぞ、これでガスが取り除かれただろう。部屋に入ることができるはずだ。",--Good, that should get rid of the gas. You can most likely enter the room now.
pln_mad_27_01 = "オーケー、ここで働く科学者はクソな次世代物を使ってるらしい。認証には主任研究員の指紋が必要だ。隠れてる彼を探してくれ。",--Okay, the scientists working here are using some next level shit. You're gonna need the lead scientist for handprint authorization. See where he's hiding.
pln_mad_27_02 = "クソッ、なんてこった! いつものドリルで開けれるセキュリティドアとは違うぞ。認証には主任研究員の指紋が必要なようだ。彼を探せ。",--Damn it to hell! What is wrong with a traditional security door that you can drill? Looks like you're gonna need the actual lead scientist for hand print authorization. Find him.
pln_mad_27_03 = "おい、SF映画の中じゃないんだぞ。あぁ、大丈夫だ。認証には主任研究員の指紋が必要だから探してくれ。どこかに隠れてるはずだ。",--Oh, I didn't know we were in a Sci-Fi movie. Well, okay then. You're gonna need to find the lead scientist for some kind of hand print authorization.See where he's hiding.
pln_mad_28_01 = "お前ら、主任研究員を探せ!",--Gang, you need to find the lead scientist.
pln_mad_28_02 = "おい、主任研究員が見つからないと、あのドアを通過できないぞ。",--Hey, if you don't find the lead scientist, you're not getting through that door.
pln_mad_28_03 = "主任研究員を見つけて、セキュリティドアまで連れてくるんだ。",--Look for the lead scientist and get him to the security door.
pln_mad_29_01 = "待て、何だ? 主任研究員は死んでるのか? そうだな、彼の手を借りる以外にあのドアを通過する方法はない...お前らの手を汚すしかないな...",--Wait, what? The lead scientist is dead? Well, the only way we're getting past that door is with the help of his hand...I guess you're gonna have to do some dirty work...
pln_mad_29_02 = "クソッ! 奴らが主任研究員を殺したのか? わからないな。俺たちには認証のために彼の手が必要だ...やるべきことはわかるな...?",--Damn! They killed the lead scientist? I don't know, guys. We still need his hand for authorization...Do what you have to do...
pln_mad_29_03 = "主任研究員が死んでる? クソッ。彼なしではセキュリティを通過できないぞ...いや、厳密には彼は必要ない、どちらかといえば必要なのは\"彼の手\"...",--The lead scientist is dead? Shit. Without him we aren't getting past security... Well, I guess technically we don't need HIM, but rather HIS hand...
pln_mad_30_01 = "こいつはエグイな。あぁ、必要なものは手に入った。そいつをスキャナーに置け、で合ってるよな?",--Jesus, that's nasty. Well, you got what we need. Place it on the scanner, I guess?
pln_mad_30_02 = "うわっ、本当にやったのか...お前ら恐ろしいな。こいつをスキャナーに持っていけ、それで今のことは全部忘れよう。",--Wow, you really did it... You guys are cold. Bring it to the scanner and let's forget this ever happened.
pln_mad_30_03 = "彼の手を切ったのか?残酷だが、仕事は仕事だ。そいつをスキャナーに置いてドアを開けるんだ。",--You cut off his hand? That's some dark stuff, but a job is a job. Place it on the scanner and get the door opened.
pln_mad_31_01 = "よし、動いてるようだ。彼の生死は関係ないようだ。テクノロジーは冷酷だな。さぁ、スキャナーを起動しよう。",--Yes, it worked. It doesn't seem to matter that the scientist was dead. Technology is cruel. Well, get started with the scanner.
pln_mad_31_02 = "うまくいったようだな。スキャンプロセスを開始できるはずだ。",--It seems to have worked. You should be able to start the scanning-process now.
pln_mad_31_03 = "オーケー、認証完了だ。スキャナーが起動したぞ。",--Okay, the authorization worked. Get the scanner working now.
pln_mad_32_01 = "電源が戻ったようだぞ、お前ら。",--Look like the power is back, gang.
pln_mad_32_02 = "いいぞ、電源が戻ったようだ。",--Nice, seems the power is back.
pln_mad_32_03 = "電源が回復したようだ。",--Looks like the power is coming back.
pln_mad_33_01 = "よし、お前ら。被験者を探してスキャナーに乗せるんだ。彼らは同じように見えるはずだ。",--Alright, gang. You need to look for the test-subjects and get them to the scanner. They are supposed to look pretty much the same.
pln_mad_33_02 = "情報が正しければスキャンが必要な被験者は全員同じだそうだ。",--If the intel is correct the test subjects that you need to scan are identical.
pln_mad_33_03 = "よし。次は被験者を探して、スキャナーに乗せるんだ。ハゲてる奴を探すんだ。",--Allright. Now find the test-subjects, and get them to the scanner. You are looking for some bald guys.
pln_mad_34_01 = "Jimmyによると被験者の1人で間違いないそうだ。スキャナーに乗せて必要な情報を回収するぞ。",--That must be one of the test subjects that Jimmy talked about. Get the body to the scanner so we can get the information we need.
pln_mad_34_02 = "オーケー、被験者の1人に違いない。スキャナーに乗せて必要な情報を回収するぞ。",--Okay, that must be one of the test subjects. Get the body to the scanner so we can get the information we need.
pln_mad_34_03 = "そいつをスキャナーに乗せるんだ。",--Get that body over to the scanner.
pln_mad_35_01 = "オーケー、スキャンの準備完了だ。",--Okay, we're all set to begin the scanning.
pln_mad_35_02 = "被験者を乗せたから、スキャンを開始できるぞ。",--Body is in place so start scanning, gang.
pln_mad_35_03 = "よし。スキャンを開始できるぞ。",--That's it. Now we can start the scanning.
pln_mad_36_01 = "オーケー、スキャン中だ。終わるまで邪魔されないようにしてくれ。",--Okay, scanning is under way. Now make sure it gets to finish without getting interrupted.
pln_mad_36_02 = "傭兵共にスキャンを止められないようにするんだ!",--Don't let the mercenaries stop the scanning process!
pln_mad_36_03 = "X線装置を守れ! 傭兵共を近づけるな!",--Protect the X-ray device! Don't let the mercenaries get to it!
pln_mad_37_01 = "奴らがスキャンを止めたぞ! 再開させろ!",--They stopped the scan! Start it again!
pln_mad_37_02 = "クソッ、スキャンが中断された! 再開させろ!",--Damn, they interrupted the scan! Restart it!
pln_mad_37_03 = "お前ら、やつらがスキャンを止めたぞ! 再開させろ!",--Guys, the bastards stopped the scan! Get it working again!
pln_mad_38_01 = "いいぞ、スキャンが再開された。",--Great, the scanning is up and running again.
pln_mad_38_02 = "よし、スキャンが再開された。",--Good, the scan is under way again.
pln_mad_38_03 = "スキャンが再開された。この状態を維持しろ。",--The scan is back in progress. Now keep it that way.
pln_mad_39_01 = "よし! スキャン完了だ。よくやった、お前ら。",--That's it! Scan has been completed.Good job, guys.
pln_mad_39_02 = "よくやった、お前ら。スキャン完了だ。",--Great job, gang. The scan is complete.
pln_mad_39_03 = "スキャン完了だ。よくやった、お前ら。",--The scan has been completed.Well done, gang.
pln_mad_40_01 = "奴らが電源を落としたぞ!",--They pulled the power!
pln_mad_40_02 = "あぁ、スキャナーの電源が落ちたぞ!",--Argh, they pulled the power for the scanner!
pln_mad_40_03 = "クソッ、奴らがスキャナーの電源を落としたぞ!",--Damn, they got the power for the scanner!
pln_mad_41_01 = "よくやった! 電源が戻ったぞ。スキャンを再開させるんだ。",--Great! Power is back. Get the scanner working again.
pln_mad_41_02 = "オーケー、いいぞ。電源が回復した。戻ってスキャンを再開させろ。",--Okay, good. You got the power back. Return to the scanning process.
pln_mad_41_03 = "電源が戻ったぞ! 被験者のスキャンを再開するんだ。",--Power is back! Get back to scanning the test-subjects.
pln_mad_42_01 = "オーケー、データは他の部屋にあるサーバーに転送された。サーバーを取りに行くか、ここで更にスキャンするか選んでくれ。Jimmyにとってそいつらは使い道があるはずだ、つまり金になるってことだ。",--Okay, the data is being transferred to the server in the other room. You can either go and get it or stay and scan more bodies. I'm sure Jimmy can find use for it and that means more cash for us.
pln_mad_42_02 = "スキャンデータは他の部屋のサーバーに記録されている。留まってもっとデータを手に入れるか、脱出するか。だがJimmyは仕事分の報酬を払ってくれるはずだ。",--The data from the scanning is being collected on that server in the other room. You can stay and get more data, or you can leave. But I'm sure Jimmy would pay us for the trouble.
pln_mad_42_03 = "データは他の部屋のサーバーに保存されている。そいつを回収してここから脱出するか、留まってもっとスキャンするかだ。Jimmyが仕事分の報酬を払ってくれるはずだ。",--The data is being stored on the server in the other room. You can get it and get the hell outta here, or you can stay and scan more bodies. I'm positive Jimmy will make it worth your while.
pln_mad_43_01 = "いい選択だ、お前ら。ここに来たのは給料のためだ。わかってるだろ、データのためにスキャンを続けるんだ。",--Good choice, gang. It's all about the payday when it comes down to it. You know the drill, keep scanning them bodies for more data.
pln_mad_43_02 = "賢い選択だ、お前ら。スキャンを続けるんだ。小遣い稼ぎのためにロシアに来たわけじゃない、そうだろ?",--That's the right choice, guys. Keep scanning away. We didn't come all the way to Russia for a small payout, now did we?
pln_mad_43_03 = "素晴らしい判断だ、お前ら。全てスキャンできたら、Jimmyが報酬を弾んでくれるそうだ。彼にとって金額は問題じゃないようだ。",--Excellent decision, guys. If you scan all the bodies Jimmy will pay us good for it. Money doesn't seem to a an issue for him.
pln_mad_44_01 = "それで全部だ! もうスキャンできるものはないぞ。俺たちはサーバーを確保する必要がある、でないと全て水の泡だ。",--That's all of them! No more bodies to scan. Now we need to get the server or we did it all for nothin'.
pln_mad_44_02 = "素晴らしいぞ、お前ら。全てスキャンしたぞ。次はデータが格納されているサーバーを確保する必要がある。",--Excellent, gang. That's all the bodies scanned. Now we need to get our hands on that server storing the data.
pln_mad_44_03 = "全てのデータを持っていったらJimmyは喜ぶだろう。Akanに逆襲できる。",--Jimmy will love it if we get all the data we can, really sticking it to Akan.
pln_mad_45_01 = "よくやった、お前ら! 今そのサーバーにはすごい価値がある。落とすなよ。",--Great job, guys! That server is worth a lot of cash right now. Don't drop it.
pln_mad_45_02 = "よし! 必ず生きて脱出するんだ。",--That's it! Now make sure you get out of there alive.
pln_mad_45_03 = "素晴らしい、サーバーを確保したぞ。よし、ここから脱出するぞ。",--Excellent, the server is secured. Now, let's get out of here.
pln_mad_46_01 = "待て! ブリーフケースのことを忘れていた...研究室のどこかにブリーフケースがあるはずだ。脱出する前に確保してくれ。中身は気にするなよ。さぁ、探せ。",--Wait! I forgot about the briefcase... There should be a briefcase somewhere in the laboratory. You need to get it before you leave. Don't mind what's in it, just do it.
pln_mad_46_02 = "クソッ! ブリーフケースのことを忘れていた。お前ら聞け。研究室のどこかにブリーフケースがあるはずだ。",--Damn! I forgot about the briefcase. Gang, listen up. There is a briefcase somewhere in the laboratory.
pln_mad_46_02a = "お前らに探して持ってきてもらう必要がある。重要かどうかなんて聞くなよ。",--I need you to find and it and bring it with you. I wouldn't ask if it wasn't important.
pln_mad_46_03 = "そうだ! すっかり忘れていた。研究所の中にブリーフケースがあるはずだ。お前らにそれを取ってきてもらう必要がある。重要な物なんだ。",--That's right! I almost forgot: there is a briefcase in the laboratory. I'm gonna need you to get it, guys. It's important.
pln_mad_47_01 = "手に入れたか?ブリーフケースか?よくやった! さぁ、ここから脱出しよう。",--You got it? The briefcase? Good! Now let's get out of there.
pln_mad_47_02 = "ブリーフケースを確保した?素晴らしい! 脱出の時間だ!",--You got the briefcase? Excellent! Time to go then!
pln_mad_47_03 = "それか?ブリーフケースか?パーフェクト! よし、ここから脱出できるぞ!",--That's it? The briefcase? Perfect! Now we can get outta here!
pln_mad_48_01 = "なんだ、心が読めるのか?あぁ、欲しいブリーフケースはそれだ。どうして知ってるんだ?",--What, are you mind readers? Yes, I do want that briefcase. How did you know?
pln_mad_48_02 = "ハッハー、察しがいいな、お前ら。それが欲しいブリーフケースだ。",--Haha, you read my mind, guys. I do want that briefcase.
pln_mad_48_03 = "どうしてブリーフケースが欲しいってわかったんだ?まぁいいや、よくやった!",--How did you know I wanted that briefcase? It doesn't matter, good job!
pln_mad_49_01 = "お前ら、Fedorが湖で待ってるぞ。脱出の時間だ。",--Guys, Fedor is waiting over at the lake. It's time to leave.
pln_mad_49_02 = "Fedorの話は聞いたな。湖で待ってるそうだ。",--You heard Fedor. Get your asses to the lake.
pln_mad_49_03 = "やれることは全てやったな。よし、湖に向かえ。Fedorがお前らを待ってるぞ。",--We got everything we came for. Now, head for the lake. Fedor is waiting for you.
pln_mad_50_01 = "素晴らしいぞ、お前ら。良いことをするのは気分がいいな。だが変なことを考えるなよ、次は銀行かどこかを襲うんだからな。",--Excellent, guys. It actually feels nice knowing we did something good. But don't get any ideas, we're robbing a bank or something next.
pln_mad_50_02 = "よくやった、お前ら。サーバーの確保にJimmyが喜ぶぞ。",--Good job, gang. The server has been secured and Jimmy will be happy.
pln_mad_50_03 = "いいぞ、サーバーを確保した。もうJimmyの助言は必要ないな。俺たちの役目は終わりだ。",--Great, the server has been secured. Now Jimmy can shut up about it. We did our part.
pln_mad_51_01 = "ここでやれることは何もないぞ。行くぞ。",--Nothing more to do here. Let's go.
pln_mad_51_02 = "いったい何を待っているんだ?脱出するぞ。",--What are you waiting for? Let's leave.
pln_mad_51_03 = "仕事は終わりだ、お前ら。脱出の時間だ。",--We are done, gang. Time to go.
pln_mad_52_01 = "よし、あのレーダーが対空砲を制御しているな。爆破しろ。",--Alright, that's the radar controlling the anti-air gun. Blow it to hell.
pln_mad_52_02 = "あのレーダーが対空砲を制御しているな。爆破する必要があるぞ。",--That radar is controlling the anti-air gun. Need to blow it up.
pln_mad_52_03 = "あのレーダーが対空砲を制御しているようだ。爆破する必要があるな。",--Seems that radar is controlling the anti-air gun. You need to blow it up.
pln_mad_53_01 = "Bileが何とか爆薬を投下できたようだ。着陸地点の近くに落ちてるはずだ、確保してくれ。",--Bile managed to drop some explosives for you. They should be near where you landed, so grab 'em.
pln_mad_53_02 = "Bileが着陸地点の近くに爆薬を投下したようだ。探してくれ。",--Bile dropped some explosives close to your landing spot. Find them.
pln_mad_53_03 = "お前ら、着陸地点の周囲を探してくれ。Bileがお前らのために爆薬を投下したぞ。",--Guys, search the spot where you landed. Bile has dropped some explosives for you.
pln_mad_54_01 = "素晴らしい、爆薬を手に入れたな。よし、レーダーに取り付けるんだ。",--Excellent, you got the explosives. Now, plant them on the radar.
pln_mad_54_02 = "よし、爆薬を見つけたな。レーダーに向かい、そいつで爆破するんだ。",--Good, you found the explosives. Head over to the radar and blow it up.
pln_mad_54_03 = "爆薬を手に入れたか?いいぞ。レーダーに行き、爆破できるようにそいつを設置するんだ。",--You got the explosives? Great. Get over to the radar and plant them so we can blow it up.
pln_mad_55_01 = "お前ら、あのレーダーを爆破する必要があるんだぞ。",--Gang, you still need to blow up that radar.
pln_mad_55_02 = "レーダーはまだ稼働中だ。爆薬を使って爆破するんだ。",--The radar is still operational. Use the explosives and blow it up.
pln_mad_55_03 = "お前ら、何でまだレーダーが稼動しているんだ?あれは破壊する必要がある。Bileが投下した爆薬を使うんだ!",--Guys, the radar is still operational? You need to destroy it. Use the explosives Bile dropped!
pln_mad_56_01 = "あのレーダーは何とかして停止させる必要がある。対空砲で爆破できないか確かめてくれ。",--That radar needs to be taken down somehow. See if you can use the anti-air gun to blow it up.
pln_mad_56_02 = "俺たちはあのレーダーの動作を止める必要がある。対空砲のミサイルが使えるんじゃないか。試してみるんだ。",--We need to take that radar out of action. The missiles from the anti-air gun should do the work. See if you can use it.
pln_mad_56_03 = "レーダーを急いで止める必要がある。対空砲の向きを変えれば爆破できるんじゃないか?",--The radar needs to be taken down ASAP. Maybe you could redirect the anti-air gun and blow it up?
pln_mad_57_01 = "ミサイルをレーダーに撃ち込むんだ!",--Bring those missiles over to the radar!
pln_mad_57_02 = "ミサイルはちゃんと動くな。レーダーを片付けるんだ!",--Those missiles will do the work. Get them over to the radar!
pln_mad_57_03 = "やったぜ。ミサイルは完璧だ。レーダーに向けて発射しろ。",--Hell yeah. Those missiles are perfect. Take them to the radar.
pln_mad_58_01 = "ミサイルをレーダーの隣に置いて起動するんだ。簡単だろ。",--Place the missiles next to the radar and activate them. Easy peasy.
pln_mad_58_02 = "ミサイルをレーダーの近くに設置して起動するんだ。ドカーンってなるぜ。",--Get the missiles close to the radar and activate them. Things are about to go BOOM.
pln_mad_58_03 = "ミサイルをレーダーの所に置いて起動するんだ。それで上手くいくはずだ。",--Place the missiles by the radar and activate them. That should do the trick.
pln_mad_59_01 = "よくやった、お前ら。BileはEMPの輸送中で、製材所の近くに投下予定だ。",--Great job, gang. Bile is on his way with the EMP now and will drop it close to the lumber mill.
pln_mad_59_02 = "対空防御システムを無力化したおかげで、Bileは自由に飛行してEMPを製材所の近くに落とすことができる。",--With the anti-air defenses out of the way, Bile has free passage to drop the EMP close to the lumber mill.
pln_mad_59_03 = "素晴らしいぞ、お前ら。対空防御システムは無力化された。BileはEMPを製材所の近くに落とすことができる。",--Excellent, gang. With the anti-air defenses gone, Bile can now drop the EMP close to the lumber mill.
pln_mad_60_01 = "対空砲があるな。あれを爆破するのは自滅を意味している。あのノートパソコンを使って、ハッキングする必要があるぞ。",--There's the AA gun. Blowing this up would mean blowing ourselves up. We need to hack it, get me access to that laptop.
pln_mad_60_02 = "こいつを無力化するには、接続されているノートパソコンをハッキングする必要がある。",--To disable this we need to hack the laptop that is hooked up to it.
pln_mad_60_03 = "たとえレーダーを爆破しても、奴らはノートパソコンでこいつを制御することができる。俺たちはこいつをハッキングする必要がある。",--Even if we blow up the radar, they can still control this from the laptop. We need to hack it.
pln_mad_61_01 = "EMPには2つの役割がある。秘密の研究所への道を作ること。だがもっと重要なのは実験体を気絶させることだ。奴らと戦闘する必要はないそうだ。",--The EMP will do two things: It will get us a way in to the hidden lab. But more importantly: It will knock out whoever they are doing tests on, from what I heard fighting them is not an option.
pln_mad_61_02 = "EMPの効果は中に入る道を作るだけでなく、実験体を気絶させることだ。信じろ、お前らだって奴らと戦いたくはないだろ。",--The EMP will not only give us a way in, but also knock out the test subjects. Trust me you don't want to deal with these guys.
pln_mad_61_03 = "EMPの効果は中に入る道を作ること、だが最も重要なのは実験体の処理効果の方だ。それがなければ、この話は引き受けなかったはずだ。",--The emp will give us a way in but it's primary function is to take care of the test subjects for us. If the stories are true, we don't want to take these guys on.
pln_mad_62_01 = "Elepantはハッキリ言っていたぞ。ブリーフケースを忘れるなってな! 探せ!",--The elephant specifically told me not to forget the briefcase! Find it!
pln_mad_62_02 = "ブリーフケースがないと脱出できないぞ!",--We can not leave without that briefcase!
pln_mad_62_03 = "お前ら、どうした?ブリーフケースがないと脱出できないぞ。",--Gang what's going on? We are not leaving without the briefcase.
pln_mad_63_01 = "こいつに何が起こったんだ!? まぁいい、必要なのはこいつの手だ。",--What the hell happened to this guy?! Whatever, we need this guys hand.
pln_mad_63_02 = "どんな奴がこんな風にしたんだ?まぁ、俺たちはこいつの手を切断する必要があるんだが...",--What kind of animal would do a thing like this? And now we need to chop off his hand...
pln_mad_63_03 = "都合がいいな、こいつが逃げないのは。手を切断してスキャナーに置いてくれ。",--How convenient, he won't run away now. Cut off his hand and bring it to the scanner.
rb14_drk_cbf_01_01 = "",--To get our hands on the EMP bomb, we're gonna have to mess with fuckin' Murkywater. They're transporting a bunch of goods via train, and will be making a scheduled stop at a hidden train yard. I, of course, would prefer to do it guns blazing, but that's too risky, yeah? So we need to this the stealthy way, lads.$NL;$NL;» Find the trains$NL;» Locate the EMP bomb parts$NL;» Get them out of there and escape
rb14_drk_outro_01_01 = "",--Smooth as silk, boys and girls! With the EMP bomb secured we now got what we need to breach the hidden facility. Mother Russia - here we come!
rb14_drk_outro_01_02 = "",--Fucking lovely, lads! With the EMP bomb secured we can breach the underground facility. It's time to go to mother fucking Russia!
rb14_drk_outro_02_01 = "",--Fuck, the alarm went off, but we made it. We good. Fucking Murkies won't know what hit them. Akan, however, will be mad as fuck. The thought of that kind of pleases me.
rb14_mad_cbf_01_01 = "",--This dirty Russian organization is conducting some very disturbing experiments from a hidden laboratory in Russia. You won't believe what shit they're doing over there. We need to fuckin' stop Akan from getting his hands on the data, yeah? It's do or die, boys and girls.$NL;$NL;» Enter the compound$NL;» Gain access to the lab$NL;» Obtain the data$NL;» Escape
pln_drk_brf_01_01 = "正直に言うぞ。俺たちはAkanを裏切るという大きなリスクを負おうとしているが、俺はこれが正しい道だと信じている。まず最初はMurkywaterによって搬送されているEMP爆弾を盗む。予定によれば奴ら、しばらく停止することになっているようだから、そこに付けこむ。静かに侵入し、EMPを見つけ、脱出する。この仕事はステルスで行う必要がある。それなりの恰好をしていけ。",--I'm not gonna lie; we are taking a huge risk by double-crossing Akan, but I believe this is the right choice. First thing is getting the EMP bomb that is being transported by Murkywater. They will be making a scheduled stop. That will be our chance. Get in quietly, find the EMP, then get out of there. You need to do this by stealth, so dress the part.
pln_drk_intro_01_01 = "情報によると例のEMP爆弾は2つに分かれるって話で、俺たちの目当てはそいつだ。とはいえ、もし他にも金目の物が手に入りそうなら頂くべきだな。",--Intel tells us the EMP bomb will be two parts, and that's what we're here for. But with that said; if you see an opportunity to grab other valuable loot you should do it.
pln_drk_intro_01_01a = "俺達の懐に金が入るほどLockeからの覚えも良くなるだろうよ。",--More money in our pockets and it should also win us some favor with Locke.
pln_drk_01_01 = "よし、お前ら。操車場は目の前だ。侵入ルートはいくつかあるだろうから、適切なのを選んでくれ。",--Okay, gang. The train yard is right in front of you. There should be several ways you can infiltrate the place, so make your choices wisely.
pln_drk_01_01a = "忘れるなよ、静かにやるんだ。もしアラームが鳴ったらおしまいだぞ。",--Remember, we are doing this silent. If the alarm goes off we're screwed.
pln_drk_01_02 = "よし、ここはうってつけだ。操車場がほぼ見渡せるぞ。巡回してる警備員とカメラを把握するんだ。",--Okay, guys, this is a good spot. You almost have a clear view of the train yard. Keep track of the patrolling guards and cameras.
pln_drk_01_02a = "段取りを考えるチャンスだ。",--This is your chance to plan your course of action.
pln_drk_01_03 = "そこだな、例の操車場は。今のうちに場内を観察するんだ。現場はMurky共とカメラで厳重警戒されてるから、一つのミスも許されないぞ。",--That's it, the hidden train yard. Use this opportunity to scout the area. The place is heavily guarded by Murkies and cameras, so we can't afford to make any mistakes.
pln_drk_02_01 = "侵入ルートを探してMurkywaterの列車を見つけろ。例のEMPの部品はそれぞれ別の貨車にある可能性が高い。",--Find your way inside and locate the Murkywater trains. The EMP parts will most likely be in different wagons.
pln_drk_02_02 = "侵入してMurkywaterの列車を探すんだ。まず簡単に見つかるだろうぜ。",--Get in and look for the Murkywater trains. You should be able to spot them fairly easy.
pln_drk_02_02a = "EMP爆弾は2つのパーツに分かれている。もちろん両方必要だぞ。",--Remember that the EMP bomb is two parts and I don't have to remind you we need both.
pln_drk_02_03 = "EMP爆弾のパーツが積まれた列車を探せ。それが一番の目的だろ。",--Focus on finding the trains containing the EMP bomb parts. That's our main priority.
pln_drk_03_01 = "野郎共、Murkywaterの列車を探すんだ。",--Guys, find the Murkywater trains.
pln_drk_03_02 = "Murkywaterの列車は見分けがつきやすい。探せ。",--The trains belonging to Murkywater should be easy to spot. Find them.
pln_drk_03_03 = "Murkywaterの列車を見つけられないなら、EMP爆弾は手に入らないぞ。",--If you don't find the Murkywater trains, we're not getting the EMP bomb.
pln_drk_04_01 = "よし、Murkywaterの列車を探すんだ。",--Okay, now you need to look for the actual Murkywater trains.
pln_drk_04_01a = "そいつには横にパネルが付いている。",--They should have some kind of panels on the side.
pln_drk_04_02 = "Murkywaterの列車はセキュリティパネルでロックされている。扉を開けるにはそいつをハッキングしないといけないだろう。",--The Murkywater trains will be locked by some kind of security panel. We'll most likely have to hack them to get the doors open.
pln_drk_04_03 = "Murkywaterの列車は側面にセキュリティパネルがある。だから開けるのにそいつをハッキングしないといけないぞ。",--The Murkywater trains will have a security panel on the side, so we'll have to hack them open.
pln_drk_05_01 = "セキュリティパネルを探すんだ、ギャング。それしか入る方法はない。",--Look for the security panel, gang. That's the only way in.
pln_drk_05_02 = "扉を開けるにはパネルをハッキングするしかない。探せ。",--Only way to get the doors open is by hacking the panel. Find it.
pln_drk_05_03 = "セキュリティパネルを見つければ扉を開けられるぞ。",--Find the security panel so we can get that door open.
pln_drk_06_01 = "よし、入れたな。EMPのパーツはどこかにあるはず。探せ。",--Excellent, you got in. The EMP parts should be there somewhere. Find it.
pln_drk_06_02 = "侵入したな。さあ、EMPのパーツを探すんだ。",--We're in. Now look for the EMP parts.
pln_drk_06_03 = "いいぞ。EMPのパ－ツがあるか見て回るんだ。",--Good job. Look around and see if you can find the EMP parts.
pln_drk_07_01 = "ちゃんと目を開けてEMPを見つけるんだ。頼むよ。",--Open your eyes and find the EMP. Come on.
pln_drk_07_02 = "EMPのパーツを探すんだ。それが一番の目的だ。",--Look for the EMP parts. That's top priority.
pln_drk_07_03 = "ギャング、EMPのパーツを探してるのか?",--Gang, are you looking for the EMP parts?
pln_drk_08_01 = "クソ! もうひとつセキュリティドアを設置してあるとはな...",--Damn! They have set up an additional security door...
pln_drk_08_02 = "なんだこりゃ? Elephantの資料にはもうひとつドアがあるなんて書いてなかったぞ...",--What the hell? Elephant's sources didn't mention an additional security door...
pln_drk_08_03 = "クソ、なんでここにドアが?すまない、ギャング。これがあるなんて知らなかったんだ...",--Damn, where did this door come from? Sorry, gang. I had no information this would be here...
pln_drk_09_01 = "...ここを通るためにはKeycardが必要なようだな...",--... looks like we're going to need a keycard to get past this...
pln_drk_10_01 = "警備員の誰かがどこかにKeycardを置いてるだろう。探すんだ。",--I bet one of the guards has left a keycard somewhere. Look around.
pln_drk_11_01 = "ギャング、Keycardなしではここを通ることは出来ないらしい。探すんだ。",--Gang, without a keycard we're not getting past that door. Look for it.
pln_drk_11_02 = "お前ら、まだKeycardが必要だ。",--Guys, we still need a keycard.
pln_drk_11_03 = "どこかにKeycardがあるに違いない。",--There must be a keycard somewhere.
pln_drk_11_04 = "ドアを開けるのにKeycardが必要なんだって。なあ。",--You really need to find a keycard to get that door open. Come on.
pln_drk_12_01 = "よくやった。Keycardを見つけたな。さあ、列車に戻ってあのクソドアを開けよう。",--Excellent, you found a keycard. Now, head back to the train and open that sucker.
pln_drk_12_02 = "探していたKeycardだな。列車に戻ってドアを開けるんだ。",--That's the keycard we needed. Get back to the train and open the door.
pln_drk_13_01 = "そのKeycardでドアを開けられるはずだ。",--With that keycard we should be able to get the door opened.
pln_drk_13_02 = "ドアのところにKeycardを持って行け。",--Bring the keycard back to the door.
pln_drk_13_03 = "本当にKeycardがいるんだよ。な?",--You need to actually use the keycard, you know?
pln_drk_14_01 = "...直接通れはしないな。Blowtorchか何かが必要だ。",--... there is no direct way to get past this. We're gonna need a blowtorch or something.
pln_drk_15_01 = "ここはトレインヤードなんだから、その辺に道具があるだろう。何か見つけろ。Blowtorchがあればピッタリなんだがな。",--We're in a train yard, there should be tools laying around somewhere. See what you can find. A blowtorch would be perfect.
pln_drk_16_01 = "野郎共、Blowtorchを探すんだ、じゃないと詰むぞ。",--Guys, you need to find a blowtorch otherwise we're screwed.
pln_drk_16_02 = "なあ、ギャング。Blowtorchを見つけてくれ。",--Come on, gang. Find a blowtorch.
pln_drk_16_03 = "まだBlowtorchを見つけてないぞ、ギャング。",--We still need to find a blowtorch, gang.
pln_drk_17_01 = "ふむ、驚いたな、Blowtorchを見つけたんだな。これであの扉を焼き切れるぞ。",--Well, I'll be damned, you found a blowtorch. Now we can burn our way through the door.
pln_drk_17_02 = "よし、本当にBlowtorchを見つけたな。列車に戻って扉を通るぞ。",--Great, you actually found a blowtorch. Head back to the train and get through that door.
pln_drk_17_03 = "いいぞ、Blowtorchを手に入れたな。あの扉を抜けるのを邪魔できるものはもう無いぞ。",--Good, you got your hands on a blowtorch. Nothing stopping us from getting through that door now.
pln_drk_18_01 = "野郎共、セキュリティドアに戻ってBlowtorchを使え。",--Guys, head back to the security door and use the blowtorch.
pln_drk_18_02 = "Blowtorchを見つけたな。さあ使うんだ。",--You found a blowtorch, and now you need to actually use it.
pln_drk_18_03 = "セキュリティドアに戻ってBlowtorchで開けるんだ。",--Get back to the security door and get it open using the blowtorch.
pln_drk_19_01 = "... 見たところ、その格子はかなり太いな。突破するには何かが必要になる。",--... by the looks of it, these bars are pretty thick. We're going to need something to help get through.
pln_drk_20_01 = "ここは工事中の箇所が多いな。何かあの鉄格子にタックル出来そうな物があるか探ってみろ。",--There is a lot of construction in this area. Check it out and see if you can find something to help us tackle that steel gate.
pln_drk_21_01 = "ギャング共、あの鉄格子を突破する手段が必要だ。利用できそうなものを探すんだ。",--Gang, we still need a way to get through that steel gate . You need to find something that we can use.
pln_drk_21_02 = "あの鉄格子を通るのに使えそうなものを探すんだ。",--You still need to find something we can use to get through those bars.
pln_drk_21_03 = "お前ら、何かあの鉄格子に使えそうな物を見つけるんだ。あまり音の立たない物だ。",--Guys, find something we can use on those bars. Something that doesn't give off too much noise.
pln_drk_22_01 = "Thermiteを見つけたのか?素晴らしい!あの鉄の門に戻って格子を溶かすんだ。",--You found thermite? Excellent! Head back to the steel gate and melt those bars.
pln_drk_22_02 = "いいぞ、Thermiteを見つけたな。これであの鉄格子を溶かして通れるぞ。",--Great, you found some thermite. Now we can melt our way through that steel gate.
pln_drk_22_03 = "Thermiteを手に入れたな、これであの鉄格子を簡単に溶かせるぞ。",--Now that you got your hands on some thermite, we can easily melt the bars on the gate.
pln_drk_23_01 = "あの防犯扉に戻ってThermiteを使うんだ。",--Get back to the security gate and use the thermite.
pln_drk_23_02 = "あの防犯扉を通り抜けるにはThermiteを使う必要がある。",--You need to use the thermite to get past that security gate.
pln_drk_23_03 = "防犯扉まで戻ってそこの格子を溶かすんだ。きっとうまくいく。",--Return to the security gate and melt those bars. It should work.
pln_drk_24_01 = "... こいつを開けるならドリルの事は忘れろ、音がでかすぎるからな。たぶんハックする方法があるんじゃないか?",--... we can forget about drilling our way through this. It would cause to much noise. Maybe we can find a way to hack it?
pln_drk_25_01 = "Murkywaterは自前の技術好きだから、持ち運び型の制御装置の類が近くにあるはずだ。見つかるか探してみろ。",--Murkywater like their technology, so they should have some kind of mobile command center nearby. See what you can find.
pln_drk_25_02 = "もしハードドライブが手に入れば、金庫のシステムをハック出来るんだが。",--If we could get our hands on a hard drive, we might be able to hack the system to the vault.
pln_drk_26_01 = "なあ、金庫のシステムをハックできる物か何かないと、あれは開けられないぞ。探し出せ!",--Gang, without something to hack the vault system, we're not getting it open. Keep looking!
pln_drk_26_02 = "金庫のシステムにハッキング出来る物が無いか、探すんだ。",--See if you can find something we can use to hack the vault system.
pln_drk_26_03 = "金庫のセキュリティシステムを突破するのに使える物が何か有るはずだ。",--There must be something we can use to get past the vault security system.
pln_drk_27_01 = "そのハードドライブならぴったりだ!接続してくれれば俺がシステムにアクセスして金庫を開けられるぞ。",--That hard drive will be perfect! Once you plug it in, I should be able to access their system and get the vault open.
pln_drk_27_02 = "このハードドライブなら奴らのセキュリティをオーバーライドさせて金庫を開けられるだろう。",--With this hard drive I should be able to override their security and get the vault open.
pln_drk_27_03 = "丁度欲しかった物だな!そのハードドライブを繋いだら俺に任せてくれ。あの金庫は一瞬で開くだろうぜ。",--Just what we needed! Plug that hard drive in and I'll take care of it. That vault should be opened in no time.
pln_drk_28_01 = "ハードドライブを金庫に持って行って繋いでくれ。",--Bring the hard drive back to the vault and plug it in.
pln_drk_28_02 = "貨物車両へ戻ってそのハードドライブを使うんだ。セキュリティをオーバーライド出来るはずだ。",--Get back to the train and use the hard drive. I should be able to override the security.
pln_drk_28_03 = "金庫の扉まで戻ってハードドライブを繋げ。その後は任せろ。",--Head back to the vault door and plug in the hard drive. I'll take care of the rest.
pln_drk_29_01 = "たぶんそいつは後で使い時が来るだろう。",--Maybe that equipment will come in handy later, so hold on to it.
pln_drk_29_02 = "もちろん、当たり前だな?後で使うかもしれないからな。",--Sure, why not? We might find use for it later.
pln_drk_29_03 = "決して間違った行動ではないぞ。後で役立つかもしれねえ。",--Could never go wrong with that, I guess. Might be somewhere it can be useful later.
pln_drk_30_01 = "そのCrowbarは、俺たちにオマケの戦利品を与えてくれるだろう。",--That crowbar will increase our chances of getting additional loot before we leave.
pln_drk_30_02 = "ようし、素早く設置された箱を開けられるぞ。良い物が入ってると思うぜ。",--Great, now we can open the crates laying around much faster. I bet you they contain some good stuff.
pln_drk_30_03 = "お前がオマケの戦利品にこだわるつもりなら、そのCrowbarで細工できるだろう。",--If you're planning on sticking around for extra loot, that crowbar will do the trick.
pln_drk_31_01 = "よし、EMPを盗むために必要なものが全てそろった。列車に戻るぞ。",--Okay, now we got all we need to steal the EMP parts. Head back to the trains.
pln_drk_31_02 = "それだ、ギャング。すぐ列車に戻ってEMPを手に入れよう。",--That's it, gang. Now get back to the trains and get your hands on the EMP bomb.
pln_drk_31_03 = "よし。列車に戻ってEMPをバッグに詰める時間だ。",--Okay. Time to head back to the trains and get that EMP in the bag.
pln_drk_32_01 = "ギャング、EMPを取るんだ。",--Gang, we still need to get the EMP.
pln_drk_32_02 = "列車に戻ってEMPを入手しろ。",--Get back to the trains and get the EMP.
pln_drk_32_03 = "もはやEMPを手に入れるのを邪魔できるモンはない。列車に戻るんだ。",--Nothing stopping us from getting our hands on the EMP. Get back to the trains.
pln_drk_33_01 = "よし、目的のブツは手に入ったな。脱出地点に行ってEMPを確保しろ。",--Excellent, we got what we came for. Get over to the escape area and secure the EMP.
pln_drk_33_02 = "よくやったな。それじゃ、他の戦利品をいただく前に脱出地点でEMPを確保しようか。",--Good job. Now, secure the EMP at the escape area before grabbing any additional loot.
pln_drk_33_03 = "でかした!脱出地点にEMP爆弾を置いてこい。",--Great job! Head over to the escape area and drop off the EMP bomb.
pln_drk_34_01 = "お前ら、まだ脱出地点でEMPの確保が残ってるぞ。",--Guys, you still need to secure the EMP at the escape area.
pln_drk_34_02 = "EMPを脱出地点に置いてこい。危険は冒したくないからな。",--Leave the EMP at the escape area. We don't wanna risk it.
pln_drk_34_03 = "EMPを脱出地点で確保してこい。安全第一だ。",--Secure the EMP over by the escape area. Better to be safe than sorry.
pln_drk_35_01 = "オーケー、目的のEMPは確保したな。だがその気なら引き返してさらに戦利品を頂くだけの時間はあるぞ。",--Okay, the EMP has been secured, which is what we came for. But there is still time to head back and get additional loot if you feel up for it.
pln_drk_35_02 = "素晴らしい、EMPを確保したぞ。もし脱出する前にもっと戦利品が欲しいなら構わない。お前たち次第だ。",--Excellent, we got the EMP secured. I won't blame you if you want to get some extra loot before you escape. Up to you.
pln_drk_35_03 = "EMPは確保したから、脱出の迎えが来るまで暇つぶしだ。",--With the EMP secured, there is some time to kill before the escape vehicle arrives.
pln_drk_35_03a = "戻ってお宝をいくつか頂いてきたらどうだ?報酬は出すぜ。",--Why not go back and get some of that juicy loot? I'll make it worth your time.
pln_drk_36_01 = "聞いてくれ、みんな。脱出用のボートを向かわせた。川の側で待っててくれ。",--Listen up, gang. I'm sending in a boat to pick you up. Look for the small water access near the river.
pln_drk_36_02 = "おい、お前らの脱出用ドライバーはボートで来てもらうことにした。川沿いの場所に来るぞ。",--Hey, I got your escape driver coming in by boat. Head over to the small water access area near the river.
pln_drk_36_03 = "脱出用のドライバーはボートで迎えに来る。川沿いの通路を確保しておけ。",--The escape driver is coming in by boat to pick you up. Make sure you are over by the small water access near the river.
pln_drk_37_01 = "聞けギャング、Twitchが車で向かっている。奴は上の橋の方から来る。",--Listen up, gang. Twitch is coming in with the van. He will come from the upper bridge side.
pln_drk_37_02 = "Twitchがお前らを迎えに車で来ている。奴は上の橋の方来るぞ。",--Twitch is arriving with the van to pick you up. He'll wait by the upper bridge side.
pln_drk_37_03 = "車にその場所までのルートを送っておいた。Twitchは上の橋の方から来る。",--Sending the van your way. Twitch will come from the upper bridge side.
pln_drk_38_01 = "おい、この通気孔は体を隠したり戦利品を運ばなくちゃならん時には絶好の設備だぜ。",--Hey, these vents should be perfect if you need hide a body or transfer loot through.
pln_drk_38_02 = "この換気システムは使えそうだな、ほら、死体を隠したり何か運んだりするのにな。",--This ventilation system could be used to our advantage, you know, to hide a body or transfer some of the extra through.
pln_drk_39_01 = "もし警備員を倒すことになったら、車両の下なら見つからず死体を隠せるだろうぜ。",--If you happen to drop one of the guards, you should be able to hide the body under the train so it doesn't get detected.
pln_drk_39_02 = "誰も殺さないようにしろ、それでやむを得ない場合は死体を車両の下に隠せば安心だ。",--Try not killing anyone, but if it has to be done, then hiding the body under the train should be safe.
pln_drk_40_01 = "くそ、ありゃドローンかよ?まったく俺たちゃ未来にきちまったのか?奴らカメラを載せてるようだから映されないようにしろよ。",--Damn, are those drones? We're really living in the future, aren't we? They seem to have a camera so stay out of sight.
pln_drk_40_02 = "カメラつきドローン、マジかよ? Murkywaterめ、気合が入ってるな。お前ら、発見されないように注意しろ。",--Drones with cameras, really? Murkywater are stepping up their game. Be careful that you don't get spotted.
pln_drk_41_01 = "よし、邪魔者がひとつ減ったな。だが気をつけろ、ガードが故障したドローンを見逃す訳無いからな。",--Nice, you took that sucker out. But hide the mess. The guards will react if they find out you destroyed one of their drones.
pln_drk_41_02 = "",--Good job, that drone won't be here to witness the robot revolution. But make sure you hide the pile of junk. We can't have one of the guards finding it.
pln_drk_42_01 = "",--Guys, you can't have searched the whole train yard. You must be missing something.
pln_drk_42_02 = "",--Have you searched through the whole train yard?
pln_drk_42_03 = "",--Don't get lazy, gang. Search the whole train yard if needed.
pln_drk_43_01 = "",--Guys, the maintenance tunnels could have what we're looking for.
pln_drk_43_02 = "",--The maintenance tunnels could have what you're looking for. Search it.
pln_drk_43_03 = "",--It might be worth to check the maintenance tunnels.
pln_drk_44_01 = "",--There's several rooms in the maintenance tunnels. Have you checked all of them?
pln_drk_44_02 = "",--There's a bunch of rooms in the maintenance tunnels. Check all of them.
