plt_mad_intro_01 = "何てことだ! 奴ら周りに対空防御を敷きやがってる! 飛行機の向きを変えろ、Bile! お前らはパラシュートを使って脱出だ。すぐに!",--Damn! They have anti-air defenses set up around the whole factory. Turn the plane around, Bile! Gang, you need to use the parachutes and get out! Right now!
plt_mad_intro_02 = "クソ! あの畜生ども対空防御を敷いてやがる! Bile、飛行機の向きをすぐに変えろ! お前らパラシュートを使って脱出だ!",--Shit! These bastards have anti-air defenses set up! Bile, turn the plane around immediately! Guys, use the parachutes and get out! We'll figure something out!
plt_mad_intro_03 = "対空防御だと? 冗談だろ? 飛行機の向きを変えろBile! お前ら、パラシュートを持って飛び出せ!",--Anti-air defenses?! Are you shitting me?! Turn the plane around, Bile! Do it now! Guys, take the parachutes and jump out!
plt_mad_02_01 = "兄弟、爆弾は何とか落とせたぜ。うまくやれよ。",--Comrads! I managed to throw out some explosives for you, better to be prepared.
plt_mad_02_02 = "C4は騒ぎの中に落とした。探せよ。",--I dropped some C4 in a rush, look around for them.
plt_mad_02_03 = "お前ら兄弟にプレゼントは投下した。ナイスなC4のバッグだ。",--There is a present down there for you comrads. A nice bag of C4.
plt_mad_03_01 = "時間は貴重だ、兄弟。対空を何とかしてくれよ。",--Time is precious comrads. Get those anti-airs down.
plt_mad_03_02 = "EMPは重いし俺の燃料も限られてる。早く落としたいんだ!",--The EMP is heavy and my fuel is limited. I need to drop it soon!
plt_mad_03_03 = "対空の処理はまだなのかい、兄弟?",--Are those anti-airs disabled yet comrads?
plt_mad_04_01 = "無効化が確認できたぜ! 待ってろよ、EMPを運んでやるからな。",--I see that you have disabled the guns! Hold on, I'm coming with the EMP.
plt_mad_04_02 = "30秒くれればEMPを落としてやるぜ。",--Give me 30 seconds and I will drop that EMP.
plt_mad_04_03 = "EMPを持って駆けつけるぜ。",--Flying in with the EMP right now.
plt_mad_05_01 = "ハハッ、きっちり製材所の中だ、美しく決まった。",--HA HA. Right in the lumber mill, that was beautiful.
plt_mad_05_02 = "しっかり既定の場所に落とした。",--Dropped it right on spot.
plt_mad_05_03 = "まっすぐ屋根を突き抜けて、バーン!",--Straight through the roof. BOOM!
plt_mad_06_01 = "",--Huh, well it's on the outside. Should work anyway right?
plt_mad_06_02 = "俺としたことが20メートルも所定地から外した、申し訳ない。",--Oh damn I missed the spot by 20 meters, sorry comrads.
plt_mad_06_03 = "しっかりと剥き出しで着地した。チンコ!",--It landed right out in the open. Zalupa!
plt_mad_06_04 = "",--It landed right out in the open.
plt_mad_07_01 = "完了か? 湖に着地する。ずらかる準備しとけよ。",--All done huh? I will land by the lake, prepare to extract.
plt_mad_07_02 = "兄弟、こっちに来い、そこら中敵だらけだ。逃げ時だ!",--Comrads get over here, soldiers everywhere. Time to leave!
plt_mad_07_03 = "焦らんでもいいぞ。飛行機はお前らを待っている。",--Take your time comrads. The plane is waiting for you.
rb14_mad_outro_01_01 = "",--We fuckin' did it, lads! We stopped that white-haired fucking freak from getting the data he was after. So, what do you say? What do you say? We burn it, yeah? Burn it straight to fuckin' hell!
pln_hlp_01_01 = "クソっ、何処だここは?",--Damn, what is this place?
pln_hlp_01_02 = "刑務所か? 俺は好きじゃないな...",--A prison? Not my favourite thing...
pln_hlp_01_03 = "うーむ... どこだか分らんな...",--I... don't know where we are...
pln_hlp_02_01 = "刑務所に入る方法を見つけないとな。",--Let's find a way into the prison.
pln_hlp_02_02 = "俺たちはたぶん刑務所に入る必要があるぞ。",--We probably need to enter the prison...
pln_hlp_02_03 = "俺は刑務所に入るべきだと思う。",--I think we need to get into the prison.
pln_hlp_03_01 = "Keycardが必要だ。だが何処にあるんだろうな?",--We need a keycard to get into the prison. But where can we get one?
pln_hlp_03_02 = "Keycard無しでは入れん。見つけるしかないぞ。",--We can't get in without a keycard. We need to find one.
pln_hlp_03_03 = "このゲートはKeycardが必要みたいだ。見つけるぞ!",--Looks like this gate requires a keycard. Find one guys!
pln_hlp_04_01 = "選択肢など無いと思う。ルーレットを回すしかない。",--I don't think we have a choice. We have to spin that wheel!
pln_hlp_04_02 = "このルーレットの景品など見たくもないが、回すしかないようだな。",--I don't like the look of the prizes on that wheel, but I think we have to spin it anyway.
pln_hlp_04_03 = "回して、何が起きるか確かめてみよう。",--Spin it, let's see what happens.
pln_hlp_05_01 = "スナイパー? ...スナイパーが出たぞ。",--Sniper? It... landed on sniper.
pln_hlp_05_02 = "スナイパーに止まった。どういう意味なのかは分らん...",--The wheel stopped on sniper. I'm not sure what that means...
pln_hlp_05_03 = "",--Soooo the wheel stopped on sniper...
pln_hlp_06_01 = "",--It landed on sniper again. Get ready guys
pln_hlp_06_02 = "",--The wheel stopped on sniper!
pln_hlp_06_03 = "",--The wheel has decided, looks like we have some more snipers incoming.
pln_hlp_07_01 = "炎?",--Flames?
pln_hlp_07_02 = "",--It landed on flames... That can't be good.
pln_hlp_07_03 = "",--The wheel stopped on flames, I don't think that is a good thing.
pln_hlp_08_01 = "",--The wheel stopped on flames. Things are about to burn!
pln_hlp_08_02 = "",--Ok the wheel landed on flames again, watch out!
pln_hlp_08_03 = "",--Flames, that means the flamethrower again!
pln_hlp_09_01 = "スモーク?",--Smoke?
pln_hlp_09_02 = "スモークに止まった。意味は分らん。",--The wheel stopped on smoke, no idea what that means.
pln_hlp_09_03 = "",--Smoke? The wheel stopped on smoke?
pln_hlp_10_01 = "",--The wheel stopped on smoke!
pln_hlp_10_02 = "",--Yep, it's smoke again!
pln_hlp_10_03 = "",--Smoke incoming guys!
pln_hlp_11_01 = "",--Drills? Not sure what that is...
pln_hlp_11_02 = "",--The wheel stopped on drills. Do you guys know what that means?
pln_hlp_11_03 = "止まったのはドリルだ。よく分らない。",--The wheel has stopped. It says drills. I got no clue.
pln_hlp_12_01 = "",--It stopped on drills. Move away!
pln_hlp_12_02 = "",--Watch out! It stopped on drills again!
pln_hlp_12_03 = "",--Drills incoming!
pln_hlp_13_01 = "",--Hmm.. I wonder what the question mark means.
pln_hlp_13_02 = "?マーク... どうなるんだ?",--Question marks? What could that be?
pln_hlp_13_03 = "何だ? ハテナに止まったぞ。意味はあるんだろうが...",--What? It stopped on the question marks. That could mean anything.
pln_hlp_14_01 = "気をつけろ。 ?マークに止まったぞ。",--Careful guys! The wheel stopped on the question marks.
pln_hlp_14_02 = "",--Question marks again. Be ready for anything.
pln_hlp_14_03 = "",--It stopped on the question marks again.
pln_hlp_15_01 = "",--Dozer? Hmmm....
pln_hlp_15_02 = "止まったのは... dozer? 気をつけろ、何が起きるか分らん。",--The wheel stopped on... dozer? Be careful guys Im not sure what that means.
pln_hlp_15_03 = "",--Dozer? That can't be good.
pln_hlp_16_01 = "",--The wheel stopped on the dozer again. Watch out guys!
pln_hlp_16_02 = "",--The wheel stopped. Get ready for another bulldozer guys!
pln_hlp_16_03 = "",--Get ready for another bulldozer!
pln_hlp_17_01 = "タイマーを守れ。SWATが邪魔しにくるぞ!",--Protect the timer, the swats will interrupt it if you don't!
pln_hlp_17_02 = "ポリ公どもにタイマーを止められるなよ!",--Don't let the cops stop the timer!
pln_hlp_17_03 = "SWATどもにタイマーの邪魔をさせるな!",--Don't let the swats interrupt that timer!
pln_hlp_18_01 = "タイマーが妨害されたぞ! 再起動だ!",--They interrupted the timer! Restart it!
pln_hlp_18_02 = "奴らタイマーを止めやがった!",--Guys the timer stopped!
pln_hlp_18_03 = "クソっ、タイマーを止めやがった。起動しなおせ!",--Damn, they stopped it. Get it going again!
pln_hlp_18_04 = "タイマーを再起動するんだ。",--Get the timer going again.
pln_hlp_18_05 = "タイマーが止まったぞ! 再起動だ!",--The timer stopped! Restart it!
pln_hlp_18_06 = "再起動だ! 奴らに止められた。",--Restart the timer! They stopped it.
pln_hlp_18_07 = "タイマーがまだ止まったままだ。起動しなおせ!",--The timer is standing still. Get it going again!
pln_hlp_19_01 = "更新が完了すればタイマーは元に戻るはずだ!",--Once the reboot is over we should be back on track!
pln_hlp_19_02 = "更新が終われば再起動するはずだ。",--When the reboot has ticked down it should restart.
pln_hlp_19_03 = "更新中のカウンターが0になれば通常のカウンターに戻るはずだ。",--When the reboot has reached zero it should start the normal timer again.
