btc_fri_01_01 = "Bain、一日中こうしてるわけにはいかないわ。蛇が穴に隠れてるなら、頭を棒で突いてやるのよ。奴の大事な物を台無しにしてみたらどうかしら。",--Bain, we don't have all day here. If the snake hides in its hole, we must goad it into sticking its head out. Maybe you should try to destroy some of his precious things.
btc_fri_01_02 = "奴が隠れて出てこないなら、おびき出すまでよ。奴の大事な宝物を壊してみましょう。",--If he's going to hide away, we'll have to draw him out. You could start destroying his treasured possessions and see if that does it.
btc_fri_01_03 = "奴が頭を出さないなら、おびき出すしかないわね。奴の持ち物を壊して怒らせれば出てきて戦おうとするかもしれない。",--If he's not going to stick his head out, we'll have to draw him out. Start destroying his things and see if that makes him mad enough to come out and fight.
btc_fri_02_01 = "絵画だけじゃ足りないようね。もっと揺さぶる必要があるわ。",--Seems the paintings are not enough. We must hit him harder.
btc_fri_02_02 = "そこまで大事な絵画じゃなかったようね。他に何かないか探してみて。",--He obviously didn't care enough about those paintings. You need to find something else.
btc_fri_02_03 = "絵画のコレクションだけじゃ苦しみ足りないようね。何か別のものを試してみましょう。",--So destroying his art collection didn't hurt enough. Let's try something else then.
btc_fri_03_01 = "奴の心の鍵は車にあったのね。これで弾丸を食らわせられるわ。",--The key to his heart was in the cars. Now go put a bullet through it.
btc_fri_03_02 = "奴は車オタクだったのね、そう... すぐに車の後を追えるわ。",--So he's a car freak. Well... soon he will be a dead car freak.
btc_fri_03_03 = "男ってどうしてこう車好きなの? まあいいわ、これで入れる。奴を始末して。",--What is it with some men and cars? Nevermind, you are in now. Kill him.
btc_fri_04_01 = "Ernesto Sosaは警備員に守られてるけど、あなた達ならなんとか出来るわ。",--So Ernesto Sosa is hiding behind his guards. You can handle it, I'm sure.
btc_fri_04_02 = "警備員を始末して、Ernesto Sosaはそれからよ。",--Kill the guards. Then you can kill Ernesto Sosa.
btc_fri_04_03 = "警備員を始末すれば、奴をやれるわ。",--If you kill his guards, you will get to him.
btc_fri_05_01 = "お見事ね。Ernesto Sosaは死んだ。私の期待通りよ。",--Good job. Ernesto Sosa is dead. My point has been made.
btc_fri_05_02 = "これは教訓よ、\"The Butcher を舐めるな\"。あなたたちの協力に感謝するわ。",--This will be a lesson to all: Don't fuck with The Butcher. Thank you for your help, my friends.
btc_fri_05_03 = "メッセージは届けられたわ。Ernesto Sosaは死んだ。仕事は完了ね。",--The message has been delivered. Ernesto Sosa is dead. Your work here is done.
btc_fri_06_01 = "警報も鳴らさず大したものね。その調子でお願い。",--Good job on not raising the alarm. Keep it up.
btc_fri_06_02 = "お見事よ。静かなものね。",--Well done. You move silently.
btc_fri_06_03 = "無音で潜入する達人ね。これからもっと仕事を頼みたくなるわ。",--You are skilled and silent infiltrators. We should work together more often.
btc_fri_07_01 = "Ernesto Sosaはオフィスに特殊な施錠システムを設けていて、合言葉を使うの。でも対策はしてあるわ、うちの手下が売りつけたボイスレコーダー入りの特別なコカインよ。探してみて。",--Ernesto Sosa has a special lock system for his office, with a spoken pass phrase. But I have planned for it - I had my people sell some special cocaine to him, with a microphone recorder hidden in the package. See if you can find it.
btc_fri_07_02 = "Ernesto Sosaのオフィスには特殊な施錠システムがあって、合言葉を使うの。そこで私の手下がボイスレコーダー入りのコカイン袋を売ったから、それを探して。",--There's an unusual lock system for Ernesto Sosa's office, using a spoken pass phrase. But my people have smuggled in a special cocaine package, with a hidden microphone recorder. Find it.
btc_fri_07_03 = "あのオフィスは特殊な施錠システムがあるわ。合言葉を使うの。だからコカインの取引で特別なものを混ぜてやったわ。ボイスレコーダー入りよ。探してちょうだい。",--The office has a special lock system. It uses a spoken pass phrase. But I had a special cocaine package smuggled in through a drugs deal. It has a hidden microphone recorder in it. Find this package.
btc_fri_08_01 = "Ernesto Sosaに電話するには合言葉が必要よ。その辺にあるはずだわ。",--You need a pass phrase when you call Ernesto Sosa. The phrase should be on there.
btc_fri_08_02 = "Ernesto Sosaを呼び出す時に合言葉が必要になるわ。その辺にあるはずよ。",--The pass phrase is needed when you call Ernesto Sosa. It should be there.
btc_fri_08_03 = "合言葉を見つける必要があるわ。奴に電話する時に必要よ。",--You should find a pass phrase there. You'll need it when you call him.
btc_fri_09_01 = "Bainに合言葉を使って電話してもらいましょう。",--Bain will make the call with the pass phrase.
btc_fri_09_02 = "Bainに電話をかけてもらう。",--Bain will make the call.
btc_fri_09_03 = "Bain、電話を掛けてもらえる?",--Bain - can you make the call?
btc_fri_10_01 = "マヌケが引っ掛かったわね。行って始末してきて。",--The bastard bought it. Get in there and kill him.
btc_fri_10_02 = "まんまと騙せたようね。素晴らしいわ。すぐ奴を始末して。",--You tricked him. Excellent. Now kill him.
btc_fri_10_03 = "かかったわね。Mr.Sosa 最期の時がきたわ。奴によろしく伝えて。",--He bought it. The time has come to kill Mr. Sosa. Give him my regards.
btc_fri_11_01 = "音もなく殺すなんて、見事だわ。私を敵に回すとこうなるのよ。",--Very good, a silent kill. This is what happens to those who cross me.
btc_fri_12_01 = "Mr.Sosaは二度と私の邪魔は出来ない。恐らく、彼の友人たちもね。",--Mr. Sosa will not disrupt my operations again. Nor will his friends, I think.
btc_fri_12_02 = "メッセージは届いたわね。依頼は完了よ、ありがとう。",--The message has been delivered. The job is done, I thank you.
btc_fri_cbf_01 = "",--I have been running guns in the Caribbean for a while. It's been very profitable, but some of the old movers in the region don't approve of my presence on the local market. The Bolivian Sosa Cartel specifically. As they could not compete with me on level terms, they decided to attack my operation - sinking one of my ships, stealing my merchandise and killing my operatives. That was very unwise. Now they must pay. You will collect that payment, in blood.
btc_fri_cnc_01 = "カリブの海賊どもとモメてるの。マイアミに行って解決してくれないかしら。",--I've had some problems with pirates in the Caribbean. I need you to go to Miami and solve these problems for me.
btc_fri_cnc_02 = "Sosaカルテルがカリブ海で私の貨物船を襲った。奴らへの復讐をお願い。",--The Sosa Cartel has attacked one of my shipments in the Caribbean. They must pay, and you will collect this payment.
btc_fri_cnc_03 = "Sosaカルテルへメッセージを届けて欲しい。血で書かれたメッセージよ。",--I need you to deliver a message to the Sosa Cartel. A message written in blood.
btc_fri_end_a_01 = "Ernesto Sosaは夢にも思わなかったでしょうね。奴が死んだおかげで、マイアミのSosaどもは活動できなくなるわ。私の期待通りよ。",--Ernesto Sosa never saw it coming. With him dead, the Sosa's Miami operations lie in ruins. My point has been made.
btc_fri_end_a_02 = "奴ら何が起きたかわからないでしょうね、でも誰がやったかは解るはず。私を舐めるとどうなるかもね。",--They will wonder how this happened, but they will know who did it. And they will learn not to fuck with me.
btc_fri_end_a_03 = "称賛すべき手際ね。静かなる罰がErnesto Sosaに下ったわ、反省するには手遅れだけど。これで奴らもThe Butcherの恐ろしさを学んだはずよ。",--I applaud your skills. Punishment came to Ernesto Sosa silently, but with deadly certainty. They will learn to fear The Butcher.
btc_fri_end_b_01 = "Sosaカルテルは私を脅したことを後悔してるはずよ。奴らはマイアミで大きな顔ができなくなって、私は仕事がしやすくなる。私の\"メッセージ\"を届けてくれて感謝するわ。",--I believe the Sosa Cartel may now be regretting their decision to try to intimidate me. Their Miami operation now lies in ruins, and I can do business in peace again. Thank you for delivering my message.
btc_fri_end_b_02 = "これでSosaのマイアミでの活動は水の泡。奴らが私にちょっかい掛けてくることも無くなると思うわ。ありがとう。",--The Sosa's Miami operation is fucked. I don't think they will be giving me more problems. Thanks to you.
btc_fri_end_b_03 = "カリブの王はSosaカルテルじゃないって証明したわね。十分過ぎるほど分からせてやったわ。",--You have demonstrated that the Sosa Cartel does not own the Caribbean. With sufficient emphasis, I believe.
