pln_dah_56_02 = "余裕があればサファイアも取っておけ。",--Grab some sapphires if you have time.
pln_dah_56_03 = "欲しけりゃ帰るまでにサファイアも少し貰っとけ。",--If you want, grab some sapphires on the way out.
pln_dah_57_01 = "畜生! 奴らコードをロックしやがった。予備のプランに移るぞ。",--Damn! They locked out the code. Need a backup plan.
pln_dah_57_02 = "コードは無効化されたから、もういい。別の手を使うぞ。",--The code has been blocked, so forget about it. Going to need another solution.
pln_dah_57_03 = "プラン変更だ、コードが無効化されちまった!",--We need a change of plan, the code has been shut down!
pln_dah_58_01 = "手に入れたコードは無効化されちまったが、システムにはマスターコードが有るはずだ。少し調べさせてくれ。",--The code you have has been disabled, but I think the system has a master code. Let me do some digging.
pln_dah_58_02 = "くそ、こうなったら使えるのはマスターコードだけだ。誰が持ってるのか調べてみる。",--Damn, looks like the only thing that will work now is the master code. Let me see if I can find out who has it
pln_dah_58_03 = "奴らお前のコードを無効化したな。恐らく別に...マスターコードでもあるんだろう、持ってるやつを探す。",--They just disabled your code. There might be another- a master code, but I'll have to find out who has it.
pln_dah_59_01 = "くそ、だがもうコソコソしなくていいぞ。次のプランに移る。",--Damn, no need to be quiet any longer. Time for a new plan.
pln_dah_59_02 = "仕方ねえ、静かにこっそりなんてのはもう止めだ。少し考える時間をくれ。",--OK, forget about staying low and quiet. Gimme a moment to think of something.
pln_dah_59_03 = "もうコソコソ歩く必要はないぞ。次のプランがある。",--No need to sneak around any longer. New plan incoming.
pln_dah_60_01 = "順番を間違えたのか、これでマスターコードが見つかるまでシステムがロックされるぞ!",--That was the wrong sequence, now the system is locked unless you find the master code!
pln_dah_60_02 = "一体どうした? コードを間違えたのか? これでマスターコードが必要になったぞ。",--What the hell happened? Wrong code? You're going to need the master code now.
pln_dah_60_03 = "やっちまったな、こうなったら何とかしてマスターコードを見つけるんだ。",--You got it wrong, now we have to find the master code somehow.
pln_dah_61_01 = "アラーム作動だ!",--There goes the alarm!
pln_dah_61_02 = "くそ、今ので確実にお前の事がバレたな。",--Damn, they know you're there now for sure.
pln_dah_61_03 = "アラームが作動した。これで奴らに気づかれたな。",--Alarm is active. They know you're there now.
pln_dah_62_01 = "しょうがない、窓拭き用のゴンドラはもう無理だ。Zip-lineでバッグを運び出せ!",--OK, forget the window cleaning platform, you're going to have to use ziplines to move the bags out!
pln_dah_62_02 = "予定変更だ! 代わりにZip-lineでバッグを運び出せ!",--Change of plan! You'' have to use ziplines instead to secure the bags!
pln_dah_62_03 = "窓拭きのゴンドラはもうだめだ。代わりにZip-lineでバッグを運び出すんだ。",--The window cleaning platform is a no-go. Use ziplines to get the bags out instead.
pln_dah_63_01 = "サツのヘリが来るぞ!",--Cop choppers are inbound!
pln_dah_63_02 = "警官共がヘリで来るぞ、油断するな!",--Blues are on the way in choppers so keep your eyes open!
pln_dah_63_03 = "面倒なのがヘリでやって来るぞ。",--Hey gang, you got trouble comin' by helicopter.
pln_dah_64_01 = "まずセキュリティをバイパスしなきゃならん、2つのルーターを探せ!",--You still need to bypass security, so find those two routers!
pln_dah_64_02 = "プランBの用意はある、まずはルーターを見つけろ!",--I've come up with a plan B, just find those routers!
pln_dah_64_03 = "ルーターボックスを見つけろ、プランB進行中だ。",--Keep looking for those router boxes, I'm working on a plan B.
pln_dah_65_01 = "頼むぞ、お前らがルーターを見つけるまで俺は手が出せん!",--Hey guys, I can't do anything until you find those routers!
pln_dah_65_02 = "パーティを楽しむヒマはないぞ、出来るだけ早くルーターを見つけろ!",--No time to stop and party, find those routers ASAP!
pln_dah_65_03 = "ルーターを探せ!",--You need to find those routers!
pln_dah_65_04 = "ルーターが見つかるまで待ってるぞ。",--Still waiting on those routers.
pln_dah_65_05 = "ルーターを見つけてくれ。",--Need you to get to those routers.
pln_dah_65_06 = "何してるんだ? ルーターを見つけろ!",--What's up guys? Find those routers!
pln_dah_66_01 = "1つめのルーターだ!",--One router down!
pln_dah_66_02 = "1つめだ、次を探せ!",--That's one, find the next!
pln_dah_66_03 = "あと1つだ。",--Just one more to go.
pln_dah_67_01 = "よし! 接続した。",--Great! I'm in.
pln_dah_67_02 = "いいぞ! どれどれ...",--Ok, let me see...
pln_dah_67_03 = "よくやった! 少し待ってろ...",--Perfect! Now gimme a second...
pln_dah_68_01 = "警官共が邪魔しに来たな。作業中のルーターを守れ!",--Cops are tryint to stop us. Defend those routers while I work!
pln_dah_68_02 = "クソ警官どもはルーターボックスの電源を切るつもりだ! 奴らを止めろ!",--Damn cops are trying to cut power to the router boxes! Stop them!
pln_dah_68_03 = "警官共は俺達の邪魔をするつもりだ、しっかり防げ!",--Blues are trying to pull the plug on us, make sure they fail!
pln_dah_69_01 = "そのままルーターを守ってろ。",--Keep those routers safe.
pln_dah_69_02 = "サツ共をルーターに近づけるなよ。",--Dont' let the cops near the routers.
pln_dah_69_03 = "奴らシャットダウンするつもりだ!",--They're trying to shut them down!
pln_dah_69_04 = "サツを止めろ!",--Stop the cops!
pln_dah_69_05 = "奴らをルーターに近寄らせるな。",--Keep them off the routers.
pln_dah_69_06 = "ルーターを守れ。",--Protect the routers.
pln_dah_69_07 = "サツをルーターから遠ざけとけ!!",--Keep the cops away from the routers!
pln_dah_69_08 = "近づく奴は撃ち殺せ!",--Drop any cop that gets close!
pln_dah_70_01 = "半分完了した。",--Halfway there.
pln_dah_70_02 = "50%完了だ。",--50 percent done.
pln_dah_70_03 = "もうそんな長くはかからない。",--No too long now.
pln_dah_71_01 = "これでよし、済んだぞ!",--That's it, I'm done!
pln_dah_71_02 = "よし、これで終わりだ!",--OK,I'm done here!
pln_dah_71_03 = "もういいぞ!",--There we go!
pln_dah_72_01 = "いいか、次に必要なのはKeycardだ。お誕生日のRalph君を探せ、まだどこかに隠れてるはずだ!",--OK, now you need that keycard. Find our birthday boy Ralph, he's probably still hiding somewhere!
pln_dah_72_02 = "いいか、次はKeycardを見つけるんだ。お誕生会の主役はまだどこかにいるはずだ、探し出せ!",--OK gang, time to find that keycard. Birthday Boy is probably still around, so go find him!
pln_dah_72_03 = "Ralph Garnetを見つけて、奴が生まれたときからケツに挟んでるKeycardを奪え。",--Go find Ralph Garnet and take that keycard from his priviledged-ass-self.
pln_dah_73_01 = "Ralph GarnetのKeycardが必要だ。奴を探せ!",--We need Ralph Garnet's keycard. Find him!
pln_dah_73_02 = "Keycardが無きゃどうにもならん。Ralph Garnetを探せ!",--We're stuck without that keycard. Find Ralph garnet!
pln_dah_73_03 = "Ralphは何処かに隠れたな。奴を探してKeycardを奪え!",--Ralph's got to be hiding somewhere. Find him and get that card!
pln_dah_74_01 = "よし、マスターコードを手に入れるぞ。CFOが持ってるだろう。",--Right, time to get the master code. The CFO will have it.
pln_dah_74_02 = "CFOを探せ。そいつがマスターコードを持ってる!",--OK, find the CFO. He's got the master code!
pln_dah_74_03 = "一番のお偉いさんをクビにしてやろう。CFOを見つけてマスターコードを奪え!",--Kick the shit out of the exacutive ladder. Find the CFO and get his master code!
pln_dah_75_01 = "CFOがマスターコードを持ってる。探し出せ!",--The CFO has the master code guys. Find him!
pln_dah_75_02 = "CFOを見つけるんだ。そいつがマスターコードを持ってる。コードが無きゃどうにもならん。",--You need to find the CFO. He's got the master code. You *need* the master code.
pln_dah_75_03 = "まだマスターコードが見つかってないぞ!",--You still need to find the master code!
pln_dah_76_01 = "息を吐くように嘘をつくやつだ。そいつをヘリに乗せろ、俺がコードを聞き出してやる。",--He's lying through his teeth. Get him to the chopper, I'll get the code out of him.
pln_dah_76_02 = "嘘つきめ、俺が聞き出してやる。屋上のヘリまで連れてこい!",--He's lying, I'll take care of him myself. Bring him to the chopper on the roof!
pln_dah_76_03 = "そいつを屋上に連れてきてヘリに乗せろ。俺が白状させてやる。",--Bring him to the roof and put him on the chopper. I'll get him to sing.
pln_dah_77_01 = "早くしてくれ、その男を屋上に連れてこい。",--C'mon guys, get that guy to the roof.
pln_dah_77_02 = "CFOを屋上に連れてこい、今すぐにだ!",--CFO to the roof, ASAP!
pln_dah_77_03 = "急いでくれよ。",--Need to hurry gang.
pln_dah_77_04 = "急げよお前ら。",--You need to hurry guys.
pln_dah_78_01 = "ヘリが着くぞ。",--Chopper coming in.
pln_dah_78_02 = "ヘリが到着するぞ、奴の準備はいいか。",--Heli is almost there, have that guy ready.
pln_dah_78_03 = "ヘリが着くぞ。用意しろ!",--Chopper is inbound. Stand by!
pln_dah_79_01 = "金庫を開ける用意をしろ。コードはすぐに知らせる。",--Get ready for the vault. I'll have the code for you soon.
pln_dah_79_02 = "すぐにこいつからコードを聞き出してやる。持ちこたえろ。",--Won't take long to squeeze this guy for the code. Hang tight.
pln_dah_79_03 = "卵みたいに口を割らせてコードを手に入れてやる。",--I'll crack this guy like an egg and have that code for you shortly.
pln_dah_80_01 = "コードを入れる前にRalphのKeycardを通せ。",--Swipe Ralph's card before entering the code.
pln_dah_80_02 = "コードの前にRalphのKeycardを通すんだ。",--You need to swipe Ralph's card before the code.
pln_dah_80_03 = "RalphのKeycardを通して、それからコードを打ち込め。",--Swipe Ralph's keycard, then punch in the code.
pln_dah_81_01 = "いいか、コードは...",--All right, the code is...
pln_dah_81_02 = "よく聞けよ、コードは...",--Listen up, the code is...
pln_dah_81_03 = "手に入れたコードは...",--Got the code for you...
pln_dah_82_01 = "0",--zero
pln_dah_82_02 = "0",--zero
pln_dah_83_01 = "1",--one
pln_dah_83_02 = "1",--one
pln_dah_84_01 = "2",--two
pln_dah_84_02 = "2",--two
pln_dah_85_01 = "3",--three
pln_dah_85_02 = "3",--three
pln_dah_86_01 = "4",--four
pln_dah_86_02 = "4",--four
pln_dah_87_01 = "5",--five
pln_dah_87_02 = "5",--five
pln_dah_88_01 = "6",--six
pln_dah_88_02 = "6",--six
pln_dah_89_01 = "7",--seven
pln_dah_89_02 = "7",--seven
pln_dah_90_01 = "8",--eight
pln_dah_90_02 = "8",--eight
pln_dah_91_01 = "9",--nine
pln_dah_91_02 = "9",--nine
pln_dah_92_01 = "繰り返す、コードは...",--Repeat, the code is...
pln_dah_92_02 = "聞こえたか? コードは...",--You get that? The code is...
pln_dah_92_03 = "繰り返すぞ。",--Let me repeat
pln_dah_92_04 = "もう一度だ、コードは...",--Once more, the code is...
pln_dah_92_05 = "もう一度だ。",--Here it is again.
pln_dah_92_06 = "もう一度だ。",--One more time
pln_dah_92_07 = "忘れたのか? コードは...",--Forget the code? It's...
pln_dah_92_08 = "今度は間違えるなよ。コードは...",--Don't screw this up. The code's...
pln_dah_93_01 = "お偉いCFOさんにサヨナラだ。 死ぬ前に俺の顔が見られてよかったな!",--Mr. big-shot CFO had to go bye-bye. At least he had the priviledge of seeing my face before he went!
pln_dah_93_02 = "まあ、俺の顔を見た後も生かしておくと約束してたわけじゃねえからな。",--Well, we didn't make him any promises about letting him live after seeing me.
pln_dah_93_03 = "まあ、そういうことだ。奴は俺の顔を見た、だから... 降ろしてやったのさ。",--Well, that's that. He got a look at me, so I had to... let him go.
pln_dah_94_01 = "金庫が開くぞ。移動開始だ!",--Vault is opening. Get ready to move!
pln_dah_94_02 = "ダイヤのつかみ取りだ!",--Be ready for a smash-and-grab!
pln_dah_94_03 = "いよいよだ! 宝石を頂きだ!",--There you go! Now get those gems!
pln_dah_95_01 = "ダイヤモンドだらけだぜ。",--That's a lot of stones.
pln_dah_95_02 = "収穫の時だぜ..",--Loot for the taking...
pln_dah_95_03 = "お宝で一杯だな。",--So much value in such a small space.
pln_dah_96_01 = "他にも金庫があるのか?",--Another vault?
pln_dah_96_02 = "2つめの金庫だと?",--A second vault?
pln_dah_96_03 = "金庫は1つだけじゃないのか? そいつは予想してなかったな。",--More than one vault? Didnt' see that one coming.
pln_dah_97_01 = "きっと一儲け出来るぞ。",--Probably worth a fortune.
pln_dah_97_02 = "さあて、きっとデカい儲けになるぞ。",--Well now, it's probably worth a hell of a lot.
pln_dah_97_03 = "よほど価値があるもんに違いない。",--It's gotta be worth a lot.
pln_dah_98_01 = "回収すれば良いボーナスになるぞ。",--Grab it and there'll be a nice bonus.
pln_dah_98_02 = "2つめの金庫を開けて美味しいボーナスを頂きだ。",--Open that second vault and you'll get a juicy bonus.
pln_dah_98_03 = "そのRed Diamondがありゃ最高の\"給料日\"になる。",--Get that red diamond and this'll be a double Payday.
pln_dah_99_01 = "目的はケースに入ってるダイヤだが、頂ける物はなんでも頂いとけ。",--The stones in cases are top priority, but grab whatever else you can.
pln_dah_99_02 = "塵も積もれば山となるというが、一番大事なのはケースの中の石ころだ。",--Every little bit helps, but the rocks in cases are most important.
pln_dah_99_03 = "目的はケースの中のモノだが、ボーナスを手に入れるのもいい。",--You came for the ones in cases, but everything else is a bonus.
pln_dah_end_loud_01 = "ちょいとハメを外しすぎたが、よくやった!",--Things got a little wild, but you got the job done!
pln_dah_end_loud_02 = "教科書通り完璧にとは行かなかったが、終わり良ければ全て良しだ!",--Not exactly textbook perfection, but who cares when it all works out!
pln_dah_end_loud_03 = "派手になっちまったが、上手く行ったな。お見事だった。",--It was loud, but it was succesful. Outstanding people.
pln_dah_end_stealth_01 = "よくやってくれたな。懐かしい仕事だった!",--Nicely done gang. A classic heist!
pln_dah_end_stealth_02 = "バレずによくやり遂げたな。屋上から怒鳴ってる甲斐があったってもんだ。",--Great job keeping it quiet everyone. Almost worth shouting from the rooftops.
pln_dah_end_stealth_03 = "お手本のような手際だったぞ。",--Textbook execution people.
pln_dah_intro_01 = "よし、侵入完了。時計合わせ... マーク!",--All right, entry point. Synchronize on my mark... mark.
pln_dah_intro_02 = "19... 20... 21... 金持ちなら窓拭きにもっとマシなゴンドラくらい用意しろってんだ! やっと着いたな、22階だ...行くぞ。.",--19... 20... 21... All that money and Garnet is too cheap to pay for a faster window washing rig! Ok that's it, 22nd floor and... go.
pln_dah_intro_03 = "よし、もうすぐ22階だ。着いたら始めるが鼻血は出すなよ。",--All right, you're almost on the 22nd. Get going and don't get a nose-bleed up there.
pln_fri_01_01 = "全く、すげえ所だな。派手に暮らしてやがる。静かにやってもいいし、ドンパチしてもいいぞ、任せる。",--Damn, look at this place. This guy rides in style. You can do this quietly or with a bang, it's your choice.
pln_fri_01_02 = "なんつー家だ! Sosaどもの稼ぎっぷりが分かるな。早速始めよう、静かに行こうと派手に行こうと、あの男の始末さえすればThe Butcherは気にしないぜ。",--What a house! You can tell the Sosas are making money. Let's hit this place - quiet or loud, the Butcher doesn't care how as long as you kill the guy.
pln_fri_01_03 = "よし、侵入しろ。静かにでも派手にでも、好きなやり方であの男を始末しろ。",--Ok guys. Let's go in. Quiet or loud, you can kill this guy any way you want.
pln_fri_02_01 = "いいぞ、まずは警備主任を見つけよう、そいつがあの屋敷のアクセスコードが入ったUSBスティックを持ってる。緑のジャケットを着た奴だ。",--Ok, the first step is to find the head of security - he'll have a USB stick with access codes for the house. He always wears a green jacket.
pln_fri_02_02 = "警備主任を見つけよう。そいつが屋敷に入るために必要な物を持ってる。セキュリティコードの入ったUSBスティックだ。緑のジャケットを着た男だ。",--Let's find the head of security. He should have what you need to get in - USB stick with security codes. He'll be wearing a green jacket.
pln_fri_02_03 = "Sosaの警備主任を見つけろ、そいつがセキュリティコードの入ったUSBスティックを持ってる。こだわりがあるのか、常に緑のジャケットを着てる。",--Find Sosa's head of security - he'll have a USB stick with security codes. He's a man of habit - always wears a green jacket.
pln_fri_03_01 = "警備主任の持つUSBスティックが必要だ。",--We need the USB stick from the head of security.
pln_fri_03_02 = "USBスティックを手に入れなきゃならん。警備主任が持ってるだろう。",--We gotta get the USB stick. The head of security should have it.
pln_fri_03_03 = "USBスティックは警備主任が持ってるぞ。",--The head of security will have that USB stick.
pln_fri_04_01 = "いいかお前ら、警備主任を探せ。そいつのUSBスティックが要るんだ。",--Remember guys, you're looking for the head of security. We need his USB stick.
pln_fri_04_02 = "警備主任を探してそいつのUSBスティックを手に入れろ。",--Find the head of security and get his USB stick.
pln_fri_04_03 = "警備主任からUSBスティックを手に入れろ。",--Get the USB stick from the head of security.
pln_fri_05_01 = "よくやった、次はそいつをコンピューターに繋げ。屋敷の周囲にノートパソコンがあるはずだ。",--Great, now plug the usb into the computer. Look for a laptop, it should be near the house.
pln_fri_05_02 = "屋敷周りのどこかにノートパソコンがあるはずだ。そいつにUSBスティックを繋げ。",--There should be a laptop somewhere near the house. Plug the USB stick into it.
pln_fri_05_03 = "ノートパソコンを見つけてUSBスティックを繋げ。近くにあるはずだ。",--Find a laptop and plug the USB in. It should be nearby.
pln_fri_06_01 = "ノートパソコンが見つからないか? 屋敷の周辺を探せ、ガレージとかな。",--Can't find the laptop? Check around the house - the garage maybe?
pln_fri_06_02 = "物置小屋はもう調べたか?",--Have you checked the tool shed for the laptop?
pln_fri_06_03 = "ノートパソコンは屋敷の周辺にあるはずだ、たぶん小屋とか建物だ。",--The laptop should be near the house, maybe in one of the smaller buildings?
pln_fri_07_01 = "オーケー、セキュリティシステムをハッキングしてみる...",--Okay, I'm trying to hack the security system now...
pln_fri_07_02 = "オーケー、システムのハッキング中だ...",--Okay, hacking the system now...
pln_fri_07_03 = "セキュリティシステムをハックしてみるから、少し待ってろ...",--Wait while I try to hack the security system...
pln_fri_08_01 = "待て...お前ら、コンピューターを守れ!",--What... guys, protect the computer!
pln_fri_08_02 = "奴らにコンピューターを止められた。頼むから守ってくれ!!",--They interrupted the computer. You gotta protect it, guys!
pln_fri_08_03 = "コンピューターが止められた。しっかり防衛してくれ!",--The computer got interrupted. You have to defend it better!
pln_fri_09_01 = "何だこりゃ... セキュリティロックが設けられてるぞ。そっちで無効化してくれ。セキュリティの配電盤を探して回路を切り替えろ。",--Wait.. what... they've got additional security blocks. You gotta disable them. Find a security switchboard and rewire the system.
pln_fri_09_02 = "ちょっと待て... うーん... 思ってたより高度なシステムだな。どこかにセキュリティの配電盤があるはずだ、そいつを見つけて回路をいじってくれ。",--Wait... hmm... this system is more advanced than I thought. There should be a security switchboard somewhere - you gotta find it and rewire it.
pln_fri_09_03 = "待てよ... おお... 奴らセキュリティブロックを置いてやがる。セキュリティの配電盤を探して回路をつなぎ直してくれ。",--Hang on... oh... they've got additional security blocks here. You gotta find a security switchboard and rewire it.
pln_fri_10_01 = "何だ... まだあるのか? お前ら、他の配電盤を見つけて同じように再配線してくれ。",--What the... Another one? Guys, there's another switchbox, rewire that one too.
pln_fri_10_02 = "当然だな... また別の配電盤だ。そいつも同じように回路をいじってくれ。",--I should've know... there's another switchbox. You've got to rewire that one too.
pln_fri_10_03 = "うーん... どうやら他にも配電盤があるな。探して回路を切り替えてくれ、1つ目と同じようにな。",--Hmm... there seems to be another switchbox. Find it and rewire it, same as the other one.
pln_fri_11_01 = "よくやった、これで上手く行くだろう。次はコンピューターを再起動してくれ。",--Great, that should do it. Now try starting the computer again.
pln_fri_11_02 = "オーケー、それでいい。次はコンピューターを再起動してくれ。",--Ok, that should do it. Now start the computer again.
pln_fri_11_03 = "よし、配電盤は片付いた。コンピューターを再起動してくれ。",--Ok, got the switchboards fixed. You can start the computer again.
pln_fri_12_01 = "いいぞ、システムのハッキングは順調だ。",--Ok, the computer is working nice and steady again, hacking the system.
pln_fri_12_02 = "よし。問題なくコンピューターが動いてるぞ。",--Good. The computer is working again without interruption.
pln_fri_12_03 = "順調に進行中だな、コンピューターからシステムをハッキング中だ。",--We're good and going, I'm hacking the system through the computer
pln_fri_13_01 = "思ったより手こずったが、何とかやれたな! これで屋敷に入れるぞ。",--That was harder than expected but we're go! You can enter the house now.
pln_fri_13_02 = "よし、終わり! 大変だったが、どうにか屋敷のシャッターを幾つか開けられた。",--Ok, it's done! That was hard but I managed to open some of the shutters on the house.
pln_fri_13_03 = "開け、ゴマ! 屋敷のシャッターが幾つか開いたぞ。",--Open sesame! I got some of the house's shutters to open.
pln_fri_14_01 = "中に入れ、野郎ども!",--Let's get inside, guys!
pln_fri_14_02 = "要塞の門は破られた! 突入しろ!",--We've breached the fortress! Get inside!
pln_fri_14_03 = "早くしろお前ら! 中に入れ!",--Come on guys! Get inside now!
pln_fri_15_01 = "ボスの部屋に行くには屋敷を全て開放しなきゃいけない。スイッチか何かを探せ。",--If we're gonna get into the boss' office, we need to open the rest of the house. Look for a switch or something.
pln_fri_15_02 = "屋敷を全開放する必要があるな。スイッチがどこかにあるはずだ。",--We need to open up the rest of the house. There must be a switch somewhere.
pln_fri_15_03 = "屋敷を全て開放するスイッチとかが有るはずだ。探してみろ。",--There must be a switch or something that opens up the rest of the house. Try to find it.
pln_fri_16_01 = "いいぞお前ら! これで屋敷は丸裸だ!",--Ok guys, that did it! The house is open!
pln_fri_16_02 = "素晴らしい! 中に入れるぞ!",--Great! We're in!
pln_fri_16_03 = "お前らよくやったな! 邪魔なシャッターはもう無いぜ!",--Great guys! No one keeps you out!
pln_fri_17_01 = "待てよ... ロビーにもSosaのオフィスにも入れないじゃないか。別のシステムで動作してやがるのか。",--Wait... we can't get into the lobby or Sosa's office. It must run on a separate system.
pln_fri_17_02 = "なあ... ええと... どうやらSosaのオフィスにはまだ行けない。システムが分離してるんだ。",--Hey guys.. uuh... it seems we can't get into Sosa's office this way. It's on a separate system.
pln_fri_17_03 = "うーん... Sosaのオフィスは別のセキュリティシステムで閉じられてるようだな... ちょっと待っててくれ...",--Hmm... Sosa's office seems to be locked up behind a separate security system.... hang on...
pln_fri_18_01 = "他のプランが要るな... まったく穴熊みたいな野郎だ... うーん...",--We need a new plan... this guy has really burrowed in... hmm...
pln_fri_18_02 = "ちょっと考えさせてくれ。どうやったら入れるのかわからん。",--I'm thinking here. I don't know how we're gonna get in...
pln_fri_18_03 = "よし、それじゃあ... うーん... 何か手はないか...",--Ok, let's see... hmm... we need a plan for this...
pln_fri_19_01 = "中に入る必要があるが、ドリルは使えん。",--We gotta get in. A drill won't do it.
pln_fri_19_02 = "うーん、爆薬は使えないな、危険すぎるし... そうだな...",--Hmm, explosives won't work, it's too dangerous... let me see...
pln_fri_19_03 = "これなら... いや... これじゃ無理だ... どうやれば入れる...",--How... eh... gotta think of something... how to get inside...
pln_fri_20_01 = "うむ...そうか、物を壊す。それでいこう。",--Umm... ok, destroy stuff. Got it.
pln_fri_20_02 = "ふむ... 彼女の言うとおりだ。あいつの持ち物を破壊して挑発してみようぜ。",--Hmm... she's right, gang. Let's destroy some of his stuff and see if we can provoke him.
pln_fri_20_03 = "オーケー、壊すのは分かった。問題は何にするかだ...",--Ok, destroy things. What should we go for...
pln_fri_21_01 = "よし、ここには奴のしゃれた絵画がたくさんある。きっと高価なもんだろう。そいつを集めて燃やしちまおう、これで奴を引っ張り出せるぞ。",--Ok, he's got a lot of fancy art around here. Must be worth a fortune. We'll gather 'em in a pile and burn 'em, that should draw him out.
pln_fri_21_02 = "どうやらErnesto Sosaは絵画の収集がお好きなようだな。全て燃やしてしまえ、それで奴を怒らせるんだ。集めて積み重ねろ。",--I can see that Ernesto Sosa likes to collect paintings. We'll burn them all, that should make him angry. Gather them in a pile.
pln_fri_21_03 = "奴の絵画を燃やそう。まずは集めて積んでおくんだ。",--Let's burn his paintings. Gather them in a pile first.
pln_fri_22_01 = "そいつは良い、そこへ積んでおけ。",--That's great, pile them up there.
pln_fri_22_02 = "おあつらえ向きの場所だな。そこに積み上げろ。",--That's a spot as good as any. Pile 'em up.
pln_fri_22_03 = "高い絵を燃やすには最高の場所だな。",--That's a great place to burn some priceless art.
pln_fri_23_01 = "どんどん積み上げろ。盛大な焚き火にしてやれ",--Keep piling 'em up. Make a nice bonfire.
pln_fri_23_02 = "もう少し絵画を集めろ。ほんの数枚だ。",--Add some more paintings. A few more.
pln_fri_23_03 = "いいぞ! もう少し加えろ、しっかりと燃え上がらせたい。",--Great! Add a few more, we want a proper blaze.
pln_fri_24_01 = "もういいぞ。次はガソリン缶を探せ。そいつを設置して撃てば火がつく!",--That's enough. Now put a gas can on it and shoot it to light it up!
pln_fri_24_02 = "よし! 次はガソリン缶を見つけて設置しろ。そしたら撃って着火だ。燃やしちまえ!",--Ok! Now find a gas can and shoot it to set it all alight. Let's burn some art!
pln_fri_24_03 = "オーケー! 次はガソリン缶を探しに行け。撃って絵画に火をつけろ。",--Okay! Now go find a gas can. Shoot it to set the paintings on fire.
pln_fri_25_01 = "ガソリン缶を絵画の上に置いたら撃って火をつけるんだ。",--Guys, put a gas can on the paintings and shoot it.
pln_fri_25_02 = "いいか、絵画を燃やすにはガソリン缶が必要だ。ガソリン缶を撃つんだ。",--Remember, you need a gas can to set the paintings on fire. Shoot the gas can.
pln_fri_25_03 = "ガソリン缶を絵画の上に置いたら、そいつを撃つんだ。",--Put a gas can on the paintings, guys. Then shoot it.
pln_fri_26_01 = "上出来だ、奴がどんな反応をするかな。",--Ok, let's see how he reacts to this.
pln_fri_26_02 = "全て煙になって立ち上っていく。これで奴の気を引けるだろう。",--It's all going up in smoke. This should get his attention.
pln_fri_26_03 = "それじゃあ、奴の出方を見よう。",--Now just wait for his reaction.
pln_fri_27_01 = "おいBile、いるか? ちょいと吊り上げて海に落として欲しい車があるんだ!",--Hey Bile, you there? We got some cars that need picking up and dropping off!
pln_fri_27_02 = "Bileか? こっちに来て何台か車を動かしてくれないか。",--Bile? I need you to fly in and move some cars for me.
pln_fri_27_03 = "Bileか? ひとつ空輸の仕事を頼みたいんだが。キャッチアンドリリース、そんなとこだ。",--Bile? I got an airlift job for you. A grab and drop, you could say.
pln_fri_28_01 = "警備員だけじゃなくタレットまで置いてるのか! あの野郎の\"セキュリティ\"は度を越してるな!",--Not just guards, but turrets too! This guy takes security seriously!
pln_fri_28_02 = "タレットまでありやがる! 気をつけろ!",--He's got turrets too! Watch it!
pln_fri_28_03 = "タレットに気をつけろ、野郎ども!",--Watch out for those turrets, guys!
pln_fri_29_01 = "よし、今のうちに戦利品を頂こう。Ernestoの金庫はオフィスの床下にある。入ってきたあたりの車道にWinchがある、そいつで引き上げろ。",--Ok, let's get some loot while we're here. Ernesto has a floor safe in his office. There are some winches near the driveway where you entered - grab them and hook them up.
pln_fri_29_02 = "この野郎は上手くやってるな。お宝を頂こう。床下の金庫だ。敷地の入口あたりにWinchを隠しておいたから、取ってきて引き上げろ。",--This guy is doing well. Let's loot the place. We're gonna go for his floor safe. You've got some winches stashed near the entrance to the property. Get them and hook 'em up.
pln_fri_29_03 = "よし、お次は床下の金庫からErnestのお宝を頂きだ。素敵なブツで一杯に違いないぜ。敷地の入口にWinchを隠してあるから、取ってきて引き上げろ。",--Ok gang, now we're gonna loot Ernesto's floor safe. I bet it's full of wonderful things. There are some winches stashed near the place where you entered the property - go get them and hook them up.
pln_fri_30_01 = "手ぶらで帰ることは無いよな。床下の金庫にErnestoの溜め込んだブツがある。拾っておいたWinchを使って引き上げろ。",--We're not leaving this place without some loot. Ernesto has floor safe where he keeps his stuff. Use the winches you picked up earlier, hook them up to the floor.
pln_fri_30_02 = "よし、いよいよErnestoのお宝拝見だ。奴はオフィスの床下に金庫を隠してる。Winchで引き上げて頂きだ。",--Ok, it's time to loot Ernesto's place. He's got a floor safe in his office. Hook those winches up to the floor and let's lift it.
pln_fri_30_03 = "さあて、カネをいただこう。床下にあるErnestoの金庫だ。Winchを使って引き上げるんだ。",--Ok, time for the money, guys. We're gonna loot Ernesto's floor safe. Hook those winches up to the floor.
pln_fri_31_01 = "早くWinchを取り付けろ!",--Attach those winches now!
pln_fri_31_02 = "早く、Winchで引き上げろ!",--Come on, get those winches hooked up!
pln_fri_31_03 = "Winchで床下から引き上げろ!",--Hook the winches up to the floor!
pln_fri_32_01 = "こいつはしばらく時間がかかる。引き上げてる間はしっかり守れ。",--This is gonna take a while. Make sure to protect the winches while they are working their magic.
pln_fri_32_02 = "Winchの作業が終わるまで、妨害されないようにしろよ。",--Now wait for the winches to work. And make sure they're not interfered with.
pln_fri_32_03 = "よし! あとは作業の間Winchを守るだけでいい。",--Ok! Just protect the winches now while they're working.
pln_fri_33_01 = "何だ? Winchが止まったぞ、再起動しろ!",--What? The winch has stopped, get it going again!
pln_fri_33_02 = "Winchが停止したようだな。再起動させろ!",--The winch seems to have jammed. Get it up and running again!
pln_fri_33_03 = "Winchが停止したぞ。直せるかやってみろ!",--That winch has stopped working. See if you can fix it!
pln_fri_34_01 = "時間がもったいない! Winchを再起動しろ!",--We're wasting time here! Get that winch going again!
pln_fri_34_02 = "Winchの再起動を忘れるなよ!",--Don't forget to get that winch running again!
pln_fri_34_03 = "早くしろお前ら! Winchを再起動させるんだ!",--Come on guys! Remember to get that winch up and running again!
pln_fri_35_01 = "よし、次は防衛だ。",--Ok, protect them now.
pln_fri_35_02 = "それでいい。今度はちゃんと守れよ。",--That's great. Now protect them.
pln_fri_35_03 = "よく直したな、このまま守ろう。",--Great, you fixed it. Now guard them.
pln_fri_36_01 = "終わったな。見ろよあのブツの量を! 逃げる前に掴めるだけ掴んで行こうぜ!",--It's done. Look at all that loot! Now grab as much as you can before you escape!
pln_fri_36_02 = "よくやったぞお前ら! 見ろよそれ! 出来るだけ持って逃げようぜ!",--Great guys! Look at that! Grab all that you can before you escape.
pln_fri_36_03 = "愛しのお金ちゃんだぞ、お前ら! 苦労した分出来るだけ頂くとしようか!",--Sweet money, guys! Now make this worth it by grabbing as much loot as you can!
pln_fri_37_01 = "大漁だな。欲しけりゃもっと取ってきていいぞ。",--That's a good amount of bling. But if you want to grab some more, you can.
pln_fri_37_02 = "そいつはいい。だが足りないならもっと取って来い!",--That's great. But if you want to grab some more, do so!
pln_fri_37_03 = "よくやった! このまま脱出するかもっと戦利品を集めてくるか、そいつは任せる。",--Great, guys! Now you can grab some more loot or take the escape, the choice is yours.
pln_fri_38_01 = "よし、根こそぎ頂いたな! もうここに用はない。",--Ok, you've cleared the place out! Time to get out of here.
pln_fri_38_02 = "そいつで全部だ、もうコイン1枚すら残ってねえ! 帰るぞ!",--That's all of it, every single dime! Now it's time to go home!
pln_fri_38_03 = "奴らの物は全部頂いたな! 夕日と共に俺たちも消えていくとしようぜ!",--You took everything they have! Time to ride off into the sunset, guys!
pln_fri_39_01 = "なあ、もう何も残ってないぞ。脱出しろ!",--Hey guys, there's nothing left. Get out of there!
pln_fri_39_02 = "何も残ってないんだから、うろつくのは無駄だぞ!",--It's all gone, gang. No point in hanging around!
pln_fri_39_03 = "なあ、カネは全て手に入れたんだ。そろそろ脱出しようぜ!",--Guys, we got all the money. You should get out of there!
pln_fri_40_01 = "あれが警備主任だ。庭園にいるようだな。",--That's the head of security. He seems to be in the garden.
pln_fri_40_02 = "おっと、そいつだ。どうやら警備主任は庭園の方にいるようだな。",--Hey, there he is. Looks like he's in the garden area.
pln_fri_40_03 = "そいつが警備主任だ。ふむ... 庭園にいるようだ。",--That's the head of security. Hmm... he's in the garden I think.
pln_fri_41_01 = "そいつが警備主任だ。桟橋にいるようだな。",--That's the head of security. He seems to be at the dock.
pln_fri_41_02 = "おっと、そいつだ。桟橋の方にいるようだ。",--Hey, there he is. Looks like he's by the docks.
pln_fri_41_03 = "そいつが警備主任だ。海に突き出た桟橋にいる。",--That's the head of security. Down by the water, at the dock.
pln_fri_42_01 = "そいつが警備主任だ。屋敷の裏手にいるようだ。",--That's the head of security. He seems to be at the back of the house.
pln_fri_42_02 = "見つけたな。屋敷の裏手にいるようだ。",--There he is. Looks like he's at the back.
pln_fri_42_03 = "そいつが警備主任だ。うーん... 屋敷の裏手かな。",--That's the head of security. Hmm... looks like he's at the back of the house.
pln_fri_43_01 = "そいつが警備主任だ。プールの横にいる。",--That's the head of security. He's by the pools.
pln_fri_43_02 = "おっと、そいつだ。プールの横にいるようだ。",--Hey, there he is. Looks like he's by the pools.
pln_fri_43_03 = "そいつが警備主任だ。プールだ、プールの側にいる。",--That's the head of security. The pools, he's by the pools.
pln_fri_44_01 = "そいつが警備主任だ。階段のあたりにいるようだ。",--That's the head of security. He seems to be at the stairs.
pln_fri_44_02 = "おっと、見つけたな。いるのは階段の辺りか。",--Hey, there he is. Looks like he's around the stairs.
pln_fri_44_03 = "そいつが警備主任だ。階段のあたりだな。",--That's the head of security. He's by the stairs.
pln_fri_45_01 = "そいつが警備主任だ。車道のあたりにいるようだ。",--That's the head of security. He seems to be by the driveway.
pln_fri_45_02 = "おっと、そいつだ。車道のあたりにいるようだ。",--Hey, there he is. Looks like he's by the driveway.
pln_fri_45_03 = "そいつが警備主任だ。うーん... 車道のあたりだと思う。",--That's the head of security. Hmm... he's by the driveway I think.
pln_fri_46_01 = "ヤクの入った袋を調べろ。",--Search those bags of coke, guys.
pln_fri_46_02 = "よし。次はヤクの包みを調べろ。",--Good. Now search the coke bags.
pln_fri_46_03 = "よし、次はヤクが詰まった袋を調べろ。",--Ok, now you gotta search those bags of coke.
pln_fri_47_01 = "ボイスレコーダーを探すんだ。",--Find that mic recorder, guys.
pln_fri_47_02 = "いいか、ボイスレコーダーを見つけるんだ。",--Remember, you gotta find that mic recorder.
pln_fri_47_03 = "ボイスレコーダーを見つけろ、あるはずだ。",--Find the mic recorder. It's gotta be there.
pln_fri_48_01 = "首無男がトマトをもらいにサンタの所へ。",--The headless man rides to Santa Cruz for tomatoes.
pln_fri_48_02 = "親指のないマリアはヒッチハイクができない。",--Maria wants to hitch-hike but has no thumbs.
pln_fri_48_03 = "ヒゲはもじゃもじゃだが長くはない。",--The beard is green but not long.
pln_fri_48_04 = "毛むくじゃらのヤギはナイフを嫌う。",--The shaggy goat is unhappy with the knives.
pln_fri_48_05 = "モンテスマは朝食にオレンジを3つ食べる。",--Montezuma wants three oranges for breakfast.
pln_fri_48_06 = "ロバのケツに3匹のハエ。",--Three flies are on the donkey's ass.
pln_fri_48_07 = "黒猫は自分のタマを食べた。",--The black cat ate its own balls.
pln_fri_48_08 = "金属バンドにはピクルスが蓄えられている。",--The metal links were stored with the preserved cucumbers.
pln_fri_48b_01 = "",--You hung up! That's the alarm!
pln_fri_49_01 = "あの、ボス。封のされた手紙が来てます。直接読んで欲しいそうです。",--Hey boss, I got a sealed letter for you here. Says for your eyes only.
pln_fri_49_02 = "あっ、ボス。小包が来てますよ。Boliviaの本部からです。",--Hey boss, got a package for you here. It's from the HQ in Bolivia.
pln_fri_49_03 = "ボスに見てほしいものがあるんです。見てもらえればわかると思います。",--I got something to show you, boss. You'll want to see it for yourself.
pln_fri_49_04 = "ボス、メキシコに送った部下からテキーラが来てますよ。いかがです?",--Hey boss, the guys in Mexico sent you some tequila. You want it?
pln_fri_49_05 = "どうも、ボス。重要な情報があるとかいう女が来てます。",--Hey boss. There's some woman here, says she has some important information for you.
pln_fri_49_06 = "新しい銃が手に入りましたよ、ボス。見てみませんか?",--Got some new guns in, boss. You wanna see them?
pln_fri_49_07 = "ボス、ヤクの中におかしなものがあります。見てください。",--Boss, there's something strange with this coke. You gotta see it.
pln_fri_50_01 = "金庫を開けるボタンか何かがあるはずだ。探してみろ。",--There should be a button or something that opens the safe. Look around.
pln_fri_50_02 = "金庫はその辺にあるボタンとかスイッチで開くんだろう。探してくれ。",--The safe is probably opened by a button or switch somewhere. You need to find it.
pln_fri_50_03 = "金庫を開けるボタンか装置があると思う、探してくれないか。",--There should be a mechanism or button to open the safe somewhere. See if you can find it.
pln_fri_51_01 = "でかした、しかも未だ静かなままだ。持てる限り持っていくが、最低でも数バッグは必要だ。",--Well done, nice and quiet. Secure everything if you can, but we need at least a few bags to make this worthwhile.
pln_fri_51_02 = "よし。出来るだけ回収しろ、少なくとも数バッグは要る。",--Good. Get as much loot as you can, but at least a few bags.
pln_fri_51_03 = "よくやった。お宝を頂こう。出来る限り全て、最低でも数バッグだ。",--Great. Now get the stuff. As much as you can, but at least a few bags.
pln_fri_52_01 = "バッグを運ぶのにZip-lineが使えるぞ。",--You could get a zipline up to move the bags.
pln_fri_52_02 = "素早くバッグを運びたいならZip-lineを設置しろ。",--If you want to move the bags faster, you can set up a zipline.
pln_fri_52_03 = "Zip-lineを設置するといい。バッグの運搬が楽になるぞ。",--Get a zipline up if you want. It'd be great for moving the bags.
pln_fri_53_01 = "ほらほら、バッグを運べ!",--Come on guys, move those bags!
pln_fri_53_02 = "お前ら、バッグを運ぶんだ!",--Get those bags out, guys!
pln_fri_53_03 = "しっかりバッグを運び出せ!",--Don't forget to get the bags out!
pln_fri_54_01 = "おい、Sosaの手下どもがその屋敷に向かってきてるぞ! すぐに来るから、そのへんに死体を転がしたままにしとくなよ。",--Hey guys, more Sosa thugs are on their way to the mansion! They'll be here any minute, I hope you don't have bodies lying around in the open.
pln_fri_54_02 = "警備強化にSosaの手下が屋敷に向かってるとの情報が入った。敷地内を綺麗にしとけよ、さもなきゃ居ることがバレちまう。",--I just got some intel about another bunch of Sosa thugs arriving at the mansion to reinforce security. The area better be clean, or they'll be onto you when they arrive.
pln_fri_54_03 = "Sosaが警備の増援を送って、すぐそこまで来てるらしい! 目につく所の死体は片付けとけよ、でなきゃ見つかっちまう。",--The Sosas were sending more men in to reinforce security, and it seems they're about to arrive now! Make sure you haven't left any bodies lying around in plain view, or they'll find out you're here.
pln_fri_55_01 = "注意しろ。屋内の警備員はPagerを持ってるぞ。",--Guys, be careful. The guards inside will probably carry pagers.
pln_fri_55_02 = "屋内の警備員はPagerを持ってるに違いない。気をつけたほうが良い。",--The guards inside will probably have pagers. You should be careful.
pln_fri_55_03 = "いいか、恐らく屋内の警備員はPagerを持ってる。注意しろ。",--Listen, the guards inside the house are likely to have pagers. Be careful.
pln_fri_56_01 = "いいかよく聞いてくれ。電話をかけ始めたら、絶対に途中で切るな。まず間違いなく奴に警報を鳴らされる、イカれてるからな。",--Guys listen carefully. Once you start making the call, you can't hang up. He will most likely sound the alarm, he is a paranoid one after all.
pln_fri_56_02 = "Ernestoはイカれてるから、電話をかけたら最後まで切るな。Pagerと同じだ。",--Ernesto is always paranoid, so once you start making that call you better finish it. Treat it like a pager
pln_fri_56_03 = "保証してもいいが、もし電話を途中で切ったら奴はアラームを鳴らすぜ。周囲の安全を確保してから始めろ。",--I guarantee you, that if you hang up while making the call he will sound the alarm. So make sure the coast is clear before starting it.
pln_fri_brf_01 = "",--Ernesto Sosa is the local boss in Miami for the Sosa Cartel, and The Butcher wants him dead. You're gonna love this: he lives in Tony Montana's old mansion in Miami Beach. Yeah that's right - Scarface, the legendary 80's drug lord. Anyway, you've got to hit the mansion, find a way in and then kill Ernesto Sosa. It won't be easy, the place is like a fortress. But you can do it. Oh yeah, I almost forgot - there should be a lot of money and other loot in that house. Steal it. Wipe them clean. But above all - kill Ernesto Sosa.
pln_fri_intro_01 = "よし、行動開始だ。The Butcherは本気だな... いいか、まずはErnesto Sosaを始末するんだ、お宝を頂くのはそれからだ。",--Ok team, lets get a move on. The Butcher means business here... remember, you've got to kill Ernesto Sosa, and steal the loot.
pln_fri_intro_02 = "いくぞお前ら。The Butcherの依頼は奴の始末だけだが、忘れるなよ、屋敷には金目の物がたんまりとあるぞ。",--Come on guys. The Butcher wants this guy dead, but don't forget, the house is full of riches too.
pln_fri_intro_03 = "マイアミビーチの豪華な屋敷、Ernesto Sosaはなんてツイてる野郎だと思うかもしれんが、ツキはツキでも運の尽きだ。",--You could say Ernesto Sosa is lucky to have this beautiful house in Miami Beach. But his luck is about to change...
rph_dah_01_01 = "",--Don't shoot me please!
rph_dah_01_02 = "",--Oh god, please don't shoot me!
rph_dah_01_03 = "",--Don't shoot me! I love life bigly!
rph_dah_01_04 = "",--Oh, fucking Christ! Mercy!
rph_dah_01_05 = "",--Don't shoot! I'll do anything! Daddyyyy!
rph_dah_01_06 = "",--Please! Mercy! Pleeeeeaaase!!
rph_dah_01_07 = "",--No, I'm too rich to die!
rph_dah_02_01 = "",--Here take it, just take it!
rph_dah_02_02 = "",--You want the card? Just take it!
rph_dah_02_03 = "",--The card? Take it! I don't give a fuck about the damn thing!
rph_dah_03_01 = "",--Don't hurt me It's my birthday.
rph_dah_03_02 = "",--My Daddy's a powerful man! He knows the President!
rph_dah_03_03 = "",--Daddy's rich, he can buy all of you!
pln_fish_01a_01 = "ワオ、なんて豪華な船だ。Powellって野郎は随分金持ちだな。",--Wow, this boat is expensive. This Powell guy's got money.
pln_fish_01a_02 = "隠し資金よりこの船の方が高かったりしてな。",--Heh, I wonder if this boat is worth more than what's hidden on it.
pln_fish_01a_03 = "この様子だと、McKendrickのお友達は成金趣味に違いないな。",--This friend of McKendrick's sure has the bling, by the looks of it.
pln_fish_01b_01 = "船の探索を始めてくれ、気をつけてな。",--Now search the boat, but be careful.
pln_fish_01b_02 = "静かに注意して行け。",--Go quiet and keep your eyes open.
pln_fish_01b_03 = "気をつけろ。音の出る靴なんて履いてないだろうな。",--Careful now. I hope you didn't bring your squeaky shoes.
pln_fish_02_01 = "隠し資金の在り処はノートパソコンで分かるはずだ。パスワードはCharonから聞いてあるから後は見つけるだけだぜ。",--There should be a laptop with information about where the cash is hidden. We got the password from Charon so all you gotta do is find the thing.
pln_fish_02_02 = "Charonがカネの隠し場所が分かるノートパソコンのパスワードを教えてくれた。そいつを探せ!",--Charon gave us a password for a laptop that contains data on where the money is. Find it!
pln_fish_02_03 = "カネの隠し場所を示すノートパソコンがあるはずだ。Charonがパスワードを教えてくれたから、見つけてくれ!",--There's a laptop with info on where the cash is stashed. Charon provided the password. See if you can find it!
pln_fish_03_01 = "ノートパソコンを探せ!",--Find that laptop, guys!
pln_fish_03_02 = "いいか、ノートパソコンを見つけるんだ!",--Remember to look for the laptop!
pln_fish_03_03 = "まだノートパソコンが見つからないのか?",--You find that laptop yet?
pln_fish_03_04 = "ノートパソコンはどこだ?見つけたか?",--Where's that laptop? Found it yet?
pln_fish_03_05 = "カネが欲しけりゃノートパソコンを探すんだ!",--You gotta find the laptop if you want to get the money.
pln_fish_03_06 = "おい、ノートパソコンは見つからないか?",--Guys, the laptop. Did you find it yet?
pln_fish_03_07 = "ノートパソコンがどこかにあるはずだ。探せ!",--The laptop must be there somewhere. Find it!
pln_fish_03_08 = "とにかくノートパソコンが見つかるまで探し続けるんだ。",--Just gotta keep looking until you find the laptop.
pln_fish_04_01 = "それだ。",--There it is.
pln_fish_04_02 = "やったな、そいつが探しもんだ。",--Yeah, that's the one we're looking for.
pln_fish_04_03 = "Ok, そのノートパソコンだ。Good job!",--Ok, that's the laptop. Good job!
pln_fish_05_01 = "さあ、パスワードを入力してくれ。",--Now enter the password.
pln_fish_05_02 = "次はパスワードの入力だ。",--Now you've got to enter the password.
pln_fish_05_03 = "パスワードを入力してファイルにアクセスしろ。",--Enter the password and access the files.
pln_fish_06_01 = "こいつはいい。カネの在り処がまるわかりだ。",--This is gold. It's got all the locations of the hidden cash.
pln_fish_06_02 = "カネの隠し場所のリストのようだな。このヨットのあちこちにある。",--Looks like a list of where the money is hidden. It's all over the yacht.
pln_fish_06_03 = "よくやった、これでカネの隠し場所が分かるぞ。",--Great job - it's got all the info on where the money's hidden.
pln_fish_07_01 = "札束の塊だ、美しい!",--Big ones and Benjamins. Beautiful!
pln_fish_07_02 = "愛しのお金ちゃんだ!早く詰めろ!",--Sweet sweet cash! Now bag it!
pln_fish_07_03 = "札の緑が鮮やかだな!袋に詰めろ!",--Green and sweet! Bag that cash!
pln_fish_08_01 = "1つめを発見だ。あと3つ!",--That's the first stash. Three to go!
pln_fish_08_02 = "1つめを見つけたな、続けろ!",--You got the first stash. Keep looking!
pln_fish_08_03 = "1つめだな、あと3つ!",--One down, three to go!
pln_fish_09_01 = "そいつで2つめだ。残り2つ!",--That's the second stash. Two to go!
pln_fish_09_02 = "2つめを見つけたな。残り2つも探せ!",--You got the second stash. Keep looking, two more!
pln_fish_09_03 = "2つめだ、残り2つ!",--Two down, two to go!
pln_fish_10_01 = "3つめだ。残るは1つ!",--That's the third stash. Only one left!
pln_fish_10_02 = "3つめを見つけたな。あと一つ!",--You got the third stash. One more now!
pln_fish_10_03 = "3つめだ、後は1つだけ!",--Three down, just one to go!
pln_fish_11_01 = "そいつで最後だ!全部見つけたな!",--That's the last stash! You got'em all!
pln_fish_11_02 = "よくやった、そいつが最後だ!",--Great - that's the last of 'em!
pln_fish_11_03 = "カネはそれで全部だ!",--That's all of the cash!
pln_fish_12_01 = "バッグを海に投げ込めば、持って帰れるぞ。",--Throw the bags into the sea. You can pick them up when you leave.
pln_fish_12_02 = "戦利品は海に投げ込んどけば、脱出時に手に入るぞ。",--If you throw the loot bags into the sea, you can pick them up when it's time to leave.
pln_fish_12_03 = "バッグは海に投げ込んどけ、帰りに拾えるから。",--Throw the bags over the side. You can fish them out of the water when you get out of there.
pln_fish_13_01 = "乗ってきたボートでバッグを確保出来るぞ。",--You can secure the loot bags in the boat you came in on.
pln_fish_13_02 = "来る時に使ったモーターボートに戦利品を確保しろ。",--Secure the loot bags in the motorboat you arrived in.
pln_fish_13_03 = "モーターボートにバッグを置けば確保出来るぞ。",--You can secure the bags down in the motorboat.
pln_fish_14_01 = "バッグはモーターボートに置くか海に投げ込めば後で手に入るぞ。",--You can secure the bags down in the motorboat or throw them in the sea and we'll pick them up later.
pln_fish_14_02 = "モーターボートでバッグを確保するか、海に放り込め。帰りに回収できる。",--Either secure the bags in the motorboat, or chuck them in the sea. We can pick them up as we leave.
pln_fish_14_03 = "海にバッグを投げ込めば帰りに回収出来る。それか直接モーターボートに乗せてもいい、好きにしろ。",--You can throw the bags in the sea and pick them up when we leave. Or take them directly to the motorboat - your choice.
pln_fish_15_01 = "Ziplineで戦利品を確保しろ。",--Use the zipline to secure the loot.
pln_fish_15_02 = "戦利品の確保にZiplineが使えるぞ。",--There's a zipline you can use to secure the bags of loot.
pln_fish_15_03 = "バッグの確保にZiplineを使え。",--Use the zipline to secure the bags.
pln_fish_16_01 = "Ok, よくやった。お次はサーバーだな...ノートパソコンまで戻って俺に繋げてくれないか、サーバールームの扉を開く。",--Ok, that's great. Now for that server... If you get back to that laptop and hook me up, I should be able to open the room where the server is.
pln_fish_16_02 = "Ok, 次はサーバールームだが....最初のほうで見つけたノートパソコンがあれば侵入出来る。戻って俺に繋げてくれ。",--Ok, now for the server room... That laptop you found earlier should enable me to give you access. Go back there and hook me up.
pln_fish_16_03 = "これでカネは全て確保したな。お次は口座のパスワードが入ったサーバーだが、ノートパソコンまで戻って俺に繋げてくれれば、サーバールームのセキュリティロックを解除できるぞ。",--That's all the cash secured. Now for the server with the bank passwords - get back to that laptop and hook me up so I can open the server room's security lock.
pln_fish_17_01 = "Ok, ノートパソコンを繋いでくれ、すぐに済む。",--Ok, connect me to the laptop, this should only take a moment.
pln_fish_17_02 = "Ok, 繋がったら俺がすぐ済ませてやる。",--Ok, connect me and I'll have this done in a few seconds.
pln_fish_17_03 = "ほんの数秒でドアを開けてやるから俺に繋げてくれ。",--Get me hooked up and I'll get that door unlocked in just a few moments.
pln_fish_18_01 = "Ok, ドアが開いた。中に入れ。",--Ok, the doors are open. Get inside.
pln_fish_18_02 = "Ok, これでサーバールームのドアは開いた。",--Ok, that's the server room door opened.
pln_fish_18_03 = "入ったな、よし。",--Ok guys, you're in.
pln_fish_19_01 = "Ok, ロックは解除したが、ECM jammerが止まるまでは開かないぞ。",--Ok, I got the doors. But they won't open until the ECM jammer stops.
pln_fish_19_02 = "ECM jammerが止まればドアが開くはずだ。",--The doors should open once the ECM jammer stops.
pln_fish_19_03 = "ECM jammerが止まるまでドアは開かない。",--The doors will only open once the ECM jammer stops.
pln_fish_20_01 = "制御装置を操作するには、システムをオーバーヒートさせて再起動させにゃならん。そうすればサーバーが手に入る。",--You'll have to overheat the system to cause a soft reboot and gain access to the controls. Then we should be able to get that server.
pln_fish_20_02 = "システムをオーバーヒートさせれば、再起動がかかって制御装置を操作出来るようになる。それからサーバーを手に入れるんだ。",--If you overheat the system it'll do a soft reboot, giving you access to the controls. Then you can get the server.
pln_fish_20_03 = "システムをオーバーヒートさせて再起動させるんだ。そうすれば制御装置を操作してサーバーを頂ける。",--You'll need to induce a soft reboot by overheating the system. That'll get you access to the controls so you can grab the server.
pln_fish_21_01 = "セカンダリサーバーをオーバーヒートさせるんだ。冷却液の流れを止めればいい。",--You'll need to overheat the secondary servers. Turning off the flow of coolant should do it.
pln_fish_21_02 = "冷却液の流れを止めろ。それでセカンダリサーバ―がオーバーヒートする。",--Turn off the flow of coolant. That should make the secondary servers overheat.
pln_fish_21_03 = "冷却液の流れを止めちまえば、セカンダリサーバ―がオーバーヒートするぞ。",--The secondary servers should overheat if you turn off the flow of coolant.
pln_fish_22_01 = "サーバーラックの下にあるバルブを閉めろ。",--Turn off the valves at the bottom of the server rack.
pln_fish_22_02 = "サーバーラックの下部にあるバルブを閉めるんだ。",--You need to turn off those valves at the bottom of the server rack.
pln_fish_22_03 = "バルブを閉めろ。",--Turn those valves off.
pln_fish_23_01 = "いいぞ、これでオーバーヒートして再起動がかかる。",--That should do it. They'll overheat now and cause that reboot.
pln_fish_23_02 = "よくやった、あとはオーバーヒートするのを待て。そのうちシステムが再起動する。",--Good work, now watch 'em overheat. You'll get that system reboot.
pln_fish_23_03 = "温度が上がってるぞ。これで再起動がかかる。",--Watch the heat rise. You'll get that reboot.
pln_fish_24_01 = "素晴らしい、これでメインパネルを開ける!",--Great, now I should be able to override the main panel.
pln_fish_24_02 = "Ok, お次はメインパネルの操作だ!",--Ok, now for overriding the main panel.
pln_fish_24_03 = "Ok, これでメインパネルを操作出来る。",--Ok. I can override the main panel now.
pln_fish_25_01 = "半分済んだな、あと2つ。",--Halfway now, just two more overrides to go.
pln_fish_25_02 = "2つ終わり、残り2つ。",--Check two overrides, two more to go.
pln_fish_25_03 = "2つ終わり、残り2つ。",--Check two overrides, two more to go.
pln_fish_26_01 = "あと1つ。",--Just one more now.
pln_fish_26_02 = "残るは1つだけだな。",--One more should do it.
pln_fish_26_03 = "あと一つだけだ。",--Just one more override.
pln_fish_27_01 = "よし行くぞ、貯金箱を頂きだ!",--There we go. Money in a box!
pln_fish_27_02 = "Ok, よくやってくれた。暗証番号を取り出すのが楽しみだな!",--Ok, we got it. Can't wait to extract those passwords!
pln_fish_27_03 = "やったな!",--We got it!
pln_fish_28_01 = "もう脱出できるが、金目のものを探してもいいぞ。お前らに任せる。",--You can escape now, or maybe look for more valuables. Your choice.
pln_fish_28_02 = "このヨットにはまだ良いものがありそうだな、目的は済んでるから、あとは任せる。",--There might be more loot on the yacht, but you got what you came for. Your choice.
pln_fish_28_03 = "金になりそうな物を探してもいいし、すぐ脱出してもいい。",--You can either look for more loot or get out of there now.
pln_fish_29_01 = "船を空っぽにしたな。脱出しよう。",--You cleaned it out. Time to leave.
pln_fish_29_02 = "根こそぎ頂いたな、そろそろ帰るぞ。",--You got everything. Time to go home.
pln_fish_29_03 = "Ok, もうめぼしいものは残ってない。脱出だ。",--Ok, there's nothing left to steal. Get out of there.
pln_fish_30_01 = "サーバールームがロックダウンされた。もう入れないぞ!",--The server room is locked down. We can't get in there now!
pln_fish_30_02 = "アラームだ! もうサーバールームはロックダウンされて入れないぞ!",--That's the alarm! The server room's locked down now - we can't access it!
pln_fish_30_03 = "サーバールームはロックダウンされてる。もう入れないぞ!",--The server room is in security lockdown. We can't access it now!
pln_fish_31_01 = "くそっ、惜しいところで!",--Damn it, so close!
pln_fish_31_02 = "もうちょっとだったのに!",--We almost had it!
pln_fish_31_03 = "あと少しだったのに!",--We almost tasted that cigar!
pln_fish_32_01 = "死体は窓から海へ捨てるといいぞ。",--You can dump bodies into the sea through the windows.
pln_fish_32_02 = "死体を捨てたいなら窓から海へ投げればいい。",--If you want to dump bodies into the sea, you can use the windows.
pln_fish_32_03 = "死体を片付けたいなら窓から投げろ。海が全て飲み込んでくれる。",--Use the windows to get rid of any bodies. The sea will swallow them.
pln_fish_33_01 = "船尾から海へ死体を投げ込むといい。",--You can throw bodies into the sea over the railing at the back of the boat.
pln_fish_33_02 = "船尾から海に投げ込めば死体を隠せるぞ。",--You could hide the bodies by throwing them into the sea at the back of the boat.
pln_fish_33_03 = "死体は船尾から海に投げ込めばいい。",--At the back you can throw any bodies over the railing into the sea.
pln_fish_34_01 = "見ろよあれ。大勢の金持ち連中がお楽しみだ。",--Look at that. A lot of rich people up there, enjoying themselves.
pln_fish_34_02 = "McKendrickには有力な支持者が大勢いるに違いない。奴を勝たせて見返りをにカネを期待してるんだ。",--McKendrick sure has a lot of influential supporters up there. They're expecting to cash in if he wins, I'm sure.
pln_fish_34_03 = "パーティってな大概上の方で開かれるが、おかげで下の方じゃ静かに仕事がやれて実にありがたいな。",--I'm sure glad most of the party is upstairs so we can work in peace and quiet down here.
pln_fish_35_01 = "あいつらTVニュースの取材か?近づかないようにしろ。",--Is that a TV news crew? Try to stay away from them.
pln_fish_35_02 = "ニュースの撮影クルーみたいだな、TVに写りたくなきゃカメラから離れてろよ。",--That looks like a television news crew. You don't want to be on TV guys, stay off their camera.
pln_fish_35_03 = "TVの取材陣か、うーん...カメラには映らないようにな。",--A TV crew. Hmm... try to stay off their camera.
pln_fish_36_01 = "ECM jammerを起動するとサーバールームのドアが開かなくなるだろうから、気をつけろよ。",--An active ECM jammer will probably make it hard to open the server room security door. Keep that in mind.
pln_fish_36_02 = "一応言っておく、奴らがサーバールームに使ってるセキュリティはECM jammerが側にあると開かなくなるタイプだ。",--Just a heads up: the type of security they use for the server room will make it harder to open if there's an active ECM jammer nearby.
pln_fish_36_03 = "ECM jammerの作動中はサーバールームを開けない。使う時は注意しろ。",--An active ECM jammer will make it harder to access the server room. So use them with caution.
pln_fish_37_01 = "恐らくそこがサーバールームだ。覚えておけ。",--That's probably the server room. Remember where it is.
pln_fish_37_02 = "多分そこはサーバールームだろう。カネを見つけるまでとっておけ。場所は忘れるなよ。",--That looks like it might be the server room. Better save it for after you find the cash. Remember where it is.
pln_fish_37_03 = "そこはサーバールームだろうな、覚えておこう。だがまずは、カネが先だ。",--I guess that's the server room. Make note of it - you should find the cash first.
pln_fish_brf_01 = "",--Ok guys, you know what's at stake here. McKendrick needs that cash to win the elections, and if you can steal it you're pulling the rug out from under his feet. Let's spoil his party, rain on his parade - get even for what that ungrateful bastard did. So get that cash. And there's another thing I found in the file that Charon gave us - somewhere on the yacht there's a server which contains passwords for illicit foreign bank accounts, some of which are also used by McKendrick. Steal that server, and we can cash in nicely on it. (pause) Uh, yeah... I almost forgot... there's a fundraising party for McKendrick on the yacht tonight. With TV and everything. But the party's mostly on the upper deck, so if you sneak in quietly you should be able to get in and out without anyone noticing.
pln_fish_end_01 = "よくやったぞ、これでMcKendrickの野郎はお手上げだ。カネが綺麗さっぱりなくなってる事に気づいたらさぞ落ち込むだろう。",--Great job, gang - you really screwed McKendrick over this time. He won't be happy when he finds out all that money's gone.
pln_fish_end_02 = "誰の仕業かMcKendrickに見当が付くかはともかく、俺たちを怒らせるべきじゃなかったな。",--I wonder if McKendrick will ever figure out who did this. In any case, he shouldn't have messed with us.
pln_fish_end_03 = "これでMcKendrick再当選の夢は潰えたな。そしてお前らこそまさしく「政界の実力者」だ!The Payday Gangは与えなさり、奪いたもう。",--That's the end of McKendrick's re-election dreams - you're true kingmakers, guys! The Payday Gang giveth and it taketh away.
pln_fish_intro_01 = "よーし海賊ども、船に乗り込んでお宝を頂いてこい。もちろん静かにな。",--Okay, pirates - board the ship and get the loot. And keep it quiet.
pln_fish_intro_02 = "注意しろよ、警備員に見られないようカネを探せ。",--Be careful now, don't let the guards see you. And find that cash.
pln_fish_intro_03 = "宝探しがんばってこいよ。ただし、静かにな。",--Good luck on your treasure hunt, guys. And remember, keep it quiet.
loc_rvd_02_01 = "用心しろ、間抜けどもが大挙してやってくるぞ! 皆がそいつらに対処している間、Mr. Blondeはそこのお友達を世話してくれ!",--Heads-up friends, you got a bunch of dwankies incoming! Mr. Blonde, you look after that kêrel while the boys take care of the others!
loc_rvd_02_02 = "間抜けどもに見つかったぞ!  Mr. Blonde, その太っちょを向こうに連れて行け、他はお客さんの相手だ。",--Bloody dwankies found you already! Mr. Blonde, take that Porky in the back and the gang will take care of the other kêrels.
loc_rvd_02_03 = "そこら中から警官共が来るぞ、思ったより早く見つかったな。応戦しろ!",--Coppers incoming everyone, they found you faster that I thought. Take care of them!
loc_rvd_03_01 = "扉に注意しろ! 警官がいるぞ!",--Cover the doors! Coppers are there!
loc_rvd_03_02 = "入り口に注意だ、諸君!",--Watch the entrances, friends!
loc_rvd_03_03 = "警官共がすぐ外にいるぞ! 準備は万端だろうね?",--Kêrels are just outside! Be ready for anything, yeah?
loc_rvd_04_01 = "諸君、いま事態の収拾にあたっている。頑張ってくれ。",--Friends, I'm still trying to sort this. Hang in there.
loc_rvd_04_02 = "何か手がないか探っているところだ。敵に集中してくれ。",--Still trying to follow up all the threads. Try to keep focus.
loc_rvd_05_01 = "奴らにしてはよくやれたものだ。まさかBainが襲われるとは想像も出来なかった。",--Can't believe they managed to pull it off. Never really thought Bain could be that vulnerable.
loc_rvd_05_02 = "Bainはあり得ると言っていたが、私には信じられなかった。君達をWashingtonから離れさせたのは正解だったな、ええ?",--Bain said it could happen but I didn't believe him. Good thing I got you out of Washington, eh?
loc_rvd_06_01 = "Mr Pinkから連絡はあったか?",--Have you heard from Mr Pink?
loc_rvd_06_02 = "Mr Pinkはどうなったんだ?",--I wonder what happened to Mr Pink?
loc_rvd_06_03 = "Mr Pinkは捕まったのか?",--Do you know if Mr Pink was captured?
loc_rvd_07_01 = "彼はそう遠くなさそうだな? 迎えに行け!",--Sounds like he's not too far away, yeah? Go get him!
loc_rvd_07_02 = "そういうことだ諸君、倉庫を出てMr Pinkを連れてくるんだ、いいかね?",--Right friends, better go out and get Mr Pink, yeah?
loc_rvd_07_03 = "では諸君、急いでMr Pinkを助けに行くんだ、いいね?",--OK, friends. Hurry out and rescue Mr Pink, right?
loc_rvd_08_01 = "まあ、これで何か良いものでも手に入れてくれ。SAWを探すんだ。",--Well friends, at least something good can come of this. Go find that saw.
loc_rvd_08_02 = "この先金が必要だが私の緊急用の金貨はインターポールに没収されている、というわけでSAWを見つけてくれ、いいかね?",--Alright, we will probably need every little bit of cash after this and my stash of emergency krugerrand was confiscated by Interpol, so go find that saw, yeah?
loc_rvd_08_03 = "外に出て少しでも稼ぎたいなら、SAWを探してくれ、いいかね?",--Might be a good to at least get some extra funding out of this, so go find that saw, yeah?
loc_rvd_09_01 = "SAWを見つけてくる必要があるな",--You need to find that saw, friends.
loc_rvd_09_02 = "ちゃんとSAWを持っていけ。",--Don't forget to pick up that saw.
loc_rvd_09_03 = "まったく、SAWはその辺にあるはずだぞ。",--Fokenwil, that saw's gotta be around there somewhere.
loc_rvd_09_04 = "SAWを探せ",--Find the saw guys.
loc_rvd_10_01 = "いいぞ、次は石ころを頂きだ!",--Good, now go get those stones, guys!
loc_rvd_10_02 = "そいつだ、後は綺麗な石ころを手に入れるだけだ。",--That's it, now you just gotta go get those pretty rocks, yeah?
loc_rvd_10_03 = "見つけたな、外の物置を開けにいけ!",--There, now get out and crack that thing open!
loc_rvd_11_01 = "物置の所へ行ってくれないか?",--Get to that storage unit, yeah?
loc_rvd_11_02 = "あまり時間はないぞ友よ、物置を開けに行け!",--Not a lot of time here friends, get that unit open!
loc_rvd_11_03 = "急げ諸君、物置を開けろ!",--Hurry friends, get that storage unit open!
loc_rvd_11_04 = "正しい物置を探せ!",--You need to find the right storage unit!
loc_rvd_11_05 = "ダイヤモンドの袋は物置の内のどれかだ。",--The bag of diamonds is in one of the storage units.
loc_rvd_11_06 = "急げ友よ、SAWで開けるんだ!",--Come on friends, saw those units open!
loc_rvd_11_07 = "物置を開けるんだ、諸君。",--You gotta open up those storage units, friends.
loc_rvd_12_01 = "よくやった、Mr Blondeの所に石ころを持っていくといい。彼のボスが捌いてくれる。",--There you go, better get those stones to Mr Blonde. His boss will be able to move them.
loc_rvd_12_02 = "バッグを見つけたな、Mr Blondeに渡しに行ってくれるかね?",--There's the bag, get it to Mr Blonde, yeah?
loc_rvd_12_03 = "Mr Blondeのボスの方が私より石ころを売るのには慣れている。バッグは彼の所に持っていってくれ、いいね?",--Mr. Blonde's boss will be able to sell those stones quicker than me, so get the bag to him, yeah?
loc_rvd_13_01 = "すぐにまた警官がやってくるぞ。Mr. Blondeの所へバッグを持っていけ。",--More coppers coming soon. Blonde needs that bag.
loc_rvd_13_02 = "ペースを上げてくれ。Mr. Blondeにバッグを渡せ。",--You need to pick up the pace. Get that bag to Mr. Blonde.
loc_rvd_13_03 = "石ころをMr. Blondeの所へ持っていけ!",--Don't forget those stones, get them to Blonde!
loc_rvd_13_04 = "Mr.Blondeはその石にはあまり関心がないようだぞ",--This Mr. Blonde doesn't appear too keen on getting those stones himself.
loc_rvd_13_05 = "その石をMr.Blondeに渡すんだ",--Get those stones to Mr. Blonde.
loc_rvd_13_06 = "急いでダイヤと一緒に倉庫へ戻るんだ、諸君。",--Hurry back to the warehouse with those diamonds, friends.
loc_rvd_14_01 = "上出来だ諸君、そろそろ御暇したほうがよさそうだな。Twitchが向かっている、もうすぐだ。",--Right friends, looks like you're not welcome there any longer. Twitch is inbound. He'll be there soon.
loc_rvd_14_02 = "よし、友よ。脱出はTwitchに依頼してある。彼を向かわせるから、しばらく耐えてくれ、いいね?",--OK, friends. I've got Twitch standing by to come get you. Let me give him the go-ahead. Hang on for a bit, yeah?
loc_rvd_14_03 = "案ずるな友よ、Twitchに話をつけている。彼が迎えに来るのにそう時間はかからない。",--Not to worry friends, I've gotten in touch with Twitch. He's not too far out and will come get you.
loc_rvd_15_01 = "Twitchは横路地にいるぞ",--Twitch is coming to the side alley.
loc_rvd_15_02 = "Twitchは路地にいる。探すんだ",--Look for Twitch in the alley!
loc_rvd_15_03 = "Twitchが到着した。彼は駐車場だ!",--Get to Twitch, he's in the parking lot!
loc_rvd_15_04 = "Twitchは駐車場だ。合流しろ!",--Get to the parking lot and meet up with Twitch, guys!
loc_rvd_15_05 = "Twitchは野外撮影場所にいる",--Twitch is coming in from the back lot.
loc_rvd_15_06 = "Twitchと合流しろ!",--Get to the far back and join up with Twitch!
loc_rvd_16_01 = "友よ、あなた方はまだ私を信頼できないだろう。だが、警察をまいてから落ち着いてお話をしよう。いいか?",--Friends, I know you still don't trust me, but we'll talk more once you're away from the cops, yeah?
loc_rvd_16_02 = "そこから脱出したら、現状あなた方の周りで何が起こってるのかお話しよう。信じられないかもしれないがな。",--Once you're out of there we can talk some more about what's going on. It's gonna get rough I suspect.
loc_rvd_brf_01 = "",--Friends! It's Locke. I know you got little incentive to trust me after Alaska, but sending you there was the only credible ruse we had time for, to get you out of DC. People Bain used to think could be trusted... were listening. And now he's gone... we knew something was going to happen but not when or what. Keeping you in the dark was my call, not Bain's. Never thought they would actually be able to go after him. Look I realise it's a kakspul to hear, but you got out with the guns I left, yeah? I'm sorry about Bain... we'll deal with it... but first we have to get you out of there. Please trust me guys, I'm not bekakin ya. I promise I'll prove it.
loc_rvd_end_01 = "",--Dear friends, even if you don't trust me you need to listen 'cause things are about to get real heavy. Not long ago, Bain got new information about this Holy-Grail-dinges he's after. He wouldn't tell me what... something about not believing him, but said others are now wanting it too. The whole operation, including Crimenet, will go to shit if we dont' get things fixed. Sure, I'm in it for the money, yeah, but I also owe Bain, and I intend to repay. Aldstone says the safehouse is safe again, so get back there and I'l be in touch. Must see to some things. We're going after the big one... and bringing a back lost soul too.
loc_rvd_intro1_01 = "",--Guys, I will try to get you an escape plan and find out what the bloody blazes is going on, yeah? The warehouse should still be safe for a quick breather.
loc_rvd_intro1_02 = "",--Bain left me instructions just in case something went wrong. I've double-checked and the warehouse meeting spot still looks quiet, for the time being. Hole up there while I try to find out what's going on.
mrb_rvd1_01_01 = "銃撃戦は続いてるか?誰かが俺たちを売りやがったんだ",--The fuck is going on? Some motherfucker sold us out.
mrb_rvd1_01_02 = "",--Thought you guys were stable? What the fuck happened back there?
mrb_rvd1_07_01 = "野郎共、俺達の分け前がどうなったか気になるかもしれないが安心しろ。お釈迦になった車は乗り捨てたが、近くの倉庫に隠しておいた。",--So, guys. You might be wonderin' what happened to our loot. Well, I had to ditch the car but I managed to hide some of it in a storage unit nearby.
mrb_rvd1_07_02 = "ニュースが2つ。車がお釈迦になっちまったが、戦利品のいくつかは無事だ。近くの倉庫に隠しておいてある。",--So, here's the thing. My car died, but I managed to haul away some diamonds. Stashed 'em in a nearby storage unit.
mrb_rvd1_07_03 = "悪いニュースと良いニュースがある。悪いニュースは車がお釈迦になったことだ。良いニュースは戦利品のいくつかは無事だということだ。近くの倉庫に隠してあるぞ。",--So, here's some good news and bad news. Bad news is my car died. Good news is that I had time to to grab some diamonds from the trunk. They're in a storage unit nearby.
mrb_rvd1_07b_01 = "",--It's by the warehouse across the street. Gonna need a saw to open it though 'cause I lost the key in the commotion. There's one in the back.
mrb_rvd1_07c_01 = "",--Out by the parking lot. Won't crack open without a saw though, but there's one of those around here somewhere.
mrb_rvd1_07d_01 = "",--It's way out there, behind the parking lot. The door to the unit is pretty thick and I don't have the key. We'll need to cut it open. Should be a saw around here.
mrb_rvd1_08_01 = "",--Swell, these will make Cabot happy after all this is done.
mrb_rvd1_08_02 = "",--Great, at least this fiasco isn't a total loss.
mrb_rvd1_08_03 = "",--Not bad, even after all the other shit that's gone down today.
mrb_rvd1_09_01 = "",--Hey, I just got word. Cabot's got a guy comin' to pick us up but you guys better split before he gets here. He ain't too happy right now.
mrb_rvd1_09_02 = "",--So, I just heard from the boss. He's on his way here to get us but he's pretty pissed, so you guys might wanna bail before he gets here.
mrb_rvd1_09_03 = "",--The boss just called and he's pissed. Got a guy comin' to get us but you should probably bail. I'll make sure you get your cut.
mrb_rvd1_12_01 = "",--Yeah, I brought it, so what now?
mrb_rvd1_12_02 = "",--Sure, I got it but what good's it gonna do now?
mrb_rvd1_12_03 = "",--Course I brought it. Cabots don't hire morons.
mrb_rvd1_16_01 = "",--Hey, was that the vault? Can't argue with your sense of style.
mrb_rvd1_16_02 = "",--Wow, you guys are kinda entertaining. I saw parts flyin' all the way out here.
mrb_rvd1_16_03 = "",--That was, you know, kind of a big explosion.
mrb_rvd1_16_04 = "",--Wonder how many donut chompers just shit their duty blues.
mrb_rvd1_28_01 = "",--Guys, I'm gonna need some help getting out of here with this stuff.
mrb_rvd1_28_02 = "",--Hey, I'm not gonna be able to break out of here without some help.
mrb_rvd1_28_03 = "",--Too much heat for me just make a break for it with the car. Gonna need some help guys.
mrb_rvd1_29_01 = "",--Thanks a bunch fellas! See you at the warehouse!
mrb_rvd1_29_02 = "",--Nice work guys! Grab me a burger while you're at it. See ya back at the warehouse!
mrb_rvd1_29_03 = "",--I lost the pigs guys, thanks! See you in a bit. And bring me a burger!
mrb_rvd1_30_01 = "",--Yeah, about that. It's out here. In my car.
mrb_rvd1_30_02 = "",--Well I didn't bring it in. I got it out here in my trunk.
mrb_rvd1_30_03 = "",--So, here's the thing. It's out here with me... in my car.
mrp_rvd_01_01 = "",--Hey, can anyone hear me? What the goddamn fuck is going on? I'm comin' in hot... took a cap in the side.
mrp_rvd_01_02 = "",--Where the fuck are you guys? How the hell did they know we were comin'? I'm comin' to the warehouse... got capped.
mrp_rvd_01_03 = "",--Hey fuckers, I got cops on my ass. I'm hit. What the fuck was that back there?
mrp_rvd_02_01 = "",--Hey, I'm here... outside... not far from the street! Piece of shit car!
mrp_rvd_02_02 = "",--Fuuuck. Guys, come get me in the parking lot!
mrp_rvd_02_03 = "",--Fucking piece of shit car! Need a hand out here guys!
mrp_rvd_02_04 = "",--Jesus Christ guys, come get me before the cops do. I'm at the far back!
mrp_rvd_02_05 = "",--Where the fuck am I? I see... Storage units?
mrp_rvd_03_01 = "",--Hurry up Goddamnit!
mrp_rvd_03_02 = "",--What's takin' so long, Goddamnit?
mrp_rvd_03_03 = "",--Hurry man, my ass is gonna be grass like if the cops had lawn-mowers!
mrp_rvd_03_04 = "",--Get your thumbs out of your asses and come get me!
mrp_rvd_03_05 = "",--The goddamn fuck is taking so long? I'm bleedin' here!
mrp_rvd_03_06 = "",--Jumpin' fuckin' Jesus guys, I'm gonna get creamed.
mrp_rvd_03_07 = "",--C'mon man, either get me or send a cab.
mrp_rvd_03_08 = "",--They're right on top of me people, can't fucking hold out much longer!
mrp_rvd_04_01 = "",--The fuck took so long, man?
mrp_rvd_04_02 = "",--Jesus H-Goddamn-Christ that took long!
mrp_rvd_04_03 = "",--Shit, man I'm dyin' out here. What'd ya do, stop for a hot dog?
mrp_rvd_05_01 = "",--*grunts, wheezes*
mrp_rvd_05_02 = "",--*grunts, wheezes*
mrp_rvd_05_03 = "",--*grunts, wheezes*
mrp_rvd_05_04 = "",--*grunts, wheezes*
mrp_rvd_05_05 = "",--*grunts, wheezes*
mrp_rvd_05_06 = "",--*grunts, wheezes*
mrp_rvd_06_01 = "",--The fuck happened back there? No way the cops knew we were there that fast.
mrp_rvd_06_02 = "",--I swear I was being followed for a while, and not by cops either.
mrp_rvd_06_03 = "",--Some weird shit happening on this job.
mrp_rvd_06_05 = "",--Someone better fucking explain this shit to me.
mrp_rvd_06_06 = "",--Cabot's is gonna have to fuckin' pay extra for this shit.
mrp_rvd_06_07 = "",--Goddamn cops knew we were gonna be there. Too many of 'em for a simple diamond job. Civvies too.
mrp_rvd_06_08 = "",--Someone please tell me if we got anything worth a damn out of that place?
mrp_rvd_07_01 = "",--Fuck this shit man.
mrp_rvd_07_02 = "",--If we get outta this one I might just leave this fuckin' town.
mrp_rvd_07_03 = "",--Ain't never seen a job this screwed.
mrp_rvd_07_04 = "",--Right now I wish I was some other guy on some other job.
mrp_rvd_07_05 = "",--So what's it like in DC? All those scumbag politicians on the payroll keep the cops off your asses?
mrp_rvd_07_06 = "",--Diamond jobs always turn into fuckin' bloodbaths. Heard they had to scrape a guy off the floor once with a shovel 'cause of all the dried blood.
mrp_rvd_07_07 = "",--Man, I could really use a beer.
mrp_rvd_07_08 = "",--Wish I were at a burger joint with my girl right now.
mrp_rvd_08_01 = "",--So what do you really know about these Payday guys? Can't imagine this shit is our fault.
mrp_rvd_08_02 = "",--This Payday gang Cabot brought in... we sure this isn't their mess?
mrp_rvd_09_01 = "",--Hey, thanks for the rescue guys. Best of luck to ya.
mrp_rvd_09_02 = "",--Best of luck with your boss and all guys.
mrp_rvd_09_03 = "",--Hey guys, it's been.. interesting.
mrp_rvd_10_01 = "",--Aw, fuck they shot Brown in the face!
mrp_rvd_10_02 = "",--OH, FUCK they got Brown!
mrp_rvd_10_03 = "",--Motherfuckin' pigs got Brown!
mrp_rvd_11_01 = "クソ、なんてこった!",--Fuck, goddamnit!
mrp_rvd_11_02 = "なんてこった、サツだ!",--Goddamn cops!
mrp_rvd_11_03 = "",--Die motherfuckers!
mrp_rvd_11_04 = "",--Yeah, well fuck you too!
mrp_rvd_11_05 = "",--Fuck man, I got Brown's brains all over me!
mrp_rvd_11_06 = "",--You fuckin' see what they did to Brown?!
mrp_rvd_11_07 = "",--How the fuck did they know we were gonna be here!?
mrp_rvd_11_08 = "",--They fuckin' shot Brown in the face!
mrp_rvd_12_01 = "",--Fuck this shit, I'm bailin'!
mrp_rvd_12_02 = "",--Who fuckin' booked this job?
mrp_rvd_12_03 = "",--Let's fuckin' blow this pop stand.
pln_rvd_01_01 = "",--Huh... everyone must be at the beach.
pln_rvd_01_02 = "",--This area is usually full of spoiled, rich movie stars buying useless junk.
pln_rvd_01_03 = "のんびりした日だ...何か良いことがありそうだ",--Slow day... should be good for us.
pln_rvd_02_01 = "役者達、中に入ってカボットの連中と合流の時間だ",--Get in character gang, time to meet Cabot's boys.
pln_rvd_02_02 = "演技の時間だ。彼らが待っているぞ",--Time to get in character, the others are waiting for you.
pln_rvd_02_03 = "",--Suck in those guts guys, let's make a good impression. Go meet the gang.
pln_rvd_03_01 = "観光してる暇はないぞ",--No time to take in the sights.
pln_rvd_03_02 = "おいお前ら、ゆっくりせずにプロになれよ",--C'mon guys, let's be professional, not late.
pln_rvd_03_03 = "",--We only have a short window of opportunity guys.
pln_rvd_03_04 = "",--Let's get this thing going, guys.
pln_rvd_03_05 = "",--Try not to be late guys, don't want to look unprofessional.
pln_rvd_03_06 = "野郎共、行動するんだ",--Guys, you need to get moving.
pln_rvd_03_07 = "コーヒーを飲んどるヒマはないぞ",--No time to stop for coffee.
pln_rvd_03_08 = "なんでゆっくりしてるんだ? 有名な映画俳優でも見つけたのか?",--What's the delay, see a movie star or somethin'?
pln_rvd_04_01 = "出口に何故Gensecのバンが?",--What's a Gensec truck doing way out there?
