pln_rvd_brf_01 = "",--Ok, guys. Cabot's people will be waiting for you outside the store. From what he tells me, this should be quick and easy. Show these professional LA gangsters what the Payday gang can do.
pln_rvd_cbf_01 = "",--Guys, we need to talk about what happened up in Alaska, but I've got another job first, while you're still out west. So, the son of an old friend of mine in L.A., member of the Cabot crime family needs help hitting a jewelry store for a haul of diamonds. I owe him big from years ago, when his dad got me out of a jam, so I promised him a little extra muscle as payback. These guys are pro's, real characters. They even use code names! You guys up for it?
pln_rvd_cnc_01 = "ロスの旧友の手伝いだ。彼はダイヤモンドの問題をかかえているようだ",--We're helping an old friend of mine in L.A. He's got a diamond problem.
pln_rvd_cnc_02 = "お前ら、天使の街でダイヤの仕事をしに行くぞ",--Guys, we're gonna partner up on a diamond job in Angel City.
pln_rvd_cnc_03 = "ハリウッドの旧友は頼りになる。Rockの居場所を特定するのを手伝ってくれるだろう。",--An old buddy out in Hollywood is calling in a favor. We're gonna help him lift some rocks.
pln_rvd_intro_01 = "ロスの静かな良い1日だ",--A nice quiet day in L.A.
pln_rvd_intro_02 = "天使の街でお買い物の時間だ",--Time for some leisurely shopping in Angel City.
pln_rvd_intro_03 = "",--A nice quiet day in the sun. Bring back some autographs.
pln_chw_01_01 = "いいか、The Elephantから聞いた通りだ、目的は分かってるよな。BCIヘッドセットとそのソフトウェアを見つけろ。上手く行けばすごいカネになるぜ。",--Okay, gang. Elephant gave you the briefing, so you know what we're after. We need to find the BCI headset and the computer software. You manage this, we'll make a lot of money.
pln_chw_01_02 = "脳ミソを使ってドローンを動かすだと? まったく、ついて行けねえな。ともかく、この技術は高く売れそうだ。バイカーどもから頂いちまおう。",--Using your brain to control a drone? Jesus, I'm getting old. Anyway, this technology is worth a lot of cash, so we need to steal it from these bikers.
pln_chw_01_03 = "Brain-Computer InterfaceについてはThe Elephantから聞いたよな? 俺たちの目当てはその脳ミソだけでドローンを動かせるようになるハイテクなヘッドセットとソフトウェアだ。実際俺にも信じられん。ともかく、Rustの話じゃ両方この列車で運ばれてるそうだ。",--The Elephant briefed you about the Brain-Computer Interface, right? We're after a high-tech headset and a software that allows you to control a drone using your brain. Trust me, I can barely believe it myself. Anyhow, according to Rust, both things are currently being transported on this train.
pln_chw_02_01 = "Rustが言うには、バイカー共に守られた先頭車両に俺たちの目当てのブツがあるらしい。邪魔する奴は蹴散らして進め。",--Rust told me the bikers have one of the cars in the front where they guard the stuff we're after. Make your way there and don't let anything stop you.
pln_chw_02_02 = "Rustの話からすると、OVERKILL MCの装置は先頭車両にあるらしい。足を止めずに出来る限り速くたどり着け。あまり時間が無いからな。",--According to Rust, the OVERKILL MC have the tech in one of the cars in the front. Get over there as fast as you can and don't stop. We don't have much time.
pln_chw_02_03 = "BCIは先頭車両にある、目的地はそこだ。",--The BCI tech is supposed to be in a car in the front of the train, so that's your destination.
pln_chw_03_01 = "押し込め、ギャング共!",--Keep pushing forward, gang!
pln_chw_03_02 = "先頭車両に行け!",--You need to get to the front!
pln_chw_03_03 = "止まるな、進め!",--Go forward and don't stop!
pln_chw_03_04 = "先頭の車両に行くんだ!",--The front of the train, gang!
pln_chw_03_05 = "先頭まで突き進むんだ、頑張れ!",--Make your way to the front, guys. Come on!
pln_chw_03_06 = "前進しろ!",--Keep going forward!
pln_chw_03_07 = "行き先は先頭車両だ!",--The car we're after is in the front, gang!
pln_chw_03_08 = "必要なのはBCIだ、進め!",--We need to get our hands on the BCI tech, gang. Go forward!
pln_chw_04_01 = "ドアが無けりゃ作ればいい。ガスバーナーの出番だ。",--If you don't have a door, you make one. Time to use the blowtorch.
pln_chw_04_02 = "ガスバーナーで車両の入り口を作れ。",--Use the blowtorch to create a way through that car.
pln_chw_04_03 = "この車両にはドアが無い、ガスバーナーを使って作れ!",--This car doesn't have a door, so you'll have to use a blowtorch to make one.
pln_chw_05_01 = "運任せは嫌だからな。見えてる箱を片っ端から開けていけ。最悪でも何か金目の物を見つけろ。",--I'm not taking any chances, gang. Search any boxes you see. Worst case scenario is you find other valuables.
pln_chw_05_02 = "ここらの箱を全部開けろ。確実に見つけたい。",--Search those boxes. I'm not willing to take any chances on this one.
pln_chw_05_03 = "全ての箱を開けろ。Rustの情報違いでBCIが見つからないなんてのは御免だからな。",--Search all boxes you find. I won't risk missing the BCI tech because Rust's information was wrong.
pln_chw_06_01 = "くそ、奴ら箱にC4を仕掛けてやがった! 解除しろ!",--Damn, they rigged the boxes with C4! Defuse them!
pln_chw_06_02 = "箱にC4が仕掛けられてるぞ! すぐに解除しろ!",--The boxes are rigged with C4! Defuse them quick!
pln_chw_06_03 = "こいつは...! 箱にC4が仕掛けられてる! 解除するんだ!",--Holy...! They rigged the boxes with C4! Defuse them!
pln_chw_07_01 = "BCIを取り逃したくないから、箱を全て開けて探せ。",--I'm not taking any chances with these boxes. Search 'em.
pln_chw_07_02 = "ゲートを開け。箱を調べてくれ。",--Don't let that gate stop you. I want those boxes searched.
pln_chw_07_03 = "ゲートを開いて箱を調べろ。",--Get that gate open and search the boxes.
pln_chw_08_01 = "大当たりだ! Rustの情報は正しかったな。それじゃ、中に入ってBCIヘッドセットとソフトウェアを取れ。",--Jackpot! Rust's info was correct. Now, get through the gate and grab the BCI headset and the software.
pln_chw_08_02 = "そこだ! ゲートをくぐってBCIヘッドセットとソフトウェアを確保しろ。",--There it is! Get through the gate and secure both the BCI headset and the software.
pln_chw_08_03 = "よし、そこだ。ゲートを開けてBCIヘッドセットとソフトウェアを手に入れろ。",--Oh yeah, there it is. Get the gate open and secure the BCI headset and the software.
pln_chw_09_01 = "何してんだ? ゲートを開けて中に入れ!",--What are you waiting for? Get through that gate!
pln_chw_09_02 = "ほら! とっととゲートを開けて目当ての物を手に入れようぜ。",--Come on! Open the gate already and get the stuff we came for.
pln_chw_09_03 = "ボケっとしてないで、ゲートを開けてBCIを確保しろ。",--Don't just stand around! Get the gate open and secure the BCI tech.
pln_chw_10_01 = "よし、手に入れたな。そいつを手放すなよ、ヘリまで運ぶんだ。Bileが待ってるぞ、移動開始だ。",--Okay, you got the stuff. That's the important thing. Time to bring it all to the helicopter. Get a move on, Bile's waiting.
pln_chw_10_02 = "手に入れたな、お見事だ。ヘリまで持っていこう。さあ、Bileが待ってるぞ!",--You got it. Excellent. Time to bring it all to the helicopter. Bile's waiting, get going!
pln_chw_10_03 = "BCIを手に入れたな、ヘリに戻るぞ! Bileが待ってるからな。",--The tech is in our hands! Time to head back to the helicopter! Don't keep Bile waiting.
pln_chw_11_01 = "何をぐずぐずしてるんだ? ヘリに戻って戦利品を確保しろ!",--What are you waiting for? Run back to the helicopter and secure the loot!
pln_chw_11_02 = "ヘリに戻ってBCIを確保しろ!",--Get back to the helicopter and secure the BCI tech!
pln_chw_11_03 = "急いでヘリまで戻ってBCIを確保しろ。",--Hurry up and get back to the chopper so we can secure the BCI tech.
pln_chw_12_01 = "BCIを確保したな、よくやった。車両に残ってる物を取りに戻ってもいいぞ。良いカネになる。",--All right, the BCI tech is in safe hands now. You still have the opportunity to go back to the wagon and get more loot. It's all worth good cash.
pln_chw_12_02 = "素晴らしい! BCIは確保できたから、もっと稼ぎたきゃ戦利品を取りに戻ってもいいぞ。",--Excellent! With the BCI tech in safe possession, you have time to get more of the loot if you want to make some good money.
pln_chw_12_03 = "修羅場になる前に脱出してほしいが、もっと戦利品を取りに戻りたいってなら構わないぜ。",--I would prefer it if you just left before anything goes wrong, but I understand if you wanna go back to get more of the loot.
pln_chw_13_01 = "それで最後だな。全部良いカネになるぜ。ヘリに戻って脱出しよう。",--That's all of it. We'll make some good money from all this fancy stuff. Head back to the chopper and get out of there now.
pln_chw_13_02 = "よくやった。ボーナスはいつだって歓迎だ。さて、ヘリまで戻って脱出しよう。",--Good job. More cash is always welcome. Now, run back to the helicopter and get out of there.
pln_chw_13_03 = "全部頂いたな、よくやった。とっとと逃げるぞ。",--You cleaned the place out. Good job. Time to get the hell out of there.
pln_chw_14_01 = "おい! 脱出しろ! 何チンタラしてんだ?",--Gang! Get out of there! What the hell are you doing?
pln_chw_14_02 = "行くぞ! ほら!",--Time to go! Come on!
pln_chw_14_03 = "行けってば!",--I said it's time to go!
pln_chw_15_01 = "くそ! サツ共がこの先の線路を封鎖してやがるぞ、つまりそこに着く前に脱出しなきゃいけないって事だ。BCIを手に入れてヘリに戻れ!",--Damn! The cops have blocked the tracks up ahead, which means you need to be gone before you reach that point. Get the BCI tech and run back to the chopper!
pln_chw_15_02 = "おい! サツはこの先で列車を止めるつもりだ。BCIを手に入れてさっさと脱出しろ!",--Hey! The cops are gonna stop the train further down the tracks, so you need to get the BCI tech and get the hell out of there!
pln_chw_15_03 = "聞いてくれ! サツが集まって前方の線路を封鎖しているから、マジで急ぐ必要がある。BCIを取ってきてBileの所まで戻れ!",--Listen up! The cops are bringing in a lot of people to block the tracks up ahead, so you really need to go. Bring the BCI tech and head back to Bile!
pln_chw_16_01 = "列車がサツの封鎖線にどんどん近づいてるぞ。戦利品の確保と脱出に使えるのはあと2分だけだ。",--The train is rapidly approaching the cop barricade. I give you a maximum of two minutes to secure the loot and get out.
pln_chw_16_02 = "およそ2分で列車が封鎖線に到達するぞ。聞こえたか? 2分だ。",--You have approximately two minutes before the train reaches the barricade. You hear me? Two minutes.
pln_chw_16_03 = "このスピードで行くと、封鎖線に列車が到達するまであと2分くらいだ。つまりそれまでに全て確保して離脱しろって事だ!",--With the speed this train is going, you'll have about two minutes before you reach the barricade. That means two minutes to secure everything and leave!
pln_chw_17_01 = "ヤバイぞ、お前ら! もう1分も無い!",--Damn it, gang! You have less than a minute now!
pln_chw_17_02 = "お前ら! あと1分しかないぞ!",--Guys! You got one minute!
pln_chw_17_03 = "あと1分! あと1分だけだ。",--One minute, gang! One minute.
pln_chw_18_01 = "残り30秒! 急げ!",--Thirty seconds, gang! You're pushing it!
pln_chw_18_02 = "30秒以内に脱出するんだ!",--You got thirty seconds to make it out of there!
pln_chw_18_03 = "あと30秒だ! 死ぬほど急げ!",--Thirty sec, guys! Hurry the hell up!
pln_chw_19_01 = "オイル缶が道を塞いでるな。ストラップを見つけて解け。他の道を探すヒマはない。",--Those oil barrels are blocking your path. Find the straps and release them. We don't have time to find another way.
pln_chw_19_02 = "畜生! オイル缶が邪魔だ。ストラップを探して解いてくれ、急いでな!",--Damn it! Those oil barrels are in the way. See if you can release the straps, and do it quickly.
pln_chw_19_03 = "オイル缶をどかしてくれ、すぐにだ。ストラップかなにかを解くだけでいい。",--You'll need to remove those barrels, and you need to do it fast. Just release the straps or something.
pln_chw_20_01 = "ガスバーナーを使わないとこの扉は通れないな。すぐにやれ。",--You'll have to use the blowtorch to get through this gate. Make it quick.
pln_chw_20_02 = "ガスバーナーを使って扉を開けろ!",--Use the blowtorch to get through the gate!
pln_chw_20_03 = "ガスバーナーを持ってるよな? 扉に使え。",--You got a blowtorch, don't you? Use it on that gate.
pln_chw_21_01 = "その扉は鍵が掛かってるな。他に出口が見つかれば進めるんだが。",--The door's locked. See if you can find another way out so we can keep going forward.
pln_chw_21_02 = "くそ、その扉は外側から鍵を掛けられてるな。たぶん他にも出口があるはずだ。",--Damn, the door must be locked from the outside. Maybe there's another way out.
pln_chw_21_03 = "どうやらその扉は外から鍵を掛けられてるな。辺りを見回して別の出口を探してみろ。",--The door appears to be locked from the outside. Look around and see if you can find another way to get out.
pln_chw_22_01 = "ちっ、奥の手を隠してやがったか。しかもどうやら彼女がkeycardを持ってたようだ。",--Damn, they really saved their big guns for last. And it looks like she had a keycard.
pln_chw_22_02 = "やれやれ、 こいつは予想出来なかったな! 彼女がゲートを開ける物を持ってないか確かめろ。",--Holy! Was not expecting that. See if she had something for the gate.
pln_chw_22_03 = "まったく、洒落にならん女だったな。彼女が落としたkeycardを拾え。",--Jesus, that bastard wasn't playing around, was she? Take the keycard she dropped.
pln_misc_sj_dgh_01_01 = "見つけたな、Wickの言ってた通りだ。とりあえず縛って車まで連れてこい。ここを離れる時一緒に来てもらう。ほら、Wickが\"お話し\"したいんだとよ。",--There they are, just like Wick said they would be. Get them to the van and tie them up for now. We'll bring them back with us when we leave. Wick wants to have a \"chat\", you see.
pln_misc_sj_dgh_01_02 = "そいつらだ! Wickの言ってた通りだな。縛り上げて車に連れてこい。戻ったらWickがそのクズどもをおもてなしする。",--That's them! They were here just like Wick said. Tie them up and leave them by the van. Wick will take care of the scum when we get back.
pln_misc_sj_dgh_01_03 = "そいつらに間違いない。見ただけでキレそうだ。縛り上げて車に連れてこい、脱出時に一緒に来てもらう。Wickからの強い希望だ。",--That's them all right. Just seeing them makes my blood boil. Tie them up and leave them by the van. They're coming with us when we leave. Wick was very specific about this.
pln_misc_sj_dgh_02_01 = "一人殺しただと? まったく。死んで可哀想だとは思わんが、そいつはWickの獲物だぞ。",--You killed one of them? Damn, I can't say the prick didn't deserve it, but Wick wanted the pleasure himself.
pln_misc_sj_dgh_02_02 = "くそっ! そいつは殺しちゃいけないんだよ...Wickが\"お話し\"したがってたからな。せめて一人はさせてやれ。",--Damn! You weren't supposed to kill one of them, guys... Wick wanted to have a \"chat\" with them himself. Guess one of 'em will have to do.
pln_misc_sj_dgh_02_03 = "我慢できなかったんだな、そうだろ? まあ、その野郎がいなけりゃ世界はもっとマシになるもんな。けどWickにも手伝わせてやらないと可哀想だから、一人は残しとけよ。",--You couldn't stop yourself, could you? Well, the world's a better place without that bastard, but Wick will be disappointed he wasn't part of it, so you better leave the other one for him.
pln_misc_sj_dgh_03_01 = "なにしてんだ、おい! まだ殺すんじゃない! Wickがそいつらを”レッスン”するはずだったのに...くたばっただけでも満足してくれるといいが。",--What the hell, guys! You weren't supposed to kill them now! Wick wanted them alive so he could teach them a lesson... Let's hope he will be content with the thought of them dead.
pln_misc_sj_dgh_03_02 = "やめろ! ああ、なんてこった...Wickの獲物だっていうのに。あいつの目の敵にしてたチンピラどもが、死んだということで納得してもらうしかないな。",--No! Dammit, gang... Wick wanted to take care of them himself. He really had it in for these bastards. I guess he will have to be content with the idea of them dead.
pln_misc_sj_dgh_03_03 = "畜生! なんで殺した? Wickの所へ連れてかなきゃいけないんだよ、殺すんじゃなくてな...あいつが知ったらどうなるか。あのおぞましい動画を見て以来、ずっとこの事ばかり話してたんだぜ。",--Dammit! Why did you do that? You were supposed to bring them to Wick, not kill them yourselves... I'm not sure how he'll react to this. This is the only thing he's been talking about since he saw that disgusting video...
pln_misc_sj_dgh_04_01 = "よし。俺たちの仕事が終わるまでここに転がしとけ。",--Good. Let the bastards squirm in fear while we take care of the bank.
pln_misc_sj_dgh_04_02 = "よくやった。銀行の片がつくまではここに放置しとけ。",--Good job. Leave them there for now while we take care of the bank.
pln_misc_sj_dgh_04_03 = "それでいい。銀行での仕事が済むまでここでズボンにシミでも作らせとけ。",--That's it. Let them piss their pants while we do our thing at the bank.
pln_misc_sj_dgh_05_01 = "おい! 奴らを逃すな! 車の側に拘束しとくんだ!",--Hey! Don't let them get away! Keep them by the van!
pln_misc_sj_dgh_05_02 = "奴らが車から逃げたぞ。隠れ家まで連れてこれなきゃWickを怒らせることになる!",--They're getting away from the van. Wick will be pissed if you don't bring them back to the safe house!
pln_misc_sj_dgh_05_03 = "奴らを逃すな! ちゃんと車の側で大人しくさせて脱出時に一緒に連れて行くんだ!",--Don't let them leave! Make sure they stay by the van so we can bring them with us when we leave.
loc_brb_00_01 = "OK、友よ。時間があまりない。銀行内部を探してみろ。",--OK, friends not much time until the coppers get there. Go have a look inside the bank.
loc_brb_00_02 = "",--Got your money's worth out of that vehicle, yeah? Time to go have a look inside the bank. Make it quick, friends.
loc_brb_00_03 = "",--That crash probably woke the dead, yeah? Hurry up and get inside that bank.
loc_brb_01_01 = "",--...You got about a minute until the kerels get there. Keep those civvis under control, yeah?
loc_brb_01_02 = "",--...Kerels are on route in squad cars, so don't dawdle, and keep those civvies out of your way, yeah?
loc_brb_01_03 = "",--...Get those civvies under control, cop cars are about one minute out, friends.
loc_brb_02_01 = "",--...Kerels will be there any second.
loc_brb_02_02 = "",--...Coppers incoming any second now, friends.
loc_brb_02_03 = "",--...Kerels right around the corner, friends.
loc_brb_03_01 = "",--Looks like a good entry point will be the teller door. Use a saw.
loc_brb_03_02 = "",--OK friends, get into the vault room by cutting open that teller door with a saw.
loc_brb_03_03 = "",--Crack open that door with a saw, friends.
loc_brb_04_01 = "",--Blerrie! You'll have to go through the back door with a saw, yeah?
loc_brb_04_02 = "",--Not going to get in that way, friends. Go outside and find a back door to crack open with a saw.
loc_brb_04_03 = "",--Looks like you're going to have to go in through the back door. Use a saw to crack it open, yeah?
loc_brb_05_01 = "",--Friends, it's probably best to go in through the back door with a saw, yeah?
loc_brb_05_02 = "",--Back door looks good. Crack it open with a saw, friends.
loc_brb_05_03 = "",--Crack open the back door with a saw and go through there, yeah?
loc_brb_06_01 = "",--Blerrie! First floor is blocked off. Get up to the 2nd by the scaffolding outside. Should be a door you can hack through with a saw.
loc_brb_06_02 = "",--Not getting in that way, yeah? There's scaffolding on the outside. Should be a door on the 2nd floor you can hack through with a saw.
loc_brb_06_03 = "",--Sealed up, donnerse! OK, there's a scaffolding outside, use it to get up to the second floor. Find a door to crack open with a saw, to get into the vault room.
loc_brb_07_01 = "",--This floor should have an accessible door... if you use a saw, yeah?
loc_brb_07_02 = "",--You can probably hack through one of the doors on this floor with a saw, yeah?
loc_brb_07_03 = "",--Friends, get a saw going through one of the doors on this floor, yeah?
loc_brb_08_01 = "",--Blerrie! All the doors are sealed. You're going to have to find another way into the vault room. Get up to the second floor and look for a weakness in the floor or something, yeah?
loc_brb_08_02 = "",--Friends, there's no going through that door, yeah? Get up to the second floor using the scaffolding outside. See if there's a weak area in the floor or something.
loc_brb_08_03 = "",--No getting through that donnerse here. There's a scaffolding outside. See if you can find weak spot on the second floor, yeah?
loc_brb_09_01 = "",--Get up to the second floor and look for a weakness in the floor or something, yeah?
loc_brb_09_02 = "",--Get up to the second floor using the scaffolding. See if there's a weak area in the floor or something.
loc_brb_09_03 = "",--See if you can find weak spot on the second floor, yeah? Use the scaffolding.
loc_brb_10_01 = "",--Lekker! That's the spot. Cut through the top layer with a saw, yeah?
loc_brb_10_02 = "",--There we go, friends. That's a good spot to cut through.
loc_brb_10_03 = "",--Looks like a good spot to cut, yeah?
loc_brb_11_01 = "",--Friends, you need to restart the saw.
loc_brb_11_02 = "",--The saw stopped, restart it, yeah?
loc_brb_11_03 = "",--You gotta restart the saw, friends.
loc_brb_11_04 = "",--The saw isn't working, you need to get it going again.
loc_brb_12_01 = "",--Get that saw off there, friends.
loc_brb_12_02 = "",--OK, friends, now remove that saw.
loc_brb_12_03 = "",--Good, now take the saw off.
loc_brb_12_04 = "",--You gotta remove that saw, yeah?
loc_brb_12_05 = "",--Can't go having that saw there friends, get it off, yeah?
loc_brb_13_01 = "",--Now you gotta blow a nice little hole to get into the vault room, yeah?
loc_brb_13_02 = "",--There, now it's time to blow a big hole in that antique floor, yeah?
loc_brb_13_03 = "",--Kiff, now you just gotta make that hole bigger to get into the vault room.
loc_brb_14_01 = "",--Don't' forget to blow up that floor, yeah?
loc_brb_14_02 = "",--The hole in that floor isn't going to get bigger, by itself friends!
loc_brb_14_03 = "",--You gotta blow the floor, friends!
loc_brb_14_04 = "",--No fat copper is going to fall through that floor and make it bigger, friends. You gotta blow it, yeah?
loc_brb_15_01 = "",--OK, now get into the vault room.
loc_brb_15_02 = "",--Kiff! Now, get into that vault room!
loc_brb_15_03 = "",--Perfect friends! Get into the vault room now.
loc_brb_15_04 = "",--There you go. Now take a look inside the vault room,  yeah?
loc_brb_16_01 = "",--Take that tarp off there, yeah?
loc_brb_16_02 = "",--Maybe get rid of that tarp, yeah?
loc_brb_16_03 = "",--Might be a good idea to get that tarp off.
loc_brb_17_01 = "",--You gotta get through that door.
loc_brb_17_02 = "",--Don't wait too long with that door, friends.
loc_brb_17_03 = "",--You gotta crack that door open, friends.
loc_brb_17_04 = "",--Don't' forget the door, yeah?
loc_brb_17_05 = "",--Hey, you can shoot coppers later. Get that door cracked.
loc_brb_17_06 = "",--Come on friends, you really must get that door open.
loc_brb_18_01 = "",--Probably a good idea to shut off that alarm. There's a button for it somewhere.
loc_brb_18_02 = "",--You guys need to shut that alarm down. Find the button, yeah?
loc_brb_18_03 = "",--That alarm needs to go quiet. Find the switch for it around there, yeah?
loc_brb_19_01 = "",--More coppers are going to arrive unless you shut that alarm off.
loc_brb_19_02 = "",--Take down the alarm, friends.
loc_brb_19_03 = "",--That alarm is bringing in more porky reinforcements Shut it down, yeah?
loc_brb_20_01 = "",--I've made arrangements to drop off some equipment for you, friends.
loc_brb_20_02 = "",--There's a load of equipment waiting for you, friends.
loc_brb_20_03 = "",--Old Locke has arranged a stash of gear for you,friends.
loc_brb_21_01 = "",--... take a look outside in the portable toilet at the construction site.
loc_brb_21_02 = "",--...sorry friends, but I had to put it in the sky-rocket [portable toilet] out by the construction site... you call them porta-potties, yeah?
loc_brb_21_03 = "",--...for some reason, my courier thought it best to hide it in the portable toilets at the construction site nearby.
loc_brb_22_01 = "",--...have a look in the dumpers at the construction site outside, yeah?
loc_brb_22_02 = "",--...it got dumped in the containers at the construction site. Go out and get it.
loc_brb_22_03 = "",--...you will find it in a dumpster out by the construction site, friends.
loc_brb_23_01 = "",--...it's waiting for you in a dumpster out by the parking lot.
loc_brb_23_02 = "",--...you'll find it in a trash container by the parking lot, friends.
loc_brb_23_03 = "",--...my courier hid it in a dumpster on the parking lot outside.
loc_brb_24_01 = "",--If you need more gear, have another look at the drop site, friends.
loc_brb_24_02 = "",--There's more gear outside if you need it, friends.
loc_brb_24_03 = "",--If you run short of equipment, go take another look at the drop site.
loc_brb_25_01 = "",--Take that drill inside to the vault room, friends!
loc_brb_25_02 = "",--You need to bring that thermal drill into the vault room, yeah?
loc_brb_25_03 = "",--Friends, you're going to need to bring that drill into the vault room.
loc_brb_26_01 = "",--How are you coming along with that drill, friends?
loc_brb_26_02 = "",--Don't forget the drill, friends.
loc_brb_26_03 = "",--You still need to bring the drill inside, yeah?
loc_brb_26_04 = "",--That drill isn't going to move itself, friends.
loc_brb_27_01 = "",--Coppers got to the drill!
loc_brb_27_02 = "",--Blerrie kerels stopped the drill, you gotta restart it!
loc_brb_27_03 = "",--Drill has been stopped friends, you gotta restart it.
loc_brb_27_04 = "",--Restart the drill, yeah?
loc_brb_27_05 = "",--The drill needs some attention, friends!
loc_brb_28_01 = "",--Blerrie that's an OLD vault! Almost a shame to blow it open, yeah?
loc_brb_28_02 = "",--That vault is a thing of beauty, yeah?
loc_brb_28_03 = "",--There's a bit of charm in those old vaults, eh? Back then you didn't need loads of dingeses to get in, just craftsmanship.
loc_brb_29_01 = "",--Right, you need to use some of the thermite I sent on those vault hinges, yeah?
loc_brb_29_02 = "",--Use the thermite I sent to weaken that vault door, friends.
loc_brb_29_03 = "",--Some thermite on that vault will weaken the hinges, yeah?
loc_brb_29_04 = "",--Friends, get some thermite on that vault door, yeah?
loc_brb_30_01 = "",--Thermite is done. Burned right through that nicely, yeah? Now get going with the winch.
loc_brb_30_02 = "",--Thermite has burned through, yeah? Time to get that winch set up.
loc_brb_30_03 = "",--OK, the thermite is through. Nasty but beautiful. Now set up the winch, yeah?
loc_brb_31_01 = "",--Blerrie paw-paw! The courier forgot the winch! Ok friends, I'll have one coming by train shortly.
loc_brb_31_02 = "",--Achhh! The paw-paw courier forgot the winch! I'll have to get one to you by train. Keep looking up, yeah?
loc_brb_31_03 = "",--Domkop courier didn't stash the winch! He's gonna get it later. Ok friends, I'll have one coming shortly by train.
loc_brb_32_01 = "",--The winch will be there in one minute, friends.
loc_brb_32_02 = "",--Got your winch incoming in about 60 seconds.
loc_brb_32_03 = "",--You'll have your winch in about a minute, yeah?
loc_brb_33_01 = "",--30 seconds until the train arrives, friends.
loc_brb_33_02 = "",--Train is almost there. 30 seconds.
loc_brb_33_03 = "",--Not long now friends. Train will be there in half a minute.
loc_brb_34_01 = "",--Achhh! MORE domkops! Courier dropped the winch parts all around. You'll need to look for them friends.
loc_brb_34_02 = "",--Blerrie courier threw the winch parts all around. Sorry, friends but you'll have to round them up.
loc_brb_34_03 = "",--The courier had to throw out the parts, so you will have to go round and find them, yeah?
loc_brb_35_01 = "",--Keep looking for those winch parts, friends.
loc_brb_35_02 = "",--Don't forget any parts of that winch, yeah?
loc_brb_35_03 = "",--You need to get all the winch parts, friends.
loc_brb_36_01 = "...金庫内に部品を持ってこい。",--...bring all the winch parts into the vault room.
loc_brb_36_02 = "...すべての部品を銀行内に持ち込む必要がある。",--...you need to move all parts of the winch into the bank.
loc_brb_36_03 = "",--...you gotta take all those winch parts into the vault room and assemble it.
loc_brb_37_01 = "",--...screw the bolts into the floor, yeah.
loc_brb_37_02 = "",--...bolts need to go into the floor.
loc_brb_37_03 = "",--...tighten those bolts down friends.
loc_brb_38_01 = "",--...Now, you gotta connect the hook to the vault door.
loc_brb_38_02 = "",--...The hook needs to go on the vault, yeah?
loc_brb_38_03 = "",--...You gotta get that hook onto the vault.
loc_brb_39_01 = "",--...Start the winch and let it work. Keep the kerels away, yeah?
loc_brb_39_02 = "",--...Now start up the winch. And keep the coppers away from it!
loc_brb_39_03 = "",--...Time to pull that door off, yeah? Start the winch and keep the kerels from getting to it!
loc_brb_40_01 = "",--Don't forget the winch, friends!
loc_brb_40_02 = "",--You gotta get that winch assembled.
loc_brb_40_03 = "",--How are you coming along with that winch, friends?
loc_brb_40_04 = "",--You almost got that winch ready?
loc_brb_41_01 = "",--Blerrie! The kerels got to the winch!
loc_brb_41_02 = "",--Winch has been stopped by kerels! Restart it, yeah?
loc_brb_41_03 = "",--The coppers have taken the winch offline!
loc_brb_41_04 = "",--You need to restart the winch, friends!
loc_brb_41_05 = "",--Coppers have stopped the winch! Keep them away from it, yeah?
loc_brb_42_01 = "",--While you're waiting on that vault door, might as well have a go at those safe deposit boxes. They're Titans, so you will not be able to just cut through.
loc_brb_42_02 = "",--Those safe deposit boxes might contain a nice bonus. Why not have a look while you're waiting? Titan doors though, so you can't just cut them open.
loc_brb_42_03 = "",--Could be those safe deposit boxes have some extra valuables we can use, yeah? Maybe you can get into them while you wait for the vault to open?
loc_brb_43_01 = "",--...If you find a keycard, opening one up would be pretty easy
loc_brb_43_02 = "",--...Maybe someone forgot a keycard or something
loc_brb_43_03 = "",--...A keycard could probably open one.
loc_brb_44_01 = "",--...Might be able to hack them with bank computers, yeah?.
loc_brb_44_02 = "",--...Could maybe open them up with a computer, yeah?
loc_brb_44_03 = "",--...Bank computers should be able to open them up, yeah?
loc_brb_45_01 = "",--Friends, you should pile all your loot somewhere close, so that you can move it later, yeah?
loc_brb_45_02 = "",--Put all the loot you find somewhere close, so you can collect it later, yeah?
loc_brb_45_03 = "",--You should probably stash that extra loot somewhere safe, so you can take it with you when you leave, yeah?
loc_brb_46_01 = "",--Kiff! Now go and have a look inside, yeah?
loc_brb_46_02 = "",--There you go, friends! Now have a look inside that vault!
loc_brb_46_03 = "",--Ah! Get inside that vault, friends! Almost done here!
loc_brb_47_01 = "",--if you need more supplies, there should still be more outside
loc_brb_47_02 = "",--If you need more equipment, go back and check the stash outside, yeah?
loc_brb_47_03 = "",--There could be more equipment in the drop outside, friends.
loc_brb_47_04 = "",--If you're low on gear, go back and check the drop point outside, yeah?
loc_brb_48_01 = "",--...grab some of that gold if you can friends, but remember that money is secondary, yeah?
loc_brb_48_02 = "",--...that gold would make a nice bonus. Bring some with you if you can friends, but remember why we're here.
loc_brb_48_03 = "",--...the object in the floor is our main priority, but it's a shame to leave all that pretty gold here. Bring some with you if you can, yeah?
loc_brb_49_01 = "",--Time to get what we came here for, yeah?
loc_brb_49_02 = "",--Looks like we're in the right place, friends!
loc_brb_49_03 = "",--No question, Bain sent us to the right bank, yeah?
loc_brb_50_01 = "",--The thing we're after is in the middle of that floor. Gotta blow a hole in it with some c4 so we can get it out of there, yeah?
loc_brb_50_02 = "",--That nice marble floor has got to have a big hole blown into it. Our prize is right under there, friends.
loc_brb_50_03 = "",--Now you gotta blow a hole into the floor, yeah? What we're after is in the foundation of the building.
loc_brb_51_01 = "",--There might be more c4 outside in the stash, friends.
loc_brb_51_02 = "",--If you need more c4, take a look in the stash outside again, yeah?
loc_brb_51_03 = "",--You can go get more C4 outside if you need it, yeah?
loc_brb_52_01 = "",--You gotta get that floor open, friends!
loc_brb_52_02 = "",--How are you coming along with that floor?
loc_brb_52_03 = "",--That floor needs to be blown open, yeah?
loc_brb_52_04 = "",--I can't pull you out of there until you've got through that floor, friends.
loc_brb_53_01 = "",--That's what we're here for, friends. Huh.. same kind of writing that Lindenhurst decrypted...
loc_brb_53_02 = "",--Rather beautiful, yeah? Old writing and all, just like the stuff that sent us here. Whatever it is.
loc_brb_53_03 = "",--That's it, yeah? Can't see what's so special, but it's why we're here. Same writing that Lindenhurst found.
loc_brb_54_01 = "",--Time to get you out of there. Grab whatever loot you can on the way out.
loc_brb_54_02 = "",--OK, friends, it's time for you to leave. Take some extra loot with you if you can.
loc_brb_54_03 = "",--Start collecting extra loot if you want to friends, it's time to get you out of there, yeah?
loc_brb_55_01 = "",--....Don't take too long. Got a feeling my old friends at Murky have been tracking our movements.
loc_brb_55_02 = "",--Don't stray too long though, friends. I'm seeing a lot of chatter in Murkywater channels. Looks like they're tracking us.
loc_brb_55_03 = "",--...I'm seeing a lot of talk on Murkywater comms, so don't stay long. They might be wanting to join us, and we don't want that, yeah?
loc_brb_56_01 = "",--Blerrie! Murkywater operatives are trying to block off the area, keep away from them, yeah?
loc_brb_56_02 = "",--Bliksem! Operatives from Murky are in the area. Watch out for them, friends!
loc_brb_56_03 = "",--Friends, Murkywater operatives are in the area. How did they find us?
loc_brb_57_01 = "",--I've got someone waiting for you ouside in the sewers. You'll need some thermite to get through.
loc_brb_57_02 = "",--Sorry about this friends, but I've got to pull you out via the sewers. Get to them outside... and you'll need some thermite to burn through the grating.
loc_brb_57_03 = "",--Make your way outside and go down into the sewers. You'll need a bit of thermite to cut through the grating, yeah?
loc_brb_58_01 = "",--I've got twitch coming with the van for you, yeah?
loc_brb_58_02 = "",--Friends, Twitch will be there shortly with the van!
loc_brb_58_03 = "",--Get outside, friends! Twitch is incoming with the van!
loc_brb_59_01 = "",--Blerrie! You gotta get that vehicle out of the way!
loc_brb_59_02 = "",--Achh! That vehicle has got to be removed!
loc_brb_59_03 = "",--Friends, get that blerrie vehicle out of the way, yeah?
loc_brb_60_01 = "",--You need to leave, friends!
loc_brb_60_02 = "",--Get out of there, yeah?
loc_brb_60_03 = "",--Don't wait around too long, yeah?
loc_brb_60_04 = "",--Kerels aren't going to stop coming, so get out of there, friends!
loc_brb_brf_01 = "",--It looks like someone at Murkywater might be behind our current predicament. They have closed all communication channels with me. Still got a couple friends there, but it looks like I am officially... ousted. Mr. Lindenhurst was kind enough to decrypt some notes an ancestor had printed on the back of a painting:The View of Mount Vernon. Bain owned the real thing you know; you have to wonder how he pulled that one off, yeah? Watookal, the notes detail that inside the vault of the Brooklyn Bank, there's something buried in the foundation; something that Bain needed, put there when the concrete was poured. I've no idea what it is, and how all this fits together, but whoever got to him put in a lot of resources, so it's probably not any old dinges. We're going in to get it before anyone else finds out, yeah?
loc_brb_cbf_01 = "",--Dear Friends, we're going back to New York. Theres something buried in the foundation of the old Brooklyn Bank that Bain was after. Could be a way out of this current predicament we're in. While we're there, it might be a good idea to pick up some extra operating cash to keep us going. Replacing all of Bain's equipment isn't going to be cheap I can tell you, and the stuff I've got running as backup isn't going to hold up for long, yeah? At the moment, we're open targets.
loc_brb_cnc_01 = "",--Friends, we need to do a bit of an unusual bank robbery, yeah?
loc_brb_cnc_02 = "",--The Brooklyn Bank has got something we need, and for once it isn't just cash!
loc_brb_cnc_03 = "",--Dear friends, we're going to New York for a quick bank job.
loc_brb_end_01 = "",--Nicely done, dear friends. We're still in a lot of trouble but old Locke is going to take care of you, yeah? I know I made some promises, and I'm still working on getting answers. Calling in all my favors for this one. Gotta pay off the Butcher too- don't want her nipping at our heels after Alaska. Have a short breather, lay low for a bit, while Mr Lindenhurst tries to figure out what's so special about this medallion dinges. I got a feeling that we haven't even cut through the frosting on this cake, yeah?
loc_brb_intro_01 = "",--Friends, I know this is serious but you still have to have a bit of fun, yeah? Watch now!
loc_brb_intro_01a = "",--Left a bit.. there we go... ACH, bekakin' civvie! Whoa, almost got that one too. A little faster.
loc_brb_intro_01b = "",--Almost there... aaaand...
loc_brb_intro_01c = "",--Hahaha that was kiff! Now get going, friends!
loc_brb_intro_02 = "",--I gotta admit it's been awhile since I broke into a place this loudly. It's gonna be jol!
loc_brb_intro_03 = "",--Ok friends, you're going to like this! A little smash and grab in the dead of winter, yeah?

