eday1_brief = "The Elephantは己のリーダーシップと誠実さで議席を獲得するとPRしているようだ、クソ食らえだな。あの舌先三寸のろくでなしは不正してでも上院まで上り詰めたいらしい、そこでお前たちの出番だ。39番の埠頭に停車しているトラックのどれかが投票機を積んでいる。トラックを見つけGPS追跡機を取り付けてくるんだ。その後の追跡は任せておけ。当然のことだが、The Elephantは自分に悪評がついてしまっては困る。そこで奴は、秘密裏に事を進められた場合、選挙の活動資金からボーナスを出すと約束している。静かにやれよ、未来のご立派な議員サマにたっぷり報酬をもらうぞ。",--The Elephant's PR will claim he came to power through depth, leadership and integrity, but that's bullshit. That oily bastard is going to cheat his way to the Senate, and this is where you come in. There are trucks at Pier 39. One of them has voting machines. Find the truck, and attach a GPS tracker to it. We'll deal with it down the line. Naturally, The Elephant wants this done with as little chance of bad press coming back to him as possible. So he's ear-marked some of his considerable campaign funds for a special black-ops bonus. You guys do this quietly, and the good politician will see you are well rewarded.
eday2_brief = "トラックを追跡した結果、 シカゴのGoose島近くにある倉庫に行き着いた。 投票機を最終目的地に配送するための物流センターだ。 俺達はちょいとした高等技術でもって、The Elephantが支持する市長選の候補者 -卑屈なクソ野郎のMcKendrick- にあの機械がもう少し賛同するようにする。 侵入したら、ハッキングして、脱出。 シンプルだな。",--I've traced the truck to a warehouse out by Goose Island. It's a distribution depot, contracted to ship the voting machines to their final destination. With a little technical wizardry, we're going to make those machines a bit more sympathetic to The Elephants' mayoral candidate - that slimy ballbag McKendrick. Get in there, get them hacked, get out - simple.
eday3_brief = "",--We may have failed to tamper with the voting machines, but we can still help rig this vote. The votes have been cast and the exit polls aren't encouraging. If we can corrupt the server with the results we can trigger a re-election. But here's the twist - to avoid suspicion, we're gonna make it look like collateral damage by robbing the bank next door.
eday3_brief_skip1 = "てめえらが追跡機を付けたトラックは別のものだった。もう投票機への工作は諦めるべきだろう。The Elephantに失望されないためにも別の方法でなんとかするぞ。投票所のサーバーを滅茶苦茶にして、再投票にしてやるんだ。The Elephantの依頼と感付かれてはまずいから、隣の銀行に入った強盗の巻き添えに見せかけてやるぞ。",--That truck you assholes tagged wasn't the right one, so we can forget about intercepting those voting machines. We're going to try something else to keep the Elephant sweet. We can trigger a re-election by scrambling the server at the polling place. To avoid suspicion on our sponsor, we'll make it look like collateral damage by robbing the bank next door.
eday3_brief_skip2 = "お前らがアップロードした輸送データで正しいトラックを追跡することはできなかったぞ。だからもう投票機を追跡するのは無理だ。だが、まだThe Elephantの機嫌を取ることはできる。投票所の隣に銀行があるんだ。そこを叩く。金庫を開けて全部かっさらえ。だが忘れるな。本当の目的は投票所を台無しにすることだからな。",--I couldn't locate the right truck through the shipping data you uploaded, so we won't be able to intercept those voting machines. However, we can still keep the Elephant sweet. There's a bank next to the polling place. We're going to hit it. Except we're not, not really, 'cos your real goal is hitting the server with the polling results next door. Hit the bank, open the vault, all that stuff, but remember that the real objective is fucking up that polling place.
heist_airport = "",--Airport
heist_airport_briefing = "風の噂では、MendozaがHectorとの抗争に備えて武器を調達しているらしい。空港に行ってその武器を探索して、それを全部頂くか破壊してしまうのが今回の仕事だ。できるなら頂戴してしまいたい、いい稼ぎになるぞ。",--OK, the airport is just down the hill. Cut through the fence and find the hangar where the truck holding the cases is. The Mendozas will probably be there. Bring those weapons back to the van, or make sure they don't. They're not going down without a fight. If it hits the fan out there - destroy the guns.
heist_airport_crimenet = "",--The FBI has intercepted Vlad's weapon deal at the airport. He needs your help retrieving his hardware$NL;$NL;» Locate the hangar where the weapons are$NL;» Bring the weapons back to the van
heist_airport_hl = "",--Airport
heist_alex = "",--Rats
heist_alex_1_briefing = "さて、Hectorから話は聞いたな。チンタラしている暇はない。$NL;これから、覚醒剤の工場へ行ってブツを抑える。$NL;どちらにしろ、これまでの素晴らしくついてない展開からしてサツが来るのにそう時間は掛からないだろう。",--Well, you heard Hector. No time to piss around. We go into the meth lab and secure the goods. I'm sure we don't have long before the law shows, either, which is in keeping with this spectacular run of bad luck we've been having.
heist_alex_1_hl = "",--Cook Off
heist_alex_2_briefing = "よしお前ら、Hectorと話してきた。$NL;Mendozaの幹部は国外に逃げようとしているが、Hectorにはそうさせるつもりはない。$NL;彼は奴等がどこに向かったのか知りたがっている。$NL;Mendozaの中枢に紛れ込んだねずみが、奴等をCobrasとかいうストリートギャングに売った。Hectorの手下も手を出さないような危険なクソどもだ。$NL;そこでお前らの出番というわけだ... 奴らと取引して覚醒剤と情報を交換するぞ。",--OK folks, I spoke to Hector. The Mendoza higher ups are fleeing the country but Hector isn't quite ready to let them leave. He wants to know where they're headed. A rat in their midst has sold them out to the Cobras street gang - vicious pricks that even Hector's people don't deal with. Which is where you come in... Trade the meth with them for the info.
heist_alex_2_hl = "",--Code for Meth
heist_alex_3_briefing = "聞いてくれ、FBIがMendozaの国外脱出の護衛についていることが判明した。$NL;取引があったのかも知れないし、なかったのかも知れない。$NL;正直、国外移送だろうと何だろうと関係ない。$NL;目標は全員バスの中だ、金も何もかもな。$NL;金を分捕り、Mendozaの幹部を皆殺しにして、グランドフィナーレといこうじゃないか。$NL;さあヘリボーンがお待ちかねだ。",--Well, turns out the FBI are escorting the Mendozas out of the country. Maybe they have a deal, maybe they don't. Frankly, I don't give a crap whether they're renditioning them or whatever. All the heads are on that bus, money and all. Get the money, eliminate the Mendoza top guys, and end this story. We'll go in by chopper.
heist_alex_3_hl = "",--Bus Stop
heist_alex_crimenet = "HectorがMendozaのリーダーたちを一掃する仕事を手伝う。$NL;$NL;» Mendozaの製造所から覚醒剤を回収する$NL;» 覚醒剤でCobrasから情報を取引する$NL;» Mendozaの幹部らを抹殺する",--Help Hector wipe out the Mendoza leaders.$NL;$NL;» Retrieve meth from the Mendoza lab$NL;» Trade meth for info with the Cobras$NL;» Eliminate the Mendoza cartel leaders
heist_arena = "",--The Alesso Heist
heist_arena_briefing = "アリーナはGensecによる強固なセキュリティーで守られている。$NL;片やVIPの為の展示場だが、それでも金庫としての役割を持っている。$NL;今夜、俺たちはこれを打つ。今回は内通者を用意した。$NL;そいつがアリーナ内部の各所にC4を放置した。それを回収して、金庫の下を爆破するんだ。$NL;このアリーナでは今、大スターが居るぞ。かの有名なAlessoだ。$NL;今夜がチケット完売のEast Coast ツアー最終日だ、そしてヤツは度胆を抜かすパフォーマンスを約束してくれた。$NL;あぁ、そうだWolf...ダンスフロアには行くなよ。",--The arena has a huge security floor run by Gensec. Part exhibition for corporate VIP's, but still a working vault. Tonight, we hit it. We got an inside man on this one. He stashed some C4 around the Arena. Gather it, blow the vault from beneath and get that sweet dirty money out. There's a big star playing here. No-one less than Alesso. Tonight's the last night of his sold-out East Coast tour, and he's promised to tear the roof up. Oh, and Wolf - stay off the dance floor.
heist_arena_crimenet = "今夜はAlessoが街に居る。Gensecアリーナでパフォーマンス中だ。$NL;そして俺たちはそこへ向かう。だけど今回の目的はAlessoではない。$NL;アリーナは要塞だ、そしてGensecのショーケースがあり、そこにある新しい金庫には投資した金が眠っている。$NL;奴らはそれが無敵の金庫だと思っているようだ。俺たちで否定してやろうぜ。$NL; $NL;» アリーナを探し回りC4を見つけ出せ$NL;» ガレージに行き、C4を金庫の下に設置せよ$NL;» Pyro Boothをハッキングして、C4を起爆しろ$NL;» ドリルで金庫を下から開けろ$NL;» 荷物を確保して脱出する",--Alesso is in town tonight. He's playing at the Gensec Arena, and that's where we're headed. But Alesso isn't the target. The Arena doubles as a secured fortress, and it's where Gensec are showcasing their new vault - the Investment Safe. They think it's impenetrable. Let's prove them wrong. $NL;$NL;» Search the arena and locate the C4 $NL;» Plant the C4 in the garage beneath the vault $NL;» Hack into the Pyro Booth and detonate the C4 $NL;» Drill the vault bottom $NL;» Secure the loot and escape
heist_arena_hl = "",--The Alesso Heist
heist_arm_cro = "",--Transport: Crossroads
heist_arm_cro_briefing = "McCarty通りとJames通りの交差点でGensecの輸送車列を足止めした。$NL;Time Outなんか読んでるヒッピー共は仰天してラテマキアートに脱糞してるだろうな。$NL;お前たちは輸送車に乗り込み、金庫をこじ開けろ。$NL;中身が何かは関係ない。取るもの取ったらずらかるぞ。",--We've forced the Gensec trucks off the road at the corner of McCarty and James. Sure it had those Time Out hipsters shitting into their latte macchiatos. You're going to need to get into the trucks, and then break open the strongboxes inside. Whatever they're carrying, get it, and get out.
heist_arm_cro_crimenet = "BainがGensecの輸送車列の情報を掴んだ。奴らが運んでいる金目の物を素早く強奪するぞ。$NL;$NL;» トラックを足止めして侵入する$NL;» 金庫をこじ開ける$NL;» 逃走車両に戦利品を積み込む",--Bain has intercepted a convoy of armored Gensec trucks. They're carrying high-value cargo and you need to get in fast and steal it.$NL;$NL;» Break into the immobilized trucks$NL;» Crack open the strongboxes$NL;» Get the loot to the getaway vehicle
heist_arm_cro_hl = "",--Transport: Crossroads
heist_arm_fac = "",--Transport: Harbor
heist_arm_fac_briefing = "磁気クレーンを使ってGensecの輸送車列にちょっとしたプレゼントをしてやろう... とびきり悪いやつ4人入りのコンテナをな。輸送車を襲撃、奪えるものを奪っておさらばだ。ここの波止場は実に多くの犯罪に利用されてきた。誇りを持ってやれよ、お前ら。",--We're using a magnetic crane to drop a little present in the path of the Gensec convoy - a steel container of professional badasses. Hit the trucks, and get the loot to the getaway. These docks have a rich history of heistery, gentlemen - do it proud.
heist_arm_fac_crimenet = "BainがGensecの輸送車列の情報を掴んだ。奴らが運んでいる金目の物を素早く強奪するぞ。$NL;$NL;» トラックを足止めして侵入する$NL;» 金庫をこじ開ける$NL;» 逃走車両に戦利品を積み込む",--Bain has intercepted a convoy of armored Gensec trucks. They're carrying high-value cargo and you need to get in fast and steal it.$NL;$NL;» Break into the immobilized trucks$NL;» Crack open the strongboxes$NL;» Get the loot to the getaway vehicle
heist_arm_fac_hl = "",--Transport: Harbor
heist_arm_for = "",--Transport: Train Heist
heist_arm_for_briefing = "お前たちが見つけた設計図だが、「RC1」と呼ばれる新型Turretのものだったようだ。まさしく次世代の代物だな。ちょっと探ってみたところ、ペンタゴン行きの特別列車がひっかかった。列車のネットワークをハッキングして、切替器の故障と見せかけて列車を足止めしてやったぞ。列車は3両あるが、そのうち1両にTurret本体、残りの2両に専用の弾薬が積み込まれてる。もちろん弾薬もいい金になるが、本体を忘れるんじゃないぞ。やつらTurretが盗まれるなんて思っちゃいないだろうな。",--That blueprint you found was for a new type of infantry turret - codenamed RC1. Real next-gen shit. Digging a little deeper, I got word of a specially chartered train, headed in to the Pentagon. I've hacked the rail network, and they think they've stopped due to a glitch in the switches. Three railcars. One has the hardware. The other two have its ammo. It all sells, but your priority is the turret. They won't be expecting you.
heist_arm_for_crimenet = "お前が前のJOBで見つけた設計図は新しい陸軍用武器「Turret」のプロトタイプの物だ。同時にそこには大量の弾薬があるはずだ、出来る事ならこれも盗みたい。$NL; $NL;» 試作品のTurretを発見しろ$NL;» Turretを分解して確保しろ$NL;» 指定個数の弾薬を確保しろ$NL;» 全てのアイテムを脱出用の乗り物に乗せろ",--That blueprint you found in the last job was for a prototype infantry weapon, a new kind of turret. It's also carrying significant amounts of ammunition, which you can also try to retrieve. $NL;$NL;» Find and break into the correct railcar$NL;» Recover the prototype turret$NL;» Dismantle and secure the turret components$NL;» Acquire the required amounts of ammunition$NL;» Secure all items in the waiting vehicle
heist_arm_for_hl = "",--Transport: Train Heist
heist_arm_hcm = "",--Transport: Downtown
heist_arm_hcm_briefing = "とあるビジネス街の、空中の渡し通路。うまく設置された5ポンドのC-4を、完璧なタイミングで起爆すれば、Gensecの車列を足止め出来る。連中がうろたえている間に襲撃しろ。輸送車をこじ開け、金庫を破り、逃走車両に'ウマいモノ'を持ってきてくれ。",--One downtown skyway, five pounds of strategically placed C-4 and impeccable timing has given us a stranded convoy of Gensec trucks. Hit them hard while they're still disoriented. Break into the trucks and the strongboxes, and return the goodies to the escape driver.
heist_arm_hcm_crimenet = "BainがGensecの輸送車列の情報を掴んだ。奴らが運んでいる金目の物を素早く強奪するぞ。$NL;$NL;» トラックを足止めして侵入する$NL;» 金庫をこじ開ける$NL;» 逃走車両に戦利品を積み込む",--Bain has intercepted a convoy of armored Gensec trucks. They're carrying high-value cargo and you need to get in fast and steal it.$NL;$NL;» Break into the immobilized trucks$NL;» Crack open the strongboxes$NL;» Get the loot to the getaway vehicle
heist_arm_hcm_hl = "",--Transport: Downtown
heist_arm_par = "",--Transport: Park
heist_arm_par_briefing = "昼飯時でSherping記念公園に人が見えるな。普段は鳩がクソしてるくらいしか見るものが無いが、今日はウンと刺激的なショーをしようじゃないか。Gensecのトラックが宝箱を抱えてやってきたぞ。",--The lunch-time crowd at Sherping Memorial Park usually don't see anything more exciting than a pigeon taking a crap, so put a good show on for them, gentlemen. You got Gensec trucks and the strongboxes inside to deal with.
heist_arm_par_crimenet = "BainがGensecの輸送車列の情報を掴んだ。奴らが運んでいる金目の物を素早く強奪するぞ。$NL;$NL;» トラックを足止めして侵入する$NL;» 金庫をこじ開ける$NL;» 逃走車両に戦利品を積み込む",--Bain has intercepted a convoy of armored Gensec trucks. They're carrying high-value cargo and you need to get in fast and steal it.$NL;$NL;» Break into the immobilized trucks$NL;» Crack open the strongboxes$NL;» Get the loot to the getaway vehicle
