heist_arm_und = "",--Transport: Underpass
heist_arm_und_briefing = "地下道でGensecの車列を襲撃する。Dulles発McLean行だから、中身も期待できるはずだ。トラックの中身は何でもかんでも奪っちまえ。ここはクソ田舎まっただ中、お巡りがすっ飛んでくることは覚悟しとけよ。",--We hit the Gensec convoy at the underpass, en-route from Dulles to their depot in McLean, so expect rich pickings. Get whatever's in the trucks to your escape driver. We're deep in Indian country here, gentlemen, so expect a fast response from D.C.'s finest.
heist_arm_und_crimenet = "BainがGensecの輸送車列の情報を掴んだ。奴らが運んでいる金目の物を素早く強奪するぞ。$NL;$NL;» トラックを足止めして侵入する$NL;» 金庫をこじ開ける$NL;» 逃走車両に戦利品を積み込む",--Bain has intercepted a convoy of armored Gensec trucks. They're carrying high-value cargo and you need to get in fast and steal it.$NL;$NL;» Break into the immobilized trucks$NL;» Crack open the strongboxes$NL;» Get the loot to the getaway vehicle
