heist_election_day = "",--Election Day
heist_election_day_1_hl = "",--Right Track
heist_election_day_2_hl = "",--Swing Vote
heist_election_day_3_hl = "",--Breaking Ballot
heist_election_day_crimenet = "こいつは政治に足を突っ込むクソッタレな仕事だ。$NL;The Elephantが支持しているBob Mckendrickを市長にするために助けてやるぞ。$NL;$NL;» 投票マシンを探し出す$NL;» 投票マシンをハッキングする$NL;» The Elephantが疑われないようにする",--Crime is an unsavoury line of work, but it's time you dipped your toes in some truly dirty business - politics. The Elephant wants you to help get his man Bob McKendrick into the Mayor's office.$NL;$NL;» Locate the voting machines$NL;» Hack the machines to swing the vote$NL;» Make sure no suspicion falls on The Elephant
heist_escape_cafe_briefing = "...やっちまった! 奴らに見つかった、警察に見つかったぞ! ブツを持って逃げろ!",--...Damn it to hell they're onto us, they're onto us! You gotta escape with the loot!
heist_escape_cafe_hl = "",--Cafe Escape
heist_escape_garage_briefing = "...荷物が... 奪われちまう... クソが... ふざけやがって! お前ら立ち上がって戦え!",--...Lose 'em... Lose 'em... Dammit... DAMMMIT! You gotta stand and fight!
heist_escape_garage_hl = "",--Garage Escape
heist_escape_overpass_briefing = "...畜生が! 奴らがお前らのすぐ右側に居るぞ、衝撃に備えろ!",--...Jesus they're right on top of you, prepare to get hit!
heist_escape_overpass_hl = "",--Overpass Escape
heist_escape_park_briefing = "...クソが! 尻尾を奴らに捕まれたぞ、これ以上好きにさせるな!",--...Shit we picked up a tail folks, no shaking 'em now!
heist_escape_park_hl = "",--Park Escape
heist_escape_street_briefing = "...奴ら現場から付いてきやがった、車も代えられない、 全員銃撃戦に備えとけ!",--...They tailed us from the scene, switch car failed, everyone batten down the hatches!
heist_escape_street_hl = "",--Street Escape
heist_family = "",--Diamond Store
heist_family_briefing = "この店のディスプレイケース1つ1つに警報が仕掛けられている。警報を解除して、それからダイアモンドと宝石を盗み出せ。逃走用の運び屋は若干ビビってるから、静かにそしてきっちりと仕事してくれ。なんでもバッグに詰めろ、全部奪ってやろうぜ!",--All the display cases in there are connected to an alarm. Disable the alarm and then steal the diamond jewelry. The escape driver is a bit jumpy so keep this quiet and methodical. Bag up everything. Let's get it all!
heist_family_crimenet = "相手はハイファッションな宝石店。ダイアモンドの多くはここに用意されている。Bainは大量のバッグを要求している。ディスプレイケースには警報が仕掛けられている。大きな問題になる筈だ。$NL;$NL;» 入念に現場を下見する$NL;» 警備、警報、カメラを確認する$NL;» ダイアモンドをバッグに詰めて逃走車両に向かう$NL;",--This is a high fashion jewelry store. Mostly diamonds in there. Bain wants a lot of bags. There is an alarm connected to the display cases. It will be a tough one.$NL;$NL;» Case the place carefully.$NL;» Check for guards, alarms and cameras$NL;» Fill your bags with diamond jewelry and get to the escape car$NL;
heist_family_hl = "",--Diamond Store
heist_firestarter = "",--Firestarter
heist_firestarter_1_briefing = "風の噂では、MendozaがHectorとの抗争に備えて武器を調達しているそうだ。空港に行ってその武器を探索して、それを全部頂くか破壊してしまうのが今回の仕事だ。できるなら頂戴してしまいたい、いい稼ぎになるぞ。",--A little bird told me the Mendozas are flying in more weapons in preparation for the war with Hector. We go to their airport, find the weapons and take them all or destroy them. Preferably take them as the money will be great that way.
heist_firestarter_1_hl = "",--Airport
heist_firestarter_2_briefing = "Hectorが言うには、機密情報を手に入れるにはMendozaを叩く必要があるとの事だ。率直に言うと奴らの活動資金のありかだな。今回はなかなか運が良いぞ、あるMendozaの構成員から奴らがFBIの捜査を受けているという情報を得た。というわけで、やることは一つだ。その捜査を担当してるFBI支部を襲撃して情報を頂くのさ。ああ、わかってる、わかってる、一難去ってまた一難ってな...",--Now Hector tells me we need to hit the Mendozas themselves for information. Where they keep their money, in fact. Lucky for us, someone in the Mendoza cartel gave up info that they're being investigated by the FBI. So all we need to do is hit the local FBI office handling the cartel to get the data. And, yes, I know. Out of the frying pan, into the fire...
heist_firestarter_2_hl = "",--FBI Server
heist_firestarter_3_briefing = "お前ら、ここがその場所だ...この銀行に北米Mendozaの活動資金の全てが保管されている。腰の曲がったばあさんが年金下ろしに行くのが見えるな。その裏に、Hectorが言うには、最低でも1億ドルの闇資金が眠ってる。お前らの仕事はそこに進入して、内部の人員を制圧、アラームを鳴らされないように金庫に進入する。そしたら中に火をつけて、その一部始終を撮影する事だ。それがHectorがお望みのやり方だ。",--This is the place, people... This bank here holds all the Mendoza capital north of the border. Little old grandmothers walk right by their blood money every day. Hidden in plain sight, Hector says. At least $100m in black cash. What you're gonna do is go in, control the crowd, get into the vault without the alarm going off. Then set a fire, and film yourself doing it. Hector wants it that way.
heist_firestarter_3_hl = "",--Trustee Bank
heist_firestarter_crimenet = "HectorはMendoza連合との闘争であなたを必要としている。$NL;$NL;» 空港でMendozaの武器の積み荷を奪う$NL;» FBIのオフィスから連合のデータを入手する$NL;» Mendozaの資金を預かっている銀行を焼き払う",--Hector needs you in the war against the Mendoza cartel.$NL;$NL;» Intercept the Mendoza weapon shipment at the airport$NL;» Retrieve cartel data from the FBI offices$NL;» Burn down the bank holding Mendoza money
heist_fish = "",--The Yacht Heist
heist_fish_crimenet = "私はMcKendrick市長がPayday Gangにとって障害になる事を知っている。非常に信頼できる所からによる情報によると彼は再選挙運動のために使う大量の違法な金を動かしている。おそらく、選挙を決めるには十分な量だろう。金はニューヨーク港に泊まっているヨットの中に隠されている。$NL;$NL;» 隠された金を見つける。$NL;» サーバーを探し、入手する。$NL;» 戦利品とともに脱出。",--I know that mayor McKendrick has been somewhat of an... obstacle for the Payday Gang. Now, I have very reliable information that he's moving a large amount of illegal cash into the country to use for his re-election campaign. Enough to decide the election, perhaps. The money is hidden on a yacht belonging to a certain Ethan Powell, an ally of McKendrick. The yacht is currently anchored in New York harbor.$NL;$NL;» Find the stashes and bag the money$NL;» Locate and retrieve the server$NL;» Escape with the loot
heist_fish_hl = "",--The Yacht Heist
heist_fish_hl_briefing = "よし、目的は分かってるな。McKendrickの選挙資金を盗んで、奴の足をすくうんだ。奴のパーティを台無しにして、晴れ舞台をぶち壊しにしてやろうぜ。恩知らず野郎へのお返しというわけだ。カネとは別に、あのヨットにはMcKendrickも使ってる海外の隠し口座のパスワードが入ったサーバーがあるとCharonの情報から分かった。そいつを盗んで、口座のカネもそっくり頂こう。おっと、忘れるとこだったが....今夜はヨットでMcKendrickの資金集めパーティが開催中だ。TVなんかも来てるが、ほとんどは上部デッキでやってるから、静かにやれば誰にも気づかれずにやり終えられるぞ。",--Ok guys, you know what's at stake here. McKendrick needs that cash to win the elections, and if you can steal it you're pulling the rug out from under his feet. Let's spoil his party, rain on his parade - get even for what that ungrateful bastard did. So get that cash. And there's another thing I found in the file that Charon gave us - somewhere on the yacht there's a server which contains passwords for illicit foreign bank accounts, some of which are also used by McKendrick. Steal that server, and we can cash in nicely on it.$NL;There's a fundraising party for McKendrick on the yacht tonight. With TV and everything. But the party's mostly on the upper deck, so if you sneak in quietly you should be able to get in and out without anyone noticing.
heist_flat = "",--Panic Room
heist_flat_crimenet = "",--Sometimes you need to take things to the extreme to earn a good payday, and that's exactly what we're doing this time. Enter the building, find the panic room, and then steal the whole god damn room by using a helicopter.$NL;$NL;» Enter the building$NL;» Locate and dismount the panic room$NL;» Lift out the panic room and escape
heist_flat_hl = "",--Panic Room
heist_flat_hl_briefing = "住宅団地の奥深く、とある要塞化されたビルがある。麻薬取引で稼いでいる土地のギャングの本拠地だ。ビルの中には床にボルトで固定されたパニックルームがあり、そしてその中には、巨額の現金がある。ビルに入るのは容易いが、パニックルームに入るのはもっと骨の折れる作業だ。開けるのには何日もかかるだろう、だが現場でそんな悠長にやっている暇はない。入れないとしたら、どうやってカネを持ち出す?簡単だ。部屋ごと盗めばいいのさ。",--Deep inside the projects there's a fortified building, the headquarters of a local gang running a lucrative drugs operation. In this building there's a panic room bolted to the floor - and inside the panic room there's a fortune in cash. $NL; $NL;Getting into the building is easy, but the panic room is a tougher nut to crack. It'll take days to cut it open, and you don't have that much time. So if you can't get in, how are you going to get to all that money? The answer is simple: steal the whole room.
heist_four_stores = "",--Four Stores
heist_four_stores_briefing = "ああ、Vladの頭がおかしいのは知ってる。だが奴は大量のコネクションを持ってるから、この先でかい仕事も待ってると俺は思う。こいつがその取っ掛かりになる。騒がれるまでは静かにやれよ。",--Look, I know Vlad is nuts. But he's got a lot of connections and I have a good feeling about him having a line on some big jobs down the line. This is a good start. Just stay frosty till things heat up.
heist_four_stores_crimenet = "Vladが街に帰ってきた。奴はロシア人の下で働く、店のオーナー達が気に入らない。忠誠心の足りない同郷人にVladがどうするか見せてやれ。$NL;$NL;» 4つの店を偵察する$NL;» 店の金を全て盗む$NL;» 開錠出来そうな金庫を探す",--Vlad is back in town and he doesn't like his store owners working for the Russians. Show them what Vlad does with disloyal countrymen.$NL;$NL;» Locate the four stores$NL;» Steal all their money$NL;» See if you can find safes to crack
heist_four_stores_hl = "",--Four Stores
heist_framing_frame = "",--Framing Frame
heist_framing_frame_1_briefing = "上院議員さまは絵画収集にご執心だ。アウトサイダーアートが特に好きらしい。幸運なことに、中央美術館で今週展示会が開催されている。印のつけられた絵画を上院議員のマンションに持っていく必要がある。絵画にはカメラを仕込む予定だ。カメラの目は俺達の仕事を楽にしてくれるだろう、保証するぜ。",--The senator loves to collect art - outsider art in particular. Lucky for us, the Capitol Art Gallery is hosting an exhibition this week. You need to take the marked paintings to the senator's apartment. They'll have cameras installed in them. Eyes on the inside will make your job easier, trust me.
heist_framing_frame_1_hl = "",--Art Gallery
heist_framing_frame_2_briefing = "よし、絵画にカメラを仕込んだぞ。準備完了だ。上院議員の取り巻きはびくついてるが、俺達との取引の用意は出来ている。さあ取引の時間だ、アートで金を稼ぐぞ。面会場所は俺が提供する。お前らは廃墟となった駅構内で奴らに会え。幸運を祈る。",--OK, the cameras are installed in the paintings. We're ready. The senator's men are jumpy but ready to deal with us. So let's deal. Money for art. I've set up the meeting location. You meet in an abandoned trainyard. Good luck.
heist_framing_frame_2_hl = "",--Train Trade
heist_framing_frame_3_briefing = "ここが上院議員のマンションだ。いい環境だが、セキュリティは厳重だ。俺達の仕掛けたカメラが起動している、どうやら奴は既に絵画を飾っているようだな。ビルの屋上で操作できるが、悪いがこれ以上の方法が無かった。奴の隠し金庫に侵入して、ゴールドを奪い、嵌めるために少々コカインを置いて逃げる。金庫に入るにはパスワードを通すしかないから、奴のガジェットをいくつか探して来てくれ、後は俺がやる。グッドラック。",--This is the senator's apartment. Nice neighborhood, high security though. He's already got the paintings hung, so our cameras are online and transmitting. You can tap the feed from the roof of the building, sorry we couldn't do better. Get into his hidden vault, take the gold, and leave a little coke there to finish the frame job. We can only get access to the vault with a password though, so find me some of his gadgets and I'll do the rest. Good luck.
heist_framing_frame_3_hl = "",--Framing
heist_framing_frame_crimenet = "The Elephantが対立する上院議員を陥れたがっている。$NL;$NL;» 上院議員が欲しがっている絵画を美術館から盗む$NL;» 盗んだ絵画にカメラを仕込み取引する$NL;» 上院議員のマンションに潜入して、金庫にコカインを入れる",--The Elephant wants to frame a rival senator.$NL;$NL;» Steal art that the senator wants from the art gallery$NL;» Install cameras in the stolen art and make a deal$NL;» Infiltrate the senator's apartment and plant coke in his vault
heist_friend = "",--Scarface Mansion
heist_friend_crimenet = "私はここしばらくカリブ海で銃の取引をしてるの。とても儲かるんだけど、昔からいる大物連中に私の参入を認めない奴らがいる。ボリビアのSosaカルテルよ。奴ら商品の質じゃこっちに対抗出来ないからって、うちの貨物船の襲撃に出たわ。船は沈むし、商品も奪われて、乗組員たちは殺されてしまった。まったくもって浅はかだわ。報いを受ける時よ。あなた達による血の報いをね。$NL;$NL;»屋敷へ侵入する$NL;»Ernesto Sosaをおびき出して殺害する$NL;»隠し金庫を開ける$NL;»戦利品を持って脱出",--I have been running guns in the Caribbean for a while. It's been very profitable, but some of the old movers in the region don't approve of my presence on the local market. The Bolivian Sosa Cartel specifically. As they could not compete with me on level terms, they decided to attack my operation - sinking one of my ships, stealing my merchandise and killing my operatives. That was very unwise. Now they must pay. You will collect that payment, in blood.$NL;$NL;» Gain access to the house$NL;» Draw Ernesto Sosa out and kill him$NL;» Open the hidden safe$NL;» Escape with the loot
heist_friend_hl = "",--Scarface Mansion
heist_friend_hl_briefing = "Sosaカルテルのマイアミ地方ボス、Ernesto SosaをThe Butcherが消したがっている。聞いて喜べ、奴はマイアミ・ビーチにあるトニー・モンタナの旧屋敷に住んでる。ああその通り、80年台の伝説的麻薬王、Scarfaceだ。そいつはさておき、お前らであの屋敷を襲って、入り口を見つけたらErnesto Sosaを殺してこい。あそこはまるで要塞だから、言うほど楽には行かないだろうがな。お前らならやれるさ。おっとそうだ、言い忘れてたがあの屋敷にはカネも金目の物もたっぷりある。盗んじまえ、一つ残らずな。だがまずは、Ernesto Sosaを消すのが先だ。",--Ernesto Sosa is the local boss in Miami for the Sosa Cartel, and The Butcher wants him dead. You're gonna love this: he lives in Tony Montana's old mansion in Miami Beach. Yeah that's right - Scarface, the legendary 80's drug lord. Anyway, you've got to hit the mansion, find a way in and then kill Ernesto Sosa. It won't be easy, the place is like a fortress. But you can do it. Oh yeah, I almost forgot - there should be a lot of money and other loot in that house. Steal it. Wipe them clean. But above all - kill Ernesto Sosa.
heist_gallery = "",--Art Gallery
heist_gallery_briefing = "俺は芸術はよく分からんが、好きな絵は分かる。－売れる絵だ。またギャラリーに行くぞ。パンフレットには「芸術の文化的な重要性」について書かれているが、もっと重要なのは金額について書いてあることだ。とてつもない値段だ。以前のようにやり方は任せる。トーマス·クラウンよろしくセキュリティーの目を掻い潜るか、オスロの素人花火みてえに派手にやろう。持てるだけ持って車でずらかるぞ。",--I don't know much about art, but I know what I like - and that is paintings that sell. We're headed back to the Gallery. The brochure talks about "the cultural importance of art", but more importantly it talks about dollars - lots and lots of dollars.$NL;$NL;As before, you make your own rules. Scope the security and sneak it like Thomas Crown, or blaze in like those Oslo amateurs. Grab as much as you can, and get it to the van.
heist_gallery_crimenet = "Bainは美術館に再び侵入することを要求している。$NL;$NL;» 慎重に下調べをする$NL;» 警備とカメラを確認する$NL;» 印のついた絵を袋詰めし逃走する",--Bain wants you to head back to the Art Gallery.$NL;$NL;» Case the place carefully.$NL;» Check for guards and cameras$NL;» Bag the marked out paintings and get to the escape van
heist_gallery_hl = "",--Art Gallery
heist_glace = "",--Green Bridge
heist_glace_briefing = "プランはシンプルだ。$NL;俺たちは闇に紛れてGreen Bridgeに来た護送車を襲う。$NL;今回は橋を爆弾で吹っ飛ばす!全ての交通は遮断だ。分かるか?$NL;そして俺たちは目的の囚人を確保し、そいつにフルトン回収を決め込む。$NL;空の彼方に消し去るって訳だ。",--The plan is simple: under cover of darkness, we hit the convoy when they cross Green Bridge. Actually - we'll blow the bridge with explosives! That should stop all traffic, don't you think? We grab the prisoner, put him in a fulton skyhook and make him vanish into thin air.
heist_glace_crimenet = "OK、Kazuoを脱獄させる時が来た。これで俺たちはKentoに関する情報を聞き出せる訳だ。それで俺はまあ...一発...ぶちかまして奴を別の所に移すつもりだ。まず俺らは護送車に不意打ちして囚人を外へ逃がす。これはコソコソやる訳にはいかない。最高に派手にやらんと護送車なぞ止められないからな。あぁそれとKazuoはこの計画は知らん。まあ驚いてもらうことになるな。$NL;$NL;»トラックを探す$NL;»トラックをSAWでこじ開け囚人を見つける$NL;»囚人を屋上まで護衛する$NL;»囚人を空輸する$NL;»脱出する",--Ok, it's time to break this guy Kazuo out of prison so we can get the information he has on Kento. I engineered some ah... trouble... to get him transferred to another facility by convoy. We'll ambush that convoy and break the prisoner out. This isn't gonna be a quiet one, guys, we'll need to take extreme measures to stop the prison trucks. And, yeah, Kazuo doesn't know we're breaking him out, so boy is he in for a surprise!$NL;$NL;» Find the trucks$NL;» Saw the trucks open and find the prisoner$NL;» Escort the prisoner to the tower$NL;» Get the prisoner airlifted out$NL;» Escape
heist_glace_hl = "",--Green Bridge
