heist_help = "",--Prison Nightmare
heist_help_crimenet = "眠るにつれ、俺たちは現実世界を離れて奇妙な世界に迷い込んだ。そこで待ち受けているものとは...",--As sleep takes us, we drift into that strange land beyond the waking world. And who knows what might be waiting for us there...
heist_help_hl = "",--Prison Nightmare
heist_help_hl_briefing = "ようこそ我が世界、我が監獄へ! もてなしてやるよ。食うものも何も無いがな!",--Welcome to my world, to my prison! I'll make you feel right at home. But you won't like the food - or anything else!
heist_hox = "",--Hoxton Breakout
heist_hox_1_briefing = "The DentistがHoxtonを再審議するように仕向けてくれた。$NL;あぁ、お前の事じゃない、Hox、俺が言ったのは前の...後で名前を整理しておいた方がいいな。$NL;再審はすぐに終わっちまうだろう。$NL;あいつの前科じゃ嫌疑が晴れることはないだろうしな。だがそこは重要じゃない。$NL;重要なのは奴が護送中で、そこを襲えるってところだ。奴の声が聞こえたらすぐに助け出すぞ。アメリカの司法制度への素敵な「罵声」だ。$NL;$NL;この計画は騒がしくなるぞ。裁判所の壁を爆破してHoxを掻っ攫い、脱獄させる。周辺地区は全て閉鎖されている。奴ら何か起こると勘づきやがったな。銃撃戦の準備をして弾は大量に用意しておけ。",--The Dentist got Hoxton a re-trial. Uh, not you, Hox - I mean Old... Look, we'll sort out names later. The trial will be quick. With his record, he ain't gonna walk, but that's not the point. The point is he's moving, and we can hit him in transit. We're going to grab him right after the hearing. A nice little "screw you" to the US justice system.$NL;$NL;The plan is as loud as it gets: we blast a wall in the courthouse, grab Hox and get him the hell out.$NL;$NL;Area's locked down for blocks around. They'll be expecting trouble. Have your guns ready and pack a lot of ammo.
heist_hox_1_hl = "",--The Breakout
heist_hox_2_briefing = "よしお前ら、脱獄させてくれた事には感謝する。だがそもそも、俺はムショにぶち込まれてる筈じゃなかったんだ。誰かがハメたんだ。そう確信している。連邦捜査官は俺の情報をかなりつかんでいる。その途方もないくそ野郎どもを捜し出せるかもしれない。誰かが密告した。誰かが俺をハメた。その誰かを見つけるつもりだ。$NL;$NL;そう簡単にはいかないだろうな。いいか、ぎりぎりの所でのらくらするんじゃないぞ。裏取引や内通みたいなおふざけも無しだ。情報源に行くぞ。FBI最大の巣穴だ。俺をハメた奴を見つけるぞ。",--Well, lads, thanks for breakin' me out. But I shouldn't have been there to begin with. Someone set me up. I'm sure of it. The Feds had too much on me. Way more than those mingebag wankers could dig up. Someone ratted. Someone fucked me. And I'm gonna find out who.$NL;$NL;Now, it ain't gonna be easy. No fannying about around the edges, right? No shadowy deals or contacts, or that bollocks. We're going to the source. The biggest FBI nest. Gonna find out who screwed me.
heist_hox_2_hl = "",--The Search
heist_hox_3 = "",--Hoxton Revenge
heist_hox_3_briefing = "よし、ようやく来たぞ。「鼠狩り」だ－奴は我々全員をハメたいようだな、だがそうはいくか。奴が現在都市郊外にあるFBIの隠れ家で篭城を決め込んでいるという情報を掴んでいる。こういうのは普通同じような設計で建ててあるもんだ。素晴らしくデカい家、敷地、24時間警備、そして中には例のごとくパニックルーム。お前が支払った税金がどう使われてるか一丁見に行くか。計画は単純だ、そこへ行って奴を見つけて殺す。俺たちに関する証拠品が確実に集積されてるだろう、賭けてもいい。だから『キレイ』に掃除も頼むぞ。",--Alright. Finally, we're going after the rat - the fink who screwed Hox, wants to screw us all. Time to put him down. We know he's currently bunkering down in an FBI safe house outside the city. These safe houses are usually built along the same lines. Nice big houses, grounds, 24 hour security, and most likely a panic room somewhere inside. See where your tax dollars go? The plan is simple - get in there, find our informer and finish him. Now, I'm betting there'll be evidence against us in there too, so be good to clean that up too.
heist_hox_3_crimenet = "サツどもはネズミを隠れ家に移送したらしい。ネズミ個人の特定はできなかったが、場所は漏れてきた。まぬけめ。さて、隠れ家に侵入してネズミを始末しよう。$NL;$NL;» セキュリティを突破する$NL;» ネズミを見つけ出す$NL;» ネズミを片付ける$NL;» 証拠品を取り除く",--The Feds have moved the rat to a safe house. They do a great job hiding his identity, but not his location. Silly pricks. So we drive out there, get in and put him down.$NL;$NL;» Scope the safe house and find a way in$NL;» Deal with any security $NL;» Locate the rat $NL;» Eliminate the rat $NL;» Remove any evidence
heist_hox_3_hl = "",--The Revenge
heist_hox_crimenet = "The DentistがHoxtonを再審議するように仕向けた。$NL;奴の声が聞こえたら、すぐに助け出せ。この計画は騒がしくなる。壁を爆破し、Hoxtonを掻っ攫い、脱獄させる。$NL;$NL;» Hoxtonを解放する$NL;» Hoxtonを装甲トラックに乗せる$NL;» Hoxtonの乗った装甲トラックを護衛する$NL;» Hoxtonと共に逃亡する",--The Dentist got Hoxton a re-trial. We're going to grab him right after the hearing. The plan is as loud as it gets: we blow up a wall, grab Hoxton and get him the hell out.$NL;$NL;» Free Hoxton$NL;» Take Hoxton to the armored truck$NL;» Escort the armored truck with Hoxton in it$NL;» Escape with Hoxton
