heist_jewelry_store = "",--Jewelry Store
heist_jewelry_store_briefing = "この街は盗んだ宝石をさばくのにはうってつけの場所だ。すぐ売れる。外交官と美人の若い奥さん達が買ってくれるさ、何の疑問も持たずにな。楽な仕事になりそうだ。さあ、行くぞ。",--This town is a great place to fence jewelry. Easy to move. Diplomats and trophy wives buying it - no questions asked. This is going to be cake. Let's get going.
heist_jewelry_store_crimenet = "Bainは典型的な宝石強盗を君たちに要求している。押し入って、宝石を強奪、そして逃げる。$NL;$NL;» 宝石店を探す$NL;» 店の事務所の金庫を確認する$NL;» 宝石をバッグに詰めて、逃走車まで運ぶ$NL;» 宝石以外の店の金目のものも盗む",--Bain wants you to do a classic jewelry heist. Get in, grab the loot, and get out.$NL;$NL;» Locate the jewelry store$NL;» Check the back office for a safe$NL;» Bag and get the jewelry to the escape car$NL;» Steal any other valuables in the store
heist_jewelry_store_hl = "",--Jewelry Store
heist_jolly = "",--Aftershock
heist_jolly_briefing = "おい野郎ども、ニュースは見たか!? 西海岸に大地震が直撃しやがった! LAは滅茶苦茶になっちまってるが、今回の目的地はそこだ。$NL;$NL;Vladは、大きな取引のために貨物をシアトルからDCに運ぼうとしていたようだが、運び屋は地震が起こった時間にLAに居たみたいだ。恐らくロングビーチから出荷するつもりだったんだろう。Vladはその荷物を安全な場所まで運んで欲しいと要求している。今回は計画を立てる時間は無い。LAは麻痺っちまって、陸路は使い物にならない。お前らにはヘリで降りてもらうぞ",--Hey, you guys see the news?! Big quake just hit the West Coast! LA is completely messed up. And that's where you're headed.$NL;$NL;Seems Vlad has set up some big deal to move some freight from Seattle to DC. The shippers he contracted were in LA when the quake hit - I guess they were going to ship out of Long Beach. Vlad wants his freight secured safely. No time for planning on this one. LA is wrecked, and the roads are messed up so we're going to drop you in by chopper.
heist_jolly_crimenet = "俺は西海岸最大のシンジケートとの契約をしてきた。東海岸に彼らの金庫を売ろうって話さ。だが、最初の出荷はトラブっちまってな-ファッキンクソ地震め! 信じられるか!? お前らはそこへ行って金庫の無事を確認してこい。クソフォルニアめ。$NL;$NL;» Vladの輸送トラックを探す$NL;» トラックをブチ開ける $NL;» 金庫を回収する",--I've struck a deal with the biggest syndicate on the west Coast, selling their safes on the east Coast. Unfortunately, first shipment of safes ran into a little trouble - a fucking earthquake! Can you believe that!? Get out there, ensure those safes are recovered. Fuck California.$NL;$NL;» Find Vlad's trucks$NL;» Open the trucks$NL;» Get the safes out
heist_jolly_hl = "",--Aftershock
heist_kenaz_briefing = "これはデカイ仕事になるぞ。俺にこんな話を寄越してきた。$NL;簡潔に言うと「Golden Grinには大きな金庫がある。それもBenevolent Bank並のものが。」$NL;静かに行ってもハデに行っても苦労はするだろう。The Dentistはハッキリとは伝えてきていないんだ。$NL;自らの存在に対して非常に用心深い。彼はただ、あるモノを持ってきたらこの契約は完了だ。と言った。彼の意図が何だったとしても...",--This is a big job. I'll talk you through it as we go, but the skinny is this: the Golden Grin has a big vault. Big. I mean Benevolent Bank big. Whether you sneak in, or go full assault, you're in for a tough time. The Dentist won't say what we're lifting out of there. Being very cagey about that. He just said that once we're done, we're done. The contract is fulfilled... whatever that means.
heist_kenaz_crimenet = "ラスベガスのGolden Grin Casinoが保有しているあるモノをThe Dentistが望んでいる。$NL;$NL;» 事前にloudで行くかstealthで行くか選択する$NL;» カジノに入る$NL;» 計画に従い行動する$NL;» 金庫に入るための方法を見つける$NL;» The Dentistが望んでいるあるモノを盗み出す",--The Golden Grin Casino in Las Vegas is holding an item of loot that The Dentist wants. Get it out for him.$NL;$NL;» Use Pre-Planning to choose a loud or stealthy entry$NL;» Enter the casino$NL;» Follow your plan $NL;» Find a way to get into the vault $NL;» Recover the mysterious loot for The Dentist
heist_kenaz_e3 = "",--Golden Grin Casino E3
heist_kenaz_full = "",--Golden Grin Casino
heist_kenaz_hl = "",--Golden Grin Casino
heist_kosugi = "",--Shadow Raid
heist_kosugi_briefing = "こいつは頭からケツまでステルスだ。Gageの要求は、この集積所へ潜入し、取れるだけ取って脱出することだ。注意点?絶対に警報を鳴らされるな、だ。見つかったら即引き上げるぞ。この倉庫はMurkywaterのものだ。名刺にはプライベート·セキュリティなんて書いてあるが、実態は傭兵と泥棒の軍団ってところさ。ここは保税倉庫ということになっているが、Gageの推測では、イラクやらアフガニスタンやら、とにかくこの野暮ったいペテン野郎共が暴れ回った地域からの盗品で溢れているはずだ。",--This is all about stealth. Gage wants you to silently enter this depot, grab what you can and get out. The important part? Do NOT set off the alarm. If you do, I'm pulling you out.$NL;$NL;This warehouse is Murkywater. Their business cards say 'private security' but they're really just a private army of mercenaries and looters. This warehouse is bonded, and Gage suspects it's full of stuff shipped back from Iraq, Afghanistan and wherever else those corn-fed crooks flex their muscle.
heist_kosugi_crimenet = "Murkywaterは古い港に保税倉庫を持ってる。奴らが何を運んでいるのか見に行くぞ。$NL;$NL;» 倉庫に気付かれず潜入する$NL;» 金目の物を盗み出す$NL;» 絶対にプランBは不可能$NL;» 荷物とともに脱出",--Murkywater has a bonded warehouse down at the old wharf. See what sort of crap they're shipping back.$NL;$NL;» Break into the warehouse undetected$NL;» Steal anything valuable you can find$NL;» Remember, there is no plan B$NL;» Escape with the loot
heist_kosugi_hl = "",--Shadow Raid
heist_mad = "",--Boiling Point
heist_mad_briefing = "良心を培うってのは大事なことだが、それが今って事か? この計画、俺は乗り気じゃないが、お前達の良心を責めることもできん。このJimmyって奴の話を信じるなら、Akanの計画は絶対に止めるべきだ。お前達の行き先は人里離れた場所にぽつんと建っている製材所で、あるロシア組織の秘密の研究施設にもなっている。Jimmyが言うには、奴らは現実離れした何かの実験をしているらしい。研究所に入り込んでAkanのデータを奪ってこい。幸運を祈る。",--Of all the times to grow a conscience, you decide now is the time? I can't say I like it, but I can't say you are making a mistake either. Based on what this Jimmy character is telling us, Akan really needs to be stopped. Your destination is a lumber mill in the middle of nowhere, that is secretly a laboratory run by a strange Russian organization. Jimmy tells me they are conducting some experiments that involve things out of this reality. Break into the lab and get the data Akan is after. Good luck, gang.
heist_mad_crimenet = "この汚れたロシアの組織は、ロシアにある秘密の研究施設で非常に邪悪な実験をしている。君たちは奴らがそこでしていることを信じられないだろう。我々はクソッタレなAkanの手にデータが渡るのを阻止する必要がある、そうだろ?これは殺るか殺られるかだ。$NL;$NL;» 製材所に侵入する$NL;» 研究所への入り口を見つける$NL;» データを手に入れる$NL;» 脱出する",--This dirty Russian organization is conducting some very disturbing experiments from a hidden laboratory in Russia. You won't believe what shit they're doing over there. We need to fuckin' stop Akan from getting his hands on the data, yeah? It's do or die, boys and girls.$NL;$NL;» Enter the compound$NL;» Gain access to the lab$NL;» Obtain the data$NL;» Escape
heist_mad_hl = "",--Boiling Point
heist_mallcrasher = "",--Mallcrasher
heist_mallcrasher_briefing = "そうだ、奴から話を聞いたな。Vladはマジだ。$NL;俺達はモールに行き、片っ端から破壊していく。$NL;十分に壊してやれば、奴のクライアントも見かじめ料について考え直すだろう。$NL;汚い仕事だが汚くなるのは好き、だろ?",--Yep. You heard him right. Vlad is serious. We go into the mall, we destroy as much as we can. Enough destruction and his client will rethink his whole stance on protection money. Dirty job but you like getting dirty, right?
heist_mallcrasher_crimenet = "VladはMr.Stoneにみかじめ料を払って欲しいそうだ。このビジネスの価値を見せるために、Stoneのモールを襲撃して欲しい。$NL;$NL;» モールを偵察する $NL;» 何もかも損傷、破壊する$NL;» 価値のある物品を奪う",--Vlad wants Mr. Stone to pay him for protection. To show that he means business, he wants you to destroy Stone's mall.$NL;$NL;» Locate the mall$NL;» Damage and destroy everything$NL;» Take any valuables you can find
heist_mallcrasher_hl = "",--Mallcrasher
heist_man = "",--Undercover
heist_man_briefing = "あの収税吏の奴、大企業と裏取引をしているらしい。$NL;本人は秘密にしてるつもりなんだろうが、情報がこっちに漏れてきた。$NL;あいつの代わりに、俺達がまるごと頂戴してやろう。$NL;取引現場を見下ろせる廃ビルを丸々一つ占拠した。コンピューターのセットアップも完璧だ。$NL;Alexがクレーンでリムジンごとビビらせてやればあいつは間違いなくサーバーとパスワードを差し出すだろう。$NL;2500万ドルのためだ、何だってやるさ。",--The Taxman thought he was clever making a deal with a big corporation, but the information leaked, and now bigger sharks want in - all in. We have a complete, run-down building to ourselves, overlooking the deal. We've got a set-up installed. Alex will help with the crane. Scare the Taxman into his limo, shake him up, and he'll be sure to give us the server and the codes. When it's about $25,000,000, anything goes.
heist_man_crimenet = "収税吏は小さな幸福と言うにははるかに重すぎるサーバーを運んできている。建物内のコンピューターで俺に繋げ。そして俺は簡単にデータを転送できる。$NL;$NL;» 収税吏のサーバーを奪う$NL;» コードを'絞り出す'$NL;» ハッキングし、データ転送を行う",--The Taxman carries a server weighting far more than just a fortune. Connect me with the computer inside the building and I can transfer the data easily. Let's show him we mean business.$NL;$NL;» Get the Taxman's server$NL;» Extract the codes$NL;» Hack and transfer the data
heist_man_hl = "",--Undercover
heist_mia = "",--Hotline Miami
heist_mia_1_briefing = "The Dentistは俺達に自称The Commissarと名乗るロシアンマフィアを探させてる。$NL;コイツはこのモーテルを含めたEast Coastの全ての犯罪利権を握ってる。$NL;俺達はコイツが何処に居るかは知らない、そこでヤツにほんの少し圧力をかけてやろう。俺達はアイツとのホットラインがある。全力でモーテルをブッ壊せばアイツはきっとキレて俺達に電話を掛けてくるだろう。そん時に逆探知すればアイツを追える。$NL;$NL;Hoxtonの為に一丁やるぞ。",--The Dentist has sent us after a Russian mobster, calls himself the Commissar. He's got criminal interests all over the East Coast, including this motel down at the heights. We don't know where he is, so you need to apply a little pressure. We've dropped him a hotline to us. Bust that place up as much as you can and he should call. And when he calls, we can trace him.$NL;$NL;We're doing this for Hoxton.
heist_mia_1_hl = "",--Hotline Miami
heist_mia_2_briefing = "俺達はThe Commissarの所に入る為に木箱に入ってる。トロイの木馬みたいにな。$NL;ヤツのアパートは街のきったねえ安っぽい所にある。$NL;セキュリティはいいとは言えないが、俺はヤツが筋力を増強する為にケツのポケットに何か隠してると思ってる。$NL;目的はシンプル、The Commissarを見つけて殺る。騒がしくなるぞ。目一杯オシャレして来い。",--We're using crates to get into the Commissar's place. Trojan horse style. His apartment is a cruddy dump in a crappy part of town. Security ain't great, but I'm sure he and his muscles have something in their back pocket. Objective is simple: find the Commissar and kill him. This is going to get loud, so dress to impress.
heist_mia_2_hl = "",--Four Floors
heist_mia_crimenet = "私の長期計画のためには、ワシントン州検察官に対する影響力が必要だ。今彼に渡りをつけているのはマイアミにいるあるロシア人だが、君たちにはこのロシア人を始末してもらいたい。D.C.の彼の活動場所でサボを行い、彼を引きずり出すんだ。幸運を願う所だが、その必要もないだろう。$NL;$NL;DentistはCommissarの始末を依頼している。$NL;$NL;» Commissarに電話をかけさせる$NL;» 電話を逆探知する$NL;» Commissarの隠れ家を襲い始末する",--My long-term plans require leverage over Washington's District Attorney. My hotline to him goes through a Russian, operating out of Miami. Your job is to eliminate this Russian. Draw him out by sabotaging his operations in D.C. I'd wish you luck, but luck has nothing to do with it.$NL;$NL;The Dentist wants you to take care of the Commissar.$NL;$NL;» Force the Commissar to call you$NL;» Trace the call$NL;» Infiltrate the Commissar's hideout and eliminate him
heist_moon = "",--Stealing Xmas
heist_moon_crimenet = "俺の義弟...クソの役にもたたない奴だが、雪を俺に、輸送中だったんだ。コロンビアン·スノーだ。分かるな? クリスマス用だ。だが奴はドジってポリに見つかっちまった。今はMidtown_Mallに隠れてるが、おそらくポリに捕まってる。アメリカの糞コップめ、この国にはクリスマスの慈愛精神ってのが無えのか! 俺は優しいから、クリスマスには大抵許すんだが、これは駄目だ。ダメ!!! 助けてくれよ、友よ。$NL;$NL;»サンタを救出する$NL;»Vladのコカインを回収する$NL;»クリスマスツリーごと盗んで脱出する",--My brother-in-law, that useless piece of trash, was transporting some snow for me - Colombian snow, you know, for Christmas. But he fucked up and was followed by the cops. He was hiding at the Midtown Mall, but I think the cops got him. Fucking American cops, there's no Christmas spirit in this country! I'm a friendly guy, and Christmas is about forgiving, but this is not ok. Not ok! You have to help me, my friends. $NL;$NL;» Rescue Santa$NL;» Recover Vlad's coke $NL;» Steal the Christmas tree and escape
heist_moon_hl = "",--Stealing Xmas
heist_moon_hl_briefing = "Vladの兄弟分が、モールの集積所で警察から逃れたのが始まりだ。奴はcokeを様々な箱に隠したらしい。今それらは、モールのあちこちの店に散らばっている。そして自身はサンタクロースに変装し、ウォッカを飲み漁っているって話だ。とんだ野郎だ。サツは酔ったサンタを不審に想い、奴を拘束した。おまえらは奴を解放し、どの箱にcokeを入れたのか聞き出すんだ。",--Vlad's brother-in-law hid from the cops in the mall's loading bay. It seems he hid the coke in various boxes, boxes that have now been distributed to shops all over the mall. He also disguised himself in a Santa Claus costume and stole some vodka and got drunk. What a mess. The cops got suspicious of the drunk Santa and apprehended him. You'll need to free him and ask him if he remembers what boxes he put the coke in.
heist_mus = "",--The Diamond
heist_mus_briefing = "こんどのはデカいぞ。とびきりのお宝-The Diamondを奪う。$NL;McKendrick博物館に侵入して、石ころを手に入れて、帰る、単純だな。そうだ、単純ってのは簡単って意味じゃねぇしこいつは簡単にいきそうもねぇ。だから単純な目標をたてる。博物館に侵入して、セキュリティを確認したら、無力化する。そしたら石ころを手に入れて、帰る。$NL;$NL;これはDentistの依頼だ。あいつはただ1人、この世界で一番有名なダイアモンドを売り捌くコネを持っている。俺たちは今まであいつに試されてきたのかもな。こういうデカい仕事をこなせるかどうかを。",--This is one of the big ones. We're going after a major prize - The Diamond. You're going to break into the McKendrick museum, get the stone, and get out. Sounds simple. Well, 'simple' doesn't always mean 'easy', and this ain't gonna be. So here are the 'simple' objectives. Break into the museum. Once you're in, check what security there is between you and The Diamond. Take it down. Once you have the stone, get out.$NL;$NL;This one is for The Dentist. He's the only one with the connections to move the most famous diamond in the world. I get the feeling he's been feeling us out so far. Seeing if we're up for a heist like this.
heist_mus_crimenet = "The Diamondは由緒正しいものだ。そして、とてつもなく価値がある。$NL;Dentistは、それを捌くことができる数少ない人物の1人だ。お前たちは今回、奴が代理人をしてる匿名の何者かのためにそれを取り戻せ。$NL;$NL;» MacKendrick博物館に侵入しろ$NL;» The Diamondの保管場所を見つけろ$NL;» The Diamondを盗め$NL;» 他に見つけた展示品を盗め",--The Diamond is historic. It is also extremely valuable. The Dentist is one of the few people with the connections to move it. You will retrieve it for an anonymous individual who he represents.$NL;$NL;» Get inside the McKendrick museum$NL;» Find where the Diamond is kept$NL;» Steal the Diamond$NL;» Steal any other artifacts you find
heist_mus_hl = "",--The Diamond
heist_nail = "",--Lab Rats
heist_nail_briefing = "俺たちは今夜遅くlabでの仕事を行う。$NL;不気味な光景を目にする事になるだろう。$NL;テーブル上で調理しろ。$NL;そして警官がもたらす問題や苦労に耐えろ。",--We're working in the lab, late tonight,$NL;letting your eyes behold an eerie sight.$NL;Get cooking on the table,$NL;bubble and boil.$NL;And keep the cops from bringin',$NL;trouble and toil.
heist_nail_crimenet = "トリックオアトリート! 俺の足を臭うかお菓子を置いてけ!$NL;お前が気にしないんなら、俺も気にしないさ。$NL;下着で調理するなよ。",--Trick or treat,$NL;smell my feet.$NL;Give me something to put on the street.$NL;If you don't,$NL;I don't care.$NL;Just don't cook in your underwear.
heist_nail_hl = "",--Lab Rats
heist_nightclub = "",--Nightclub
heist_nightclub_briefing = "OK。Tastefulクラブにお邪魔する事になったぞ、奴らの売り上げを解放して差し上げる。難しいことは何も無い。マネージャーオフィスを見つけて、客を押さえつけ、まんまと売り上げを頂く。 $NL;$NL;ああそうだ、多分そこには敵対するロシアンマフィアの奴らもいるはずだ。そして、今回Vladは俺と一緒には来ない事になってる。",--OK, we're going to pay a visit to the Tasteful club and uh, liberate their cash reserve. Nothing special. Find the manager's office, contain the crowd, make sure we leave in one piece.$NL;$NL;Oh, and there's probably rival Russian mobsters here. I know, Vlad is not being forthcoming with me either.
heist_nightclub_crimenet = "VladがDmitriのナイトクラブから金を盗んでくるように依頼している。$NL;$NL;» ナイトクラブを探す$NL;» 事務所の金庫をこじ開ける$NL;» Dmitriの金をバッグに詰めて車に持ち帰る",--Vlad wants you to steal money from Dmitri's nightclub.$NL;$NL;» Locate the nightclub$NL;» Break into the safe in the office$NL;» Bag Dmitri's money and get it to the car
heist_nightclub_hl = "",--Nightclub
heist_pal = "",--Counterfeit
heist_pal_briefing = "サンシャイン州へようこそ!ここにいるのは金目当ての女と詐欺師の男だ。$NL;Mitchell氏に会え。表の顔は、立派なカントリークラブのゴルフコーチだ。$NL;裏の顔は、資金洗浄と偽札作りのプロで大犯罪者。$NL;Mitchellと犯罪の相棒Wilsonは、捜査の網をかいくぐって文字通り何百万ドルもこしらえてきた。$NL;それも今日までだ。",--Welcome to the sunshine state! Where the women are gold diggers and the men are crooks. Meet Mr. Mitchell: on the surface, a golf coach for a respectable country club. Under the surface, a professional money launderer and counterfeiter - a master criminal. Mitchell and his partner in crime, Wilson, have managed to stay under the radar literally making millions. Until now.
heist_pal_crimenet = "",--Pack your bags, gang. This one is south of the Mason-Dixie. We're going after Mitchell and Wilson - couple of counterfeiters down in Pensacola. Running a printing operation out of his basement. It's a discrete operation, and this guy's work is solid, so he's making serious bank. Let's grab a piece!$NL;$NL;» Meet up with Mitchell$NL;» Breach into the basement$NL;» Extract the counterfeit plates and escape
heist_pal_hl = "",--Counterfeit
heist_pbr = "",--Beneath the Mountain
heist_pbr_briefing = "Lockeの依頼は砂漠にあるMurkyの施設、Black ridgeの襲撃だ。$NL;昔は空軍の施設だったが、Murkyが冷戦明けに買い取った。$NL;今では奴らの｢フォートノックス」となっている。$NL;だからマジでお宝があると思え。中の詳細はわからない。$NL;あまり外部とネットがつながってなくて事前調査にも限界があるんだ。$NL;ただ、一つ確実なのは、事はこっそりと行わない。ドンパチの準備をしておけよ。",--Locke has us hitting a Murky facility out in the desert. Black Ridge. Was an old air force place, back in the day. Murkywater bought it up after the Cold War, turned it into their own Fort Knox, so you can bet they're holding some serious loot here. Not sure what to expect. Not much online, so we got little in the way of intel. One thing is certain though - you're not going to sneak through this one. Dress for loud.
heist_pbr_crimenet = "標的は砂漠にあるMurkywaterの施設だ。この施設は奴らの｢フォートノックス」だと思ってくれ。無理やり押し入って奴らの戦利品を奪って来い。$NL;$NL;» Lockeが用意したassetsを回収する$NL;» 戦いながら施設に侵入する$NL;» 金庫を開け戦利品を確保する$NL;» Lockeに会う$NL;» レーダを破壊して脱出する",--The target is a Murkywater facility in the desert. Consider it their Fort Knox. Force your way in, and bring out whatever loot they're holding.$NL;$NL;» Retrieve assets left by Locke$NL;» Fight your way to the inner complex$NL;» Open the vaults and retrieve the loot$NL;» Meet with Locke$NL;» Destroy the radars and escape
heist_pbr_hl = "",--Beneath the Mountain
heist_pbr2 = "",--Birth of Sky
heist_pbr2_briefing = "よし、作戦はこうだ。Lockeの手引きでお前らは機内に忍び込んでおく。奴からの合図を待って、飛び出せ。激しい抵抗には遭わないだろう―なにしろ乗員だけだからな。金はでかい塊になってまとまっている。貨物扉からそいつを放り出し、地上に着いたら回収する。簡単だろ?",--Okay, here's the plan. Locke is going to have you smuggled onto the plane. Wait until you get his signal and burst out. Resistance should be light - just the crew. The money is packed into large pallets. Get them out of the cargo doors, and we'll collect them when they hit the ground. Simple.
heist_pbr2_crimenet = "標的はMurkywaterの輸送機だ。こいつは札束のパレットを運んでいる。お前達は密航することになるだろう。輸送機からお金を投下し、それを回収しろ。$NL;$NL;» 貨物室に出る$NL;» 輸送機のハッチを開き、現金のパレットを投下する$NL;» 輸送機を飛び降りる$NL;» 街中に落ちた現金のパレットを回収し、Lockeに合図を送る$NL;» 下水道に降りて脱出する",--The target is a Murkywater transport plane. It is carrying pallets of currency. You will be smuggled aboard. Drop the money from the plane and recover it.$NL;$NL;» Emerge into the cargo compartment$NL;» Open the cargo doors and release the money pallets$NL;» Skydive to the surface$NL;» Recover the money pallets in the town and signal Locke$NL;» Descend into the sewers and escape
heist_pbr2_hl = "",--Birth of Sky
heist_peta = "",--Goat Simulator
heist_peta_briefing = "ホンジュラスカルテルがダウンタウンを通ってトラックでブツを運んでる。Vladが襲撃の手はずを整えたから、俺たちでそいつらを始末する。それからブツを頂く。実働部隊ってやつだな。",--This Honduran cartel has a truck moving its product through Downtown. Vlad has arranged to have it hit. We're on clean-up. We go in afterwards, make sure the product gets out. Boots on the ground, you know?
heist_peta_crimenet = "Hectorがくたばったことでヤクの市場に穴ができちまった。自然は足らざるを補う。クソッタレだ。そこら中から間抜け共がやってくる。ホンジュラス人の連中が手を広げようとしている。こいつらが根を張る前に、潰しちまおう。密輸団の連中をバラバラにして、ブツは頂きだ。単純だろ? $NL;$NL;» Goatを見つけろ$NL;» Goatを確保しろ$NL;» 脱出しろ",--Hector's death left a vacuum in the powder trade. Nature abhors a vacuum. Fucking abhors it! There's muck-fuckers crawling in from everywhere. Bunch of Hondurans are trying to spread. Let's hit them before they can take root. Break up their smuggling ring. Steal their product. What can go wrong?$NL;$NL;» Locate the goats$NL;» Secure the goats$NL;» Escape
heist_peta_hl = "",--This was not the deal
heist_peta2 = "",--Goat Simulator
heist_peta2_briefing = "オーケー、最悪の状況は乗り越えたな。 Vladの運び屋が郊外の農場にヤギを運んで、包みを取り出す準備が出来た。近くで待っていろ。周辺を監視しろ。簡単な仕事だ、そうだろう?",--Okay, I think the worst is behind us. Vlad's driver got the goats to a farm outside the city, ready to perform the extraction of the packages. Stick around. Watch the perimeter. Easy work, right?
heist_peta2_crimenet = "Vladの運び屋が郊外の農場にヤギを運んだ。手袋をはめろ。汚れ仕事の時間だ。$NL;$NL;»ブツを守る$NL;»周囲を警戒する$NL;»脱出する",--Vlad's driver got the goats to a farm outside the city. Snap on your gloves - time for some dirty work. $NL;$NL;» Make sure the product is secure$NL;» Watch the perimeter$NL;» Leave the area and escape
heist_peta2_hl = "",--Dirty work
heist_pines = "",--White Xmas
heist_pines_briefing = "急いで向かって貰いたいが、あいにくの森の中だ。だから空挺みたいに行ってもらうぞ。パイロットを探してくれ－多分墜落機のとこに居るはずだ－そしたら脱出用のヘリを回す。無事に脱出できるまで付いてやってくれ。それから、Vladが言うには飛行機にゃ商品が詰まっていたらしい。森の中を探してみてくれ、出来るだけ持って帰ってほしい。クリスマス資金が多すぎるってことはないからな。",--We need you there fast, but it's really out in the sticks, so you're going in like the paras. Find the pilot - he's probably near the wreck - and then we'll send in a chopper to extract him. Stay with him til he's safely out. Also, Vlad says that plane was loaded with product. Search the forest and get as much out as you can. Can always use a little extra cash at Christmas.
heist_pines_crimenet = "Vladが彼の泥酔したパイロットを救出するよう依頼している。$NL;$NL;» パイロットを探す$NL;» 彼を守りヘリで脱出させる$NL;» コカインをできる限り拾う",--Vlad wants you to rescue his drunken pilot and recover his product.$NL;$NL;» Locate the pilot$NL;» Keep him safe and get him to the rescue helicopter$NL;» Recover as much cocaine as possible
heist_pines_hl = "",--White Xmas
heist_rat = "",--Cook Off
heist_rat_briefing = "これは単純なjobだが、簡単という訳じゃない。俺たちはあの森に戻る。覚えてるだろ?あそこでHectorの為に一仕事したよな。とにかく、調べると今でも使えるようだ。というわけで、あそこに行って出来る限りのMethを調理しよう。好きなだけ居ていいぞ。もし材料が尽きたら空から届けてやる。良い稼ぎになるはずだ。",--This is a simple job, but that doesn't mean it will be easy. We're going to head out to the forest. You remember the place. We did some work for Hector out there. Anyway, I scoped the place out and it is still intact. So, we're headed there to cook up as much meth as we can. You can stay as long as you want. If you run out of supplies, I'll get more flown in. Should be easy money.
heist_rat_crimenet = "またあの森の調理場でMethを作ろう。今回はクソHectorの奴とは関係ない。ただ利益の為にやるだけだ。$NL; $NL;» 調理場を見つけろ$NL;» Methを調理しろ$NL;» Methを確保して脱出する",--We're headed back to cook in the meth lab in the forest. None of Hector's shit this time. This is just for profit. $NL;$NL;» Locate the meth lab $NL;» Cook meth $NL;» Secure the loot and escape.
heist_rat_hl = "",--Cook Off
heist_red2 = "",--First World Bank
heist_red2_briefing = "金庫室は銀行の奥深くにある。入り込むには中々強固だが、俺たちには手助けもある。内通者が準備してお前らを待っているぞ。彼らはお前らがそこに入るのを手伝ってくれるだろう。$NL;$NL;騒がしくやることも、静かにやることも出来る。お前ら次第だ。",--The vault is buried deep in the back of the bank. Getting through to it will be tough, but we have some help. An Inside Man is prepped and waiting for you. They're going to help us out once you're in there.$NL;$NL;You can do this loud, or you can take it softly. Up to you.
heist_red2_crimenet = "First World Bankは十分眺めたな。今こそトリガーを引く時だ。$NL;奴らを組み伏せあいつ等が不正に得た金を奪い取れ。$NL;$NL;» マネージャーの位置を突き止めろ$NL;» サーバールームに侵入しろ$NL;» 金庫まで突き進め$NL;» バッグに金をつめて脱出しろ",--We've been eyeing the First World Bank for a while. Now it's time to pull the trigger. Get down there and relieve them of their ill-gotten gains.$NL;$NL;» Locate the manager$NL;» Get access to the server room$NL;» Force your way to the vault$NL;» Bag all the money and escape
heist_red2_hl = "",--First World Bank
heist_roberts = "",--GO Bank
heist_roberts_briefing = "今回のターゲットは銀行だ。それほどデカい支店ってわけじゃないが、たまたま今日は金庫に外国証券がたんまり積まれてるらしい。$NL;$NL;手順はいつも通り－忍び込むもよし、血の海を作るもよし、だ。だがどっちにしても、今回はちょっとした面白いものを見せてやれると思うぜ。金を運び出す方法について俺に考えがある。",--We got a bank here. Not a big branch but I've learned the vault is temporarily holding stacks of cash in transit. Foreign exchange notes.$NL;$NL;Anyway, you know how to do it - your way. Sneak in silent, or unleash hell. Either way, I got a little idea for how to lift the money out of there. You'll see what I mean. I think you'll like it.
heist_roberts_crimenet = "いつもの銀行強盗だ。金庫を破って、貸し金庫をカラにして金目の物を運び出す。難しいことは何もない。Bainの情報によると、この支店は国内で最も被害が少ないそうだ。その数字を変えてやろう。$NL;$NL;» Keycardを探す。金庫には二枚必要$NL;» 無ければドリルを使う$NL;» 金庫内の貸し金庫を開ける$NL;» スカイフックを組み立てる$NL;» 金を盗み出す",--This is a classic bank job. Break the vault, empty the deposit boxes and get the loot out. Simple. Bain's intel says this branch has the lowest hit-rate in the country. It's time to change that.$NL;$NL;» Search the environment for keycards. Two are needed for the vault$NL;» Failing that, use a drill on the vault$NL;» Crack open the deposit boxes$NL;» Assemble the skyhook$NL;» Get the money out
heist_roberts_hl = "",--GO Bank
heist_run = "",--Heat Street
heist_run_briefing = "いいかお前ら、話の出処が誰だったか忘れるなよ。$NL;胡散臭いLockeの野郎のことだ、奴の話に裏があるのは間違いない。$NL;目ン玉ひん剥いて警戒しろよ。",--Okay guys. Remember who you're dealing with here. Locke is a smelly fish. There's bound to be more sides to this than what he's telling you. Keep your eyes peeled.
heist_run_crimenet = "知っての通り、私の生業は諜報と情報だが、そこで諸君らに関わる重大な情報が手に入った。何者かが君たちPayday Gangの破壊と殺戮を目論み躍起になっている。今朝傍受した通信で、その連中のエージェントがDowntownで誰かと会合を行う事が分かった。連中の正体は不明だが、知っての通り、諸君らは私にとって貴重な人材であるから、諸君らがそのエージェントを捕らえて尋問出来るよう手助けがしたい。場所を伝えよう。それから作戦の遂行を見守らせてもらう。$NL;$NL;» エージェントを見つけて捕らえる。$NL;» 不測の事態に注意。",--As you know, intelligence and information is my business. And I recently came across something important that concerns you. the Payday Gang. Someone is out to destroy you, possibly kill all of you. This morning I intercepted a message indicating that an agent of these people is meeting someone at a certain location downtown. I don't know yet who these people are, but as you know, I find you a valued asset, and so I want to help you apprehend this agent so you can squeeze information out of him. I'll give you the location and then keep an eye on you while you conduct the operation.$NL;$NL;» Find and apprehend the agent$NL;» Watch out for surprises
heist_run_hl = "",--Heat Street
heist_rvd = "",--Reservoir Dogs Heist
heist_rvd_crimenet = "",--Bain has got a job available out west. The Cabot crime family in L.A. needs help hitting a jewelry store for a haul of diamonds. It's an easy walk-in-crack-vault-get-out sort of deal, with a meetup afterward in an old mortuary warehouse.$NL;$NL;» Meet up with Cabot's people outside the store$NL;» Break into the vault and steal the diamonds$NL;» Rendezvous with Cabot's people at the warehouse by Highland Mortuary$NL;» Gather the diamonds at the back of the warehouse$NL;» Wait for Twitch to arrive with the escape vehicle
heist_rvd1_briefing = "",--I know you got little incentive to trust me after Alaska, but sending you there was the only credible ruse we had time for, to get you out of D.C. People Bain used to think could be trusted... were listening.  And now he's gone. We knew something was going to happen but not when or what. Keeping you in the dark was my call, not Bain's. Never thought they would actually be able to go after him. Look I realise it's a kakspul to hear, but you got out with the guns I left, yeah? I'm sorry about Bain... we'll deal with it... but first we have to get you out of there. Please trust me guys, I'm not bekakin ya. I promise I'll prove it.
heist_rvd1_hl = "",--Highland Mortuary
heist_rvd2 = "",--Reservoir Dogs Heist
heist_rvd2_briefing = "",--Ok, guys. Cabot's people will be waiting for you outside the store. From what he tells me, this should be quick and easy. Show these professional L.A. gangsters what the Payday gang can do.
heist_rvd2_hl = "",--Garnet Group Boutique
heist_safehouse = "",--The safe house
heist_safehouse_briefing = "Safe Houseはお前のもう一つの家であり、砦であり、お前が熟考する場であり、金をまとめて置いておく場所だ。Safe Houseはプレッシャーの少ない環境で お前のスキルを研ぎ澄ます場所だ。色々な武器や、金庫破り、カメラを無効化する機械を試すこともできる。金庫で現金の山を眺められるし、資産を購入して、この場所を周りの奴らが羨むホワイトハウスにすることだってできる。",--The safe house is your home away from home, your fortress, your place of contemplation, the place where your money takes shape and form. The safe house gives you a place to sharpen your skills in a low-pressure environment. You'll be able to test out various weapons, mechanics like cracking safes and disarming cameras, admire the fat stacks of cash in your vault, and even purchase assets to make the place the envy of every crook from here to the White House.
heist_safehouse_briefing_2 = "Safe houseによく戻ってきたな。",--Welcome back to the safe house.
heist_safehouse_crimenet = "",--Bain has set you up with a safe house.
heist_safehouse_hl = "",--The safe house
heist_short1_stage1 = "",--Stealth - Flash Drive
heist_short1_stage1_briefing = "Dallas、旧友よ、2年ぶりに戻って来てくれて嬉しい。知っての通り、俺は完璧主義だ。だから、指輪に付いてるかもしれない錆を取り除きたいのは、別に驚くことじゃない。昔のように俺の指示に従って欲しい、これはちょっとした散歩だ。俺達は後で必要になるアクセスコードを狙っている。だが、単純な強盗の犯行にカモフラージュする必要がある。これを静寂の中で行う、ふさわしい服を着てくれ。",--Dallas, old friend, I'm glad to have you back after two years. Now you already know I'm a thorough man, so it should come as no surprise that I want to get rid of any ring rust that might exist. Follow my instructions just like old times and this will be a walk in the park. We're after some access codes that we will be needing later, but we need to make it look like nothing but a simple robbery. You're doing this in the quiet, so dress appropriately.
heist_short1_stage1_crimenet = "",--Break into the Police storage compound and get your hands on some access codes we will need later.
heist_short1_stage1_hl = "",--Stealth - Flash Drive
heist_short1_stage2 = "",--Stealth - Erasing History
heist_short1_stage2_briefing = "よし、Dallas。昨夜盗んだアクセスコードを使う時が来た。建物への入り口を見つけろ。警察のデータベースにアクセスして、Crime.Netに関する全ての情報を削除するんだ。これは散歩じゃない、だからまだ素質が残っていることを俺に見せてくれ。",--All right, Dallas. It's time to use those access codes we stole last night. Find a way inside the building - access the Police database and delete all the intel they have on Crime.Net. This won't be a walk in the park, so show me you still got what it takes.
heist_short1_stage2_crimenet = "",--Break into the building - access the Police database and delete all the intel they have on Crime.Net.
heist_short1_stage2_hl = "",--Stealth - Erasing History
heist_short2 = "",--Get The Coke - Loud
heist_short2_stage1 = "",--Loud - Get The Coke
heist_short2_stage1_briefing = "さて、Dallas。俺達が一緒に仕事をしていた頃から2年も経ったな。俺はお前がまだ素質を持っているか確認する必要がある。簡単なことから始めよう、いいな?俺の知り合いは最近、コカインの取引でチンピラ共に騙された。奴らのナイトクラブに侵入し、盗まれたコカインを探して、取り戻してもらいたい。簡単だろ?",--Okay, Dallas. It's been two years since we worked together, and I need to see that you still got what it takes. We'll start with something simple, all right? An acquaintance of mine recently got robbed on a cocaine deal by some low-life mobster. I need to you to break into his night club and see if you can find the stolen cocaine and get it back. Easy, right?
heist_short2_stage1_crimenet = "",--Okay, Dallas. It's been two years since we worked together, and I need to see that you still got what it takes. We'll start with something simple, all right? An acquaintance of mine recently got robbed on a cocaine deal by some low-life mobster. I need to you to break into his night club and see if you can find the stolen cocaine and get it back. Easy, right?
heist_short2_stage1_hl = "",--Loud - Get The Coke
heist_short2_stage2b = "",--Loud - Plan B
heist_short2_stage2b_briefing = "まだ終わってないぞ、Dallas! 予想以上に追撃され、警察はお前のすぐ後ろだ。包囲されて状況が悪化する前に奴らを振り払ってみろ!",--It's not over yet, Dallas! We picked up more heat than I expected and the cops are on your tail. Try to shake them before they close you off and things get hairy!
heist_short2_stage2b_hl = "",--Loud - Plan B
heist_shoutout_raid = "",--Meltdown
heist_shoutout_raid_briefing = "俺たちはVladの為にMurkywater倉庫を叩きに行く。何が狙いかは分からないし、どこにあるのかも分からない。だがそれは輸送コンテナの金庫の中にある事は分かっている。中に入って金庫を探し出し、あのイかれたロシア人が欲しい物を持ってきてやれ。$NL;$NL; Murkyは警戒状態で待っているはずだ。警察の対応も早いだろう、つまり俺たちは早めにこの仕事を終わらせないといけないぞ。早めにという事はloudだ。忍び隠れる事は捨てろ。始めた瞬間からセーフティーは外せ。そして忘れるな、貴重品が大量にあるはずだ。持てるようなら持って来い。",--We're hitting the Murkywater warehouse for Vlad. Don't know what the target is, or where it is, but it's tucked away in a vault, which itself is in one of their branded shipping containers. Get in there, find the vault and get out whatever it is that crazy Russki wants. $NL;$NL;Murkies will be on high alert when you get there, and the cops'll be quick to respond, so you gotta get in there and do the job fast. Fast means loud. No tiptoeing this one. It's safeties off from the get-go. And, don't forget, there's loot all around. See what you can grab.
heist_shoutout_raid_crimenet = "お前たちがMurkywaterから幾つか物を盗んできた素晴らしい功績は耳にしたことがある。非常に感心している。お前たちにはそこに戻って行って欲しい。あの傭兵ども、今度は何か新しい物を抱え込んでいるらしい。その「ある物」は私が欲しいものだ。Murky達はこれに感づいて移動を始めている。私はあれがrabbit-holeに消えてしまう前に奪取したい。$NL;$NL;» Murkywaterの倉庫に侵入しろ$NL;» 金庫を特定しろ$NL;» 金庫のファンを止めろ$NL;» 貴重品を電車に持っていけ",--I heard about the outstanding job you did sneaking into that Murkywater warehouse. Most impressive. I need you to go back there. Those mercenaries've got a 'little something' tucked away. A little something I would like. The Murkies are pulling out, and I need this before it disappears down some rabbit-hole.$NL;$NL; » Access the Murkywater compound $NL; » Locate the vault $NL; » Jam the vault vent $NL; » Transport the loot to the train
heist_shoutout_raid_hl = "",--Meltdown
heist_spa = "",--Brooklyn 10-10
heist_spa_crimenet = "今夜はニューヨークで明かすぞ。The Continentalから、彼らの主要人物が何者かの待ち伏せに遭って捕まったと連絡が入った。男の名前はCharon、襲われた直後にかけてきた電話で居場所は分かってる。すぐに彼を助け出せ。襲った奴らを片付けて、無事にThe Continentalの元へ帰れるようにしてやれ。$NL;» 奪われた物を取り戻す$NL;» 脱出",--You're going to New York tonight. The Continental called - one of their key staff has been ambushed and is being held by unknown assailants at an address in Brooklyn. We have the location from a call he made just as they took him. The target's name is Charon. We need to get there fast, take out whoever's got him and send him back to the Continental safe and sound.$NL;$NL;» Locate Charon$NL;» Rescue Charon and protect him from the attackers$NL;» Get back what was stolen$NL;» Escape
heist_spa_hl = "",--Brooklyn 10-10
heist_spa_hl_briefing = "よし、Charonを助け出そう。俺の個人的事情も絡んでいるが、まあそういうことだ。しっかりやってくれ。",--Okay... Let's get Charon out. This is personal for me, so let's stay sharp.
heist_ukrainian_job = "",--Ukrainian Job
heist_ukrainian_job_briefing = "Vladは、このDmitriという男が大嫌いだ。故国からの長い確執ってわけだ。Vladの妹と一発ヤっちまったかなんかだろう。とにかく、仕返しの手助けをしてやろうじゃないか。ティアラを頂戴しに行くぞ。奥の部屋にあるはずだ。あまり早くからバレると脱出に手間取るだろう。アセットを確認しておけ。さあ、仕事だ。",--Vlad really doesn't like this Dmitri guy. One of these old-country feuds. Maybe he shagged his sister or something. Anyway, let's help the man settle the score. We go for the tiara - back room from what I understand. Don't get the heat on you too early or your escape is going to be rough. Check your assets. Let's go.
heist_ukrainian_job_crimenet = "Vladを刑務所送りにした裏切り者の結婚式をぶち壊すのに手を貸してほしい。$NL;$NL;» 宝石店を探す$NL;» ティアラを見つけて盗み出す$NL;» それ以外の金目のものを盗む",--Help Vlad destroy the wedding of the rat who sent him to prison.$NL;$NL;» Locate the jewelry store$NL;» Find and steal the tiara$NL;» Steal any other valuables you find
heist_ukrainian_job_hl = "",--Ukrainian Job
heist_watchdogs = "",--Watchdogs
heist_watchdogs_1_briefing = "この仕事では、俺たちは番犬だ。$NL;$NL;分厚い防弾チョッキと目いっぱいの重装備を持って行け。知っての通り、Hectorの輸送車が狙われている。お前らはトラックの荷台に乗り込むんだ。コカインを奪われるなよ。",--We're watchdogs on this job.$NL;$NL;Wear a heavy jacket and carry heavier weapons. We know Hector's transports are getting hit. You'll ride in the back of the truck. Don't let the coke go anywhere.
heist_watchdogs_1_hl = "",--Truck Load
heist_watchdogs_2_briefing = "よし、お前たちは計画通り港に向かってくれ。トラックからコカインを降ろすんだ。$NL;Hectorをそこに呼ぶために倉庫の奴のボートへ合図を送らなくちゃならん。$NL;奴が到着したら、コカインをボートに乗せろ、あとはボートの運び屋に任せておけ。",--OK, you go to the harbor like we planned. Offload the coke from the pick-up. You'll need to signal Hector's boat in the warehouse to get him to come in. Once he's there, get the coke onboard and the boat driver will do the rest.
heist_watchdogs_2_hl = "",--Boat Load
heist_watchdogs_crimenet = "Hectorがコカイン輸送の護衛(watchdogs)を必要としている。$NL;$NL;» トラックに積まれたコカインを守る$NL;» 新たな状況に対応する$NL;» 港へ向かう$NL;» コカインをボートの運び屋に届ける",--Hector needs watchdogs for transporting cocaine.$NL;$NL;» Guard the cocaine in the truck$NL;» Adapt to new situations$NL;» Reach the harbor$NL;» Deliver the shipment to boat driver
heist_welcome_to_the_jungle = "",--Big Oil
heist_welcome_to_the_jungle_1_briefing = "The ElephantがBiker Gangの居場所を寄越してきた。$NL;こいつらは科学者がいじりまわしてる実験装置の強奪計画を立ててる。$NL;科学者の場所を突き止めるのは時間の問題だろう－情報を奪って先回りしてしまうという計画だ。$NL;俺ならそういう情報は金庫に入れておく、賭けたっていいぞ。",--The Elephant gave us the location of the biker gang hunting for the scientist's little device. I think they're close to finding him - we need their intel so we can get to him first. I'm betting it's in their safe.
heist_welcome_to_the_jungle_1_hl = "",--Club House
heist_welcome_to_the_jungle_2_briefing = "よし、情報に目を通したところだ。こいつはおもしろい仕事になるぞ。アセットを良く見てくれ。ひっくり返してでも全部の情報を見逃すんじゃない。こっそり入って探し出すんだ。奴の研究室と、そこにある核融合炉をな。",--Well, I've been through the intel, and this is gonna be interesting. Check out the assets. Get to know them upside down. We need to sneak in to find this guy's lab, and, in the lab, his fusion engine.
heist_welcome_to_the_jungle_2_hl = "",--Engine Problem
