menu_gage_assignment_introduction_desc = "まずは、運び屋の仕事を請け負ってくれて感謝するぜ。最近は自分で運ぶこともほとんどなくてな。仕事についてだ。 D.C.中に散らばった\"ブツ\"を回収するために大勢の人間を雇ったんだが、、誰一人として\"ブツ\"を運んできやがらねぇ。まぁ、相当危険な仕事だからな。お前の仕事はそんな\"ブツ\"...つまりパッケージを探して持って帰ってくることだ。パッケージの数が一定数になったらいいものをやろう。$NL;$NL;パッケージには、必要な量によって色分けされた、Green Mantis, Yellow Bull, Red Spider, Blue Eagle, そしてPurple Snake の五種類がある。 緑色は基本的なもので、紫色は非常に魅力的な商品だ。なんとなく分かるだろう。$NL;$NL;パッケージを見つけたら、近づいて拾うんだ。その日の終わりにそれらを得るだろう。パッケージの数は、チーム全体で取得されるから、ninja loot(コッソリ無断で獲得)する必要はないぜ。十分な数の特定の色のパッケージを獲得すると、報酬は自動的にお前のインベントリに追加されるぜ。パッケージの報酬の中のすべてのmodsを1つずつが手に入るんだ。詳細は、パッケージページを確認してくれ。$NL;$NL;パッケージをコンプリートした後は、再び解放され、何度でも収集をはじめられる。うちにパッケージを持ってくる限り、お前はより多くの報酬をかせぎ続けられる。$NL;楽しんでくれ。$NL;$NL;- Gage.",--First, thanks for taking on the courier assignment. Not much of a runner myself these days. This is how it works: There are packages scattered across D.C. I hire a lot of people to courier these things, but no one gets to transport a package the whole way. Not very safe to do that. Your job is to pick up any packages you spot and bring them back to me. If you bring enough packages, I'll give you free stuff.$NL;$NL;There are 5 types of packages, color coded by value: Green Mantis, Yellow Bull, Red Spider, Blue Eagle, and Purple Snake. Green is basic stuff, purple is highly desirable goods. You get the idea.$NL;$NL;When you spot a package, just approach it and pick it up. You get them at the end of each day. The entire team gets the package count, so there's no need to ninja loot from your team mates. Once you earn enough packages of a specific color, the rewards will be automatically added to your inventory, free of charge. You get one each of all mods in the reward package. Check the package pages for details.$NL;$NL;After completing a package, feel free to start collecting again: You'll keep earning more rewards as long as you bring home packages. Happy hunting.$NL;$NL;- Gage.
menu_gage_assignment_summary_desc = "これがお前の探している5種類のパッケージだ。$NL;進捗が気になるなら、いつでもここで確認できる。$NL;$NL;パッケージ集めは、何度でも達成可能だから忘れるなよ。$NL;配達を完了するたびに、報酬はインベントリに自動的に送られ、別の報酬アイテムのセットが設定される。$NL;特定の報酬リストは、個々のパッケージページを確認してくれ。",--These are the five package types you're looking for. Come back here to check your progress whenever you need to.$NL;$NL;Remember that you can complete the package runs as many times as you want; each time you complete a delivery, you get another set of the reward items automatically transferred to your inventory. For a specific reward list, check the individual package pages.
american_desc_codex = "",--Houston could never hold a job even if his life would depend on it. His life style turned him to a life of cons and burglary. He committed his first major felony at the age of 24 and the stakes have only increased since.
german_desc_codex = "",--Wolf can be happy-go-lucky one second and mad as hell the next. After his mental breakdown he reinvented his personality and it's now a mash-up of action movie characters and his own ideas of what criminals should be like.
heist_contact_bain = "",--Bain
heist_contact_bain_description = "CRIME.NETの背後に潜む謎の人物。リスクを最小限にするため誰とも実際に接触しようとせず、仕事相手どころかギャング達もその正体を知らない。",--The shadowy figure behind Crime.net. No one, not even the crew, has ever met Bain, and his interaction with the contacts and the crew is carefully managed to ensure minimum risk to all parties.
heist_contact_continental = "",--The Continental
heist_contact_continental_description = "",--The Continental is a mysterious institution, a hotel but also a safe haven for professional assassins and others who move in the shadows. Sometimes the Continental has need of services, services that require special talents. This is where the Payday Gang comes into the picture.
heist_contact_gage = "",--Gage
heist_contact_gage_description = "Gageは国内で最高の武器商人...そして腕のいい\"暗殺者\"でもある。 アフガンでの兵役経験があり、現在は暗殺されかけた後遺症で車イス生活をしている。どんな武器を求めるにしろ、彼に任せればいい。",--Gage is an Afghanistan war veteran, known for being in a wheelchair after an assassination attempt. He is the best weapons dealer within the border - and a good assassin at that. Anything you might need, he's your man.
heist_contact_hector = "",--Hector
heist_contact_hector_description = "Hectorは、細部にこだわる元管理職のビジネスマンで、東海岸最大の麻薬密輸入者だ。メキシコのSinaloanカルテルの次期リーダー候補でもある。",--A detail-oriented former business administrator, Hector is the biggest drug trafficker on the Eastern Seaboard and next in line for leadership of the Sinaloan Cartel in Mexico.
heist_contact_hoxton = "",--Hoxton
heist_contact_interupt = "",--Car chase
heist_contact_jimmy = "",--Jimmy
heist_contact_locke = "",--Locke
heist_contact_locke_description = "南アフリカ生まれで、リンカーン研究所で教育を受け、MI5で訓練され、そして今はMurkywaterに雇用されている。Vernon Lockeは、Crime.netの侵入を任された特別なサイバー戦争部門、Lockeはこれを管理している。だが、彼はこれをチャンスと見て、BainとPAYDAYギャングに手を差し伸べた。契約?奴は一緒に働くか、Crime.netを永遠に葬り去るかだ。",--Born in South Africa, educated at Lincoln Laboratory, trained under MI5, and now employed by Murkywater. Vernon Locke heads their special cyberwarfare division, which has been tasked with infiltrating Crime.net. Locke has managed this. However, he sees this as an opportunity, and has reached out to Bain and the Payday gang. The deal? Work with him, or he brings Crime.net down forever.
heist_contact_the_butcher = "",--The Butcher
heist_contact_the_butcher_description = "\"肉屋\"の仕事は武器商だ。Gageが\"長期休暇\"をとってる間、彼女はBainらと実り多いビジネス関係を持てることを期待している。",--The Butcher's business is weapons - their procurement, sale and distribution. With Gage on an "extended vacation", she is looking forward to a long and fruitful business relationship with Bain and the PAYDAY gang.
heist_contact_the_dentist = "",--The Dentist
heist_contact_the_dentist_description = "\"歯医者\"についての詳細は殆ど判明していない。 彼が「患者」と呼ぶ、ビッグなお客様達からの依頼を我々に代行させているようだ。 彼は冷静沈着で注意深い策士で、 PAYDAYギャングに関心を持っている。 そしてHoxtonを解放する方法を唯一知っている人物である。",--Little is known about the Dentist. He represents a large clientele whom he refers to as his patients. He is a determined, meticulate planner who has taken a great interest in the PAYDAY gang. He is the only one who knows how to free old Hoxton.
heist_contact_the_elephant = "",--The Elephant
heist_contact_the_elephant_description = "\"The Elephant\"こと\"John Henry Simmons\"は、汚い共産党の市会議員だ。彼はトップにまで繋がる奇妙な\"コネ\"を持ってる。",--John Henry Simmons, called the Elephant by press. A dirty Republican Congressman with mysterious connections that go all the way to the top.
heist_contact_vlad = "",--Vlad
heist_contact_vlad_description = "かつて祖国であるロシアで恐れられていたウクライナ人。 ここ数年のVladは根城の\"ベーカリー\"から、 DCで恐喝や密売を行っている。",--A Ukrainian who used to be a feared enforcer in the Russian motherland, Vlad's been running his own extortion and crime racket in DC out of his local bakery for years.
houston_desc_codex = "",--Dallas younger brother might be able to keep the Hoxton mask, but he's not keeping the name. The consensus among the PAYDAY gang was that from now on, New Hoxton will go by the nicknamed Houston. It's a relatively cheap price to pay to calm Hoxton down and - if anything - partially forgive the PAYDAY gang for leaving him in jail.
jowi_desc_codex = "",--John was a feared Hitman known among some of the largest crime syndicates. After having gone dark for a long time, John recently resurfaced and helped Chains out of a delicate situation. In return, John told Chains he was in need of a crew. How could Chains say no? He invited him into the PAYDAY gang in order to help his old friend.
menu_bodhi_desc_codex = "",--Bodhi is known as one of the greatest legends in the world of crime, but few know the man behind the mask. As the founding father of the Ex-Presidents gang, Bodhi's renowned in the criminal underworld for his extreme athleticism and daring heists. His recent feats of strength in Mumbai and Austria got Bain's attention, granting him an invitation to the PAYDAY gang.
menu_bonnie_desc_codex = "Bonnieはグラスゴーからやってきた。男の心に恐怖を湧き立たせるにはそれだけで十分だろうが、Bonnieはなんと1980年代のグラスゴーからやってきたのだ。この年代と言えば、サッチャーの年代で、もう既に生き辛かった町が更に過酷な物へと変わった時期だ。その結果、決して忘れない、野心のあるスコットランドが出来上がった時代だ。Bonnieはこの時代の人間の一人なのだ。",--Bonnie is from Glasgow. That should be enough to strike fear into a man's heart, but Bonnie is also from 1980's Glasgow. These years, the Thatcher era, made already tough towns even harder, and bred a generation of determined, unforgiving Scots. Bonnie is cut from this cloth.
menu_chico_desc_codex = "",--They don't make 'em like Tony anymore. A fast talker who knows what he wants and how to get it. He's the real deal when the shit hits the fan, a true-born heister. He doesn't back down for anyone and he dishes it out just as hard as he can take it. This guys got balls.
menu_clover_desc_codex = "Cloverは治安の悪い街の劣悪な家庭環境で育った。彼女の先祖達はみな'戦士'だった。そして彼女もまたアイルランドの地位確立に命を削ると決意した。幸運のクローバーを身につける彼女はこう言う 'アイルランド人である事、それは誇りだ'。",--Clover grew up in a rough house in a rough part of town. Her ancestors were fighters in every generation, and she is fiercely dedicated to her Irish heritage. She wears the clovers for luck, as well as a way to say "I'm Irish, and I'm proud".
menu_cn_contact_info = "連絡先データベース",--Contact Database
menu_cn_contact_info_desc = "Crime.netの詳細情報",--Learn more about Crime.net
menu_contacts = "契約者のデータ",--Contacts
menu_continental = "",--The Continental
menu_continental_desc_codex = "",--The Continental is a mysterious institution, a hotel but also a safe haven for professional assassins and others who move in the shadows. Sometimes the Continental has need of services, services that require special talents. This is where the Payday Gang comes into the picture.
menu_dragan_desc_codex = "Draganは元捜査官らしい。ただし、クロアチアのだが。そこでの彼の手段はMPDCがまるで子守でもしていると称されるほどだった。彼はThe Butcherに気に入られ、アメリカへ送り込まれると共にPAYDAYギャングに加わった。最初は彼が本当に信頼出来るのか疑いがあったが、彼の能力と献身に疑う余地はない。",--Dragan may be a former cop, but he's a former Croatian cop, which means his methods make the MPDC look like timid babysitters. He was brought to America and accepted into the PAYDAY gang as a favor to The Butcher. While there were some early suspicions regarding his true loyalties, his ability and commitment are indisputable.
menu_dragon_desc_codex = "青年時代に極道の道に進むまで、Jiroは受け入れられなかった。しかし、そこでも誠実と実力があったにも完全には受け入れられず、最後には裏切られた。刑務所での長い懲役の後、次郎は長いこと行方不明となっていた彼の息子である、Kentoを探しにアメリカに渡って来た。",--In his youth, Jiro was never accepted, until he found his way into the yakuza. Yet even here, despite his loyalty and ability, he was never fully embraced and was ultimately betrayed. Following a lengthy prison term, Jiro has come to America to find his long-lost son, Kento.
menu_ecp = "",--Ethan and Hila
menu_ecp_desc_codex = "",--Ethan and Hila should not be underestimated. You might think they're just a pair of soft video celebrities, but these guys are highly motivated, they need the cash. And Hila's been in the army.
menu_jacket_desc_codex = "",--Although Jacket is the last one to brag - he doesn't speak at all - his achievements in the criminal underworld are widely known. Allegedly, he once wiped out the entire Russian mafia in Miami all on his own. His background in the military and his unflinching attitude towards over-the-top violence has made him an excellent hitman - or "messenger" as some like to call it. For unknown reasons he remains completely mute.
menu_jimmy_desc_codex = "最初は疑ってたが、今は認めよう。JimmyはCrime.netに見合った凶悪なスキルを持った人間だ。彼には限界がない。契約を断ることもなければ、毎日が命日のように生きている。彼は忠実で、予想の斜め上を行った優れた人間だということがわかった。",--I had my doubts at first, I'll admit, but Jimmy has turned out to have all the skills to excel as a heister of Crime.Net caliber. He has no limits, never turning down a contract and lives every day like it's his last. He is loyal and has proven to be an excellent addition I never thought we needed.
menu_max_desc_codex = "",--Sangres is a dangerous man. He spent many years working as an enforcer and assassin for a drug cartel in Monterrey, Mexico. Then one day he decided to defect and crossed the border to the US, looking to make the big bucks. Gage introduced him to the Payday Gang. He's as skilled as he's ruthless and with those revolvers he can really light things up. And yeah... check out that razor-sharp machete.
menu_myh_desc_codex = "",--If Duke weren't a crook, he'd be a Gentleman Adventurer straight out of a 1950s movie. Well educated and read, with a powerful steady voice, he steals more for the thrill and craftsmanship of pulling off a successful heist than any need for monetary sustenance.
menu_playable_characters = "",--The PAYDAY Gang
menu_sokol_desc_codex = "若くしてSokolは伝説的な強盗になれる素質を持っていた。アスリートとしても才能を光らせるSokolは鋭い知能とチームでの自分の役割を常に理解している。彼は恐れ知らずで肉体的だ。そしてこいつはそれを敵に使っていく、例えそれが相手のホッケープレイヤーであれ、SWATのチームであれな。",--Though young, Sokol has everything to become a legendary heister. A gifted athlete, Sokol also possesses keen intelligence and understands his role in a team. He is fearless and physical, and uses this to get amongst the enemy, whether that be a team of hockey players or a team of SWAT.
menu_sydney_desc_codex = "Kelli 'Sydney' Kingは、PAYDAYのギャングの頭に気付いて挑戦しようとした。そして、彼女は間違いなく成功した。 彼女はまだ若く、学ぶことがたくさんあるが、Sydneyは鉄の意志を示し、私の世界に彼女の印を残すことに決めた - 私は非常に尊敬するもの。 そして、今日の子供たちは野心がないと言いますか?",--Kelli 'Sydney' King challenged the PAYDAY gang heads on in an attempt to get noticed and... well, she definitely succeeded. Although she's still young and has a lot to learn, Sydney has showed an iron-will and is determined to leave her mark on our world - something I greatly respect. And they say kids today have no ambitions?
menu_wild_desc_codex = "",--I've had my eyes on the OVERKILL MC operation for quite some time now, and I knew my way in would be through the man called \"Rust\". Together with the Elephant we offered Rust a deal he couldn't turn down, and in return, he proved his new loyalty to Crime.Net by killing off his former friends. And just to seal the deal, we're going to help him retrieve something he cares deeply about. Win-win all around.
old_hoxton_desc_codex = "",--Hoxton is one of the original PAYDAY crew members. After a successful stint of major heists up until 2012, Hoxton was captured by the FBI and sent to prison. In 2014, the PAYDAY gang helped him escape. Ever since he got out, he has been convinced someone set him up.
russian_desc_codex = "",--Dallas is experienced, cunning and methodical. He has no problem working as a part of a team but he isn't the social kind. He will carry out his part in a plan perfectly and expects everyone else to do the same.
spanish_desc_codex = "",--As a teenager, Chains always got into trouble. After years of jumping between foster homes and juvenile institutions, he ended up in the military. There he became an excellent soldier.
