menu_challenge_still_retrieving = "Side jobをCrime.netからダウンロード中",--Downloading Side Jobs from Crime.net
menu_challenge_summary_desc = "Side Jobは、JOB中に一定の条件を達成すると報酬がもらえる、JOBチャレンジです。$NL;デイリー、ウィークリー、マンスリーの3種類が存在し、定期的に更新されます。$NL;また、未達成のSide Jobがあっても、新たなSide Jobを受注することが可能です。$NL;Side Job達成時には、専用のSEが鳴り報酬を受け取れる状態になります。$NL;報酬を受け取ると、Side Jobは更新されるまで追加されません。$NL;$NL;Side Jobは達成すると、黄色で表示され、報酬アイコンを押すことで報酬を受け取ることができます。$NL;$NL;デイリーJOB$NL;24時間に1度追加されるもので、報酬は好きな種類の武器MODをランダムに1つと現金です。$NL;ウィークリーJOB$NL;7日間に1度追加されるもので、報酬はマスクと現金です。$NL;マンスリーJOB$NL;月に1度追加されるもので、報酬は武器MODのステータスブースト又はチームブーストです。",--The side jobs feature is a way to earn rewards by successfully completing specific challenges. There are three types of side jobs: the dailies, weeklies and the monthlies. These side jobs will be updated on regular intervals which means that you will be able to get access to new dailies, weeklies and monthlies as well as be able to complete previously uncompleted ones. As soon as a side job has been completed, a cheering sound can be heard notifying you of this. You can only complete them once, until they are updated$NL;$NL;Once you did what was required of you, the side job will turn yellow. This means you can now claim your reward. To claim it go to the daily, weekly or monthly that is marked yellow and click on each item that is displayed in the reward box to claim it.$NL;$NL;Dailies award you with a random mod for the weapon of your choice and cash. These are replaced every 24 hours.$NL;Weeklies award you with a specified mask and cash. These are replaced every 7 days.$NL;Monthly side jobs awards you with a Stat Boost or Team Boost weapon mod. These are replaced every month.
