menu_challenge_any_100_headshot_kills_desc = "",--Precision and effectiveness can often go hand-in-hand with brutal mercy. We, well most of us, don't take pleasure in the necessary downing of our enemies, so why not ease their suffering with a quick kill?
menu_challenge_art_ghost = "",--Phantom of the Gallery
menu_challenge_art_ghost_desc = "",--Sometimes the best way to prove that thieves like us can be just as cultured as art snobs is to take their precious items nice and quite-like, with no bashing of skulls.
menu_challenge_art_ghost_obj = "Art GalleryをStealthで誰も殺さずにすべての絵を盗み出します。$NL;$NL;この挑戦を完了するためには、最初から最後まで強盗をプレイしなければなりません。",--In the Art Gallery job, steal all marked paintings and leave in stealth without killing anybody. To complete this challenge, you have to have played the heist from start to end.
menu_challenge_clone_1 = "",--Attack of the clones - Bulldozer
menu_challenge_clone_1_desc = "",--There are times you gotta go back for family, no matter the cost, no matter the opposition. It's the only way to right the scales of crime.
menu_challenge_clone_1_obj = "Hoxton BreakoutをOVERKILLの難易度以上で、MutatorのClone Army - Bulldozersを有効化してクリアする。$NL;$NL;この挑戦を完了するためには、最初から最後まで強盗をプレイしなければなりません。",--Complete the Hoxton Breakout job on the OVERKILL difficulty or above, with the Clone Army - Bulldozers mutator active. To complete this challenge, you have to have played the heist from start to end.
menu_challenge_clone_2 = "",--Attack of the clones - Tazer
menu_challenge_clone_2_desc = "",--Go grab your 10-gallon hat and be ready to take some electrocution for the team.
menu_challenge_clone_2_obj = "Big OilをOVERKILLの難易度以上で、MutatorのClone Army - Tasersを有効化してクリアする。$NL;$NL;この挑戦を完了するためには、最初から最後まで強盗をプレイしなければなりません。",--Complete the Big Oil job on the OVERKILL difficulty or above, with the Clone Army - Tasers mutator active. To complete this challenge, you have to have played the heist from start to end.
menu_challenge_clone_3 = "",--Attack of the clones - Shield
menu_challenge_clone_3_desc = "",--Police hiding behind a movable wall when you're trying to shoot at them is just so unsporting.
menu_challenge_clone_3_obj = "WatchdogsをOVERKILLの難易度以上で、MutatorのClone Army - Shieldsを有効化してクリアする。$NL;$NL;この挑戦を完了するためには、最初から最後まで強盗をプレイしなければなりません。",--Complete the Watchdogs job on the OVERKILL difficulty or above, with the Clone Army - Shields mutator active. To complete this challenge, you have to have played the heist from start to end.
menu_challenge_clone_4 = "",--Attack of the clones - Cloaker
menu_challenge_clone_4_desc = "",--"One of the worst fates would be to constantly have to face and flee from wave after wave of the these dishonorable enemies."
menu_challenge_clone_4_obj = "Prison NightmareをOVERKILLの難易度以上で、MutatorのClone Army - Cloakersを有効化してクリアする。$NL;$NL;この挑戦を完了するためには、最初から最後まで強盗をプレイしなければなりません。",--Complete the Prison Nightmare job on the OVERKILL difficulty or above, with the Clone Army - Cloakers mutator active. To complete this challenge, you have to have played the heist from start to end.
menu_challenge_clone_5 = "",--Attack of the clones - Medic
menu_challenge_clone_5_desc = "",--Using thermite to melt your way past an obstacle never gets old. That stuff is just nasty fun. Whackin' the same dumb-ass cops over and over does though. Still, gotta see it through to the end thoruth these guys that just won't stay down.
menu_challenge_clone_5_obj = "First World BankをOVERKILLの難易度以上で、MutatorのClone Army - Medicを有効化してクリアする。$NL;$NL;この挑戦を完了するためには、最初から最後まで強盗をプレイしなければなりません。",--Complete the First World Bank job on the OVERKILL difficulty or above, with the Clone Army - Medic mutator active. To complete this challenge, you have to have played the heist from start to end.
menu_challenge_cookoff_mutated = "",--Extreme Cooking
menu_challenge_cookoff_mutated_desc = "",--"I can brew up a smashingly tasty pot of chili you know, but I doubt even my Five-alarm Habanero Special would be enough to match that chemical intoxocation you are so fond of dealing with.."
menu_challenge_cookoff_mutated_obj = "COOK OFFで少なくとも6個のMutatorを有効化してクリアする。$NL;$NL;この挑戦を完了するためには、最初から最後まで強盗をプレイしなければなりません。",--Complete the Cook Off job with at least 6 mutators active. To complete this challenge, you have to have played the heist from start to end.
menu_challenge_crime_spree_heists = "",--Speedy Spree
menu_challenge_crime_spree_heists_desc = "",--On the six heists of this challenge, my true love gave to me, lots of guns and money, in a lovely Crime Spree.
menu_challenge_crime_spree_heists_obj = "Crime SpreeでJobを6つクリアする。$NL;$NL;この挑戦を完了するためには、最初から最後まで強盗をプレイしなければなりません。",--Complete 6 heists in the Crime Spree. To complete this challenge, you have to have played the heist from start to end.
menu_challenge_critical_100_kills = "",--Target Practice: Critical Hits
menu_challenge_critical_100_kills_desc = "",--Ammunition can, unfortunately, be scarce at times, so it's important to be able to take down the enemy effectively.
menu_challenge_do_no_harm = "",--Do No Harm
menu_challenge_do_no_harm_desc = "",--There's a sadistic kind of fun to be had dragging out the punishment of those who would take us down.
menu_challenge_do_no_harm_obj = "任意のJobでMedicに敵を50回回復させる。",--In any single day of any job, cause Medics to heal enemies 50 times.
menu_challenge_explosion_100_kills = "",--Target Practice: Explosive
menu_challenge_explosion_100_kills_desc = "",--Things that go BOOM and cover everything in big balls of fire can be such great entertainment.
menu_challenge_farm_1 = "",--Not Hard Enough
menu_challenge_farm_6 = "",--Pork Royale
menu_challenge_farm_6_desc = "",--Pulled pork sandwiches got popular again after that gringo serial-killer talked about them in that TV show a few years ago. Don't believe me? Go back and check how many places sold 'em before then. And now I'm hungry. Maybe we stop and get a pig on the next job.
menu_challenge_farm_6_obj = "難易度OVERKILL以上のSLAUGHTERHOUSEで、印が付けられた豚を回収してクリアする。",--In the Slaughterhouse job, find the marked pig, secure it in the container and then finish the heist on OVERKILL or above.
menu_challenge_fwb_no_medics = "",--Geneva Convention
menu_challenge_fwb_no_medics_desc = "",--"Hey, doctors have rights too... even if they're helping scum."
menu_challenge_fwb_no_medics_obj = "",--Complete the First World Bank job on OVERKILL difficulty or above, without anybody ever killing a medic. To complete this challenge, you have to have played the heist from start to end.
menu_challenge_lmg_100_kills = "",--Target Practice: LMGs
menu_challenge_lmg_100_kills_desc = "",--There are situations that require the deft hand of a cold blade, but this one demands the wild and short bursts of death that come from a high rate of fire.
menu_challenge_mallcrasher_stealth = "",--Silent Smash-up
menu_challenge_mallcrasher_stealth_desc = "",--"Hey, it's gonna be just like in that zombie movie... except without all the carnage and blood."
menu_challenge_mallcrasher_stealth_obj = "Mallcrasherをステルスクリアする。$NL;$NL;この挑戦を完了するためには、最初から最後まで強盗をプレイしなくてはならない",--Complete the Mallcrasher job in stealth. To complete this challenge, you have to have played the heist from start to end.
menu_challenge_melee_100_kills = "",--CQC Practice
menu_challenge_melee_100_kills_desc = "",--If action movies of the 1980s taught us one thing, it's that bullets don't last forever and eventually so have to get in close to take out your enemy.
menu_challenge_melee_creep_kills = "",--Self Preservation Instinct
menu_challenge_melee_creep_kills_desc = "",--Gentlemen, choose your implement of skull-bashing and get to making corpses. Just watch out for the exploding bodies.
menu_challenge_menu_challenge_farm_1_desc = "",--Imagine the Mall Santa's most-wanted dream... being able to zip-tie up the parents of all those kids that kneed him in the groin on a given day.
menu_challenge_menu_challenge_farm_1_obj = "STEALING XMASで、クリスマスツリーの周りにある4本の柱の中で10人以上の縛った市民を生きたまま保つ。",--Complete the Stealing Xmas job. While haveing at least 10 zip-tied civilians alive within the 4 pallars around the Christmas Tree.
menu_challenge_menu_challenge_moon_6_desc = "",--"You know, we should go for a hamburger run after we deal with the thing in the slaughter house. No time to stick around for anything unnessesary"
menu_challenge_menu_challenge_moon_6_obj = "難易度Overkill以上のSLAUGHTERHOUSEを、Captain Wintersを残したままクリアする。",--Complete the Slaughterhouse job on the OVERKILL difficulty or above while Captain Winters is still present on the level.
menu_challenge_monthly_overdrill = "",--OVERDRILL
menu_challenge_monthly_overdrill_desc = "",--"Those that say "it's only money" don't know what the hell they're sayin'."
menu_challenge_monthly_overdrill_obj = "難易度Death Wish以上のFIRST WORLD BANKでシークレットであるOVERVAULTに進入する。$NL;$NL;この挑戦を完了するためには、最初から最後まで強盗をプレイしなくてはならない",--In the First World Bank job, solve the PAYDAY: The Heist secret on the Death Wish difficulty or above and enter the OVERVAULT. To complete this challenge, you have to have played the heist from start to end.
menu_challenge_monthly_prison = "",--Prison Nightmare
menu_challenge_monthly_prison_desc = "",--"Four dudes slammin' whatever gets in their way under some hell-raisin' circumstances. It's like some Tarantinoesque slasher movie. Who wants to carve some pumpkins?"
menu_challenge_monthly_prison_obj = "難易度Overkill以上のPrison Nightmareを全クルーが近接武器のみを使用してクリアする。$NL;$NL;この挑戦を完了するためには、最初から最後まで強盗をプレイしなくてはならない",--Complete the Prison Nightmare job on OVERKILL difficulty or above, with all teammates only using melee weapons. To complete this challenge, you have to have played the heist from start to end.
menu_challenge_monthly_tabula = "",--Classic Crime Spree
menu_challenge_monthly_tabula_desc = "",--"Y'know, sometimes I miss the days when all we had was basic, half-crap gear and our own damn hands to get shit done."
menu_challenge_monthly_tabula_obj = "",--Complete a Crime Spree of rank 100 or above, with all heisters using the AMCAR rifle, Chimano 88 pistol, and no skills. To complete this challenge, you have to have played the heist from start to end.
menu_challenge_moon_6 = "",--Christmas Party
menu_challenge_safehouse_raid_weekly = "",--Safehouse Defender
menu_challenge_safehouse_raid_weekly_desc = "",--"There's no place like home. We got trouble comin' to raid our flat and they aren't no bloody wizards."
menu_challenge_safehouse_raid_weekly_obj = "",--Successfully defend the safehouse in the Safehouse Raid job 3 times. To complete this challenge, you have to have played the heist from start to end.
menu_challenge_safehouse_td = "",--Safehouse TD
menu_challenge_safehouse_td_desc = "",--"Never send a micro-wave to guard your front door. Tripwire axes and motion detectors are all dandy but they don't amount to much unless you got proper firepower as well. Let see if we can't upgrade our defences somewhat."
menu_challenge_safehouse_td_obj = "",--Complete the Safehouse Raid on OVERKILL or above, with everybody using only Sentry Guns to kill enemies. To complete this challenge, you have to have played the heist from start to end.
menu_challenge_sentry_100_kills = "",--Target Practice: Sentry Practice
menu_challenge_sentry_100_kills_desc = "",--Sometimes it's better to let machines take over a job. Now, that doesn't mean we get to be lazy about it, but if things go right, we get the job done faster.
menu_challenge_sniper_100_kills = "",--Target Practice: Sniper Rifle
menu_challenge_sniper_100_kills_desc = "",--While getting your hands dirty is part of the job, there are occasions when you need to keep your distance and go for the elegance of a sniper-kill.
menu_challenge_winters_mutated = "",--Captain of Clones
menu_challenge_winters_mutated_desc = "",--It's not often we get a singular nemesis to overcome, so when we do, it could almost be thought of as a blessing.
menu_challenge_winters_mutated_obj = "",--Defeat Captain Winters while on any job, while the Hydra mutator is active.
menu_challenge_xmas_all = "",--Christmas Calamity
menu_challenge_xmas_all_desc = "",--I'm dreaming of a Christmas where the cops all drink some bad eggnog and stay out of our way for a change.
menu_challenge_xmas_all_obj = "",--Complete the White Xmas, Santa's Workshop, and Stealing Xmas jobs. To complete this challenge, you have to have played the heist from start to end.
menu_challenge_any_25_shield_kills = "",--Build a raft of shields
menu_challenge_any_25_shield_kills_desc = "何かしらの武器を使ってShieldを25体倒せ。",--Kill 25 shields using weapons of your choice.
menu_challenge_any_25_sniper_kills = "",--Sniperino
menu_challenge_any_25_sniper_kills_desc = "何かしらの武器を使ってSniperを25体倒せ。",--Kill 25 snipers using weapons of your choice.
menu_challenge_any_25_spooc_kills = "",--Into the Dark
menu_challenge_any_25_spooc_kills_desc = "何かしらの武器を使ってCloakerを25体倒せ。",--Kill 25 Cloakers using weapons of your choice.
menu_challenge_any_25_tank_kills = "",--Bulldozer
menu_challenge_any_25_tank_kills_desc = "何かしらの武器を使ってBulldozerを25体倒せ。",--Kill 25 Bulldozers using weapons of your choice.
menu_challenge_any_25_taser_kills = "",--Greased Lightning
menu_challenge_any_25_taser_kills_desc = "何かしらの武器を使ってTeserを25体倒せ。",--Kill 25 tasers using weapons of your choice.
menu_challenge_any_300_kills = "",--Mass murderer
menu_challenge_any_300_kills_desc = "何かしらの武器を使って敵を300体倒せ。",--Kill 300 enemies with the weapons of your choice.
menu_challenge_any_50_headshot_kills = "",--In the head!
menu_challenge_any_50_headshot_kills_desc = "何かしらの武器を使ってヘッドショットで敵を50体倒せ。",--There's that one spot where you know it hurts the most... Kill 50 enemies with headshots using weapons of your choice.
menu_challenge_any_6_jobs = "",--Record low crime rate
menu_challenge_any_6_jobs_desc = "ここ数十年の犯罪率低下を塗り替えるんだ。難易度不問で好きなjobを6つクリアしろ。",--Reports have come in that the crime rate is at its lowest point this decade. Lets do something about that, finish 6 jobs on any difficulty.
menu_challenge_any_6_jobs_objective = "Jobs 完了度: $progress;/$max_progress;",--Jobs completed: $progress;/$max_progress;
menu_challenge_assault_rifle_100_kills = "戦闘訓練:アサルトライフル",--Target Practice: Assault Rifle
menu_challenge_assault_rifle_100_kills_desc = "アサルトライフルカテゴリの武器を使って敵を100体倒せ。",--Kill 100 enemies using only assault rifles.
menu_challenge_bain_4_jobs = "",--Bain it up!
menu_challenge_bain_4_jobs_desc = "Bainがお前たちの力を必要としている。Bainのjobを難易度不問で4つクリアしろ。",--Bain is desperate for your attention. Finish 4 of Bain's jobs on any difficulty.
menu_challenge_bain_4_jobs_objective = "Jobs 完了度: $progress;/$max_progress;",--Jobs completed: $progress;/$max_progress;
menu_challenge_big_deal = "",--Big Deal
menu_challenge_big_deal_desc = "The ElephantはFraming Frameの仕事に期待している。ミスは許されないぞ。9つの絵画を取引しろ。",--The Elephant has a lot riding on the Framing Frame job. Leave no room for error. Trade nine paintings.
menu_challenge_big_deal_objective = "FRAMING FRAME DAY2で、9つの絵画を取引しろ。",--On day 2 of the Framing Frame job, trade 9 paintings.
menu_challenge_bob_4 = "",--Storage Hunter
menu_challenge_bob_4_desc = "The Elephantは不正な選挙運動のために協力者を必要としている。Election DayのDay2で追加報酬を全て回収する。",--The Elephant always needs a few extra dollars for his crooked campaigns. Grab all the additional loot in the storage bins in Election Day 2.
menu_challenge_bob_4_objective = "Election DayのDay2で、追加報酬を全て回収しろ。",--On day 2 of the Election Day job, steal all of the extra loot in the storage bins.
menu_challenge_bob_8 = "",--Hot Lava 2.0
menu_challenge_bob_8_desc = "The Dentistがイカれたテストを出してきた。彼はElection Day (Day1)で警報を作動させず、地面に触ることなくコンピュータを使うお前らを見たがっている。",--The Dentist has an unusual test for you. He wants to see you use the computers in Election Day (Day 1) without setting off the alarm or touching the ground.
menu_challenge_bob_8_objective = "ELECTION DAY DAY1にて、ステルス中に一度も地面に足を付けずにコンピュータを操作しろ。",--On day 1 of the Election Day job, use the computer in stealth without ever touching the ground.
menu_challenge_butcher_4_jobs = "",--The Butcher needs you!
menu_challenge_butcher_4_jobs_desc = "The Butcherがお前たちの力を欲している。Butcherのjobを難易度不問で4つクリアしろ。",--The Butcher is desperate for your attention. Finish 4 of The Butcher's jobs on any difficulty.
menu_challenge_butcher_4_jobs_objective = "Jobs 完了度: $progress;/$max_progress;",--Jobs completed: $progress;/$max_progress;
menu_challenge_caribbean_pirate = "",--Caribbean Pirate
menu_challenge_caribbean_pirate_desc = "",--The Mendoza's want to show the Cobra's what it means to play in the big leagues. Take them four meth bags on Rats (Day 2), but steal the payment instead.
menu_challenge_caribbean_pirate_objective = "RATS DAY2で、追加のMethを取引現場に運びつつ、用意された報酬を盗め。",--On day 2 of the Rat job, bring additional meth bags to the trade, but steal your payment instead.
menu_challenge_charliesierra_1 = "",--Sewer Rats
menu_challenge_charliesierra_1_desc = "難易度Overkill以上ですべての獲物をGO Bankから持ち出したいが、どこの報道ヘリにも見つからないようにしろ。下水道だけを使え。",--We want to haul every bag of cash out of the GO Bank on OVERKILL or harder, but stay out of the eye of any press choppers. Use the sewers only.
menu_challenge_charliesierra_1_objective = "難易度Overkill以上のGO BANKにて、下水道を通ってすべてのバッグを確保しろ。",--In the GO Bank job, complete the heist having secured all bags of cash via the sewers on the OVERKILL difficulty or above.
menu_challenge_charliesierra_5 = "",--All Eggs in One Basket
menu_challenge_charliesierra_5_desc = "Skyhook回収システムが、潜在的な新しい仕事に対してどれほど実用性があるか確認したい。GO BANKに行って、全てのバッグをSkyhookで回収してくれ。",--I want to show some potential new contacts just how effective the skyhook system can be. Head to GO Bank, and extract every bag of cash with the skyhook.
menu_challenge_charliesierra_5_objective = "GO Bankで全てのバッグをSkyhookで回収しろ。",--In the GO Bank job, have the plane pick up all bags of cash with the skyhook.
menu_challenge_choose_global_value = "武器のタグ",--Weapon Tag
menu_challenge_choose_weapon = "武器",--Weapon
menu_challenge_choose_weapon_category = "武器の種類",--Weapon category
menu_challenge_choose_weapon_mod = "武器MOD",--Weapon mod
menu_challenge_claim_reward_title = "獲得する報酬: ランダムな武器MOD",--Claim reward: Random weapon mod
menu_challenge_deer_7 = "",--Impossible, It Can't Be. Is It?
menu_challenge_deer_7_desc = "",--God knows why, but someone is willing to pay big bucks for Almir's Toast. I'm not going to complain. Get into White Xmas and secure that out of there.
menu_challenge_deer_7_objective = "WHITE XMASにて、Almirのトーストを回収しろ。",--In the White Xmas job, secure the rare Almir's Toast.
menu_challenge_dentist_4_jobs = "",--Dentist appointment!
menu_challenge_dentist_4_jobs_desc = "The Dentistがお前たちに仕事を頼みたいそうだ。The Dentistのjobを難易度不問で4つクリアしろ。",--The Dentist is desperate for your attention. Finish 4 of The Dentist's jobs on any difficulty.
menu_challenge_dentist_4_jobs_objective = "Jobs 完了度: $progress;/$max_progress;",--Jobs completed: $progress;/$max_progress;
menu_challenge_diamonds_are_forever = "",--Diamonds Are Forever
menu_challenge_diamonds_are_forever_desc = "俺たちは宝石を手早く頂く必要ある。Jewelry Storeで逃走車を離脱させずに宝石を4つ盗め。",--We need to get the jewels out fast, so I need you to bag and secure four bags from the Jewelry Store without the escape car bailing.
menu_challenge_diamonds_are_forever_objective = "JEWELRY STOREで、逃走車が離脱する前にバッグを4つ盗みだし確保しろ。",--In the Jewelry store job, steal and secure 4 bags without the escape car leaving the first time.
menu_challenge_doctor_fantastic = "",--Doctor Fantastic
menu_challenge_doctor_fantastic_desc = "",--The Elephant wants to send a message to Prof. Rossy. Not only does he want the engine stolen, but he wants that brainiac to know that we know his shit. Get the right engine on the first try.
menu_challenge_doctor_fantastic_objective = "BIG OIL DAY2で、最初に選んだ正しいエンジンで強盗を完遂しろ。",--On day 2 of the Big Oil job, complete the heist with the first engine being correct.
menu_challenge_earn_2000k_offshore_cash = "",--For the pension fund
menu_challenge_earn_2000k_offshore_cash_desc = "海外口座$2,000,000分を強奪しろ。",--Earn 2 000 000 in offshore money.
menu_challenge_earn_250k_cash = "",--Earn some pocket money
menu_challenge_earn_250k_cash_desc = "インスタントキャッシュを$250,000分を強奪しろ。",--Earn 250 000 in spendable cash.
menu_challenge_elephant_4_jobs = "",--Longing for attention
menu_challenge_elephant_4_jobs_desc = "The Elephantがお前たちの力を必要としている。The Elephantのjobを難易度不問で4つクリアしろ。",--The Elephant is desperate for your attention. Finish 4 of The Elephant's jobs on any difficulty.
menu_challenge_elephant_4_jobs_objective = "Jobs 完了度: $progress;/$max_progress;",--Jobs completed: $progress;/$max_progress;
menu_challenge_frog_1 = "",--Tabula Rasa
menu_challenge_frog_1_desc = "",--The press will be watching the Hoxton trial, so there will be eyes on his breakout. Do it with style. No skills, sharp suits, Golden AK.762's and Chicago Typewriters. Oh, and OVERKILL style too.
menu_challenge_frog_1_objective = "難易度OVERKILL以上のHOXTON BREAKOUTを、クルー全員がスキルを一切取得せずに、スーツ·Golden AK.762·Chicago Typewriterを装備してクリアしろ。",--In the Hoxton Breakout job, complete the heist on OVERKILL difficulty or$NL;above with each crew member using no skills, wearing suits, wielding$NL;Golden AK.762 rifles and Chicago Typewriter submachine guns.
menu_challenge_gage2_1 = "",--Doctor Miserable
menu_challenge_gage2_1_desc = "",--Don't tip your hand to the Professor during Big Oil (Day 2). Make sure the last engine you haul out is the correct one, and do it OVERKILL.
menu_challenge_gage2_1_objective = "難易度Overkill以上のBIG OIL DAY2にて、最後に正しいエンジンを回収してクリアしろ。",--On day 2 of the Big Oil job, complete the heist with the last engine being correct on the OVERKILL difficulty or above.
menu_challenge_gage4_5 = "",--Shotgun 101
menu_challenge_gage4_5_desc = "The Butcherが本物の銃の腕を見せてほしいと言っている。ショットガンで最低50体の敵を倒し、命中率101%以上にしろ。",--The Butcher wants to see a weapon masterclass. Kill at least 50 enemies and attain a hit accuracy of 101% or above with any shotgun.
menu_challenge_gage4_5_objective = "ショットガンで最低50体の敵を倒し、命中率101%以上にしろ。",--Kill at least 50 enemies and get 101% accuracy or above using any shotgun.
menu_challenge_get_weapon_mod_reward = "ランダムな武器MODを獲得する",--Claim random weapon mod
menu_challenge_going_all_in = "",--I'm Going All-in!
menu_challenge_going_all_in_desc = "勝者になるには、大きな賭けをしなくちゃな。Nightclubのポーカーの机の上に現金のバッグを乗っけてやれ。",--You need to be a big gambler to be a big winner. Throw a bag of cash on the poker table in the Nightclub.
menu_challenge_going_all_in_objective = "Nightclubにてポーカーのテーブルを現金の詰まったバッグでいっぱいにしろ。",--In the Nightclub job, put a bag filled with money on the poker table.
menu_challenge_halloween_1 = "",--I Am the One Who Knocks
menu_challenge_halloween_1_desc = "",--We can't risk any interference while we cook up a little product. Produce three bags worth of meth on Rats (Day 1) without letting a single fucking cop in the house.
menu_challenge_halloween_1_objective = "RATS DAY1にて、警察を一人も家に入れずにMETHを3個作れ。",--On day 1 of the Rats job, cook 3 bags worth of meth without letting any law enforcer enter the house.
menu_challenge_halloween_2 = "",--Full Measure
menu_challenge_halloween_2_desc = "",--The secret to successful cooking is using the right ingredients in the right quantities. Hmm... can you smell something burning?
menu_challenge_halloween_2_objective = "難易度OVERKILL以上のRATS DAY1にて、精製機を爆発させずMETHを7個作り全て確保する。",--On day 1 of the Rats job, cook and secure 7 bags worth of meth without blowing up the lab on the OVERKILL difficulty or above.
menu_challenge_halloween_3 = "",--Afraid of the Dark
menu_challenge_halloween_3_desc = "",--The Elephant wants an uninterrupted feed when you hit the Senators apartment on Framing Frame (Day 3). Make sure the pigs don't pull the power.
menu_challenge_halloween_3_objective = "FRAMING FRAME DAY3のPlan Bで、敵に電源を落とされずにハッキングを完了させろ。",--On day 3 of the Framing Frame job, while doing plan B, don't let law enforcers pull the power.
menu_challenge_hector_4_jobs = "",--Hector begs you for mercy
menu_challenge_hector_4_jobs_desc = "Hectorがお前たちの力を必要としている。Hectorのjobを難易度不問で4つクリアしろ。",--Hector is desperate for your attention. Finish 4 of Hector's jobs on any difficulty.
menu_challenge_hector_4_jobs_objective = "Jobs 完了度: $progress;/$max_progress;",--Jobs completed: $progress;/$max_progress;
menu_challenge_i_knew_what_i_was_doing_was_wrong = "",--I Knew What I Did Was Wrong
menu_challenge_i_knew_what_i_was_doing_was_wrong_desc = "",--The Elephant needs every cent for his campaigns. Loot all of the ATM machines in the basement of Big Oil (Day 1).
menu_challenge_i_knew_what_i_was_doing_was_wrong_objective = "BIG OIL DAY1で、地下室の全てのATMを開けて中身を盗め",--On day 1 of the Big Oil job, enter the basement, open the ATMs and take the loot.
menu_challenge_i_wasnt_even_there = "",--I Wasn't Even There!
menu_challenge_i_wasnt_even_there_desc = "",--In this uncertain economy, the price of gold is rocketing. Zip-line it out of the senator's apartment in Framing Frame (Day 3) without tripping the alarm.
menu_challenge_i_wasnt_even_there_objective = "FRAMING FRAME DAY3で、アラームを作動させずにzip-lineで金塊を送れ。",--On day 3 of the Framing Frame job, send the gold by zip-line without ever tripping the alarm.
menu_challenge_kills_objective = "",--Enemies killed: $progress;/$max_progress;
menu_challenge_kosugi_3 = "",--I Will Take With Impunity
menu_challenge_kosugi_3_desc = "",--Variety is the spice of life, huh? The Elephant is refurbishing his pad. He wants one of every piece of loot from the Murkywater warehouse in Shadow Raid.
menu_challenge_kosugi_3_objective = "SHADOW RAIDで、現金、金塊、コカイン、芸術品、絵画、武器、サーバーを含む、回収可能なものをすべて1つずつ確保しろ",--In the Shadow Raid job, secure a piece of every available type of loot, including money, gold, cocaine, artifact, painting, weapons and server.
menu_challenge_kosugi_4 = "",--I Will Walk Faceless Among Men
menu_challenge_kosugi_4_desc = "",--The Dentist has a buyer ready for the samurai armor locked away in the Murky warehouse in Shadow Raid. A big movie director, apparently. Lights, camera, action, guys.
menu_challenge_kosugi_4_objective = "SHADOW RAIDで、Samurai Armorのすべての部品を確保しろ",--In the Shadow Raid job, secure all 4 pieces of the samurai armor.
menu_challenge_kosugi_5 = "",--I Am Ninja
menu_challenge_kosugi_5_desc = "",--Gage is feeling greedy, but is willing to reward generously. He's asking for sixteen pieces of loot from the Murkywater warehouse in Shadow Raid. Also, he wants all of the samurai armor.
menu_challenge_kosugi_5_objective = "SHADOW RAIDで、バッグを16個とSamurai Armorのすべての部品のバッグ計20個を確保しろ",--In the Shadow Raid job, secure 16 bags of random loot and all 4 pieces of$NL;the samurai armor.
menu_challenge_lets_do_this = "",--Let's do Th...
menu_challenge_lets_do_this_desc = "",--Vlad is one crazy motherfucker. He's also an impatient motherfucker. Fetch him that tiara in Ukrainian Job in thirty-five seconds or less.
menu_challenge_lets_do_this_objective = "UKRAINIAN JOBで、35秒以内に強盗を完遂しろ。",--In the Ukrainian job, complete the heist within 35 seconds.
menu_challenge_loot_drop = "",--Loot Drop Cards
menu_challenge_lord_of_war = "",--Lord of War
menu_challenge_lord_of_war_desc = "",--Gage has been asked to fulfill a large order of weapons, and will pay top dollar for anything we can recover. Secure all of the weapons from the Firestarter (Day 1) airport.
menu_challenge_lord_of_war_objective = "FIRESTARTER DAY1で、格納庫にある武器を全て盗め。",--On day 1 of the Firestarter job, steal all the weapons from the hangar.
menu_challenge_melee_kills = "戦闘訓練:近接武器",--Target Practice: Melee weapon
menu_challenge_melee_kills_desc = "近接武器を使って敵を35体倒せ。",--Kill 35 enemies using only melee weapons.
menu_challenge_monthly_firestarter = "",--Nostalgia
menu_challenge_monthly_firestarter_desc = "",--Nostalgic people prefer to only think about what was good back in the day, easily forgetting the bad days. Like when you're robbing a bank with shoddy weapons and poor armor.
menu_challenge_monthly_firestarter_objective = "難易度OVERKILL以上のFIRESTARTERを全てのメンバーがスキル無しでスーツ·AMCAR·Chimano 88を用いてクリア。",--Complete the Firestarter job on OVERKILL or above with your crew using only the AMCAR Rifle, Chimano 88 Pistol, the Two-piece Suit and no skills.
menu_challenge_monthly_rats = "",--Old Memories
menu_challenge_monthly_rats_desc = "",--Dallas is thinking about the good old days and he would appreciate it if you did that too.
menu_challenge_monthly_rats_objective = "難易度OVERKILL以上のRATSを全てのメンバーがスキル無しでスーツ·AMCAR·Chimano 88を用いてクリア",--Complete the Rats job on OVERKILL or above using only AMCAR Rifle, Chimano 88 Pistol, the Two-piece Suit and no skills.
menu_challenge_monthly_reward = "",--Team Boost or random Stat Boost.
menu_challenge_monthly_shadowraid = "",--Shadow Dance
menu_challenge_monthly_shadowraid_desc = "",--Just like old people shadow dances to their favorite song played from a grammophone, heisters bring out their first kit to remember the old times.
menu_challenge_monthly_shadowraid_objective = "難易度OVERKILL以上のSHADOW RAIDを全てのメンバーがスキル無しでスーツ·AMCAR·Chimano 88を用いてクリア。",--Complete the Shadow Raid on OVERKILL or above using only AMCAR Rifle, Chimano 88 Pistol, the Two-piece Suit and no skills.
menu_challenge_num_owned_mods = "この武器で利用できる $count; 種類のMODの内 $inv_count; 種類を所持しています。",--You own $inv_count; of $count; of available mods for this weapon.
menu_challenge_pink_panther = "",--Painting Yourself Into a Corner
menu_challenge_pink_panther_desc = "",--Art can really pay, and I have a guy who will pay for it. Steal all of the sold paintings in Framing Frame (Day 1). He's antsy, though, so do not be seen.
menu_challenge_pink_panther_objective = "FRAMING FRAME DAY1で、発見されずに全ての絵画を盗め。",--On day 1 of the Framing Frame job, steal all sold paintings without being seen.
menu_challenge_pistol_100_kills = "戦闘訓練:ピストル",--Target Practice: Pistol
menu_challenge_pistol_100_kills_desc = "ピストルカテゴリの武器を使って敵を100体倒せ。",--Kill 100 enemies using only pistols.
menu_challenge_safehouse_daily_reward = "",--Continental Coins to purchase safe house upgrades and weapon mods.
menu_challenge_short_fuse = "",--Short Fuse
menu_challenge_short_fuse_desc = "",--We want the cash, but we don't want anyone to know we have the cash. Get seven bags of money in Rats (Day 3) without defusing a bomb.
menu_challenge_short_fuse_objective = "RATS DAY3で、C4を解除せずにバッグを7つ手に入れろ。",--On day 3 of the Rat job, get away with 7 bags without defusing any bombs.
menu_challenge_shotgun_100_kills = "戦闘訓練:ショットガン",--Target Practice: Shotgun
menu_challenge_shotgun_100_kills_desc = "ショットガンカテゴリの武器を使って敵を100体倒せ。",--Kill 100 enemies using only shotguns.
menu_challenge_slakt_1 = "",--Speedlock Holmes
menu_challenge_slakt_1_desc = "",--We're going to send a special fuck-you to the authorities. On Election Day, tag the correct truck and get out in 60 seconds.
menu_challenge_slakt_1_objective = "ELECTION DAY DAY1にて、開始から1分以内に正しいトラックにGPS発信機を設置しろ。",--On day 1 of the Election Day job, tag the right truck and leave within a minute of the start of the heist.
menu_challenge_slakt_2 = "",--Nothing Out of the Ordinary
menu_challenge_slakt_2_desc = "",--Show Gen-Sec just how basic their security really is. Answer 4 pagers, yourself, within 90 seconds.
menu_challenge_slakt_2_objective = "一人で最初のPager応答から90秒以内に4人のPager応答を行え。",--Answer 4 pagers by yourself within 90 seconds from first to last pager.
menu_challenge_slakt_3 = "",--Situation Normal
menu_challenge_slakt_3_desc = "",--The Dentist doesn't want the FBI to look into revising their own security protocols. Don't ask why. Just complete Hoxton Breakout Day 2 without using any keycards.
menu_challenge_slakt_3_objective = "難易度OVERKILL以上のHOXTON BREAKOUT DAY2にて、Keycardを一切使用せずにクリアしろ。",--In the Hoxton Breakout job, complete day 2 without using a single keycard on OVERKILL difficulty or above.
menu_challenge_slakt_4 = "",--Keep the Party Going
menu_challenge_slakt_4_desc = "",--Vlad's niece is celebrating her sweet sixteenth. The DJ she wanted isn't willing to play at her party. Change his mind by going to the Nightclub, tying him and bringing him to the van.
menu_challenge_slakt_4_objective = "NIGHTCLUBにてDJを拘束し、逃走車の横の脱出地点まで連れてこい。",--In the Nightclub job, zip-tie the DJ and bring him to the escape zone by the escape van.
menu_challenge_slakt_5 = "",--It's Getting Hot in Here
menu_challenge_slakt_5_desc = "",--In Firestarter Day 3, I want to make sure that not a single dollar is recoverable. The whole crew must remain in the vault until all the money is burnt. On Deathwish.
menu_challenge_slakt_5_objective = "難易度DEATH WISHのFIRESTARTER DAY3にて、資金が燃え尽きるまでプレイヤー全員が金庫内に留まれ。",--In the Firestarter job, complete day 3 with you and your crew staying inside the vault while all of the money burns out on the Death Wish difficulty or above.
menu_challenge_smg_100_kills = "戦闘訓練:サブマシンガン",--Target Practice: Submachine Gun
menu_challenge_smg_100_kills_desc = "サブマシンガンカテゴリの武器を使って敵を100体倒せ。",--Kill 100 enemies using only submachine guns.
menu_challenge_spending_cash_earned = "",--Offshore cash earned: $$progress; / $$max_progress;
menu_challenge_stat_boost = "",--Random Stat Boost
menu_challenge_the_first_line = "",--The First Line
menu_challenge_the_first_line_desc = "The Elephantは希少なスポーツの記念品を収集している。FIRESTARTER(DAY 3)の貸金庫にOVERKILLホッケーチームのレアなポスターが保管されている。回収しろ!",--The Elephant collects rare sports memorabilia. There is a rare poster of the Overkill hockey team in one of the deposit boxes in Firestarter (Day 3). Recover it!
menu_challenge_the_first_line_objective = "FIRESTARTER DAY3で、OVERKILLホッケーチームのレアポスターを見つけろ。",--On day 3 of the Firestarter job, find the rare hockey poster of the OVERKILL hockey team.
menu_challenge_the_wire = "",--Guessing Game
menu_challenge_the_wire_desc = "The ElephantはFBIが平穏な状態であり続けることを望んでいる。FIRESTARTERのDAY2を警報を鳴らさず、コンピュータをハッキングしないでクリアする。",--The Elephant wants to keep things quiet down at the bureau. Finish Firestarter (Day 2) without setting off the alarm or hacking a computer.
menu_challenge_the_wire_objective = "FIRESTARTER DAY2で、コンピュータをハッキングせずにステルスを完遂しろ。",--On day 2 of the Firestarter job, complete the heist in stealth without hacking the computer.
menu_challenge_vlad_4_jobs = "",--Vlad is mad!
menu_challenge_vlad_4_jobs_desc = "Vladがお前たちの力を必要としている。Vladのjobを難易度不問で4つクリアしろ。",--Vlad is desperate for your attention. Finish 4 of Vlad's jobs on any difficulty.
menu_challenge_vlad_4_jobs_objective = "Jobs 完了度: $progress;/$max_progress;",--Jobs completed: $progress;/$max_progress;
menu_challenge_voff_1 = "",--Saint Francis
menu_challenge_voff_1_desc = "",--There's a line one must never cross. And it's not hurting pigs - it's hurting dogs. They're man's best friend and unlike humans they are loyal and obedient. So it's not more than fair that we will hunt you down for even looking at a loveable little dachshund or schnauzer in the wrong way.
menu_challenge_voff_1_objective = "難易度OVERKILL以上のBANK HEISTの駐車場で2人のチンピラを探し、殺すこと無く彼らをバンの隣に連れて来た後にクリアする。",--Complete the Bank Heist job after finding the 2 punks in the parking lot and bringing them next to the van, without letting them get away or die on the OVERKILL difficulty or above.
menu_challenge_voff_2 = "",--High Times
menu_challenge_voff_2_desc = "",--Getting ahold of drugs might be a pain, but it's worth it once it's done. If you manage to not get killed in the process. The Butcher is keen, however, to get all meth available. So don't spill it and stay alive!"
menu_challenge_voff_2_objective = "THE BOMB:DOCKYARDで2個のMethを作り、回収する。",--In the The Bomb: Dockyard job, cook 2 bags of meth and secure them.
menu_challenge_voff_3 = "",--Looting in the Dark
menu_challenge_voff_3_desc = "",--Jimmy is all high on blow and has his mind set on \"glorifious swagger stuff\" as he screams in a drug frenzy without a seeming end. Murky Station is full of loot. So get it, get out and don't kill anyone.
menu_challenge_voff_3_objective = "難易度OVERKILL以上のMURKY STATIONで、誰も殺さずに全てのLootを確保してクリアする。",--Complete the Murky Station job by finding and securing all loot without killing anyone on the OVERKILL difficulty or above.
menu_challenge_voff_4 = "",--Mellon
menu_challenge_voff_4_desc = "",--One does not simply board a plane, kill the hostiles, stay alive and manage to find the nine rings given to kings from all the corners of the world. But worth trying.
menu_challenge_voff_4_objective = "BIRTH OF SKYで、9つの指輪を見つける。",--In the Birth of Sky job, find all 9 rings.
menu_challenge_voff_5 = "",--Kiss the Chef
menu_challenge_voff_5_desc = "",--Cooking can be relaxing as hell. Hanging out at the stove and stir up some good stuff that's just gonna be so darn tasty. Just add a bit of hydrochloric acid and get a whiff of that fantastic stew.
menu_challenge_voff_5_objective = "難易度OVERKILL以上のCOOK OFFで25個のMethを作る。",--In the Cook Off job, cook 25 bags of meth on the OVERKILL difficulty or above.
menu_challenge_xmas_walking_nightmare = "",--The Walking Nightmare
menu_challenge_xmas_walking_nightmare_desc = "",--"So, last night I had this dream about a skeleton in a Santa suit. But when he took it off, it wasn't a skeleton, but a King Cloaker. No idea how that's supposed to work. Dreams are some weird-ass shit."
menu_challenge_xmas_walking_nightmare_obj = "MutatorのWaking Nightmareが有効の時、White Xmas、Santa's Workshop、またはStealing Xmasのいずれかのジョブを完了します。$NL;$NL;この挑戦を完了するためには、最初から最後まで強盗をプレイしなければなりません。",--While the Waking Nightmare mutator is active, complete any of the White Xmas, Santa's Workshop, or Stealing Xmas jobs. To complete this challenge, you have to have played the heist from start to end.
menu_challenge_yeah_hes_a_gold_digger = "",--Yeah He's a Gold Digger
menu_challenge_yeah_hes_a_gold_digger_desc = "詐欺師から身を守るため、Vladは正確な計測をするために純金の延べ棒を必要としている。どうやらFOUR STORESのマネージャーが金庫に保管しているらしい。",--To help protect against counterfeiters, Vlad needs an ingot of pure gold to measure its precise weight. We have heard that a manager at Four Stores has one in a safe.
menu_challenge_yeah_hes_a_gold_digger_objective = "FOUR STORESで、金庫から金の延べ棒を見つけろ。",--In the Four Stores job, find a gold bar in a safe.
menu_challenge_you_shall_not_pass = "",--You Shall Not Pass!
menu_challenge_you_shall_not_pass_desc = "警察に我々のなわばりの為に戦うとメッセージを送れ。脱出するまで橋に警官を突入させるな。",--Send a message to the cops that we fight for our territory. Don't let a single cop set foot on the bridge before you escape.
menu_challenge_you_shall_not_pass_objective = "Overpass escapeにて、脱出可能になるまで警官を橋に突入させるな。",--In the Overpass escape, don't let the cops set foot on the bridge before you can escape.
daily_akimbo = "",--Hong Kong Gun Fu
daily_akimbo_desc = "",--Show John Wick that you can handle a pair of guns.
daily_akimbo_objective = "アキンボとサプレッサー付きのピストルだけを使って命中精度80%以上でクリアする。ステルス可。",--Complete a job with an accuracy of 80% or above using only Akimbo primary weapons and a silenced pistol as a secondary weapon.
daily_art = "",--Artsy Fartsy
daily_art_desc = "全ての絵画をHoustonが欲しがっている。インテリアにするつもりらしい",--Houston wants all the paintings. For interior decoration, you know.
daily_art_objective = "ART GALLERYで全ての絵画を盗み出す。",--Steal all the paintings from the art gallery.
daily_cake = "",--Bodhi's Bodies
daily_cake_desc = "",--Just a quick scan. Then another one. Then another, and another.
daily_cake_objective = "難易度OVERKILL以上のBOILING POINTを20分以内に4人の死体をスキャンしてからクリアする。$NL;$NL;ジョブの最初から最後までプレイしないとこのサイドジョブは達成できない。",--Finish Boiling Point on OVERKILL in less than 20 minutes after scanning all 4 bodies. To complete this daily, you have to have played the job from start to finish.
daily_candy = "",--Nose Candy
daily_candy_desc = "",--Jimmy would like you to help refill his stash. No - he doesn't use that much, but you know, for a rainy day, or the apocalypse.
daily_candy_objective = "計$max_progress;個のコカインを確保する。",--Secure $max_progress; bags of Cocaine.
daily_candy_progress = "",--Bags of Cocaine Secured
daily_classics = "",--A Trip Down Memory Lane
daily_classics_desc = "",--Dallas is feeling nostalgic. Help him take a trip down memory lane!
daily_classics_objective = "クラシックJOBを$max_progress;つクリアする。",--Finish $max_progress; Classic Heists.
daily_classics_progress = "",--Classic Heists Completed
daily_coke_run = "",--Cocaine Rush
daily_coke_run_desc = "",--Rust thinks it'd be a shame to see all that coke wasted. Quick, rush for it!
daily_coke_run_objective = "難易度MAYHEM以上のHOTLINE MIAMIのDay2で、コカインが一つでも処理される前にCommisarのセーフルームに辿り着く。",--On day 2 of the Hotline Miami job, reach the Commisar's(sic) saferoom before he can destroy any bags of cocaine, on the MAYHEM difficulty or above.
daily_discord = "",--Cop vs Cop
daily_discord_desc = "",--Even a cop can be turned to crime. Ask Bain. Ask Dragan.
daily_discord_objective = "Jobを$max_progress;回、警官を味方につけてこなせ",--Finish $max_progress; heist with a converted cop.
daily_discord_progress = "",--Heists Completed
daily_dosh = "",--Nu Muny
daily_dosh_desc = "",--If you want to be sure it's genuine and proper, better make it yourself. Bring Sydney some money.
daily_dosh_objective = "COUNTERFEITで最低$1,000,000分の偽札を印刷する。",--Print money to a value of at least $1,000,000 on Counterfeit.
daily_fwtd = "",--First World TD
daily_fwtd_desc = "",--Look - no hands! No hands!
daily_fwtd_objective = "難易度OVERKILL以上のFirst World Bankで、Equipmentのみを使用してクリアする。",--Complete the First World Bank job on OVERKILL or above with everybody only using deployable weapons.
daily_gears = "",--Saw Right Through You
daily_gears_desc = "",--Wolf wants you to show that you can be a real blademaster.
daily_gears_objective = "難易度OVERKILL以上で、4つ全てのTRANSPORTを全てのメンバーがOVE9000のみを使用してクリアする。",--Complete one of the transport heists on overkill or above, with all members of the team only using saws as weapons.
daily_grenades = "",--Boom!
daily_grenades_desc = "",--Nothing creates mayhem quite as effectively as a bunch of grenades.
daily_grenades_objective = "手榴弾で敵を$max_progress;体殺す",--Kill $max_progress; enemies with grenades.
daily_grenades_progress = "",--Grenade Kills
daily_hangover = "",--Drinks on Me
daily_hangover_desc = "",--Bonnie wants to share that sweet taste of whisky with the cops.
daily_hangover_objective = "Rivertown Glen Bottle(片手鈍器)で市民以外を$max_progress;体殺す",--Kill $max_progress; enemies using the Rivertown Glen Bottle melee weapon.
daily_hangover_progress = "",--Enemies Glassed
daily_heirloom = "",--Total Shogun
daily_heirloom_desc = "",--Clover knows what's in that secret vault. She wants it. Get it for her.
daily_heirloom_objective = "SHADOW RAIDでSAMURAI ARMORを全て盗んでクリアする。",--Collect all the armors in Shadow Raid. To complete this daily, you have to have played the job from start to finish.
daily_helicopter = "",--Just Like the Old Days
daily_helicopter_desc = "",--Dragan says escape plans are for sissies. 'Let's just do it,' he says.
daily_helicopter_objective = "THE BIG BANKで貸金庫内含む全loot回収後、屋上のヘリで脱出する。",--Complete the Big Bank job securing all loot and using the default escape plan.
daily_honorable = "",--Honorable Death
daily_honorable_desc = "",--A cold execution is certainly cleaner than dying in a firefight.
daily_honorable_objective = "制圧した敵を近接武器で$max_progress;回殺す。",--Dominate an enemy and kill them using a melee weapon, $max_progress; times.
daily_honorable_progress = "",--Enemies Dominated and Killed
daily_lodsofemone = "",--Accumulate!
daily_lodsofemone_desc = "",--Bonnie wants more money. You know she'll spend it.
daily_lodsofemone_objective = "計$max_progress;個のMoney Bagを獲得する。",--Secure $max_progress; bags of money.
daily_lodsofemone_progress = "",--Bags of Money Secured
daily_mortage = "",--No More Debts
daily_mortage_desc = "",--Houston knows that when you have a pile of diamonds, you'll never owe anyone money again.
daily_mortage_objective = "DIAMOND STOREで16個のバックを確保してクリアする",--Complete the Diamond Store with 16 bags.
daily_my_bodhi_is_ready = "",--My Bodhi is Ready
daily_my_bodhi_is_ready_desc = "",--Bodhi is collecting corpses. You don't need to know why - just bring him some.
daily_my_bodhi_is_ready_objective = "死体を$max_progress;体袋詰めする。",--Bag $max_progress; bodies.
daily_my_bodhi_is_ready_progress = "袋詰した死体の数",--Bodies Bagged
daily_naked = "",--Naked on the Ice
daily_naked_desc = "",--Sokol challenges you to show that you've got what it takes.
daily_naked_objective = "難易度OVERKILL以上のBIRTH OF SKYかBENEATH THE MOUNTAINをメンバー全員がTwo-Piece SuitとArmorer Perkを使用し、スキルを一切取得していない状態でクリアする。$NL;$NL;ジョブの最初から最後までプレイしないとこのサイドジョブは達成できない。",--Complete the Birth of Sky or the Beneath the Mountain job with all members of your team using the Two-Piece Suit and the Armorer perk deck, while also using no skills, on the OVERKILL difficulty or above. To complete this daily, you have to have played the job from start to finish.
daily_night_out = "",--Jacket's Night Out
daily_night_out_desc = "",--Jacket wants you to go party downtown.
daily_night_out_objective = "NIGHTCLUBを近接と投擲武器のみを使ってクリアする。$NL;$NL;ジョブの最初から最後までプレイしないとこのサイドジョブは達成できない。",--Complete Nightclub using only melee weapons or throwables. To complete this daily, you have to have played the job from start to finish.
daily_ninja = "",--Ninja!
daily_ninja_desc = "",--Jiro wants you to go medieval. Can you do it for him?
daily_ninja_objective = "TRANSPORT:CROSSROADSを近接、属性なしの武器だけでクリアする。",--Complete the Armoured Transport: Crossroads job using only melee and non-explosive throwable weapons. To complete this daily, you have to have played the job from start to finish.
daily_phobia = "",--Drill-o-Phobia
daily_phobia_desc = "俺はポンコツクソドリルを使わずに成功したぞ!",--I'm not using that piece of shit drill ever again!
daily_phobia_objective = "難易度MAYHEM以上で、いずれかのTRANSPORTをドリルを使わずにクリアする。",--Complete any loud only transport heist on Mayhem or above without ever using a drill on armored van.
daily_professional = "",--I'm a Professional
daily_professional_desc = "",--It gets so messy when you shoot people in the face. But on a dark suit you barely notice the wounds. John Wick knows this.
daily_professional_objective = "難易度OVERKILL以上の何らかのジョブをヘッドショットせずにクリアする。",--Complete a heist on OVERKILL and above without performing a single headshot.
daily_rush = "",--Rush B
daily_rush_desc = "ホッケーは早さが勝負。特にロシアでは",--Hockey is fast. Russian hockey is faster.
daily_rush_objective = "GO BANKで6分30秒以内に金庫の中にTripMineを設置する。$NL;$NL;ジョブの最初から最後までプレイしないとこのサイドジョブは達成できない。",--In the GO Bank heist, place a tripmine in the bank vault within 6 minutes and 30 seconds. To complete this daily, you have to have played the job from start to finish.
daily_secret_identity = "",--Jacket of Invisibility
daily_secret_identity_desc = "",--With no cameras they don't see you coming. That's just how Jacket likes it.
daily_secret_identity_objective = "難易度VERYHARD以上のSHADOW RAIDで監視カメラを9つ壊し、ステルスでクリアする。",--Destroy 9 cameras on Shadow Raid and complete it on Stealth, on the Very Hard difficulty or above.
daily_sewers = "",--Only Room for One
daily_sewers_desc = "",--Dragan doesn't like to be crowded in small spaces. Give him some room!
daily_sewers_objective = "難易度OVERKILL以上のGO BANKを、常に最大1人が下水道にいる状態で、更に4人全員が下水道を通る脱出方法でクリアする。$NL;$NL;ジョブの最初から最後までプレイしないとこサイドジョブは達成できない。",--Complete the GO Bank job on the OVERKILL difficulty or above, with a maximum of 1 person in the sewers at any one time, with all 4 team members escaping via the sewers. To complete this challenge, you have to have played the heist from start to finish.
daily_snake = "",--Rattle my Bones
daily_snake_desc = "",--Sydney wants to see some snakes. Bring her a bunch.
daily_snake_objective = "Purple SnakeのGage packagesを$max_progress;個集める",--Collect $max_progress; Purple Snake Gage packages.
daily_snake_progress = "",--Purple Snake Packages Collected
daily_spacetime = "",--Spacetime Paradox
daily_spacetime_desc = "",--Bain helps those who help themselves.
daily_spacetime_objective = "HOXTON BREAKOUTをHoxtonをクルーに入れてクリアする。",--Complete Hoxton Breakout having Hoxton in the crew.
daily_tapes = "",--Hector Sings
daily_tapes_desc = "",--Hoxton wants to know everything about how he was ratted out.
daily_tapes_objective = "Hoxton Revengeで全てのテープを聴く。",--Listen to all the tapes on Hoxton Revenge.
daily_tasty = "",--New Taste
daily_tasty_desc = "",--Jimmy wants you to bring him some more meth. No, lots more.
daily_tasty_objective = "COOK OFFでMethを$max_progress;個、調理しろ",--Cook $max_progress; bags of Meth in the Cookoff heist.
daily_tasty_progress = "",--Meth Cooked
daily_toast = "",--Get me a Sandwich
daily_toast_desc = "",--Clover really wants that sandwich. No, not any sandwich - that one.
daily_toast_objective = "WHITE XMASで黄金のトーストを見つける。",--Find Almir's toast on White Xmas.
daily_whats_stealth = "",--Loud Enough?
daily_whats_stealth_desc = "",--You can ask a biker to be silent but you can't make him.
daily_whats_stealth_objective = "難易度DEATH WISH以上のSHADOW RAIDを全てのメンバーがICTVを着てクリアする。$NL;$NL;ジョブの最初から最後までプレイしないとこのサイドジョブは達成できない。",--Complete the Shadow Raid job on the Death Wish difficulty or above, with all team members wearing the Improved Combined Tactical Vest. To complete this challenge, you have to have played the heist from start to finish.
menu_cs_daily_available = "$character;はあなたのために利用可能なチャレンジを持っています。 彼らの挑戦を受け入れるために、Safe Houseで彼らを訪ねてください。",--$character; has a challenge available for you. Visit them in the safe house to accept their challenge.
menu_cs_daily_challenge = "",--Side Jobs
menu_cs_daily_desc = "隠れ家の仲間から与えられる、日替わりのチャレンジです!$NL;彼らに会って依頼をもらい、チャレンジに出かけましょう。$NL;見事成し遂げられれば、あなたの労をねぎらってContinental Coinが贈られます。$NL;$NL;John Wickが苦労の末にPAYDAYメンバーをThe Continentalの会員にしてくれたおかげで、仕事をこなすとContinental Coinが手に入るようになりました。$NL;十分なコインが集まれば、Charlieとその手下達にちょっとした改装を頼むことが出来ます。$NL;もちろん、人目に付くこともありません。",--Every day a heister in the safe house will have a challenge for you! Meet with them in the safe house to accept their challenge, and then go out into the world to complete the requirements. Complete the challenge, and they'll give you a few Continental Coins for your troubles.$NL;$NL;Wick managed to get the PAYDAY crew membership to The Continental, so they're giving you coins for every heist you pull off. With enough coins, Charlie and his boys will come in and do a little redecorating for us, and make sure that any work done stays off the books.
