menu_mutators_desc = "Mutatorsは特定の機能の動作を変更したり、変わった効果を追加して、PAYDAY2をカスタマイズできます。いくつかのMutatorsは控えめな効果ですが、それ以外はゲームの難易度を劇的に変化させることが出来ます。",--Mutators let you customize your PAYDAY 2 experience by changing how certain features work or by adding unusual effects to gameplay. Some mutators have modest effects while others can drastically change the feel or the difficulty of the game.
