des_toolset = "",--The toolkit allows the owner to organize, carry and protect the tools, making them more effective. How much more depends on the upgrade level.
des_trip_mine = "",--The trip mine consists of a beam projector affixed to a shaped explosive casing. The laser activates once the trip mine is placed, acting as a tripwire to detonate the mine. If the beam is broken or the charge fired upon, the mine will detonate.
