dlg_pln_bb1_intro_01_01 = "",--Security here is tight. We might be able to do this heist silently. But if things go loud, don't worry. I've always got a Plan B.
dlr_flt_01_01 = "",--Welcome. Put the money on the table.
dlr_flt_02_01 = "",--Show me the money.
dlr_flt_02_02 = "",--You're messing with ME? Show me the money!
dlr_flt_02_03 = "",--Put the bag on the table. I'm waiting.
dlr_flt_03_01 = "",--I'll ask my main man Chavez to fetch you guys' shipment. You guys hang around.
dlr_framing_stage2_01_any_01 = "",--Hello gentlemen. Our client is very pleased that you agreed to do this with us. But know this - the only way this is going through is if we do it our way.
dlr_framing_stage2_02_any_01 = "",--Start with putting all the paintings on the table in the train car. I'll contact you when you are done.
dlr_framing_stage2_03_any_01 = "",--So you got nine of the paintings? That's awesome.
dlr_framing_stage2_04_any_01 = "",--We count eight paintings. Good job.
dlr_framing_stage2_05_any_01 = "",--I can see seven paintings.
dlr_framing_stage2_06_any_01 = "",--So that's 6 paintings.
dlr_framing_stage2_07_any_01 = "",--OK, I count 5 paintings.
dlr_framing_stage2_08_any_01 = "",--4 paintings, not much, but we'll take it.
dlr_framing_stage2_09_any_01 = "",--OK. So listen - our client is a little jumpy. He doesn't do things involving, you know, lawbreaking otherwise. So we need to have all of you in the train.
dlr_framing_stage2_10_any_01 = "",--It's not that we don't trust you, we just need to make sure that nothing will happen.
dlr_framing_stage2_11_any_01 = "",--Don't worry, it's just for safety.
dlr_framing_stage2_12_any_01 = "",--Alright, our dealer is arriving, hold on for a second.
dlr_framing_stage2_13_any_01 = "",--OK, throw me the paintings, and you'll get your money!
dlr_framing_stage2_14_any_01 = "",--Great, money coming down.
dlr_framing_stage2_15_any_01 = "",--Thanks, here's the cash!
dlr_framing_stage2_16_any_01 = "",--Great, we got it!
dlr_framing_stage2_17_any_01 = "",--Thats everything, nice doing business with you gentlemen!
dlr_framing_stage2_18_any_01 = "",--Doors are open for you, we are leaving!
dlr_framing_stage2_19_any_01 = "",--Oh shit, it's the cops! Let's get out of here!
