elp_bigoil_brf_intro_01 = "",--Politics is as you know global - I need you for a global effort.
elp_bigoil_brf_outro_01 = "",--Like an oiled machine, gentlemen - onwards.
elp_bigoil_brf_outro_02 = "",--Like a precision clock, gentlemen - keep ticking.
elp_bigoil_brf_speak_01 = "",--Our contacts tell me a new invention have seen the light of day. Cold fusion energy, the end of fossil fuels and death of oil conglomerates. We are all about risk management here.
elp_bigoil_brf_speak_01b = "",--I have information on a team tracking the inventor. Find them, find the inventor and end that chapter in history. Quick and clean.
elp_bigoil_brf_speak_02 = "",--An inventor named Rossy - residing somewhere in DC - may have found a cheap way to produce energy from water.
elp_bigoil_brf_speak_02b = "",--This device should be found and delivered to my client for... "Evaluation". Also, the know-how should be erased so it does not end up in the wrong hands.
elp_bigoil_brf_speak_03 = "",--Cold fusion energy may be the next big thing for my clients. Unfortunately, they do not own the most promising prototype - yet.
elp_bigoil_brf_speak_03b = "",--I want you to find it, bring it to me and erase any trace of it being invented. I will provide info on where to start.
elp_bigoil_cmc_01 = "",--Gentlemen - an opportunity to change the world awaits. Your effort will count!
elp_bigoil_cmc_02 = "",--Gentlemen - oil is the blood of our world, without it we die. Time to make sure it keeps flowing.
elp_bigoil_cmc_03 = "",--Gentlemen - lobbyists inclined to stay on the current path of energy policy want your help. It is lucrative indeed - I say we answer their call.
elp_bigoil_cnc_01 = "",--Gentlemen - an opportunity to change the world awaits. Your effort will count!
elp_bigoil_cnc_02 = "",--Gentlemen - oil is the blood of our world; without it we die. Time to make sure it keeps flowing.
elp_bigoil_cnc_03 = "",--Gentlemen - lobbyists inclined to stay on the current path of energy policy want your help. It is lucrative indeed - I say we answer their call.
elp_bigoil_debrief_01 = "",--Thank you for the safe delivery gentlemen. The device will now be tested for a long time... A very long time. In the meantime enjoy the PAYDAY!
elp_bigoil_debrief_02 = "",--Gentlemen it seems our mutual friends were quite pleased. Thank you for the prompt delivery of this invention. Now the world will return to business as usual.
elp_bigoil_debrief_03 = "",--Forget what you just saw and concentrate on counting your reward! The Big Eight send their regards.
elp_bigoil_debrief_04 = "",--Thank you for preserving our way of life. Money is coming your way like a ten million gallon oil spill.
elp_election_brf_outro_01 = "",--May the best man win.
elp_election_brf_outro_02 = "",--May the best man win.
elp_election_brf_speak_01 = "",--The voting will begin tomorrow. We need to act now to make a difference. New voting machines have arrived in the harbor.
elp_election_brf_speak_01b = "",--You need to reprogram them to swing votes my way. Software has been provided. Do it without getting discovered.
elp_election_brf_speak_02 = "",--Gentlemen - today we vote. They say: one man, one vote. I say: four men and lots of votes. I need you to rig the voting machines in my district.
elp_election_brf_speak_02b = "",--Find them in the harbor and make sure they are reprogrammed before reaching their destination in the mall.
elp_election_brf_speak_03 = "",--Help the citizens of DC to vote right. We need to find the ballot machines in the harbor and intercept them before they get deployed. The machines must swing votes to me!
elp_election_cmc_01 = "",--Gentlemen - we are at a tipping point in the election. I need you to help tip it the right way.
elp_election_cmc_02 = "",--Gentlemen - voting in DC is about to commence. We need to swing a few voters the right way. You can help.
elp_election_cmc_03 = "",--Gentlemen - new voting machines have arrived in DC. You need to rig them to swing my way a bit more. Do it silently.
elp_election_debrief_01 = "",--Absolute class my friends! Thanks to you, we will have a better outcome tomorrow. Much appreciated!
elp_election_debrief_02 = "",--That was very innovative. No one suspected a thing and the ballot machines are in play - ready to swing for the fence! Thank you.
elp_election_debrief_03 = "",--A very unorthodox way of solving it - a heist in the heist. I appreciate your cleverness. Votes will be cast correctly now!
elp_election_debrief_04 = "",--Congratulations on now having friends in high up places! Thank you for supporting your senator in such a direct way. I will not disappoint you!
elp_framing_brf_intro_01 = "",--I require your assistance in a matter...
elp_framing_brf_outro_01 = "",--Best of luck, gentlemen.
elp_framing_brf_speak_01 = "",--Senator Borrico is advancing in politics and business. I have learned he has made a lucrative arms deal on a national scale. This nation has paid him in pure gold.
elp_framing_brf_speak_01b = "",--I want you to infiltrate his penthouse apartment and place politically questionable items there. You will proceed to remove the gold he received for the arms deal.
elp_framing_brf_speak_01c = "",--If you manage to do this quietly it will hurt his party and thus pay substantially more to you.
elp_framing_brf_speak_02 = "",--Senator Borrico just closed a lucrative arms deal on a national scale - with a somewhat questionable nation. Find a way to get into his penthouse apartment.
elp_framing_brf_speak_02b = "",--Hit him for his gold but do it as quietly as you can - no one must know our affiliation. If you frame him and his party I will increase the payment substantially.
elp_framing_brf_speak_03 = "",--Now that senator Borrico has closed his little arms for gold deal, he is ripe for the taking.
elp_framing_brf_speak_03b = "",--Find a way to sneak into his apartment, steal the gold and plant incriminating evidence against him. Then leave undetected.
elp_framing_cmc_01 = "",--Gentlemen - I have a golden opportunity for you. Politics and art at its best.
elp_framing_cmc_02 = "",--Gentlemen - I need your steady hands to remove a competitor from the political scene. The reward is golden.
elp_framing_cmc_03 = "",--Gentlemen - I need you to assist me in transferring someone's wealth to benefit my party's best... Interest.
elp_framing_cnc_01 = "",--Gentlemen - I have a golden opportunity for you. Politics and art at its best.
elp_framing_cnc_02 = "",--Gentlemen - I need your steady hands to remove a competitor from the political scene. The reward is golden.
elp_framing_cnc_03 = "",--Gentlemen - I need you to assist me in transferring someone's wealth to benefit my party's best... Interest.
elp_framing_debrief_01 = "",--The 6 o'clock news ate this story up, and Reddit lit up like a Christmas tree! The senator is done for. Enjoy your spoils, gentlemen - my party is pleased.
elp_framing_debrief_02 = "",--Not a trace of your or my involvement. The senator is now publically a thieving drug lord - his party scrambling. Hats off to you gentlemen!
elp_framing_debrief_03 = "",--I trust you enjoy the gold. The senator is moving off the campaign - poorer and none the wiser. Well done!
elp_framing_debrief_04 = "",--Nice touch using the art as method of infiltration - I particularly enjoyed the footage on TV of the senator and the drugs. I'm very pleased! Good day.
elp_quote_set_a_01 = "",--Politics is a dirty business at best, right? Sometimes you need people to help you clean up.
elp_quote_set_a_02 = "",--Politicians like me do what is necessary, not what is expedient... And necessary can be dirty.
elp_quote_set_a_03 = "",--I don't think of myself so much as a politician - I think of myself as a warrior in a suit.
elp_quote_set_a_04 = "",--In politics, you have to be the change to make the change.
elp_quote_set_a_05 = "",--Who am I? I'm the opposite of every politician you've ever known.
elp_quote_set_a_05_alt = "",--Who am I? I'm the opposite of every politician you've ever known... Motherfucker!
elp_quote_set_a_06 = "",--What matters to me is that people take their lives seriously. That's all politics is at the end of the day: be serious and present.
elp_quote_set_a_07 = "",--Am I in this business for power? Of course - it would be dishonest to say otherwise. But I seek the power because I want to do the right thing.
elp_quote_set_a_08 = "",--I am John Henry Simmons. If you want to know more... We should talk. I might have something of interest, if you don't mind a little political intrigue...
