gus_bb1_cbf_01_01 = "",--The Benevolent Bank is located in downtown Washington. Today, you are going to make a significant withdrawal. Preparation is everything. Set up your plan. Execute it. As a gesture of goodwill, I have prepared a crane beside the bank. Use it how you see fit. That is all.
gus_bb1_cbf_01_02 = "",--The Benevolent Bank stands at 1500 Pennsylvania. You're going to rob it. Preparation is vital. Lay out your plan - and then execute it. Through a patient of mine, who works in construction, I have arranged a crane to be erected near the bank. I suggest you utilize it.
gus_bb1_cbf_01_03 = "",--Your target will be the Benevolent Bank. Security is high, so preparation must be thorough. A patient of mine heads a nearby construction site. They have been kind enough to erect a crane next to the bank. Use it. I'd wish you luck, but luck has nothing to do with it.
gus_bb1_cnc_01_01 = "",--The time has come. The Benevolent Bank is ready. Make sure you are too.
gus_bb1_cnc_01_02 = "",--You have an admirable record of criminal endeavors. Today, you'll be taking down the Benevolent.
gus_bb1_cnc_01_03 = "",--Today is the day. The day the Benevolent Bank goes down.
gus_bb1_debrief_01_01 = "",--Your talent for planning is as impressive as your talent for execution. Enjoy your well deserved PAYDAY. I will be in touch.
gus_bb1_debrief_01_02 = "",--You have delivered as promised. You proposed a plan, and you executed it. Enjoy your PAYDAY. You will hear from me again.
gus_bb1_debrief_01_03 = "",--I respect your stringency. Discipline under pressure is admirable. Enjoy your PAYDAY. I will be in touch.
gus_bb1_debrief_02_01 = "",--Few plans survive first contact with the enemy. You adapted well, and showcased an impressive capacity for violence. Enjoy your PAYDAY. I will contact you again once things cool down.
gus_bb1_debrief_02_02 = "",--This type of situation is often fluid - you reacted well. Decisively. Enjoy this PAYDAY. You will hear from me in due course.
gus_bb1_debrief_02_03 = "",--You responded to a changing situation with admirable proficiency - and impressive firepower. Enjoy your PAYDAY. You will hear from me again.
gus_preplan_01_01 = "",--Every successful venture requires a plan.
gus_preplan_01_02 = "",--A plan is essential for a successful conclusion to any heist.
gus_preplan_01_03 = "",--Proper planning prevents piss poor performance.
gus_preplan_01_04 = "",--Thorough planning can turn a speculative venture into a guaranteed result.
gus_preplan_01_05 = "",--In 1957, Eisenhower said that plans are worthless. Eisenhower never robbed a bank.
gus_preplan_01_06 = "",--This heist will need thorough planning.
gus_preplan_01_07 = "",--Luck favors the prepared.
gus_preplan_01_08 = "",--Luck has nothing to do with a successful heist.
gus_preplan_01_09 = "",--Good luck is a residue of preparation.
gus_preplan_01_10 = "",--Luck is a matter of preparation meeting opportunity.
gus_preplan_01_11 = "",--The meeting of preparation and opportunity generates the offspring we call luck.
gus_preplan_01_12 = "",--Luck is where opportunity meets preparation.
gus_preplan_01_13 = "",--Spectacular achievement is always preceded by unspectacular preparation.
gus_preplan_01_14 = "",--Before anything else, preparation is the key to success.
gus_preplan_01_15 = "",--Always be prepared.
gus_preplan_01_16 = "",--By failing to prepare, you are preparing to fail. Benjamin Franklin was a wise man.
gus_preplan_01_17 = "",--Hope for the best, prepare for the worst.
gus_preplan_01_18 = "",--The will to win is nothing without the will to prepare.
gus_preplan_01_19 = "",--Opportunity is a haughty goddess who wastes no time with those who are unprepared.
gus_preplan_01_20 = "",--Consider these wise words: He who doesn't know where he's going should not start his journey.
gus_preplan_01_21 = "",--Theodore Roosevelt once said: Make preparations in advance. You never have trouble if you are prepared for it.
gus_preplan_01_22 = "",--A prudent person foresees the danger ahead and takes precautions; the simpleton goes blindly on and suffers the consequences. I'm quoting the Holy Book.
gus_preplan_01_23 = "",--Abraham Lincoln once said: Give me six hours to chop down a tree and I will spend the first four sharpening the axe. He knew the importance of preparation.
gus_preplan_01_24 = "",--Allow me to quote Colin Powell: There are no secrets to success. It is the result of preparation, hard work, and learning from failure.
gus_preplan_01_25 = "",--Some fortune cookie wisdom for you: Success depends upon previous preparation, and without such preparation there is sure to be failure.
gus_preplan_01_26 = "",--Consider this quote by George Washington: There is no short cut to achievement. Life requires thorough preparation.
gus_preplan_01_27 = "",--I have yet to be involved in a heist where luck was involved. Well-prepared enterprisers take down scores.
gus_preplan_01_28 = "",--You know I prefer to be involved in jobs where preparation is taken seriously. Don't disappoint me.
gus_preplan_01_29 = "",--Consider the punishment, and prepare accordingly - so that you can escape that punishment.
gus_preplan_01_30 = "",--As you shall sow, so shall you reap. That's the Bible telling you to make preparations with care.
gus_preplan_02_01 = "",--Thermite is effective at forcing a breach, silently.
gus_preplan_02_02 = "",--Thermite will burn through concrete, steel and advanced polymers.
gus_preplan_02_03 = "",--Thermite is slower than C4, but it gets inside without the noise.
gus_preplan_02_04 = "",--Thermite takes longer than eplosives, but it doesn't create as much commotion either.
gus_preplan_02_05 = "",--Thermite burns through enything - not as quickly as explosives, but much more silently.
gus_preplan_02_06 = "",--Thermite is the best way to get through reinforced steel without making too much noise.
gus_preplan_03_01 = "",--I can arrange for this keycard to be left where you indicate.
gus_preplan_03_02 = "",--Keycards can open many doors.
gus_preplan_03_03 = "",--Magnetic keycards are useful for stealthy entry.
gus_preplan_03_04 = "",--Keycards will swiftly get you through doors that would otherwise require brute force.
gus_preplan_03_05 = "",--Locked doors can force you to do detours or noisy breaches. A keycard is a simple solution.
gus_preplan_03_06 = "",--Keycards are a simple yet brilliant solution when you encounter locked doors.
gus_preplan_03_07 = "",--Keycards - is there any game that don't have them?
gus_preplan_04_01 = "",--This will provide an effective distraction for any guards.
gus_preplan_04_02 = "",--Using this will distract any nearby guards.
gus_preplan_04_03 = "",--This should keep the guards busy.
gus_preplan_04_04 = "",--This will distract the guards in a way I'm sure you will find very useful.
gus_preplan_04_05 = "",--Guards - you'll like them better when their focus is on something other than you.
gus_preplan_04_06 = "",--This will make the guards preoccupied - and much less likely to notice your presense.
gus_preplan_05_01 = "",--I can arrange for extra ammunition to be left.
gus_preplan_05_02 = "",--This heist may turn violent. If so, extra ammunition will allow you to prosecute that violence effectively.
gus_preplan_05_03 = "",--Violence is always an option. Prosecute it longer with this.
gus_preplan_05_04 = "",--Ammunition - can you ever have too much of it?
gus_preplan_05_05 = "",--When you find yourself in a tight spot, there are few things more important than ammunition.
gus_preplan_05_06 = "",--Extra ammunition is your best friend when you find yourself running dry.
gus_preplan_06_01 = "",--My contacts can ensure that medical supplies are left for your use.
gus_preplan_06_02 = "",--Additional medical supplies will increase your chances of survival.
gus_preplan_06_03 = "",--This will keep you in the fight longer.
gus_preplan_06_04 = "",--If there's one thing you don't want to find yourself in shortage of, it's medical supplies.
gus_preplan_06_05 = "",--In some situations, an extra medical kit may be the difference between life and death.
gus_preplan_06_06 = "",--I can make sure a contact of mine places medical supplies where you request them to be placed.
gus_preplan_07_01 = "",--This is an effective way of gaining entry.
gus_preplan_07_02 = "",--This will allow you to gain entry.
gus_preplan_07_03 = "",--You should get in easier with this.
gus_preplan_07_04 = "",--All you'll have to say is Open Sesame.
