gus_quote_set_a_01 = "",--My legal business identifies me as a practicing dentist. My real vocation is the organization of heists, or the application of criminal theory if you will. I am a facilitator. An agent. Some choose to hide in the shadows, some behind monitors and servers.
gus_quote_set_a_02 = "",--You can tell a lot about a man by how he takes care of his teeth. This makes me a formidable judge of character.
gus_quote_set_a_03 = "",--Dentistry is a job that requires a lot of precision and attention to detail - just like my alternative line of work.
gus_quote_set_a_04 = "",--My line of work has allowed me to lay the groundwork for an impressive network of contacts.
gus_quote_set_a_05 = "",--Keep in mind: If you cross me, I have the capability to make you disappear in a way that makes it impossible to identify you even by your teeth.
gus_quote_set_a_06 = "",--In dentistry, I have become very appreciative of people who keep things... clean.
gus_quote_set_a_07 = "",--Make sure, to floss.
hct_firestarter_brf_outro_01 = "",--I want the ashes of their money to cloud their eyes. Get to it.
hct_firestarter_brf_speak_01 = "",--The Mendoza cartel is threatening us. But this town is ours. It is where power is and we control it. We will show them who the threat truly is.
hct_firestarter_brf_speak_02 = "",--The Mendoza cartel runs a lot of guns through DC. We need you to hit one of their weapons caches here, weaken their soldiers.
hct_firestarter_brf_speak_02b = "",--And when that is done, we want you to find their cash reserve here and burn it. Leave them nothing but ash.
hct_firestarter_brf_speak_03 = "",--We want the Mendoza cash stream stopped completely. Their entire cash reserve is here in DC. To get to it we need to disarm their soldiers by destroying their weapons cache.
hct_firestarter_brf_speak_03b = "",--Then you can go for their bank and burn all their money. Leaving them nothing.
hct_firestarter_brf_speak_04 = "",--We have information about the Mendoza cashflow. Over $100 million from their American operations. We want to send a message - their money and their weapons are null and void.
hct_firestarter_brf_speak_04b = "",--Hit their soldiers first, destroy their weapons, then find their secret bank. The FBI knows all about it.
hct_firestarter_cnc_01 = "",--The cartel requests your assistance again. Now we are going on offense, as you say in football. Las Mendozas and the FBI will regret not eliminating me when I was weak. For I am strong now.
hct_firestarter_cnc_02 = "",--I want to send a clear message to the FBI and the whoring Mendozas. You can contribute.
hct_firestarter_cnc_03 = "",--We are hitting the Mendoza cartel hard for money, information and blood. You are of great use to us now.
hct_firestarter_debrief_01 = "",--I hear conversations from down south - the Mendozas are having problems paying even their own families. Good.
hct_firestarter_debrief_02 = "",--The Mendoza money in the US is gone. You have done well. We will not stop here of course. I will call upon you again.
hct_firestarter_debrief_03 = "",--The FBI and the Mendozas are now scrambling. They are weakened but not dead. We need to see to that later. We will be in touch.
hct_firestarter_debrief_04 = "",--We have driven nails into Mendoza's organization. Crucified them the way they would have done to us. No salaries no organization. The FBI grip is faltering and the Mendozs are losing ground.
hct_firestarter_debrief_04b = "",--Well done.
hct_generic_debrief_outro_01 = "",--I am pleased with this outcome.
hct_generic_debrief_outro_02 = "",--You have done phenomenally well.
hct_generic_debrief_outro_03 = "",--You are exceptionally gifted. I am not disappointed.
hct_generic_debrief_outro_04 = "",--Thank you for being forthright.
hct_quote_set_a_01 = "",--My name is Hector Moralez. I am a businessman. I would be uncomfortable being called anything else, to be quite honest.
hct_quote_set_a_02 = "",--I was born in Colombia but have become quite successful building a small import/export business here in Washington DC. I feel my calling is to help others secure things of value at cost.
hct_quote_set_a_02b = "",--It is a moderate ambition, I admit, but one that I find pleasing.
hct_quote_set_a_03 = "",--I don't believe in fate, for if I did, none of what I achieved ever would have come to me.
hct_quote_set_a_04 = "",--There are so many stupid criminals in the world that to be smart is a relatively easy thing. It only takes deliberation where most would choose action.
hct_quote_set_a_05 = "",--Perhaps the thing I am most sorry for in my life is that I showed mercy to Carlito Mendoza when we were young. And I have been repaid in blood... I will never make such a mistake again.
hct_rats_brf_outro_01 = "",--Hurry you have no time, get to it.
hct_rats_brf_speak_01 = "",--The Mendoza cartel is hitting our meth lab in the woods. They're relentless but stupid. We will show them the error of their ways.
hct_rats_brf_speak_02 = "",--Our Meth lab in the Richmond countryside is being attacked. It is the Mendoza cartel making a last desperate move. We need to protect it and secure the meth that our cooks have going.
hct_rats_brf_speak_02b = "",--Make sure the cooks gets finished. Give them nothing.
hct_rats_brf_speak_03 = "",--We know the Mendozas are on the run - seems they are making a last hit on us to retaliate. Our meth lab is under attack - save the meth and save the cooks. You know how to treat the enemy. Do so.
hct_rats_cnc_01 = "",--Our rivals, the Mendozas, are fleeing like rats off a ship. They are still dangerous as any cornered animal. Protect our meth lab at all costs.
hct_rats_cnc_02 = "",--The Mendoza cartel is hitting our methamphetamine operation here in DC. It appears they have grown bold or desperate. Go there and make them sorry.
hct_rats_cnc_03 = "",--I have taken a call from our cooks. The Mendoza cartel is planning a hit on our operation in the "country". Make sure they fail. Go there now.
hct_rats_debrief_01 = "",--I am humbled and grateful. Your good work has elevated my cartel in status and wealth. I will not forget and neither will the cartel.
hct_rats_debrief_02 = "",--The bus had all the Mendoza lieutenants in it. You have done my cartel great justice and respect. You should come to Colombia sometime friends.
hct_rats_debrief_03 = "",--The future of the Mendoza cartel in the USA is ended. All thanks to you. You are a hot topic down here. I thank you.
hct_rats_debrief_04 = "",--The senior family of the Mendoza has sworn death upon all of you... A good sign you have now made a important impact on our cartel's future in the USA. Muchas gracias por todo, muchachos...
hct_watchdogs_brf_speak_01 = "",--Hombres, my organization requires we move swiftly to get our cocaine out of DC before the law catches up with us. You would be the insurance crew.
hct_watchdogs_brf_speak_02 = "",--You will board the meat truck and accompany our shipment to the harbor. My people will offload the coke. A speedboat will be on standby to expedite the transport of the goods.
hct_watchdogs_brf_speak_02b = "",--Make sure that happens. If not, I have been told you are good at improvising.
hct_watchdogs_brf_speak_03 = "",--You ride with the drugs. You ensure my product arrives in the harbor and makes it onto the speedboat...
hct_watchdogs_brf_speak_03b = "",--In the meantime, perhaps you can enjoy the refrigerated comfort of my meat truck and cool off a little because the heat will be on...
hct_watchdogs_brf_speak_04 = "",--We know the FBI and our rival cartel, the Mendozas, are hitting our cocaine supply in DC. We need you men to ride with this transport and secure it. Make sure it reaches our boat in the harbor.
hct_watchdogs_brf_speak_05 = "",--Anyone tries to stop you - Mendoza, police, whoever - deal with them in an appropriate fashion. It does not have to be socially acceptable.
hct_watchdogs_brf_speak_05b = "",--I only ask you deliver what is mine to its proper destination, and this must happen, no matter what. No matter what!
hct_watchdogs_cnc_01 = "",--This is a transportation security detail. Muy importante.
hct_watchdogs_cnc_02 = "",--The cartel wants these transport trucks to reach the harbor safely for delivery...
hct_watchdogs_cnc_03 = "",--Our product needs to reach the harbor. Guards are needed. This is where you come in...
hct_watchdogs_debrief_01 = "",--The cartel is content. You have done well. The cocaine has left DC and is now safe.
hct_watchdogs_debrief_02 = "",--The cocaine is in the hands of the distributors now, and all is well. Enjoy the fruits of your labor.
hct_watchdogs_debrief_03 = "",--Our position is now less difficult. The cocaine supply is not under threat. We will now move against our enemies. Whoever stands in our way.
hct_watchdogs_debrief_04 = "",--Your money has been sent. We will meet again as this conflict is now about obliterating the others. Keep your phones on.
