loc_quote_set_a = "",--Hello. My name is Locke. I lead a cyber task force organised by Murkywater. Due to your many attacks on our interests, we've been mandated to infiltrate your Crime.Net, and destroy you. As you can no doubt ascertain, the infiltration part has been achieved. However, rather than bringing you down, which I could do with the press of this button, I come with a proposal. How would you like to work with me? I can supply you with intelligence, opportunities and materiel regarding Murkywater. Further, I can keep you hidden from the attentions of my co-workers. So...what do you say?
loc_wwh_01_01 = "すまないな、友よ。他に方法があれば良かったのだが、どうにも断れぬ申し出だったのでね!",--Sorry friends, I would have liked to do this another way, but I was made an offer I couldn't say no to!
loc_wwh_01_02 = "仕方がなかったのだ、友よ。これもビジネスというやつだ、わかるね?",--Couldn't be helped my friends. Just business, you understand yeah?
loc_wwh_01_03 = "諸君らは私を恨むだろうが、それもすぐに終わる。悪く思わんでくれ!",--You'll hate me for this, but only until you're dead. Nothing personal!
loc_wwh_02_01 = "愉快で愛しい友人たちよ、さらば!",--So long my little smiling friends!
loc_wwh_02_02 = "ご機嫌よう、親愛なる友よ。二度と会うこともないだろう!",--Farewell dear friends, we'll not meet again I think!
loc_wwh_02_03 = "友よ、素晴らしい一日を。また会う日...が来ることはないが!",--Have a beautiful day friends, until we never meet again!
loc_wwh_intro_01 = "ああ、こんな事をしなければならないとは心苦しいが、これは私の清算なのだ。恨むなよ!",--Well, I'm sorry to have to do this, but here's where I clear off. It's nothing personal!
loc_wwh_intro_02 = "どう伝えるべきかわからないが、予定に変更が出来た。さらばだ!",--Don't know how to say this really, but there's been a change of plan. Gotta leave you now!
loc_wwh_intro_03 = "すまない友よ、お先に失礼させてもらうが、諸君らにサプライズを用意してある。",--Sorry friends, but it's time for me to leave, but I've left a surprise for you.
