pln_watchdogs_stage1_86_any_01 = "",--Protect the car!
pln_watchdogs_stage1_86_any_02 = "",--Protect him!
pln_watchdogs_stage1_brief_01 = "",--We're watchdogs on this job. Wear a heavy jacket and carry heavier weapons. We know Hector's transports are getting hit. You'll ride in the back of the truck. Don't let the coke go anywhere.
pln_watchdogs_stage1_end_a_01 = "",--I knew you'd get out of that mess. You got all of it too! I'll let Hector's boat know. See you at the harbor.
pln_watchdogs_stage1_end_a_02 = "",--That's all the coke nice and secure. Even for you, this was a hell of a win.  Let's get the stuff to the boat so we can get our PAYDAY on.
pln_watchdogs_stage1_end_b_01 = "",--You got most of it, and most of it is better than none of it. Hector will be happy with how you handled yourself. Gotta get to the boat now.
pln_watchdogs_stage1_end_b_02 = "",--That's enough coke, not all, but enough. Hector's people are at the harbor - you need to meet them and get this stuff onto their boat. Then call it a day... OK, a PAYDAY.
pln_watchdogs_stage1_intro_a_01 = "",--The FBI's onto us! Guns up! Don't lose that coke!
pln_watchdogs_stage1_intro_a_02 = "",--Dammit they're pulling your truck over! FBI... Don't let em take what's Hector's!
pln_watchdogs_stage1_intro_a_03 = "",--Ah, it's an FBI operation - no way out - they're gonna take you down unless you shoot your way outta there!
pln_watchdogs_stage2_12_any_01 = "",--I've sent the helicopter for you, you'll be picked up soon.
pln_watchdogs_stage2_13_any_01 = "",--Your escape helicopter is here, try and secure the rest, but if you can't I suggest you get the hell out of there!
pln_watchdogs_stage2_14_any_01 = "",--The place was under surveillance! We are going for the bridge!
pln_watchdogs_stage2_15_any_01 = "",--Come on, get the bags!
pln_watchdogs_stage2_16_any_01 = "",--You probably want to hunker down by the warehouse.
pln_watchdogs_stage2_17_any_01 = "",--Get the bags onto the boat.
pln_watchdogs_stage2_18_any_01 = "",--Just hold on, the boat will be there any second now.
pln_watchdogs_stage2_19_any_01 = "",--The helicopter is ready to pick you up.
pln_watchdogs_stage2_20_any_01 = "",--We need to show the boat pick-up our position, see if you can get into the warehouse and use those floodlights.
pln_watchdogs_stage2_21_any_01 = "",--Flip the switch a couple of times, that should be enough to get his attention.
pln_watchdogs_stage2_22_any_01 = "",--Flip the switch, we need to signal the boat!
pln_watchdogs_stage2_22_any_02 = "",--Flip that switch!
pln_watchdogs_stage2_23_any_01 = "",--Alright, I see the boat - it's almost there. Get ready with those bags.
pln_watchdogs_stage2_24_any_01 = "",--They are taking the bags!
pln_watchdogs_stage2_brief_01 = "",--OK, you go to the harbor like we planned. Offload the coke from the pick-up. You'll need to signal Hector's boat in the warehouse to get him to come in.
pln_watchdogs_stage2_brief_01b = "",--Once he's there, get the coke onboard and the boat driver will do the rest.
pln_watchdogs_stage2_end_a_01 = "",--The coke's shipped out. Well done, sailors. Go get your PAYDAY.
pln_watchdogs_stage2_end_a_02 = "",--I know you had things under control. Not like that other time. You handled it in style. Hector owes us big.
pln_watchdogs_stage2_end_b_01 = "",--We lost a little coke on this job, but it could have been worse. Hector will still be pleased with us saving what we could.
pln_watchdogs_stage2_end_b_02 = "",--Well, you did lose some of the coke, but you finished the job, so good on you. We'll get our PAYDAY yet, just put some eyes in the back of your head in the meantime.
pln_watchdogs_stage2_intro_a_01 = "",--Get out, get to the bags before the FBI catches up to us again. I know, they're persistent little bastards, aren't they.
pln_watchdogs_stage2_intro_a_02 = "",--Take the coke to the harbor... Signal the boat with the floodlights and he'll come get it.
pln_watchdogs_stage2_intro_a_03 = "",--Don't give the cops a damn thing - just signal Hector's guys with the flood lights in the warehouse and get that coke onto the speedboat. Nothing fancy here.
pln_watchdogs_stage2_intro_b_01 = "",--Well the cops are all over the pick-up... I told Alex to set you down further away so you could claim the coke from a safer position. Once you have it, signal the boat and hustle the coke onboard.
pln_watchdogs_stage2_intro_b_02 = "",--Hector's worried... We're too far away from the coke in this chopper. Once you're on the ground get to the coke, signal his courier, and load it on to the pick-up boat.
plt_chw_01_01 = "諸君、俺がいられるのは短い間だけだ。確保したいものがあれば、今しかないぞ。あとで戻ってくるけどな。",--Gentlemen, I see an opening for me to come in a short period of time. If you have any loot to secure, now is the time. I'll be at the back of the train.
plt_chw_01_02 = "よう、お前ら。俺がいるのは少しの間だけだから、確保したいものがあれば何でも持って来いよ。",--Hey, guys, I'm coming in for a short period of time, so bring me any loot you want to secure.
plt_chw_01_03 = "あとでまた来るぜ、仮面フレンズ。長くは居られないから、確保したいものは急いで持って来てくれ。",--Coming in at the back, my masked friends. I'll only stay a short while so bring me anything you want to secure, and do it fast.
plt_chw_02_01 = "着いたぞ。すぐに戦利品を持って来い、長くは待てないからな。",--I'm here. Bring me the loot pronto, because I can't stay too long.
plt_chw_02_02 = "よう、後部車両で待ってるぞ。確保したい戦利品は急いで持って来い。",--Hey, I'm here in the back now. Hurry up and get me any loot you want secured.
plt_chw_02_03 = "よう、後部車両で待ってるぞ。確保したい戦利品は急いで持って来い。",--Hey, I'm here in the back now. Hurry up and get me any loot you want secured.
plt_chw_intro_01 = "よっしゃカウボーイども、ここで降ろすぜ。ブツを積みに呼ばれるまで辺りを飛んでるからな。",--All right Cowboys, I'm dropping you off here, and I'll circle around until you call me back to pick up the goods.
plt_chw_intro_02 = "諸君、こいつはまるで俺の好きな西部劇だ! それはともかく、ここで降りてくれ。戦利品を積みに合図で呼ばれるまで待機してるからな。",--This feels like something out from a cowboy movie and Bile likes it, gentlemen! Anyhow, here's where I drop you off. I'll be on standby until you give me the signal to come back and pick up the loot.
plt_chw_intro_03 = "イーハァー! 着いたぜ! お前らが目的のモンを手に入れるまで辺りを飛んでるが、合図をくれたら回収に戻る。幸運を祈る!",--Yihaaaa! Here we are! I'll circle around until you get whatever you came for. Just give me the signal and I'll be back to pick the loot up. Good luck!
